INSERT INTO `Card` VALUES (1,3,'Dark','C','Special Edition','2X-7KPR (Tooex)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/2x7kprtooex.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','0','2','2','Where present under \'nighttime conditions,\' each of your Imperials and aliens at same planet site is power +2 and immune to attrition < 3.','Basic security droid. Monitors perimeter sensors and floodlights at Imperial outposts. Responsible for maintenance of security devices. Stolen from Jabba.','2X-3KPR (Tooex)','7_163'),(2,4,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•3,720 To 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/3720to1.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Insert in opponent\'s Reserve Deck. When Effect reaches top it is lost and up to the three lowest destiny numbers of each player\'s characters on table are totaled. Player with lower total loses Force equal to the difference. (Immune to Alter.)','What are the odds of having a Corellian, a Wookiee and a protocol droid together with an Alderaanian princess who happens to be the daughter of the Dark Lord of the Sith?','Never Tell Me The Odds','4_114'),(3,188,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Bane Malar','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/banemalar.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','1','4','3','At the start of a battle, may use 1 Force to \'mindscan\' one opponent\'s non-droid character of lesser ability present. Adds that character\'s power and game text to his own for remainder of battle. Immune to attrition < 3.','Mysterious bounty hunter of an unknown species. Rumored to be somewhat telepathic. Infrequent member of Jabba\'s court. Plotting to kill Jabba.',NULL,'6_95'),(4,4039,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 0','•A Day Long Remembered (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/adaylongremembered.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. All immunity to attrition is -3. You may not fire [Permanent Weapon] weapons. If opponent just lost a Jedi or a battle, they lose 1 Force. During your draw phase, lose 1 Force or place this Effect in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','\'It has seen the end of Kenobi and will soon see the end of the Rebellion.\'','Down With The Emperor (V)','200_101'),(5,7,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•3B3-21','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/3b321.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','3','3','3','If opponent just initiated a battle at same site, may use X Force to reveal the top X cards of your Reserve Deck. (maximum 4). Any battle droids revealed this way may deploy for free; all other cards are lost.','Infantry battle droid equipped with command programs to call reinforcements into his patrol zone when needed. Assigned to escort Amidala soon after her capture.',NULL,'14_71'),(6,8,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•3B3-888','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/3b3888.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','3','3','Once per turn may use 1 Force to target an opponent\'s character present; target is defense value -3 for remainder of turn. While with another battle droid at a site, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.','Infantry battle droid belonging to the squad that captured Jar Jar Binks and Captain Tarpals at the Naboo battle plains.',NULL,'14_72'),(7,4019,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 0','•4-LOM With Concussion Rifle (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/4lomwithconcussionrifle.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','2','3','3','Permanent weapon is •4-LOM\'s Concussion Rifle (may target a character for free; target is power -1 until end of turn).  Once per turn, may place a card from hand on bottom of Used Pile to draw top card from Reserve Deck.','Accomplished thief and information broker. Modified by Jabba to be an effective bounty hunter. The Hutt often teams 4-LOM with other hired killers.',NULL,'200_71'),(8,5,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•3B3-10','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/3b310.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','3','2','3','While at Theed Palace Hallway, opponent\'s characters may not move from here. Once per game may take Halt! Into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Infantry battle droid who assumed command after his regiment\'s commander fell to Amidala\'s blaster. Re-routed Droid Control Ship order to himself in the heat of battle.',NULL,'14_69'),(9,12,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•5D6-RA-7 (Fivedesix)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/5d6ra7.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','4','5','Power +1 if at same site as Motti or Yularen. Adds 1 to deploy cost of each opponent\'s droid (and your \'mouse\' droids) when deploying to same location. Immune to attrition during \'nighttime conditions.\'','Aide to Admiral Motti\'s staff. Foul-tempered and vindictive. Feared by other droids. A spy for the ISB. Secretly investigates Imperial officers whose loyalties are in question.',NULL,'1_163'),(10,10,'Dark','PM','Enhanced Cloud City','•4-LOM With Concussion Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedCloudCity-Dark/large/4lomwithconcussionrifle.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','2','3','3','Adds one battle destiny if with Jabba or Zuckuss. Permanent weapon is •4-LOM\'s Concussion Rifle (may target a character for free; target may not use its game text for remainder of turn).','Accomplished thief and information broker. Modified by Jabba to be an effective bounty hunter. The Hutt often teams 4-LOM with other hired killers.',NULL,'109_6'),(11,46,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•Ability, Ability, Ability','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/abilityabilityability.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s side of table. At the end of opponent\'s deploy phase, if they did not deploy a card with ability, opponent loses 2 Force. Effect lost if opponent has more cards with ability on table than you. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Ben. . . Ben, please! Ben. . . Leia! Hear me, Leia!\'','Civil Disorder','5_110'),(12,14,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•A Bright Center To The Universe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/abrightcentertotheuniverse.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Death Star system or Coruscant system. Target another system. At locations related to target system, opponent\'s Force drain modifiers are canceled. Effect canceled if opponent controls this system. (Immune to Alter.)','The intimidating power of the Empire was focused in the core systems, allowing the Emperor to ignore minor activities occurring on the Outer Rim.',NULL,'7_218'),(13,9,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•4-LOM','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/4lom.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','1','2','2','3','Total power at same site is +1 for each of your alien/droid pairs present. Once during each battle, if present with Zuckuss, may use 1 Force to search any Used Pile and move 1 character there to the Lost Pile. May initiate battle and be battled.','Information Broker. Thief. Overrode and reprogrammed its own selfgoverning software. Convinced Jabba the Hut to upgrade its armor and weaponry. Became a bounty hunter.',NULL,'4_91'),(14,11,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•4-LOM\'s Concussion Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/4lomsconcussionrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on your warrior, free on 4-LOM. May target a character or creature for free at same site or exterior site up to 2 sites away. Draw destiny. Add 1 if Blaster Scope attached. If total destiny - distance to target > defense value, target hit.','BlasTech LJ-90. Not as accurate as the E-11 Blaster Rifle, but uses the same scope mount and has much better range. Acquired by 4-LOM after teaming up with Zuckuss.',NULL,'4_174'),(15,17,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•A Dangerous Time','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/adangeroustime.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Examine the cards in opponent\'s Force Pile. Reorder however you wish and replace.  LOST: Search your Reserve Deck and take one Dark Forces into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.\"','\'This is a dangerous time for you, when you will be tempted by the dark side of the Force.\'',NULL,'4_136'),(16,6,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•3B3-1204','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/3b31204.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','3','3','While with two other battle droids, may use 1 Force to target an opponent\'s Jedi present. Target\'s immunity to attrition is canceled for remainder of turn.','Infantry battle droid programmed with anti-Jedi combat tactics by the blockade flagship. Was to begin uploading his program to the rest of the unit when the Jedi escaped.',NULL,'14_70'),(17,4020,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 0','•5D6-RA-7 (Fivedesix) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/5d6ra7.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','4','5','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Power +1 while with your leader. If at a Scomp link when opponent draws a destiny of: 1-3, you may activate one Force; 4-6, you may draw top card of your Reserve Deck; 0 or 7 you may retrieve 1 Force.','Aide to Admiral Motti\'s staff. Foul-tempered and vindictive. Feared by other droids. A spy for the ISB. Secretly investigates Imperial officers whose loyalties are in question.',NULL,'200_72'),(18,6112,'Dark','C2','Virtual Set 9','•Bala-Tik','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/balatik.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While with Han, he may not add battle destiny draws or play an Interrupt from Lost Pile. While at opponent\'s battleground, opponent may not cancel or reduce your Force drains here.','Gangster, information broker, and leader.',NULL,'209_33'),(19,33,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•A Real Hero','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/arealhero.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Take Lobot into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: If your Lando is in a battle at a Cloud City site, add two battle destiny. OR If Han and your Lando are involved in the same battle, cancelone opponent\'s battle destiny just after it is revealed.\"','\'I got my own problems.\'',NULL,'7_245'),(20,52,'Dark','C','Endor','Accelerate','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/accelerate.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Adds 2 to maneuver, 1 to power and 1 to landspeed of either your speeder bike piloted by a biker scout or your swoop for remainder of turn. (Interrupt may even affect the result just after a destiny draw targeting the vehicle\'s maneuver.)','The Empire trains its personnel to operate a variety of specialized equipment in demanding environments. This training allows troops to take seemingly risky actions.',NULL,'8_134'),(21,181,'Dark','C','Dagobah','Awwww, Cannot Get Your Ship Out','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/awwwwcannotgetyourshipout.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a landed starship (not at a docking bay). Starship may not move. OR Deploy on a starship or vehicle on Dagobah. Starship or vehicle may not move. At the start of you next control phase, starship or vehicle \'sinks\' to the Used Pile.','\'Listen, friend, we didn\'t mean to land in that puddle, and if we could get our ship out, we would, but we can\'t so why don\'t you just...\'',NULL,'4_115'),(22,5139,'Dark','C','Demo Deck','•Asajj Ventress With Lightsabers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DemoDeck-Dark/large/asajjventresswithlightsabers.gif?raw=true','Character','Sith','1','4','5','7','Power +1 with Dooku. Permanent weapon is •Asajj\'s Lightsabers (may target a character for free, or target two characters using 1 Force; draw two destiny; target(s) hit and forfeit -2 if total destiny > total defense value).','\'Female Dathomirian assassin.\'','Ahsoka Tano With Lightsabers','301_3'),(23,56,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Accuser','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/accuser.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','7','8','9','May deploy -3 as a \'react\'. May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1.','Modified for optimal crisis response time. Veteran crew experienced at monitoring shipping lanes and Imperial port traffic.',NULL,'9_152'),(24,156,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•At Last We Are Getting Results','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/atlastwearegettingresults.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your [Trade Federation] starfighters are forfeit +2. During every draw phase, opponent loses 1 Force unless they occupy a battleground system. Effect lost if you do not occupy two battleground systems with [Trade Federation] starships.','First sign that your blockade is going well: the Queen\'s on the comlink.','It\'s On Automatic Pilot!','14_95'),(25,119,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','Antipersonnel Laser Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/antipersonnellasercannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Vehicle','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on your transport vehicle. If your warrior aboard here, may target a character or creature using 3 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +2 > defense value. May fire repeatedly for 2 Force each time.','Rapid-fire weapon. Requires three power cells to operate. Has no stun setting. Lightweight enough to be stored and then quickly mounted when the need arises.',NULL,'6_174'),(26,63,'Dark','XR','Death Star II','•Admiral Piett','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/admiralpiett.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','4','6','Deploys -2 to Executor. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if a Star Destroyer). Your capital starships deploy -1 to same system. Once per game, you may take one Admiral\'s Order or any commander into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Veteran of the Imperial military machine. Leader of the Imperial fleet at Endor. Skilled at political maneuvering and appeasing his powerful superiors.',NULL,'9_98'),(27,166,'Dark','C','Endor','•••AT-ST Pilot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/atstpilot.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','1','2','3','Adds 2 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots. When piloting an AT-ST in battle, adds 1 to his forfeit, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise and cumulatively adds 1 to your attrition against opponent.','Due to the unstable control characteristics of AT-STs, only the most talented recruits are assigned to them.',NULL,'8_91'),(28,79,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Alderaan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/alderaan.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : -',NULL,'Alderaan','1_281'),(29,98,'Dark','U','Coruscant','Alter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/alter.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target an Effect, Utinni Effect, or Political Effect (even if just being deployed), and one of your characters on table. Draw destiny. If destiny < ability of character, target Effect is canceled. OR Cancel Sense.','Those who can use the Force are able to manipulate the objects around them to their advantage.','Alter (EP1)','12_145'),(30,40,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•A Useless Gesture','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/auselessgesture.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Cancels Don\'t Underestimate Our Chances. When opponent plays an Interrupt and has 3 smugglers on table, if that Interrupt is placed in Lost Pile, place it out of play. Ketwol may exchange a docking bay only once per game.','Imperial officers aboard the Death Star considered the Rebellion a minor threat.',NULL,'13_51'),(31,92,'Dark','U','Coruscant','•Allegations Of Corruption','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/allegationsofcorruption.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per game, may use 1 Force to stack one Interrupt just played here. To play any new Interrupt of the same name, player must first stack it here and use +1 Force for each Interrupt in stack, even if Interrupt is normally free. (Immune to Alter.)','With the Republic groaning under the weight of its own bureaucracy, senators accuse, bicker and fight to further their own agendas.',NULL,'12_128'),(32,77,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Ak-rev','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/akrev.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','1','Subtracts 1 from attrition against you at same site. Once during each of your control phases, may use 1 Force to take one musician into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Weequay musician from Sriluur. Studied in a monastery devoted to the Weequay god of thunder. Jabba\'s drum master. Trained in several forms of hand-to-hand combat.',NULL,'7_164'),(33,6090,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 9','•Apology Accepted (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/apologyaccepted.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During battle, lose an Imperial leader piloting your Star Destroyer. For remainder of turn, that Star Destroyer draws 2 battle destiny if unable to otherwise, is immune to attrition, and its power may not be increased by Imperial pilots aboard (except Vader).','\'I shall assume full responsibility for losing them and apologize to Lord Vader.\' Needa discovered that Vader was only slightly more forgiving than the Emperor.',NULL,'209_46'),(34,6089,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 9','An Inkling Of Its Destructive Potential','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/aninklingofitsdestructivepotential.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per game, may take a [Set 9] Epic Event into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. During your deploy phase, if Krennic on Death Star, may flip Set Your Course For Alderaan (flip back at end of turn)(Immune to Alter.)','Blank.',NULL,'209_41'),(35,4101,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 1','•According To My Design','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/accordingtomydesign.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Starting','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Unless your starship site or Death Star on table, deploy Emperor to your site (even if converted) and up to three Effects that deploy for free, are [Immune to Alter], and have \'deploy on table\' (or \'deploy on your side of table\') in game text. Light Side goes first. Place Interrupt in Lost Pile.','From his throne room aboard the second Death Star, Emperor Palpatine monitors activity throughout the galaxy.',NULL,'201_34'),(36,49,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Abyssin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/abyssin.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','2','Power +2 and Forfeit +1 while Myo at Audience Chamber. If lost or forfeited during a battle, may use 2 Force to \'regenerate\' (place Abyssin in your Used Pile).','Abyssins have an extremely violent culture. They also possess tremendous regenerative abilities. Often become mercenaries once they leave their homeworld, Byss.',NULL,'6_91'),(37,6087,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 11','••Always Two There Are','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/alwaystwothereare.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just lost a Dark Jedi and have exactly one Dark Jedi on table, take a Dark Jedi into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Once per game, if you have exactly two Dark Jedi on table, choose: Opponent loses 2 Force OR make a just drawn destiny = 2.','\'At last we will reveal ourselves to the Jedi.\'',NULL,'211_12'),(38,87,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•All Too Easy','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/alltooeasy.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If an opponent\'s character at the Carbonite Chamber was just \'hit\' by a lightsaber, deploy on that character. Character is instead immediately captured and \'frozen.\' If captive released, lose Immediate Effect. (Immune to Control.)','\'Perhaps you are not as strong as the Emperor thought.\'',NULL,'5_112'),(39,124,'Dark','R','Endor','•Aratech Corporation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/aratechcorporation.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Carida system. Your speeder bikes piloted by biker scouts are power +1 and forfeit +1 and may follow (for free) an opponent\'s vehicle or character that just moved from same site (if within range). (Immune to Alter while you occupy Carida.)','Aratech Corporation sent support staff to various Imperial outposts and garrisons. Gave advanced briefings and training to biker scout personnel.',NULL,'8_117'),(40,196,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Barada','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/barada.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','5','3','Deploys only to a Jabba\'s Palace site. Power = 0 at any location other than a Tatooine site. Power +2 at any Jabba\'s Palace site while Jabba is on the table. Your transport vehicles lost from same site may go to your Used Pile rather than your Lost Pile.','Male Klatooinian in charge of Jabba\'s repulsorpool. Sold onto slavery and won by Jabba in sabacc. Responsible for maintenance and supplies for Jabba\'s vehicles.',NULL,'6_96'),(41,47,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Ability, Ability, Ability (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/abilityabilityability.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table.  You may not play Imperial Barrier.  Senators are deploy +2.  Whenever you initiate a battle, may retrieve your topmost non-[Permanent Weapon], non-[Maintenance] character.  May place the top card of your Reserve Deck in Lost Pile to place a combat card in owner\'s Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Ben. . . Ben, please! Ben. . . Leia! Hear me, Leia!\'','Civil Disorder (V)','200_102'),(42,146,'Dark','R2','Premiere','Assault Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/assaultrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on your warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.','BlasTech model DLT-19 \'heavy blaster rifle.\' Enhanced with extra power packs and greater range.',NULL,'1_311'