th-Dark/large/blizzard1.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-AT','2','7','6','7','May add 2 pilots and 8 passengers. Immune to attrition < 4. When using AT-AT cannon to Target The Main Generator, adds 1 to total. Landspeed may not be increased.','General Veers\' AT-AT. Enclosed. Equipped with highly sophisticated communications gear. Employs an experimental targeting system.',NULL,'3_154'),(84,276,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Blockade Flagship: Bridge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/blockadeflagshipbridge.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Unless your Jedi here, Force drain -1 here.',NULL,NULL,'12_164'),(85,298,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•Bok Askol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/bokaskol.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','4','Once during your deploy phase, may draw destiny: (0-2) no result; (3-4) Askol draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise for remainder of turn; (5+) Askol is power +4 for remainder of turn.','At birth, a Pacithhips gene configuration usually indicates if they\'re to become a farmer, an intellectual, or a warrior. Bok Askol\'s destiny remained a mystery for years.',NULL,'14_75'),(86,134,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•••Armored Attack Tank','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/armoredattacktank.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AAT','2','5','4','5','May add 1 pilot and 3 passengers. While piloted at same site as a battle droid, adds two battle destiny. Landspeed may not be increased. Immune to attrition < 4.','The AAT is the most powerful vehicle in the Trade Federation arsenal. It includes range-enhanced laser cannons, projectile launchers and anti-personnel blasters. Enclosed.',NULL,'14_121'),(87,5008,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 2','•Binder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Dark/large/binder.gif?ra