f battle.','Aurra Sing\'s weapon of choice when she isn\'t using an opponent\'s lightsaber against them. Targeting mechanism is so complex only Aurra Sing can decipher it.',NULL,'13_53'),(91,292,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Boba Fett, Bounty Hunter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/bobafettbountyhunter.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','7','5','6','Text: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Adds one battle destiny if with your alien or Imperial (or adds two battle destiny if with your bounty hunter or Vader). Immune to attrition < 5. End of your turn: Use 2 Force to maintain OR Lose 2 Force to place in Used Pile OR Place out of play.','The most feared bounty hunter in the galaxy. Justifiably, his fee is as large as his reputation.',NULL,'13_59'),(92,6138,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 6','•Boba Fett (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual6-Dark/large/bobafett.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','4','4','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys -1 aboard Slave 1. Adds one battle destiny with Vader (or while piloting Slave 1). Once per game, if a battle was just initiated here, may exchange a card in hand with a card in Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Feared bounty hunter. Collected bounties on Solo from both the Empire and Jabba the Hutt. Took exquisite pleasure in using Solo\'s friend to capture him.',NULL,'206_9'),(93,153,'Dark','U2','A New Hope','•Astromech Shortage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/astromechshortage.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on opponent\'s side of table. All opponent\'s starships with a [Nav Computer] icon are deploy +1.','Imperial pilots often target astromech aboard Rebel starfighters in an attempt to prevent hyper-escapes. Scarcity of undamaged astromechs can delay starfighter deployment.',NULL,'2_116'),(94,363,'Dark','U1','Hoth','•Captain Lennox','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/captainlennox.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if starship is Tyrant). When on a Star Destroyer, may use its tractor beam once during each of your control phases.','Captain of the Imperial Star Destroyer Tyrant. An able leader. Unlike most Imperial officers, he is dedicated to his ship and crew. Finds political maneuvering distasteful.',NULL,'3_84'),(95,214,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Beedo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/beedo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','*','2','* Replaces any male Rodian for free (Rodian goes to the Used Pile) or deploys for 3 Force. While at Audience Chamber, all your Rodians are power +2, and whenever Greedo threatens a smuggler, may add 2 to destiny draw.','Rodian bounty hunter. Relative of Greedo. Taking Greedo\'s place in Jabba\'s court. Fearful of Jabba\'s wraith. Notorious sycophant.',NULL,'6_97'),(96,61,'Dark','R2','Virtual Set 0','•Admiral Motti (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/admiralmotti.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots.  Chiraneau may not modify your Force drains.  Kuat Drive Yards is [Immune to Alter].  Unless your Senate on table, unique (•) Star Destroyers are power +2 and immunity to attrition +1.  Once per game, may deploy non-[Set 0] Kuat Drive Yards from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Senior Navy Commander of Death Star. Believes in technology. Ridiculed the Force. Ambitious leader. Promoted due to support of New Order, not military skills. Hates Vader.',NULL,'200_73'),(97,274,'Dark','U2','Hoth','•••Blizzard Walker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/blizzardwalker.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-AT','1','6','6','6','May add 2 pilots and 8 passengers. Immune to attrition < 4. Landspeed may not be increased.','Enclosed All Terrain Armored Transport. Commonly called an Imperial walker. One of the most terrifying and deadly weapons in the Empire\'s arsenal. 15.5 meters tall.',NULL,'3_157'),(98,112,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Anoat','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/anoat.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, all opponent\'s Ugnaughts on table are forfeit -1.',NULL,'Anoat','4_154'),(99,4401,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 0','•A Useless Gesture (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Dark/large/auselessgesture.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. In order to play an Interrupt from Lost Pile, opponent must first stack it here (if possible) and use +1 Force for each card here, even if Interrupt is normally free. Revolution is canceled.','Imperial officers aboard the Death Star considered the Rebellion a minor threat.',NULL,'200_93'),(100,4056,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•Bossk In Hound\'s Tooth (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/bosskinhoundstooth.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Modified Corellian Freitghter','1','6','4','6','Permanent pilot is •Bossk, who provides ability of 2.  During battle with opponent\'s [Independent] starship (or Falcon), may add one destiny to total power or attrition.  Immune to attrition < 4.','Bossk once said of his ship, \'Greeezeg out nikek!\'',NULL,'200_131'),(101,102,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Amanaman','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/amanaman.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','3','4','2','Once per battle, may use 2 Force to \'behead\' (place out of play) one opposing non-droid character lost or forfeited where present. Adds X to attrition in battles at same site where X = the number of \'beheaded\' victims.','Male Amanin. Hangs the heads of his victims on his staff. Nicknamed Amanaman; his real name is unknown on Tatooine.',NULL,'6_92'),(102,237,'Dark','U','Dagobah','<>Big One: Asteroid Cave Or Space Slug Belly','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/bigoneasteroidcaveorspaceslugbelly.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Cave Rules\' in effect here.',NULL,'Big One: Asteroid Cave or Space Slug Belly','4_157'),(103,73,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Aiiii! Aaa! Agggggggggg!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/aiiiiaaaagggggggggg.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a Rebel of ability > 1 captive at a prison you control, opponent loses X Force, where X = the number of opponent\'s characters with ability > 2 on table.','\'They never even asked me any questions.\'',NULL,'5_130'),(104,254,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Blast Points','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/blastpoints.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your trooper just fired a character weapon during a battle, add one battle destiny. OR During your deploy phase, deploy on your trooper one character weapon from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','\'Only Imperial stormtroopers are so precise.\'',NULL,'7_247'),(105,6064,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 11','A Stunning Move / A Valuable Hostage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/astunningmove.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'A Stunning Move:Deploy 500 Republica (with Insidious Prisoner there) and Coruscant: Private Platform.{For} remainder of game, you may not deploy Sidious, First Order characters, or Imperials. Grievous is immunity to attrition +2. Once per turn, may deploy an Invisible Hand site or a non-unique [Separatist] droid from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.{Flip} this card if Insidious Prisoner is at an Invisible Hand site.A Valuable Hostage:{While} this side up, immunity to attrition of opponent\'s Jedi, starships, and vehicles is limited to < 5. During your control phase, if your [Separatist] character with Insidious Prisoner, opponent loses 1 Force. Once during your turn, may search your Force Pile and reveal any one card; reshuffle. Opponent may lose 2 Force to place that card on bottom of your Used Pile; otherwise, take it into hand.{Flip} this card if Insidious Prisoner is not at an Invisible Hand site.',NULL,NULL,'211_26'),(106,106,'Dark','U','Endor','•An Entire Legion Of My Best Troops','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/anentirelegionofmybesttroops.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Stormtroopers (except biker scouts) have armor = 4. Also, your blaster rifles, Stormtrooper Utility Belts and Blaster Scopes are deploy -1 and are destiny +2 when drawn for weapon or battle destiny. (Immune to Alter.)','Stormtrooper standard gear includes plastoid composite armor, utility belt, positive-grip boots and energy sinks to dissipate blaster fire.',NULL,'8_116'),(107,94,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Alter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/alter.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel one Effect (or Utinni Effect) by drawing a destiny < ability of your highest-ability character on table. OR Cancel one Sense card just played.','A user of the Force can subjugate the will of others or alter the environment at a distance, as when Vader \'disciplines\' those whose lack of faith disturbs him.','Alter','1_234'),(108,296,'Dark','C','Dagobah','Bog-wing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/bogwing.gif?raw=true','Creature','Avian','5','*','2','0','* Ferocity = destiny -1. Habitat: Dagobah. Parasite: Character (that can move). Relocate Bog-wing and host up to two sites away (opponent of victim chooses). Bog-wing then detaches.','Avian jungle-dweller. Fiercely territorial. Uses powerful talons to pick up and bear off victims. Carries up to nine times it\'s own body weight. Feeds primarily on root lizards and vine snakes.','Bog-wing','4_108'),(109,252,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Black Sun Fleet','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/blacksunfleet.gif?raw=true','Admiral\'s Order',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Any [Independent] starship with an alien pilot character aboard is immune to attrition < 4. At any site related to a system you occupy, your Black Sun agents are also information brokers. Information Exchange is immune to Alter. You may not retrieve Force for initiating a battle. During your control Phase, one of your [Independent] starships may make a regular move.',NULL,NULL,'10_32'),(110,366,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Captain Needa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/captainneeda.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Avenger, that starship is also immune to attrition < 4. You may re-target applicable Utinni Effects to Needa. If in a battle where you choose to forfeit characters, you must forfeit Needa first.','Able leader and captain of the Avenger. Was given his command by Admiral Ozzel. Treated with suspicion by Darth Vader and the Emperor, who distrust Ozzel\'s close advisors.',NULL,'4_93'),(111,22,'Dark','U1','Premiere','•A Disturbance In The Force','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/adisturbanceintheforce.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Once per game, during your deploy phase, \'insert\' (face down) into opponent\'s Reserve Deck; reshuffle. When effect reaches top it is immediately lost, but opponent may not activate any more Force that turn. (Immune to Alter.)','The destruction of Alderaan caused a great disturbance in the Force \'...as if millions of voices suddenly cried out in terror and were suddenly silenced.\'','A Tremor In The Force','1_208'),(112,125,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•Aratech Corporation (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/aratechcorporation.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. AT-STs and speeder bikes are power and forfeit +1. During your deploy phase, may reveal an AT-ST or Speeder Bike from hand to take a unique (•) [Endor] Imperial pilot of ability < 3 (or vice versa) into hand from Reserve Deck, and deploy both simultaneously; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Aratech Corporation sent support staff to various Imperial outposts and garrisons. Gave advanced briefings and training to biker scout personnel.',NULL,'200_103'),(113,6105,'Dark','R','Tatooine','•Aurra Sing (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/aurrasingai.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','4','4','3','May use any \'stolen\' lightsaber. Once per turn, may steal a lightsaber from an opponent\'s character just lost where present. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 while armed with a lightsaber).','Bounty hunter. Former student of the Force. After failing her Jedi training, Aurra became known for hunting down and killing Jedi Knights.',NULL,'11_52'),(114,257,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•Blasted Droid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/blasteddroid.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, fire (for free) one of your blasters carried by a trooper or one of your automated weapons. Any hit targets are immediately lost.','\'Oh my! Oh, uh, I\'m, I\'m terribly sorry. I. . . I didn\'t mean to intrude. No, no, no, please don\'t get up. No!\'',NULL,'5_132'),(115,303,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Boosted TIE Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/boostedtiecannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your TIE Advanced x1. May target a starship using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Subtract 1 if targeting a capital starship. Add 1 if targeting a starfighter. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Enhanced TIE blaster cannon prototype. Greater range and power. Improved targeting software. Requires more powerful energy cells. Tested by elite TIE squadrons.',NULL,'1_313'),(116,209,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Battle Order','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/battleorder.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Unless Battle Plan on table, for either player to initiate a Force drain, that player must first use 3 Force unless that player occupies a battleground site and a battleground system.','Administration of the Imperial installation on Endor includes coordination of troops on the ground and tight security provided by the Empire\'s space fleet.','Battle Plan - Defensive Shield','13_54'),(117,176,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Avenger','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/avenger.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','8','8','9','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles, and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 2. Subtract 2 from asteroid destiny draws targeting Avenger.','Key starship used to subjugate Outer Rim worlds. Reassigned to Death Squadron under the command of Captain Needa. Communications ship at the Battle of Endor.',NULL,'4_166'),(118,82,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Alert My Star Destroyer!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/alertmystardestroyer.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your admiral, moff or Dark Jedi just shuttled aboard your Star Destroyer, deploy on that character. Star Destroyer is immune to attrition and Flagship deploys free on that starship. Immediate Effect lost if character not aboard that starship.','For important Imperial dignitaries, an individual Star Destroyer is placed at their disposal.',NULL,'7_220'),(119,206,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•••Battle Droid Officer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/battledroidofficer.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','3','3','3','Your infantry battle droids deploy -1 to same site. While with another battle droid, adds 1 to your total battle destiny here. Your battle droids may move to this site for free.','Leader. Officer battle droids contain programming that permits them to adapt to unusual situations. Known to malfunction from time to time.',NULL,'14_73'),(120,4053,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Black 5','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/black5.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','3','2','2','5','May add DS-61-5 as pilot.  During battle, if about to be lost before the damage segment, is instead \'hit.\' If targeted by Watch Your Back!, it is a Used Interrupt.  Immune to Don\'t Get Cocky and attrition < 4.','-',NULL,'200_128'),(121,200,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Baron Soontir Fel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/baronsoontirfel.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','2','3','5','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Saber 1, adds one battle destiny and 2 to maneuver. Adds 1 to your total battle destiny for each of your piloted TIE Interceptors in same battle.','Corellian Baron. Leader of famed 181st Imperial Fighter Wing. Taught at the Imperial Academy on Prefsbelt IV. Instructed Biggs Darklighter.',NULL,'9_99'),(122,422,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Close Call (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/closecall.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: During battle, cancel and redraw a just drawn destiny.  LOST: A just drawn battle or weapon destiny is -3.\"','If this little one doesn\'t pulverize you, the next one just might.',NULL,'200_116'),(123,427,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Cloud City Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcityblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior at a Cloud City site. May target a character or creature using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit (and may not be used to satisfy attrition) if destiny > defense value.','Relby-k23 blaster pistol. Inflicts severe pain prior to death. Safety known to fail. Although these blasters are on the civilian restricted list, Imperial agents use them anyway.','Cloud City Blaster','5_180'),(124,425,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Cloud Car','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcar.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: Twin-Pod Cloud Car','2','2','2','3','May add 1 pilot or passenger. At cloud sectors, power +1, may deploy as a \'react\' and may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','Bespin Motors\' enclosed upper atmosphere craft. Utilizes a combination of ion engines and powerful repulsorlift drives to gain maximum power at high altitudes.','Cloud Car','5_178'),(125,430,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•••Cloud City Engineer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcityengineer.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','3','3','When present at a converted site, may use 2 Force to raise your site to the top. Also, when present at an opponent\'s site that has a Scomp link, your Force drains are +1 there. Ugnaughts deploy -1 to same Cloud City site.','Maintenance specialist Lee Phenets. Assigned to ensure the smooth operation of Cloud City. One of the few humans respected by the city\'s Ugnaughts.','Cloud City Technician','5_94'),(126,203,'Dark','U','Coruscant','•Baskol Yeesrim','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/baskolyeesrim.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','3','5','Agenda: blockade. While in a senate majority, once during your control phase opponent loses 1 Force for each Naboo location you control.','Gran senator who is part of the Malastare delegation. Supported Aks Moe\'s suggestion for a commission to be sent to Naboo.',NULL,'12_98'),(127,431,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Cloud City Occupation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/cloudcityoccupation.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Bespin system if you occupy at least two Cloud City battleground sites. During each of your control phases, opponent loses 1 Force for each Cloud City battleground site you occupy. Canceled if opponent controls this system. (Immune to Alter.)','\'I advise everyone to leave before more Imperial troops arrive.\'',NULL,'7_223'),(128,355,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Captain Bewil','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/captainbewil.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','3','4','During your control phase, may search your Reserve Deck, take one Laser Gate, Heart Of The Chasm or Rite Of Passage into hand and reshuffle. Opponent\'s characters may not move from same site as Bewil to a mobile site.','Tactical officer from Dentaal. Leader. Familiar with utilizing computer controls to lure an invading enemy into a tactically weak position.',NULL,'5_92'),(129,336,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Broken Concentration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/brokenconcentration.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Apprentices subtract X from training destiny, where X = ability - Jedi Test number (minimum zero). Also, once per turn, you may use 2 Force to move the top card of opponent\'s Force Pile to the top of opponent\'s Reserve Deck.','To effectively use the Force, a Jedi is required to learn concentration. A Jedi who gives in to distraction places both himself and his friends in peril.',NULL,'4_118'),(130,5021,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 3','•Cad Bane','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Dark/large/cadbane.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','4','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Your other bounty hunters here are power +1. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. During battle, if with your other bounty hunter, may cancel the immunity to attrition of a Jedi here.','Duros bounty hunter.',NULL,'203_24'),(131,413,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Chyler','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/chyler.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','2','3','While on Cloud City, adds 4 to destiny of each of your miners drawn for battle destiny and adds 1 to your Force drains at related cloud sectors where you have a minor or refinery (adds 2 if both).','Placed several ISB agents and Aqualish in the Cloud City miner\'s guild. Promised a position when the Empire took over Cloud City. She\'s still waiting.',NULL,'7_170'),(132,293,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Boba Fett\'s Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/bobafettsblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on Boba Fett, or 3 on your other bounty hunter. May deploy as a \'react.\' May target a character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a vehicle. Target hit if total destiny > defense value. May fire repeatedly for 1 Force each time.','Sawed off BlasTech EE-3 blaster rifle. Although its barrel is a few centimeters under the legal limit, no one has lived to file an official complaint.',NULL,'5_179'),(133,432,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Cloud City Sabacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcitysabacc.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Requirements: a gambler, thief or smuggler on Cloud City. Wild cards (1-6): Lando and Weather Vane. Clone cards: Locations and Ugnaughts. (Gamblers may use clone cards as zeroes.) Stakes: One starfighter, weapon or device.\"','Sabacc variant popular among the miners. Ugnaughts and chief administrators of Bespin\'s city in the clouds.','Cloud City Sabacc','5_134'),(134,441,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•Cloud City: Chasm Walkway','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcitychasmwalkway.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If Weather Vane on table, characters \'hit\' here are instead immediately relocated there.',NULL,'Cloud City: Chasm Walkway','5_167'),(135,447,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•Cloud City: East Platform (Docking Bay)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcityeastplatformdockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force.',NULL,'Cloud City: Platform 327 (Docking Bay)','5_169'),(136,437,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Cloud City: Carbonite Chamber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcitycarbonitechamber.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy, subtract 2 from opponent\'s Carbon-Freezing destiny.',NULL,'Cloud City: Carbonite Chamber','5_166'),(137,444,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Cloud City: Dining Room','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcitydiningroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Blue Milk, Beru Stew and Yoda Stew are doubled. Jek is deploy -2 here.',NULL,NULL,'5_168'),(138,391,'Dark','R2','Premiere','Charming To The Last','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/charmingtothelast.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Tarkin and a Rebel with ability > 2 are involved in the same battle, you may add one battle destiny (add two destiny if Rebel is Leia).','\'You\'re far too trusting. Dantooine is too remote to make an effective demonstration. But don\'t worry...We will deal with your Rebel friends soon enough.\'',NULL,'1_236'),(139,6163,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 11','•Carbonite Chamber Console (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/carbonitechamberconsole.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Carbonite Chamber. Once during opponent\'s turn, if a frozen captive on table, may activate 1 Force. Once per turn, may use 1 Force to take He\'s All Yours, Bounty Hunter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Most often used to freeze Tibanna gas for transport. Modified by Ugloste to work on humans. Intended to capture Luke Skywalker, the Emperor\'s prize.',NULL,'211_8'),(140,451,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Cloud City: Interrogation Room','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/cloudcityinterrogationroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain +1 here.',NULL,NULL,'7_271'),(141,439,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Cloud City: Casino','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/cloudcitycasino.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Unless you have a gambler here, you may not use wild cards in Cloud City Sabacc.',NULL,'Cloud City: Casino','7_269'),(142,320,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Brangus Glee','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/brangusglee.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','3','Power +2 at Cantina. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Once per turn, may exchange a docking bay from hand with top card of Lost Pile. Your docking bay transit is free when moving to or from same site. Immune to attrition < 3.','Elder of a dextrous race of renowned travelers. Gambler. Frequents casinos, bars and spaceports. Originally from distant planet Dor Nameth',NULL,'7_169'),(143,435,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Cloud City Trooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcitytrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Deploys only on Cloud City, but may move elsewhere. Power -1 when at a site other than a Cloud City site.','Officially titled Cloud City Wing Guards. Some are holdovers from previous administrations which were more totalitarian. A moderate pay scale breeds corruption.','Cloud City Trooper','5_95'),(144,384,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•Cease Fire!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/ceasefire.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated, lose 2 Force to prevent all weapons from being fired for remainder of battle. OR Target all your battle droids at a site. Targets may not have their forfeit value reduced for remainder of turn. OR Cancel Blaster Proficiency.','The amount of time it takes for a subcommand to transfer to an officer battle droid, and then to the rest of his regiment, is .396 of a second.','Keep Your Eyes Open (V)','14_101'),(145,449,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•Cloud City: Incinerator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcityincinerator.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control Force drain -1 here.',NULL,'Cloud City: Incinerator','5_170'),(146,393,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Chevin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/chevin.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','3','2','Power +2 and forfeit +1 while Ephant Mon is at Audience Chamber. When forfeited at same site as one of your alien leaders, may satisfy all remaining attrition against you.','Most Chevin are mercenaries, gun runners and slavers. Have strong communities on their homeworld. Wear clothing only because others do.',NULL,'6_99'),(147,406,'Dark','U1','Premiere','•Chief Bast','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/chiefbast.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Power +1 at same site as Tarkin. If a battle was just initiated at a system where Bast is present with your non-droid character, may \'evacuate\' (relocate) both to a related site.','Aide to Grand Moff Tarkin. Rarely underestimates enemies. Learned cunning and patience hunting big game as a youth.',NULL,'1_165'),(148,388,'Dark','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','•Chall Bekan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Dark/large/challbekan.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','4','4','When deployed, you may take one non-unique alien into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Your aliens deploy -1 to same or adjacent Tatooine site.','Male Morseerian leader. Methane breather. Has ties to Tatooine\'s Imperial government. Uses alien agents to maintain surveillance on Jabba and the Rebellion.',NULL,'106_11'),(149,409,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Chief Retwin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/chiefretwin.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','3','3','May use 3 Force to \'hide\' (be excluded) from a battle. May use 2 Force to target one device or weapon present which deploys on a site. Draw destiny. If destiny > target\'s deploy cost, target is lost.','Highly skilled saboteur. Former Imperial sympathizer who worked for the defense forces on his home planet, Ralltiir. Joined the Empire after Ralltiir\'s subjugation.',NULL,'5_93'),(150,273,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 0','•Blizzard Scout 1 (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/blizzardscout1.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-ST','4','3','3','5','May add 1 pilot or passenger. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. May move as a \'react.\' During battle, if with your piloted AT-AT, may cancel game text of an opponent\'s character present.','Enclosed All Terrain Scout Transport (AT-ST). Provides flanking support to the AT-ATs of Blizzard Force. Modified for cold weather combat.',NULL,'200_140'),(151,295,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Boelo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/boelo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','4','3','Deploys only on Tatooine or to same site as Jabba. When in a battle either at Audience Chamber or with your alien leader, may cancel one opponent\'s battle destiny just drawn.','Naroon Cuthus\' predecessor as Jabba\'s right hand man. Sees what he wants to see. Hears what he wants to hear. Has a pet womp rat named Worra.',NULL,'7_168'),(152,216,'Dark','U','Coruscant','•Begin Landing Your Troops','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/beginlandingyourtroops.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your unique (•) Republic characters are forfeit +2 and immune to Goo Nee Tay. Unless Imperial Arrest Order on table, once during your deploy phase, may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Once begun, the occupation of Naboo was swift, and devastatingly effective.','Security Control','12_130'),(153,304,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Boring Conversation Anyway','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/boringconversationanyway.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel either: Report To Lord Vader, Scomp Link Access, Rebel Planners, Rebel Reinforcements, Gift of the Mentor, Panic, Don\'t Get Cocky, Skywalkers, Demotion, Combined Attack or Surprise Assault.','\'Uh...had a slight weapons malfunction. But, uh, everything\'s perfectly all right now. We\'re fine. We\'re all fine here, now, thank you. How are you?\'',NULL,'1_235'),(154,6151,'Dark','R','Death Star II','Bring Him Before Me / Take Your Father\'s Place','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/bringhimbeforeme.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Bring Him Before Me:Deploy Throne Room, Insignificant Rebellion and Your Destiny.{For} remainder of game, Scanning Crew may not be played. Opponent\'s cards that place a character out of play may not target Luke. You may deploy Emperor (deploy -2) from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Opponent may deploy Luke from Reserve Deck (deploy -2; reshuffle) or Lost Pile. If Luke is present with Vader and Vader is not escorting a captive, Luke is captured and seized by Vader. Vader may not transfer Luke.{Flip} this card if Luke captured.Take Your Father\'s Place:{While} this side up, lose 1 Force at end of each of your turns. Once during each of your turns, when Vader, Luke (even as a non-frozen captive) and Emperor are all present at your Throne Room, you may initiate a Luke/Vader duel: Each player draws two destiny. Add ability. Highest total wins. If Vader wins, opponent loses 3 Force. If Luke wins, shuffle Reserve Deck and draw destiny; if destiny > 12, Luke crosses to Dark Side, totally depleting opponent\'s Life Force.{Flip} if Luke neither present with Vader nor a captive.',NULL,NULL,'9_151'),(155,208,'Dark','U','Endor','•Battle Order','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/battleorder.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. You may initiate battles for free. Also (unless Battle Plan on table), for either player to initiate a Force drain, that player must first use 3 Force unless that player occupies a battleground site (except a holosite) and a battleground system. (Immune to Alter.)','Administration of the Imperial installation on Endor includes coordination of troops on the ground and tight security provided by the Empire\'s space fleet.','Battle Plan','8_118'),(156,359,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Captain Godherdt','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/captaingodherdt.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Adds 3 to power of any capital starship he pilots. While aboard a Star Destroyer, adds 1 to armor, adds 1 to hyperspeed and, once during each of your move phases, may cancel Landing Claw at same system or sector.','Elite fleet engineer. Technically brilliant. Key operator of magnetic signature sensors monitoring Star Destroyer hulls.',NULL,'9_100'),(157,263,'Dark','U1','Virtual Set 0','Blaster Rack (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/blasterrack.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per turn, may / a matching weapon on your unique (•) character present at a site. [Immune to Alter.]','Imperial facilities like the Death Star and garrison bases have blaster racks at key locations to equip soldiers with weapons like blaster rifles and thermal detonators.','Sai\'torr Kal Fas (V)','200_104'),(158,271,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Blizzard 4','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/blizzard4.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-AT','4','8','5','5','May add 6 passengers. Permanent pilots provide 