dition-Dark/large/combatcloudcar.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: Talon 1 Combat Cloud Car','3','3','3','4','Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. At cloud sectors, power and maneuver +1, may deploy as a \'react\' and may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter.','Enclosed Ubrikkian Talon I Combat Cloud Car. Speeds up to 1,875 kph. Exceptional maneuverability makes this a favorite of outer Rim security forces.',NULL,'7_311'),(194,518,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Conduct Your Search','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/conductyoursearch.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once during your deploy phase, you may deploy a non-Interrupt card with \'door\' in title from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle. At Endor sites where you have a scout, Rebel scouts are power -1 and forfeit -3. (Immune to Alter.)','\'...and bring his companions to me.\'',NULL,'13_62'),(195,227,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','Bespin Motors Void Spider THX 1138','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/bespinmotorsvoidspiderthx1138.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Shuttle','2','1','2','4','May add 3 passengers.  Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. May move as a \'react.\'  *Landspeed = 3.  OR  Up to 3 characters may shuttle to or from same site for free.','This light, enclosed shuttle is used for courier runs to large orbiting transports.',NULL,'2_156'),(196,458,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Cloud City: Upper Plaza Corridor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcityupperplazacorridor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Force drain +1.',NULL,'Cloud City: Upper Plaza Corridor','5_173'),(197,220,'Dark','C','Tatooine','•Ben Quadinaros\' Podracer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/benquadinarospodracer.gif?raw=true','Podracer',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Adds 1 to each of your race destinies here. Once during each of your control phases may lose 2 Force to exchange the topmost race destiny here with topmost race destiny of another Podracer.','Balta-Trabaat BT310 Podracer that utilizes four engines instead of two. Has the potential to be the fastest Podracer on the track, despite its inconsistent performance.',NULL,'11_95'),(198,4052,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Cloud City: Security Tower (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/cloudcitysecuritytower.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, may use 3 Force to release a captive here. Captive Pursuit is canceled.',NULL,NULL,'200_126'),(199,4096,'Dark','U1','Virtual Set 1','•Colonel Wullf Yularen (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/colonelwullfyularen.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','1','2','5','Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots (2 if a capital starship). When deployed, may activate up to X Force (limit 4), where X = number of ISB agents on table. While aboard a starship, its power may not be reduced by opponent.','Imperial Security Bureau (ISB) officer assigned to brief Tarkin. Also ordered to ensure absolute loyalty to the Emperor. Leader. Will stop at nothing to fulfill the Emperor\'s will.',NULL,'201_22'),(200,262,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Blaster Rack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/blasterrack.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. At any time, you may transfer one of your character weapons from any site to the Blaster Rack. During your deploy phase, weapon may be transferred to your character on table for an expenditure of Force equal to the weapon\'s deploy cost.','Imperial facilities like the Death Star and garrison bases have blaster racks at key locations to equip soldiers with weapons like blaster rifles and thermal detonators.',NULL,'1_211'),(201,460,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Cloud City: Upper Walkway','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/cloudcityupperwalkway.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain -1 here. If you control, opponent\'s Upper Walkway game text is canceled.',NULL,NULL,'7_273'),(202,277,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•Blockade Flagship: Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/blockadeflagshipdockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your Docking Bay transit to and from here requires +8 Force.',NULL,'Blockade Flagship: Docking Bay','14_111'),(203,496,'Dark','R','Endor','•Commander Igar','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/commanderigar.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','4','5','Adds 3 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots. When piloting Tempest 1 or a non-unique AT-AT, adds one battle destiny. When in battle with Veers or Tagge, may use 2 Force to cancel and redraw one just-drawn battle destiny.','Leader. Served with General Veers\' Blizzard unit at Battle of Hoth. Assigned by Vader to coordinate surface defense of Endor\'s moon. Kuat native.',NULL,'8_94'),(204,280,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Blow Parried','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/blowparried.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take top card of Force Pile into hand. OR If opponent just revealed a combat card, it is canceled (place in opponent\'s Used Pile) and opponent must draw destiny instead (that destiny is reduced by 1). OR Cancel Glancing Blow, Clash Of Sabers, or Obi-Wan\'s Journal.','Offense may win battles, but defense keeps you alive long enough to mount an offense.',NULL,'13_58'),(205,380,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Carbonite Chamber Console','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/carbonitechamberconsole.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Carbonite Chamber. Adds 3 to Carbon-Freezing destiny. Also, once during each of your turns, you may use 1 Force to take one Ugnaught, Prepare The Chamber or Carbon-Freezing into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Most often used to freeze Tibanna gas for transport. Modified by Ugloste to work on humans. Intended to capture Luke Skywalker, the Emperor\'s prize.',NULL,'5_107'),(206,361,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Captain Jonus','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/captainjonus.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Deploys -2 aboard Scimitar 2. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When forfeited from a TIE/sa, also satisfies all remaining attrition and battle damage against you.','Often flies as top cover during bombing runs. Served with Death Squadron. Narrowly escaped death by space slug. Scored several kills against rebel blockade runners.',NULL,'9_101'),(207,473,'Dark','R','Endor','•Colonel Dyer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/coloneldyer.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','4','While at Bunker of an Endor battleground site, prevents Ominous Rumors from being canceled. Your [Endor] troopers may move as a \'react\' to same site.','Responsible for defense of control bunker. Leader. Worked closely with Moff Jerjerrod to plan the installation\'s defense. Instructed to hold troops in reserve.',NULL,'8_93'),(208,452,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Cloud City: Lower Corridor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/cloudcitylowercorridor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Force drain -1 here.',NULL,'Cloud City: Lower Corridor','5_171'),(209,225,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Bespin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/bespin.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, your characters and vehicles deploy -1 to Cloud City locations.',NULL,NULL,'5_164'),(210,467,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Collateral Damage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/collateraldamage.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'An accident occurs at the beginning of a battle at any site where opponent has at least two characters and one weapon. Draw destiny. If destiny < number of opponent\'s characters at that site, one is lost. (Opponent\'s choice.)','Blast vests and helmets with blast shields cannot protect Rebel soldiers from grenades, panel explosions and other combat hazards.','Friendly Fire','1_237'),(211,465,'Dark','C2','Hoth','Cold Feet','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/coldfeet.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target a character at any marker site. Draw destiny. If site under \'nighttime conditions,\' add 2 to destiny draw. If total destiny > ability, character may not move for remainder of turn.','Wampas pack snow around the appendages of captured prey, making use of Hoth\'s cold environment to immobilize them.',NULL,'3_117'),(212,57,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•Activate The Droids','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/activatethedroids.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Blockade Flagship (may not deploy on a site). Whenever you initiate a battle at a related planet site where youhave a battle droid, you may activate 2 Force or retrieve 1 Force.','The activation of droids requires a transmission from a Droid Control Ship on a top-secret frequency. Only a Trade Federation captain has access to these frequencies.',NULL,'14_93'),(213,45,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','AAT Laser Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/aatlasercannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Vehicle','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your AAT. May target a character (use 1 Force) or vehicle (for free) at same or adjacent site. Draw destiny. Character lost if destiny +1 > defense value. Vehicle lost if destiny +3 > defense value. May target a creature for free. Creature is lost.','High caliber primary tank weapon. Just as effective against massed ground troops as vehicles. Cannot penetrate energy shields.',NULL,'14_126'),(214,93,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Allegations Of Corruption','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/allegationsofcorruption.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Once per game, may use 1 Force to stack one Interrupt just played here. To play any new Interrupt of the same name, player must first stack it here and use +1 Force for each Interrupt in stack, even if Interrupt is normally free.','With the Republic groaning under the weight of its own bureaucracy, senators accuse, bicker, and fight to further their own agendas.','A Tragedy Has Occurred - Defensive Shield','13_52'),(215,5191,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 8','Alert My Star Destroyer! (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/alertmystardestroyer.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. During your deploy phase, you may reveal one Star Destroyer from hand to take its matching pilot character (or vice versa) into hand from Reserve Deck, and deploy both simultaneously (for -1 Force each); reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','For important Imperial dignitaries, an individual Star Destroyer is placed at their disposal.',NULL,'208_38'),(216,4021,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Arica (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/arica.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien/Imperial','1','4','5','7','Power +1 on Tatooine. Once per game, during your move phase, may relocate Arica to Luke\'s location. During your control phase, if present at a battleground (and Luke is not), may retrieve 1 Force. Immune to Undercover and attrition < 4.','Mara Jade posed as a dancer at Jabba\'s Palace in an attempt to complete her master\'s task and kill Luke. Musician. Spy. Unable to convince Jabba to take her on his skiff.',NULL,'200_74'),(217,270,'Dark','R2','Virtual Set 0','•Blizzard 2 (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/blizzard2.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-AT','2','6','6','6','May add 1 pilot and 8 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. During your control phase, may take one Trample or Walker Barrage into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Walker Barrage total is +2. Immune to attrition < 4.','AT-AT commanded by the treacherous General Nevar before he was assassinated. Fortified with an extra layer of armor by the paranoid general. Enclosed.',NULL,'200_139'),(218,103,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Amanin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/amanin.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','2','When Attacking or being attacked by a creature, power +3 and may add one destiny. If Amanin is alone and causes a non-selective creature to be lost, creature is placed out of play and you may retrieve Force equal to its deploy cost.','Amanin are a primitive hunting species. Exposed to space travel when their planet became a mining world for the Empire. Fierce-tempered when angered.',NULL,'6_93'),(219,48,'Dark','U','Cloud City','Abyss','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/abyss.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If a unique (•) card is drawn for destiny and a duplicate is on table, destiny card is lost (destiny = 0). If duplicated card is a character, it loses immunity to attrition for rest of turn and player must lose 2 Force or lose that character. (Immune to Alter.)','Careless abuse of the Force by a young Jedi trainee can have dire consequences. When hanging from the weather vane of Cloud City, Luke\'s balance was his only hope.','Chasm','5_111'),(220,6085,'Dark','U1','Virtual Set 0','Alter (Premiere) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/alterpremiere.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Sense.  LOST: Target an Effect, Political Effect, or Utinni Effect, and one of your characters on table. Draw destiny. If destiny < character\'s ability, target Effect is canceled (you lose no Force to Do, Or Do Not). (Immune to opponent\'s Objective.)\"','A user of the Force can subjugate the will of others or alter the environment at a distance, as when Vader \'disciplines\' those whose lack of faith disturbs him.',NULL,'200_115'),(221,51,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Abyssin Ornament & •Wounded Wookiee','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/abyssinornament&woundedwookiee.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Take one non-unique alien into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: During a battle, if opponent drew more than two battle destiny, cancel all but two of those destiny draws (your choice). OR If your non-unique alien is in a battle, cancel game text of one Rebel for remainder of turn.\"',NULL,NULL,'10_28'),(222,50,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Abyssin Ornament','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/abyssinornament.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Once per game, target one non-unique character on table. Draw destiny. If destiny is less than X, retrieve X Force, where X equals the number of copies of that card you have on table (immune to Sense). OR search your Reserve Deck and take one non-unique alien into hand; reshuffle.','The Abyssins are known for their regenerative abilities. Jabba keeps several statue heads of Abyssin creatures on his repulsor sled.','Nar Shaddaa Wind Chimes','6_151'),(223,160,'Dark','C2','Hoth','AT-AT Driver','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/atatdriver.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','1','2','2','Adds 2 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots (3 if combat vehicle is an AT-AT).','Piloting walkers high above the battlefield, AT-AT drivers are protected by 15 centimeters of reinforced armor. Accordingly, they are regarded with contempt by the infantry.',NULL,'3_83'),(224,158,'Dark','U1','Hoth','AT-AT Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/atatcannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Vehicle','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your AT-AT. May target a starfighter (use 3 as defense value), character, creature or vehicle at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a character or creature, 2 if a vehicle. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Laser cannons mounted on the head of an Imperial walker provide devastating coordinated firepower. Effective against a wide variety of targets.',NULL,'3_158'),(225,194,'Dark','R','Special Edition','••Bantha Herd','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/banthaherd.gif?raw=true','Effect','Mobile','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an exterior Tatooine site. Specify starting location. During your control phase, moves to next adjacent site (reversing direction as necessary). During battle here, if your tusken raider or bantha here may add one battle destiny.','While banthas are found on many worlds, the largest herds are found on Tatooine. The Sand People of that planet learned to tame the beasts.',NULL,'7_221'),(226,207,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','Battle Droid Pilot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/battledroidpilot.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','0','2','2','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 while piloting a battleship). While piloting a battleship, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.','Pilot battle droids require navigational programming not found in other types of battle droids. Therefore, even though they lack weaponry, their manufacturing cost is still the same.',NULL,'14_74'),(227,193,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Bantha Fodder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/banthafodder.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel As Good As Gone or Innocent Scoundrel. OR Search your Reserve Deck and take one bantha, Tusken Raider, Taym Dren-garen or Weequay into hand; reshuffle.','\'Uu a\'kingsa riika pagh bagla bis kachata weenow con bantha poodoo.\'',NULL,'6_152'),(228,185,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Bad Feeling Have I','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/badfeelinghavei.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s side of table. Luke, Leia, Han, Chewie, Lando, Yoda, and Obi-Wan are deploy +2. Also, opponent may not play any cards with the words \'bad feeling\' in the title.','\'Ready are you? What know you of ready?\'',NULL,'4_116'),(229,114,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Anoat Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/anoatoperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','2','While at an Anoat site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your Ugnaught is on Anoat) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Anoat from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Independent mercenaries operating out of Anoat work with some of the locals, such as Ugnaughts. These operatives inform the Empire of all suspected Alliance activities.','Anoat Operative','7_165'),(230,6079,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','Agents of Black Sun / Vengeance of the Dark Prince','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/agentsofblacksun.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Agents of Black Sun:Deploy Imperial City (With Xizor there) and Coruscant system.{For} remainder of game, your aliens with \'Black Sun\' in lore, bounty hunters, and information brokers are Black Sun Agents. You may not deploy cards with ability except Black Sun Agents, Emperor, or Independent starships. During your control phase, each of your bounty hunters may make a regular move to an adjacent site where there is a bounty. Scanning Crew may not be played.{Flip} this card if Xizor is at a battleground site and Luke is not at a battleground site.Vengeance of the Dark Prince:{While} this side up, once per turn, may place a card from hand in Used Pile to peek at cards in your Force Pile. Once during each of your battle phases, may peek at top X cards of any Reserve Deck, where X= number of locations you occupy. For each Black Sun Agent in battle, attrition against opponent is +1. During your control phase, opponent loses 1 Force for each battleground location occupied by Xizor or Emperor.{Flip} this card if Luke is at a battleground site or if Xizor not on table.',NULL,NULL,'10_29'),(231,4102,'Dark','C1','Virtual Set 1','•A Dark Time For The Rebellion (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/adarktimefortherebellion.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent\'s starting location was Massassi Throne Room, opponent loses 1 Force when you play this Interrupt. Add or subtract 1 from opponent\'s just drawn destiny. OR Activate 1 Force. OR Until end of turn, battle destiny draws may not be canceled (unless being redrawn) or modified.','Absolute control wielded by the Emperor enables the Imperial forces to dominate planetary systems before the Rebel Alliance can gain a foothold.','They\'re Tracking Us (V)','201_33'),(232,60,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Admiral Motti','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/admiralmotti.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','3','5','Deploys -2 if at least two Imperial starships on table. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Subtracts 1 from forfeit of Rebel pilots at same system.','Senior Navy Commander of Death Star. Believes in technology. Ridiculed the Force. Ambitious leader. Promoted due to support of New Order, not military skills. Hates Vader.',NULL,'1_164'),(233,6083,'Dark','U1','Virtual Set 0','Alter (Coruscant) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/altercoruscant.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Sense.  LOST: Target an Effect, Political Effect, or Utinni Effect, and one of your characters on table. Draw destiny. If destiny < character\'s ability, target Effect is canceled (you lose no Force to Do, Or Do Not). (Immune to opponent\'s Objective.)\"','A user of the Force can subjugate the will of others or alter the environment at a distance, as when Vader \'disciplines\' those whose lack of faith disturbs him.',NULL,'200_144'),(234,78,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Aks Moe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/aksmoe.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','3','2','5','Agendas: ambition, blockade. While in a senate majority, your capital starships are each power +2, and your Force drains are +1 at each battleground system where you occupy a related site.','Gran senator from Malastare. A skillful politician who demanded that a commission be sent to Naboo to investigate the alleged occupation there.',NULL,'12_97'),(235,121,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•Apology Accepted','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/apologyaccepted.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'At the end of any battle phase, lose one of your Imperials of ability < 6 who survived a battle you lost this turn. Activate Force up to either that character\'s forfeit value or the amount of your battle damage in that battle.','\'I shall assume full responsibility for losing them and apologize to Lord Vader.\' Needa discovered that Vader was only slightly more forgiving than the Emperor.',NULL,'4_137'),(236,357,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Captain Daultay Dofine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/captaindaultaydofine.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','3','3','5','Adds 3 to power of any capital starship he pilots. Once per game may take Activate The Droids into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While aboard Blockade Flagship, it is immune to attrition < 5 and Activate The Droids is immune to Alter.','Neimoidian captain of the Trade Federation Droid Control Ship blockading Naboo. Cowardly, lazy, and extremely greedy.',NULL,'14_76'),(237,5092,'Dark','R2','Virtual Set 4','•Captain Phasma','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/captainphasma.gif?raw=true','Character','First Order','2','4','3','4','Adds one battle destiny with a stormtrooper. If you just won a battle at same or related location, may retrieve a trooper.','Female leader. Stormtrooper.',NULL,'204_38'),(238,269,'Dark','R2','Hoth','•Blizzard 2','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/blizzard2.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-AT','2','6','6','6','May add 1 pilot and 8 passengers. Immune to attrition < 4. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 2. Landspeed may not be increased.','AT-AT commanded by the treacherous General Nevar before he was assassinated. Fortified with an extra layer of armor by th