so, S-foils and Maneuvering Flaps are suspended where you have either a weapon present or a starship (or vehicle) with maneuver > 3 present. (Immune to Alter.)','Scout walker pilots are trained to set up a deadly heavy fire zone. This tactic can be disrupted by enemy weapons fire.',NULL,'8_121'),(279,589,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Crossfire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/crossfire.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. S-foils and Maneuvering Flaps are suspended where you have either a weapon present or a starship (or vehicle) with maneuver > 3 present.','Scout walker pilots are trained to set up a deadly heavy fire zone. This tactic can be disrupted by enemy weapons fire.',NULL,'13_63'),(280,591,'Dark','PM','Enhanced Cloud City','•Crush The Rebellion','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedCloudCity-Dark/large/crushtherebellion.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per turn, may take I Have You Now or Evader into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. At mobile sites, opponent draws no more than two battle destiny per battle. Evader is immune to Sense. May lose 1 Force to cancel Clash of Sabers. (Immune to Alter.)','After dueling his son and seizing control of a city in the clouds, Vader resumed his quest to destroy the Alliance.',NULL,'109_9'),(281,594,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','CZ-4','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/cz4.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','2','3','Opponent may not \'react\' to or from same site. You may \'react\' to a battle or Force drain at same or adjacent Jabba\'s Palace site by deploying (at normal use of the Force) one non-unique alien to that site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Very common communications droid. Some have been modified to be defense drones. Programmed to warn their masters of an imminent attack.',NULL,'6_100'),(282,596,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Dagobah','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/dagobah.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Dagobah','7_279'),(283,599,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Dagobah: Cave','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/dagobahcave.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Lose 1 Force during each of your control phases if Yoda on table but not on Dagobah.',NULL,NULL,'4_158'),(284,605,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•Dannik Jerriko','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/dannikjerriko.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','*','4','2','Once per battle, may use 1 Force to \'eat the soup\' of (place out of play) one opposing non-droid character just lost or forfeited at same site. * Power = 1 + total ability of all victims whose soup was eaten.','Anzati assassin. Cheek-folds hide proboscises which allow him to \'eat the soup\' (consume the life Force) of his victims. Smokes t\'bac. Currently working for Jabba.',NULL,'2_84'),(285,607,'Dark','U1','Premiere','•Dantooine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/dantooine.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : (none)',NULL,'Dantooine','1_282'),(286,610,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Dantooine Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/dantooineoperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','2','While at a Dantooine site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your thief is on Dantooine) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Dantooine from Reserve Deck- reshuffle.','Corrupt Pacithhip businessmen. Report to the Empire on who makes contributions to the Alliance.',NULL,'7_174'),(287,611,'Dark','U2','A New Hope','•Danz Borin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/danzborin.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of anything he is aboard as a passenger.','Cocky gunner and bounty hunter. Maintains a residence on Nar Shaddaa, the spaceport moon of the Hutt homeworld. To his companions\' delight, he\'s nearly as good as he boasts.',NULL,'2_85'),(288,613,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Dark Collaboration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/darkcollaboration.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Tarkin and either Tagge or Motti are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny. OR Cancel Restricted Deployment or Rebel Barrier.','Imperial leaders are ruthlessly effective when working together. Tarkin, Motti and Tagge presented a deadly combination as they plotted to \'crush the Rebellion.\'',NULL,'1_239'),(289,614,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Dark Deal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/darkdeal.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Bespin: Cloud City if you control that sector and at least three related sites. At each Cloud City site, your total power is +4 and your Force drains are +2. Effect canceled if opponent occupies four Bespin locations. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Perhaps you think you\'re being treated unfairly?\' \'No.\' \'Good. It would be unfortunate if I had to leave a garrison here.\'',NULL,'5_115'),(290,617,'Dark','PM','Jedi Pack','•Dark Forces','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JediPack-Dark/large/darkforces.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. When Surprise Assault is played, may use 1 Force to add one destiny to your total. Also, when Sense or Alter is played, may use X Force to exclude X Jedi from being the \'highest-ability character.\'','\'The ability to destroy a planet is insignificant next to the power of the Force.\'','For Luck','102_6'),(291,619,'Dark','U2','Premiere','•••Dark Hours','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/darkhours.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Select one site under \'nighttime conditions.\' Target every character there (except droids) and draw one destiny each. If destiny > ability, character \'sleeps\' (power, forfeit and ability = 0, \'game text\' unusable) until the end of your next turn.','After surviving Tarkin\'s extortion, kidnapping, threats of execution and the assault of the Interceptor droid, Princess Leia was asleep when her rescuers came.',NULL,'1_212'),(292,620,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Dark Jedi Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/darkjedilightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use X Force to deploy on your warrior where X = (7 - warrior\'s ability). May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature using X Force. Draw two destiny. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Multifaceted jewels focus light into a deadly blade. Projects a meterlong beam of pure energy. A lightsaber is constructed personally by a Jedi as a part of training.','Jedi Lightsaber','1_314'),(293,6216,'Dark','U1','Virtual Set 11','Dark Jedi Lightsaber (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/darkjedilightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Aurra, Grievous, or your warrior of ability > 4. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and may not be used to satisfy attrition, if total destiny > defense value.','Multifaceted jewels focus light into a deadly blade. Projects a meterlong beam of pure energy. A lightsaber is constructed personally by a Jedi as a part of training.',NULL,'211_25'),(294,621,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Dark Jedi Presence','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/darkjedipresence.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your Dark Jedi is present during any battle, use 1 Force to cause all other Imperials there to battle at double power.','A Dark Lord\'s presence motivates Imperial troops. \'See to it personally, Commander.\'','Jedi Presence','1_240'),(295,622,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Dark Maneuvers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/darkmaneuvers.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add 2 to maneuver and 1 to power of any starfighter for the remainder of this turn. If it has hyperdrive, also add 2 to hyperspeed. (Interrupt may even affect the result immediately after a destiny draw targeting the starfighter\'s maneuver.)','Imperial TIE fighters, while easily damaged, are very fast and agile. Sophisticated tactics are executed to take advantage of Rebel X-wing and Y-wing weaknesses.','A Few Maneuvers','1_241'),(296,623,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','Dark Maneuvers & Tallon Roll','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/darkmaneuvers&tallonroll.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add 2 to maneuver and 1 to power of any TIE for the remainder of this turn. (Interrupt may even affect the result immediately after a destiny draw targeting the TIE\'s maneuver.) OR Target two starfighters (your TIE/ln and any Rebel starfighter) present at same system or sector. Each player draws destiny. Opponent totals destiny and starship\'s power. You total destiny, TIE\'s power, and TIE\'s maneuver. Lowest total loses starfighter (if tied, neither starfighter is lost).',NULL,NULL,'10_35'),(297,624,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Dark Rage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/darkrage.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a duel, use 3 Force to cancel it. OR Take Deep Hatred into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If Maul has no combat cards, target a Jedi to place one of their combat cards (random selection) in opponent\'s Used Pile. (Immune to Sense.)','While Qui-Gon meditated to regain strength lost during the ferocious duel, Darth Maul paced impatiently outside the energy barrier like a caged krayt dragon.',NULL,'13_64'),(298,625,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•Dark Strike','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/darkstrike.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just targeted with a lightsaber, add 3 to your weapon destiny. OR Cancel Swing-And-A-Miss. OR Lose 1 Force to cause one opponent\'s character just \'hit\' to be immediately placed in Lost Pile.','Many have experienced the awesome power of the Dark Lord in battle. Few have lived to tell about it.','Blaster Proficiency','5_135'),(299,626,'Dark','R2','A New Hope','Dark Waters','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/darkwaters.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any exterior planet site (except Hoth) or any interior vehicle site. Opponent\'s Force drains are -1 here. (Immune to Alter when a swamp creature is present.)','Swamp predators require damp and cluttered environments to enhance their camouflage and stealth. \'Something just moved past my leg.\'',NULL,'2_119'),(300,628,'Dark','R','Tatooine','•Daroe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/daroe.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. If opponent initiates a battle at same system, may reveal the top card of your Reserve Deck. If it is a Star Destroyer, may deploy it here for free. Otherwise, card is 