location, you may immediately move one vehicle or starship, if within range, to that location (as a regular move).','The Imperial Nacy boasts the best communications network in the galaxy. Sophisticated control technology allows the Empire to dispatch armed forces without delay.',NULL,'3_119'),(305,524,'Dark','U','Coruscant','Control','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/control.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel Sense or Alter. (Immune to Sense.) OR Cancel an Immediate or Mobile Effect (even if just deployed), or Force drain.','Maul channeled his rage within himself, thus drawing on the dark side of the Force in his confrontation with the Jedi.','Control (EP1)','12_146'),(306,4000,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 0','•Conquest (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/conquest.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','8','8','8','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles, and 4 TIEs. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. During battle, may lose 1 Force to cancel a non-[Immune to Sense] Interrupt.','One of the Imperial cruisers that chased the Millennium Falcon from Tatooine. It scanned the Falcon just before Han punched his starship to lightspeed.',NULL,'200_133'),(307,542,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Corporal Grenwick','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/corporalgrenwick.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','1','2','While Grenwick is on Death Star, your Death Star Sentry is not unique ( •), is doubled, deploys free, applies all three of its modifiers and is immune to Alter. Power -1 when not on Death Star.','Death Star trooper who witnessed Leia\'s interrogation. Senior tactical advisor to Sergeant Major Enfield. Coordinates security duty assignments for Detention Block AA-23.',NULL,'7_171'),(308,535,'Dark','U','Endor','•Corporal Avarik','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/corporalavarik.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots (when piloting it in battle, also adds 1 to your total battle destiny). When in a Local Trouble battle, adds one destiny to your total power.','Frequently engaged in brawls at the local enlisted clubs on homeworld of Corulag. Stormtrooper assigned to biker scout unit. Monitors Yuzzum activity.',NULL,'8_95'),(309,520,'Dark','U','Dagobah','Control','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/control.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel one Sense or Alter card. (Immune to Sense.) OR Cancel one Immediate Effect, Mobile Effect or Force drain.','Users of the Force can mysteriously manipulate their own physiology and psychology. Control allows rapid healing and provides some immunity to pain, poison and disease.','Control','4_139'),(310,540,'Dark','U','Endor','•Corporal Drazin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/corporaldrazin.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Once during each of your control phases, may take one Special Delivery into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Special Delivery is immune to Alter. When Drazin completes Special Delivery, you may take two additional cards into hand.','Stormtrooper assigned to Commander Igar\'s honor guard. Accompanied Vader on Drazin\'s homeworld of Bespin. Shot C-3PO there.',NULL,'8_96'),(311,547,'Dark','R','Endor','•Corporal Misik','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/corporalmisik.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots. When firing a Scout Blaster, adds 1 to his total weapon destiny. When with Barich in a battle and piloting or driving a vehicle, may add that vehicle\'s maneuver to your total power.','Son of a Tatooine diplomat. Stormtrooper. Biker scout. Deadly shot. Develops speeder bike tactics with Sergeant Barich. Hopes for promotion to Emperor\'s Demonstration Team.',NULL,'8_98'),(312,522,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','Control & Set For Stun','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/control&setforstun.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel one Sense or Alter card. (Immune to Sense.) OR Cancel one Immediate Effect, Mobile Effect, or Force drain. OR Use 3 Force to target one opponent\'s character. Draw destiny. If destiny > character\'s ability, character immediately returns to opponent\'s hand. (Cards deployed on character return to owners\' hands.)',NULL,NULL,'10_34'),(313,516,'Dark','C','Death Star II','Concussion Missiles','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/concussionmissiles.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your bomber, TIE Defender, freighter or transport. May target a starship for free. Draw destiny. Add 1 when targeting a starfighter or squadron. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Originally developed by smugglers and pirates as defense against starfighters. Adapted by the Empire to serve as onboard defense for slow moving bombers.','Concussion Missiles','9_177'),(314,526,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Coordinated Attack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/coordinatedattack.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: During a battle at a system or sector, instead of firing one of your starship weapons at a target, reduce that target\'s power by 4 until end of turn.  LOST: During a battle at a system or sector, use 3 Force to cancel one battle destiny just drawn.\"','\'Stay in attack formation.\'','Precise Hit','7_248'),(315,551,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Corporal Vandolay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/corporalvandolay.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','May use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one Spice Mines Of Kessel or Detention Block Corridor into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace. While at a mobile site, We Have A Prisoner is a Used Interrupt.','ISB attache to the Executor. Detention Officer. Political Liaison for COMPNOR. Responsible for all prisoner transfers. Fiercely loyal to the Emperor\'s New Order.',NULL,'4_99'),(316,538,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Corporal Derdram','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/corporalderdram.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','3','Power +1 when at any Executor site. While at Detention Block Corridor, cancels game text of Detention Block Control Room. May use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one IT-O or Hypo into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.','Member of Imperial Intelligence, Internal Security division. Assigned by IntSec to Executor. Responsible for physical safety of Imperial personnel against Rebel saboteurs.',NULL,'4_98'),(317,548,'Dark','R','Endor','•Corporal Oberk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/corporaloberk.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots. Once during each of your control phases, may target one opponent\'s missing character at same site. Draw destiny. Add 2 if Oberk is armed with a blaster. Target captured if total destiny > ability.','Originally from Ukio. Stormtrooper assigned to search for Rebel activity on Endor. Trying to impress the commander of his biker scout detachment.',NULL,'8_99'),(318,501,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Commander Nemet','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/commandernemet.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','1','2','3','Adds 1 to power and maneuver of anything he pilots. Opponent may not \'react\' to or from same location.','Logistics officer for the Avenger, member of the Line Branch of the Imperial Navy. Relays important scanner information to Captain Needa. Fiercely competitive.',NULL,'4_97'),(319,500,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Commander Merrejk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/commandermerrejk.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','3','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When he is present with a Scomp link, once during each of your deploy phases, you may deploy one battleground system from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Elite Imperial scout and spy. Often poses as a freighter captain making runs to the Outer Rim. Monitors activites of Rebels and other criminals.',NULL,'9_106'),(320,491,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Commander Brandei','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/commanderbrandei.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','1','3','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Once during each of your control phases, when aboard a Star Destroyer or at any docking bay, may use 1 Force to take one TIE into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Technical Services Officer of the Fleet Support Branch. Responsible for keeping Executor\'s 12 TIE squadrons serviced and combat ready. Just received transfer to Judicator.',NULL,'4_95'),(321,502,'Dark','U2','Premiere','•Commander Praji','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/commanderpraji.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','1','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Devastator, also adds 1 to hyperspeed. Where present, cancels game text of C-3PO or R2-D2.','Vader\'s aide on the Devastator. Personally supervised search for Death Star plans on Tatooine by Vader\'s order. Was graduated with honors from Imperial Navy Academy on Carida.',NULL,'1_167'),(322,549,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Corporal Prescott','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/corporalprescott.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','4','2','3','When at a prison, instead of Force draining there, may use X Force to retrieve X Force, where X = number of imprisoned Rebels there. Power -2 when not on Death Star.','Death Star trooper and detention block guard. Volunteered for prison detail. Takes sadistic pleasure in seeing Imperial justice enforced.',NULL,'7_172'),(323,541,'Dark','R','Endor','•Corporal Drelosyn','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/corporaldrelosyn.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','1','2','3','Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots or anything he drives. When in battle with Irol at a site, adds one battle destiny. Power +1 at any mobile, interior or spaceport site.','Stormtrooper from Coruscant. Honed piloting skills by racing swoops in underworld of Imperial capital. Still tempering his skills as a biker scout.',NULL,'8_97'),(324,233,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Bib Fortuna','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/bibfortuna.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','2','3','While with Jabba, power +3 and, during your draw phase, may use 1 Force to count the number of cards in your Force Pile, place your Force Pile in your Used Pile, and then activate Force up to the counted number.','Twi\'lek who serves as Jabba\'s major-domo. First to discover the profitability of ryll spice found on Ryloth.',NULL,'13_55'),(325,275,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Blockade Flagship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/blockadeflagship.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Trade Federation Battleship','1','6','7','7','May add 4 pilots, 4 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 droid starfighters. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. Once per game, may deploy a Neimoidian pilot aboard from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Aware that the Senate was sending a commission to Naboo, the Trade Federation evacuated many of its battleships, leaving its flagship to operate as the Droid Control Ship.',NULL,'14_114'),(326,310,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Bossk In Hound\'s Tooth','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/bosskinhoundstooth.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Modified Corellian Freitghter','1','5','8','5','May add 6 passengers and 1 vehicle. Permanent pilot is •Bossk, who provides ability of 2, adds 2 to power and adds one battle destiny. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. Has ship-docking capability.','Bossk once said of his ship, \'Greeezeg out nikek!\'',NULL,'7_301'),(327,6125,'Dark','U1','Virtual Set 10','•Black 3 (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Dark/large/black3.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','3','1','1','3','May add 1 pilot. While with a Black Squadron TIE, Force drain +1 here. While DS-61-3 piloting, immune to attrition < 4 and during battle, players draw destiny from the bottom of their Reserve Deck.','TIE/ln fighter of pilot DS-61-3. Stylized image of Corellian slice-hound painted on inner hatch.',NULL,'210_28'),(328,272,'Dark','R1','Hoth','•Blizzard Scout 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/blizzardscout1.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-ST','4','3','3','5','May add 1 pilot or passenger. May move as a \'react.\' Power +1 at any Hoth site. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1.','Enclosed All Terrain Scout Transport (AT-ST). Provides flanking support to the AT-ATs of Blizzard Force. Modified for cold weather combat.',NULL,'3_156'),(329,4055,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Boba Fett In Slave I (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/bobafettinslavei.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Firespray-Class Attack Ship','1','7','6','7','Permanent pilot is •Boba Fett, who provides ability of 3.  Draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.  Slave I\'s power may not be reduced by opponent.  Immune to Eject! Eject! and attrition < 5.','Dangerous and deadly starfighter piloted by its notorious owner. Uses combat-grade shields and sensors. Hidden weapons provide lethal surprises for Fett\'s victims.',NULL,'200_130'),(330,423,'Dark','R','Endor','•Closed Door','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/closeddoor.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Back Door. Opponent may not deploy or move to Bunker. Effect canceled if opponent controls Back Door or Landing Platform or if you initiate at Force drain at Bunker. (Immune to Alter.)','Double durasteel doors are often enough to protect important Imperial installations.',NULL,'8_120'),(331,287,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Boba Fett','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/bobafett.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','4','5','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Slave I, also adds 2 to maneuver and may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. When escorting a captive, captive is forfeit +5. May \'fly\' (landspeed = 3). Immune to attrition < 3.','Feared bounty hunter. Collected bounties on Solo from both the Empire and Jabba the Hutt. Took exquisite pleasure in using Solo\'s friend to capture him.',NULL,'5_91'),(332,242,'Dark','C','Endor','Biker Scout Trooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/bikerscouttrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','1','1','2','Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots. Power -1 while not at a forest, jungle or Endor site. Forfeit +2 aboard a speeder bike. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy a speeder bike to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Scout troopers, or \'biker scouts\' as they are commonly called, are stormtrooper specialists. Given wide latitude to operate independently of Imperial control.',NULL,'8_92'),(333,243,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Binders','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/binders.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one of your warriors or bounty hunters. May now escort any number of captives. If device removed from your character, select one captive escorted by that character to remain and release all others.','Because standard binders are durable but not easily adaptable, bounty hunters often carry special binders which automatically tighten around a captive\'s appendages.',NULL,'5_106'),(334,246,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Black 11','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/black11.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','2','1','2','3','Deploy -1 to any mobile system. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. When with Vader in battle, may draw destiny and subtract that amount from opponent\'s total power.','Stationed aboard command ship Executor. Pilot known as \'Wampa\' for icy precision in battle. Often serves as escort to Lord Vader\'s shuttle.',NULL,'9_153'),(335,330,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Brief Loss Of Control','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/brieflossofcontrol.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Just after the weapons phase of a battle, use 2 Force to cause each player to target one of that player\'s characters involved in the battle. Target characters cannot apply their ability toward drawing battle destiny this turn.','Eliciting fear from the opponent gives the dark side a powerful advantage.',NULL,'5_133'),(336,5101,'Dark','R2','Virtual Set 4','•Bow To The First Order','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/bowtothefirstorder.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per game, may take Finalizer into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per character, when you deploy Hux, Kylo, Phasma, or Snoke to a battleground, may take any one card from Used Pile into hand; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Blank.',NULL,'204_47'),(337,374,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Captain Yorr','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/captainyorr.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if a starfighter). When piloting a TIE Defender and with Jendon, adds one battle destiny.','Former member of Imperial Demonstration Team. Flew test flights during development of various TIE prototypes. Jendon\'s wingman. Has scored 24 combat victories.',NULL,'9_103'),(338,5124,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 5','•Captain Jonus in Scimitar 2','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Dark/large/captainjonusinscimitar2.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SA','2','4','2','4','Permanent pilot is *Jonus, who provides ability of 2. This starship\'s missile weapon destiny draws are +1. If at a system you control, your total power at related sistes is +1.','TIE bomber repaired after being struck by an asteroid in the Anoat system. Stationed aboard second Death Star battle station.',NULL,'205_21'),(339,379,'Dark','U','Cloud City','Carbon-Freezing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/carbonfreezing.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Carbonite Chamber. During your control phase, may target one captive present. Draw destiny. If destiny < 5, captive lost. If destiny > 10, place on captive. Captive is \'frozen\' and opponent loses 8 Force. If captive released, lose Effect. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Oh, they\'ve encased him in carbonite. He should be quite well protected. If he survived the freezing process, that is.\'',NULL,'5_114'),(340,358,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Captain Gilad Pellaeon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/captaingileadpellaeon.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','5','Deploys for free to Thrawn\'s location. Each other Imperial aboard same capital starship is forfeit +2. Adds 2 to power of any capital starship he pilots (3 if Chimaera). While aboard Chimaera with Thrawn, also adds 2 to that starship\'s armor and hyperspeed.','Corellian leader. Lied about his age to enter the Academy. Took command of Chimaera when its captain was killed at the Battle of Endor. Admires Grand Admiral Thrawn.',NULL,'10_33'),(341,264,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/blasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.','Stormtrooper BlasTech E-11 blaster rifle. Can convert from a pistol to a rifle configuration by using extendable stock. Carries 100 shots. Military issue only.','Blaster Rifle','1_312'),(342,5123,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 5','•Boba Fett\'s Blaster Rifle (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Dark/large/bobafettsblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your non-[maintenance] bounty hunter. If on Boba Fett, once per game, during your move phase, may use 2 Force to relocate him (with any captive he is escorting) to a [Jabba\'s Palace] site. May target a character or vehicle for free. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +2 > defense value.','Sawed off BlasTech EE-3 blaster rifle. Although its barrel is a few centimeters under the legal limit, no one has lived to file an official complaint.',NULL,'205_22'),(343,210,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Battle Order & •First Strike','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/battleorder&firststrike.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. You may initiate battles for free. During a battle you initiate, each time opponent plays an interrupt, opponent must first use 1 Force. For either player to initiate a Force drain, that player must first use 3 Force unless Battle Plan on table, or that player occupies a battleground system and a battleground site. (Immune to Alter.)',NULL,'Battle Plan & Draw Their Fire','12_129'),(344,299,'Dark','R','Dagobah','<>Bombing Run','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/bombingrun.gif?raw=true','Effect','Mobile','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a non-interior planet site (except Dagobah). May move to an adjacent non-interior site at start of your move phase. Your bombers at a related system you control may move to this site. Bombers must return to system at end of your battle phase (if possible).','Bombers can sometimes slip past orbital defenses. Making a lowaltitude bombing run allows \'surgical strikes,\' even in cramped situations such as canyons and city streets.',NULL,'4_117'),(345,4054,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•Blockade Support Ship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/blockadesupportship.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Trade Federation Battleship','2','5','5','7','Unless Fondor on table, may deploy -3 as a \'react.\' May add 3 pilots and 4 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2.','These heavily modifed battleships are used to control and direct the Trade Federation\'s automated army. Easily identified by its array of sensors and antennae.','Spiral','200_129'),(346,383,'Dark','U','Endor','•Carida','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/carida.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain -1 here. If you do not occupy, all your troopers are forfeit -1.',NULL,NULL,'8_156'),(347,5009,'Dark','C2','Virtual Set 2','•Black 6','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Dark/large/black6.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','6','1','1','3','May add 1 pilot. While Tanbris piloting, power +1. Once per game, may retrieve bottom card of Lost Pile. Your total battle destiny here is +X, where X = this TIE\'s power - 5.','Blank.',NULL,'202_14'),(348,266,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Blaster Scope','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/blasterscope.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your non-[Permanent Weapon] blaster. Scope allows that weapon to target at an adjacent site.','The effectiveness of a blaster can sometimes be enhanced through an electronic targeting scope mounted on top, especially for long range targets.',NULL,'1_199'),(349,421,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•Close Call','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/closecall.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel one asteroid destiny and cause it to be drawn again.  LOST: Lose 1 Force. Opponent must reveal the top card of Reserve Deck, Force Pile and Used Pile. Card(s) with lowest destiny number greater than zero are lost.\"','If this little one doesn\'t pulverize you, the next one just might.',NULL,'4_138'),(350,316,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Bounty','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/bounty.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an opponent\'s non-droid character. If subsequently captured, seized by a bounty hunter and then transferred to a prison, retrieve Force equal to character\'s forfeit -2 and place Effect in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','One of the most profitable occupations in the galaxy is hunting down and capturing wanted beings. The more notable the quarry, the more profitable the venture.',NULL,'5_113'),(351,445,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Cloud City: Downtown Plaza','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/cloudcitydowntownplaza.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, opponent\'s Downtown Plaza game text is canceled.',NULL,'Cloud City: Downtown Plaza','7_270'),(352,5023,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 3','•Darth Maul, Lone Hunter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Dark/large/darthmaullonehunter.gif?raw=true','Character','Sith','1','7','7','8','If drawn for destiny, may take into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny. Cancels Blaster Deflection (and Amidala\'s game text) here. Maul\'s weapon destiny draws may not be modified or canceled by opponent. Immune to attrition < 5.','Trade Federation.',NULL,'203_26'),(353,631,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Darth Maul, Young Apprentice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/darthmaulyoungapprentice.gif?raw=true','Character','Sith','1','7','7','8','Deploys -2 to Coruscant. When Maul swings a lightsaber at a Jedi, each weapon destiny draw is +1. If Maul hits a Jedi Master during battle, that Jedi Master is power -3 for remainder of battle. Immune to Clash Of Sabers and attrition < 5.','Fueled by a hatred of the Jedi and an arsenal of dark abilities, this Sith warrior is a powerful weapon for his dark mentor, Darth Sidious.',NULL,'12_101'),(354,6221,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Darth Maul, Young Apprentice (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/darthmaulyoungapprenticeai.gif?raw=true','Character','Sith','1','7','7','8','Deploys -2 to Coruscant. When Maul swings a lightsaber at a Jedi, each weapon destiny draw is +1. If Maul hits a Jedi Master during battle, that Jedi Master is power -3 for remainder of battle. Immune to Clash Of Sabers and attrition < 5.','Fueled by a hatred of the Jedi and an arsenal of dark abilities, this Sith warrior is a powerful weapon for his dark mentor, Darth Sidious.',NULL,'12_102'),(355,633,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Darth Sidious','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/darthsidious.gif?raw=true','Character','Dark Jedi Master','1','5','6','8','While no other characters present, if opponent just lost a Jedi from table, may lose 1 Force to place that Jedi out of play. While on Coruscant, may use 1 Force to add one battle destiny in a battle your Neimoidian is in. Immune to attrition.','Mysterious Sith Master who is manipulating the Trade Federation for his own nefarious ends. Shrouded in mystery, his identity and aganda remain unclear.',NULL,'14_78'),(356,6222,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Darth Sidious (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/darthsidiousai.gif?raw=true','Character','Dark Jedi Master','1','5','6','8','While no other characters present, if opponent just lost a Jedi from table, may lose 1 Force to place that Jedi out of play. While on Coruscant, may use 1 Force to add one battle destiny in a battle your Neimoidian is in. Immune to attrition.','Mysterious Sith Master who is manipulating the Trade Federation for his own nefarious ends. Shrouded in mystery, his identity and aganda remain unclear.',NULL,'14_79'),(357,634,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Darth Vader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/darthvader.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','6','6','8','When in battle, adds 1 to each of your battle destiny draws. Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots (or 4 to power and 3 to maneuver if Vader\'s Custom TIE). Immune to attrition < 5.','Dark Lord of the Sith. Servant of Emperor\'s. Encased in armor with cybernetic life support. Student of Obi-Wan Kenobi. Was the best starpilot in the galaxy. 