modifiedriotgun.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on Dengar, or 5 on your other bounty hunter. May target a non-droid character using 3 Force. Draw destiny. Character immediately captured if destiny +3 > defense value.','Originally at area-effect weapon. Modified by Dengar to concentrate on one target. Induces an extended period of unconsciousness.',NULL,'6_175'),(413,710,'Dark','F','Special Edition','<>Desert','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/desert.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : May not deploy to Bespin, Coruscant, Dagobah, Hoth, Kessel or Naboo. Each of your battle destiny draws is -1 here. Sandwhirl here moves only if on Tatooine.',NULL,'Desert','7_281'),(414,712,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Desilijic Tattoo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/desilijictattoo.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Hutt. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one Jabba\'s Influence or Death Mark from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While at Audience Chamber, no battles or Force drains may take place here unless a Rebel present. (Immune to Alter.)','Jabba the Hutt\'s clan requires all members to carry ritual scarring identifying them forever as heirs to the Nal Hutta legacy. These tattoos are considered marks of power.',NULL,'7_225'),(415,714,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Despair','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/despair.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a Rebel was just captured or \'frozen,\' deploy on another Rebel. That Rebel may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny (if Leia, she is also excluded from being the \'highest ability character\'). If captive released, lose Immediate Effect.','The carbonite froze more than just Han\'s body.',NULL,'5_116'),(416,715,'Dark','R'