e). While with another destroyer droid, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','These Trade Federation droids are basically a mobile weapons platform. They were commissioned by the Trade Federation from the Colicoids of Colla IV.',NULL,'12_104'),(420,723,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Devastator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/devastator.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','9','8','9','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 2.','Supported the devastating subjugation of Ralltiir. While under the command of Darth Vader, chased and captured the traitor Princess Leia Organa aboard the consular ship Tantive IV.',NULL,'1_301'),(421,724,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Dewback','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/dewback.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Creature','5','2','2','4','Deploy only to a desert or Tatooine site. Ability = 1/4. May add 1 \'rider\' (passenger). When \'ridden\' by a Sandtrooper, may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Protected by hard skin composed of tough armored scales. Frequently ridden by sandtroopers stationed in desert environments.',NULL,'7_312'),(422,725,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•••DFS Squadron Starfighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/dfssquadronstarfighter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Droid Starfighter','2','2','1','3','Deploys -1 to Naboo or same system as your battleship. While at same system as your battleship, may deploy Droid Starfighter Laser Cannons aboard from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Starfighters assigned to DFS Squadron are provided with advanced targeting routines to assist them in protecting Trade Federation command ships.',NULL,'14_115'),(423,726,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•DFS-1015','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/dfs1015.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Droid Starfighter','2','2','1','3','Deploys -1 to same location as your battleship. While with another droid starfighter at a system, once per battle if about to draw a battle destiny here, may instead draw two and choose one.','Tactical support starfighter that utilizes learning subroutines to maximize the effectiveness of droid starfighter offensive strategies.',NULL,'14_116'),(424,727,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•DFS-1308','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/dfs1308.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Droid Starfighter','2','2','3','3','Deploys -1 to same location as your battleship. While with another droid starfighter at a system, opponent may not draw more than one battle destiny here.','1308 was one of several droids who aralyzed the N-1 starfighter during the Trade Federation\'s occupation of Naboo. Was unable to calculate the \'human factor\' inside the N-1.',NULL,'14_117'),(425,728,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•DFS-327','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/dfs327.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Droid Starfighter','2','2','2','3','While at same system as your battleship, DFS-327 is power +3, and opponent\'s pilots deploy +2 to starfighters at this system.','Droid starfighter programmed for battleship defense. Will not pursue enemy starfighters once repelled, but can disable vital systems on attacking capital starships.',NULL,'14_118'),(426,729,'Dark','R2','A New Hope','•Dianoga','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/dianoga.gif?raw=true','Creature','Swamp','3','*','4','0','* Ferocity = (power/ferocity of last character or creature eaten) + destiny. Habitat: exterior Dagobah sites, Trash Compactor and Dark Waters.','\'Garbage squid\' from Vodran\'s jungles. Changes color to match last meal. When unfed, turns transparent. Eats almost anything. Flexible eyestalk. 7 tentacles. Up to 6 meters long.',NULL,'2_110'),(427,731,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Dioxis','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/dioxis.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to target two opponent\'s Jedi at same interior battleground. Targets may not participate in battle for remainder of turn. OR Target opponent\'s Jedi. Draw destiny. If destiny > 2, target\'s game text is canceled for remainder of turn.','Green gas that is lethal to most carbon-based life forms.',NULL,'12_147'),(428,733,'Dark','U1','Hoth','Direct Hit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/directhit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add X to one weapon destiny (before weapon destiny is drawn) when targeting a combat vehicle.USED: X = 1.  LOST: X = 3.\"','Snowspeeders move much faster than AT-AT cannons can track, but if approaching on a poor attack vector, the snowspeeder is at the mercy of the well-trained AT-AT gunner.','Lucky Shot','3_122'),(429,5154,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 7','•Director Orson Krennic','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Dark/large/directororsonkrennic.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. During your control phase, if with opponent\'s Undercover spy, opponent loses 2 Force (may not be reduced). While at a site, opponent may not cancel or modify your battle destiny draws here.','Commander. Leader.',NULL,'207_20'),(430,734,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Disarmed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/disarmed.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If both players have a character with a weapon present at same site, deploy on that opponent\'s character during any control phase. Character loses all weapons, is power -1 and may no longer carry weapons. (Immune to Alter.)','C-3PO\'s arm was pulled off by attacking Tusken Raiders. \'I don\'t think I can make it. You go on, Master Luke...I\'m done for.\'','Disarmed','1_214'),(431,738,'Dark','F','Special Edition','Disruptor Pistol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/disruptorpistol.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior (1 on your non-unique warrior). May target a character or creature using 2 Force (for free if on your non-unique warrior). Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny > defense value.','Highly specialized weapon used for disintegration. Commonly found on the black market and in criminal arsenals. One of the favored weapons of the Black Sun.','Disruptor Pistol','7_319'),(432,741,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Djas Puhr','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/djaspuhr.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','1','4','4','Power +1 for each [Dark Side Force] present, +2 under \'nighttime conditions.\' Immune to attrition < 3.','Male Sakiyan, a race often employed as assassins. Bounty hunter. Incredible infrared peripheral vision. Has excellent aural and olfactory senses. Often tracks by scent.',NULL,'1_171'),(433,742,'Dark','R2','Virtual Set 1','•Djas Puhr (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/djaspuhr.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','2','4','4','Power, defense value, and forfeit +1 for each [Dark Side Force] icon here. Your total ability may not be reduced at same site. Your Force drains here may not be canceled by [Reflections III] Leia.','Male Sakiyan, a race often employed as assassins. Bounty hunter. Incredible infrared peripheral vision. Has excellent aural and olfactory senses. Often tracks by scent.',NULL,'201_24'),(434,744,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Do They Have A Code Clearance?','https: