 Mos Eisley Cantina.',NULL,'1_202'),(452,779,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Droid Racks','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/droidracks.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on table. If your battle droid was just lost, may place it here. During your control phase, may use 2 Force (1 Force if your piloted MTT on table) to take any battle droid from here into hand. (Immune to Alter.)','The Trade Federation utilizes such efficient methods of droid deployment that it is rumored even they do not know exactly how many battle droids are in circulation',NULL,'14_96'),(453,5192,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 8','•Droid Racks (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/droidracks.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on table. While present with a Jedi, destroyer droids are defense value +2. If your destroyer droid was just lost, may stack it here. During your control phase, may use 2 Force to play any destroyer droid here in Used Pile.(Immune to Alter.)','The Trade Federation utilizes such efficient methods of droid deployment that it is rumored even they do not know exactly how many battle droids are in circulation',NULL,'208_39'),(454,782,'Dark','C','Coruscant','Droid Starfighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/droidstarfighter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Droid Starfighter','2','3','2','2','Deploys -1 to same location as your battleship. Power -1 unless your droid control ship present. While another droid starfighter here, opponent\'s starfighters present are each power -1.','These automated starfighters are managed by the Droid Control Ship and are used en masse by the Trade Federation to overwhelm an opponent with sheer numbers.',NULL,'12_181'),(455,783,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','Droid Starfighter Laser Cannons','https://github.com/swccgpc/holo