ooine-Dark/large/dudboltspodracer.gif?raw=true','Podracer',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Adds 1 to each of your race destinies here. If Sebulba\'s Podracer on table, may lose this Podracer to cancel Losing Track or Neck And Neck; place all race destinies here in owner\'s Used Pile.','RS 557 Podracer. Secretly hired by Sebulba to protect him during Podraces.',NULL,'11_96'),(467,796,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Dune Sea Sabacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/duneseasabacc.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Requirements: A Jawa at a Tatooine site. Wild cards (0-7): sandcrawler sites, Magnetic Suction Tube, Jawa Siesta and Jawa Pack. Clone cards: Tatooine locations, sandcrawlers, Jawa weapons, and Utinni! Stakes: One device or droid with out armor.\"','Popular among Tatooine\'s native population. Apart from the Jawas, no one else seems to understand the rules.','Dune Sea Sabacc','6_153'),(468,798,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•••Dune Walker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/dunewalker.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-AT','1','5','7','6','Deploy -1 to a desert or Tatooine site. May add 1 pilot and 6 passengers. Immune to attrition < 4. Landspeed may not be increased. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1.','Enclosed armored transport adapted for hot climates by replacing tertiary weapons systems with additional Sienar t23 heat dissipation units.',NULL,'7_313'),(469,800,'Dark','C','Cloud City','E Chu Ta','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/echuta.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'One of your protocol droids \'insults\' one character present, canceling that character\'s game text for remainder of turn. OR During your battle phase, initiate a battle where both players have droids (but no presence or spies). Both sides add one battle destiny.','\'How rude!\'',NULL,'5_138'),(470,801,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•E-3PO','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/e3po.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','2','3','Total power at same site is +1 for each of your alien/Imperial pairs present. Once during every turn, may use 1 Force to \'insult\' one opponent\'s droid present (except R2-D2), canceling that droid\'s game text for remainder of turn.','Brought to Cloud City by the Empire. Facilitates Imperial-to-alien cummunication. Relayed carbonite chamber modifiation instructions to Ugloste. Arrogant. Rude. Vulgar.',NULL,'5_97'),(471,894,'Dark','C1','Hoth','E-web Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/ewebblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Artillery','5',NULL,'3','1','Deploy on any site. May be moved with two warriors for 1 additional Force. Your warrior present may target a starfighter (use 5 as defense value), character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.','Massive infantry weapon powerful enough to damage even starfighters.',NULL,'3_159'),(472,803,'Dark','R','Endor','<>Early Warning Network','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/earlywarningnetwork.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an interior site that has a Scomp link. While you occupy this site, once per battle you may deploy a non-unique Imperial starship as a \'react\' (for free if starfighter) to the related system from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to alter.)','Listening posts are often constructed as part of a standard Imperial installation. On Endor, such a post was incorporated into the control bunker.',NULL,'8_122'),(473,812,'Dark','C','Coruscant','•Edcel Bar Gane','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/edcelbargane.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','1','3','5