ssing character under \'nighttime conditions\' to be lost.','\'Sir, the temperature\'s dropping too rapidly.\' \'That\'s right, and my friend\'s out in it.\'',NULL,'3_123'),(525,914,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Expand The Empire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/expandtheempire.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any site. \'Expands\' your \'game text\' for that site to add to your \'game text\' at the adjacent sites.','The Emperor disbanded the Imperial Senate \'for the duration of the emergency,\' seizing absolute power. He planned to extend rule by terrorizing planets into submission.',NULL,'1_215'),(526,916,'Dark','U1','Hoth','Exposure','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/exposure.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use X Force during your control phase, where X = the total number of characters present or missing at exterior marker sites under \'nighttime conditions.\' Those characters are lost.','\'Artoo says the chances of survival are 125 to 1.\'',NULL,'3_124'),(527,5108,'Dark','C2','Virtual Set 4','F-11D Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/f11dblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your First Order warrior. May target a character or vehicle for free. Draw destiny. Add 1 if fired by a stormtrooper. Target hit, and may not be used to satisfy attrition, if destiny > defense value.','Blank.',NULL,'204_57'),(528,918,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Failure At The Cave','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/failureatthecave.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Dagobah: Cave. Target an apprentice on Dagobah. All Jedi Test game text is suspended. If target present during any battle phase, opponent draws destiny. If destiny < 4, you retrieve 2 Force (also, if destiny = 0, target is lost). Otherwise, Utinni Effect canceled.','\'That place is strong with the dark side of the Force. A domain of evil it is. In you must go.\'',NULL,'4_120'),(529,5032,'Dark','F','Virtual Set 3','•Falleen\'s Fist','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Dark/large/falleensfist.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Skyhook Platform','2','6','9','8','Deploys -3 if your Black Sun agent is at a related site. May add 3 pilots and 6 passengers. Permanent pilots provide total ability of 4. Immune to attrition < 8.','Blank.',NULL,'203_35'),(530,927,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Fanfare','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/fanfare.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Cancels Order To Engage and Scramble. Once per game you may take any Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While opponent occupies no battleground systems, Staging Areas is suspended.','The Boonta Eve crowds are always looking for new and exciting developments at every Podrace.','Don\'t Do That Again - Defensive Shield','13_68'),(531,926,'Dark','C','Tatooine','•Fanfare','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/fanfare.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Cancels Order To Engage and Scramble. Once per game you may take any Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While opponent occupies no battleground systems, Staging Areas is suspended. (Immune to Alter.)','The Boonta Eve crowds are always looking for new and exciting developments at every Podrace.',NULL,'11_69'),(532,6293,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Fanfare (Tatooine) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Dark/large/fanfaretatooine.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Ice Storm, Lost In The Wilderness, Order To Engage, Sandwhirl, and Scramble are canceled. Once per game, may /\\ an Immediate Effect. Unless opponent occupies a battleground system, Staging Areas is suspended.','The Boonta Eve crowds are always looking for new and exciting developments at every Podrace.',NULL,'11_69'),(533,4402,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Fanfare (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Dark/large/fanfare.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Cancels Order To Engage and Scramble. Once per game, may take an Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While opponent occupies no battleground systems, Staging Areas is suspended. \'Missing\' on Lost In The Wilderness is treated as \'landspeed = 0 for remainder of turn.\'','The Boonta Eve crowds are always looking for new and exciting developments at every Podrace.','Don\'t Do That Again (V) - Defensive Shield','200_95'),(534,929,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•Fear','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/fear.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Opponent must choose to lose either 2 Force from hand or 1 Force from top of Reserve Deck.','\'I\'m not afraid.\' \'Oh. You will be.\' One of the lessons Luke learned was that fear of the unknown can be stronger than fear of the known.',NULL,'4_141'),(535,931,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Fear Is My Ally','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/fearismyally.gif?raw=true','Effect','Starting','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Before any starting cards are revealed, deploy on table with up to 10 cards from outside your deck face-down under here. Cards under here do not count toward your deck limit. Three times per game, may play a Defensive Shield from here, as if from hand.','Maul\'s arsenal includes much more than simple combat training.','An Unusual Amount Of Fear','13_69'),(536,932,'Dark','R2','Premiere','Fear Will Keep Them In Line','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/fearwillkeeptheminline.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any capital starship. When that starship is at a system or sector you control, your total power is +1 in battles at related sites.','\'The regional governors now have direct control over their territories. Fear will keep the local systems in line. Fear of this battle station.\'',NULL,'1_216'),(537,934,'Dark','U1','Premiere','•Feltipern Trevagg','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/feltiperntrevagg.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','4','2','2','3','While no droid present with Trevagg, to initiate battles at same location as Trevagg, player must use X Force, where X = total number of [Dark Side Force] and [Light Side Force] present with him.','Corrupt tax collector. A male Gotal. Bounty hunter. Once sought a bounty on Obi-Wan. Has limited sensing ability to droid emanations. Romanced M\'iiyoom Onith.',NULL,'1_176'),(538,935,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Feltipern Trevagg\'s Stun Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/feltiperntrevaggsstunrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Feltipern Trevagg or use 2 Force to deploy on your other bounty hunter. May target a character using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Add 2 if target is the target of any bounty. Target may be captured if total destiny > defense value.','Assault rifle modified by Feltipern. Used by the Gotal bounty hunter before he became a tax collector. Occasionally brought along to \'ease\' Feltipern\'s collection duties.',NULL,'7_321'),(539,937,'Dark','R','Dagobah','Field Promotion','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/fieldpromotion.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an Imperial of ability < 5 present with Vader, Emperor or one of your admirals, generals, or moffs. Imperial gains {leader} skill, is power +1, and is immune to Demotion, Report to Lord Vader, and What is Thy Bidding, My Master? (Immune to Alter.)','Imperial officers are fiercely competitive, especially on the Executor. Lord Vader\'s flagship is a place where devious political calculation prospers. The naive are doomed to failure.',NULL,'4_121'),(540,939,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Fighter Cover','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/fightercover.gif?raw=true','Admiral\'s Order',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Each starfighter that fires a weapon in battle is power +3 for the remainder of battle. Once per turn you may cancel and redraw your starship weapon destiny just drawn. At sites related to systems you occupy, your characters who have immunity to attrition each add 2 to immunity and 1 to each of that character\'s weapon destiny draws.',NULL,'Concentrate All Fire','9_93'),(541,941,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•Fighters Straight Ahead','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/fightersstraightahead.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your Force generation is +1 at systems you control. Opponent\'s non-unique starfighters are deploy +1 (or +2 to a system you occupy). (Immune to Alter.)','Sometimes a swarm of starfighters can look more imposing than it really is. Mostly though, it\'s just best to avoid them altogether.',NULL,'14_97'),(542,940,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Fighters Coming In','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/fighterscomingin.gif?raw=true','Admiral\'s Order',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Unique (•) starfighters without permanent pilots are immune to attrition < 4 (or add 2 to immunity if starfighter already has immunity). Starships without pilot characters aboard are power -2. At docking bays related to systems you occupy, your Force drains are +1. Once per turn, your starfighter just lost from a system may be relocated to a related docking bay.',NULL,'I\'ll Take The Leader','9_94'),(543,6263,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 9','•Dr. Chelli Lona Aphra','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/drchellilonaaphra.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','3','3','3','Adds 1 to power of anything she pilots. Deploys free to an unoccupied site. Your droids are deploy -1 here. When deployed, may search your Lost Pile and move one card there ot the top of that pile (if that card is a droid, may retrieve it into hand).','Female information broker, spy, and thief. Trade Federation.',NULL,'209_35'),(544,768,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Dr. Evazan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/drevazan.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. The not-so-good doctor may \'operate\' on any other character present that was just \'hit\' or just Disarmed; \'patient\' is lost.','Thug. Smuggler. Twisted \'doctor\'. Disfigured by blaster. Has death sentence in over 12 systems. Notorious partner of Ponda Baba. Aliases: Dr. Cornelius and Rooboo.',NULL,'1_172'),(545,769,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Dr. Evazan & •Ponda Baba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/drevazan&pondababa.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','6','4','6','Adds 3 to power of anything they pilot. Power -3 if opponent has a lightsaber present. Draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. May target any other character present that was just \'hit.\' Target character is lost.','Smugglers who met each other in the Corellian system. Gained the rights to Han Solo\'s old smuggling routes from Jabba the Hutt. They don\'t like you either.',NULL,'10_37'),(546,770,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Dr. Evazan\'s Sawed-off Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/drevazanssawedoffblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Dr. Evazan (may deploy on him as a \'react\') or use 3 Force to deploy on your warrior. May target a character or creature at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value. May fire repeatedly.','Equipped with powerful infrared scope. Extremely sensitive trigger mechanism. Used to earn Evazan the death sentence on several systems.',NULL,'7_320'),(547,945,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Firepower','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/firepower.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Each of your starships with two or more starship weapons aboard is power +2. Once during each of your deploy phases, you may use 2 Force to deploy from Lost Pile one starship weapon, vehicle weapon or artillery weapon (for free).','\'About twenty guns. Some on the surface, some on the towers.\'',NULL,'7_228'),(548,946,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Firepower (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Dark/large/firepower.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. If opponent moves from a location you occupy during your turn (unless \'moving through\' the location), they lose 2 Force. At end of opponent\'s turn, if you control two battlegrounds (a site and system) and opponent deployed a card with ability and did not initiate a battle, you may retrieve 1 Force.','\'About twenty guns. Some on the surface, some on the towers.\'','Weapons Display (V)','200_96'),(549,6300,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 9','•••First Order Special Forces TIE','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/firstorderspecialforcestie.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SF','2','3','2','4','May add 1 pilot and 1 passenger. Matching starfighter for any First Order pilot of ability < 3. Power +1 at opponent\'s system. While matching pilot aboard, immune to attrition < 3.','Blank.',NULL,'209_52'),(550,5093,'Dark','C3','Virtual Set 4','First Order Stormtrooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/firstorderstormtrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','First Order','3','2','2','3','Deploys -1 to same site as a First Order leader. Opponent\'s characters here are cumulatively defense value -1 (limit -3).','Blank.',NULL,'204_40'),(551,950,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•First Strike','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/firststrike.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Whenever a battle is initiated, player initiating battle retrieves 1 Force and defender loses 1 Force. Also, during a battle you initiate, each time opponent plays an interrupt, opponent must first use 1 Force. (Immune to Alter.)','\'There\'ll be no escape for the princess this time.\'','Draw Their Fire','7_229'),(552,951,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Flagship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/flagship.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your Star Destroyer. Your other starships may move as a \'react\' to same system or sector (for free). If starship lost, you lose X Force, where X = starship\'s armor. (Immune to your Alter.)','After the Battle of Yavin, it was politically necessary to demonstrate the unstoppable might of the Empire. The Executor and Death Squadron ensured this objective.',NULL,'4_122'),(553,953,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Flagship Executor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/flagshipexecutor.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Super-Class Star Destroyer','4','12','12','15','May add unlimited pilots, passengers and starfighters. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 3. Immune to attrition if target of Flagship Operations.','Command ship of the Imperial Fleet at the Battle of Endor. Originally constructed at the Fondor shipyards. Admiral Piett stationed aboard.',NULL,'9_157'),(554,954,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Flagship Operations','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/flagshipoperations.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any Star Destroyer if at least 5 Executor sites on table. Your TIEs are deploy -1, forfeit +2 and destiny +2. At systems where you have a TIE, your Imperial capital starships are deploy -3 and your battle destiny draws are +1 each. (If on Executor, immune to Alter.)','\'There\'s too many of them!\'',NULL,'9_125'),(555,956,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Flare-S Racing Swoop','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/flaresracingswoop.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','5','0','2','2','May add 1 driver and 1 passenger. Landspeed = driver\'s ability, and may be used at any time to follow an opponent\'s vehicle or character that just moved from same site (if within range).','Attain speeds of up to 600 kph. 3 meters long. Extremely difficult to control at high speeds. Dengar rode a similar swoop when injured in a race with Han at Agrilat.',NULL,'7_314'),(556,959,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Flawless Marksmanship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/flawlessmarksmanship.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add X to one starship weapon or tractor beam destiny (before destiny is drawn) when targeting opponent\'s starship.USED: X = 2.  LOST: X = 4.\"','Heavy-weapons gunners assigned to Imperial facilities undergo intense training. The Imperial Navy boasts a higher weapons accuracy rate than that of the Imperial Army.',NULL,'7_250'),(557,960,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Flight Escort','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/flightescort.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, if you have at least two combat vehicles at same cloud sector, relocate one starfighter present to a related docking bay or system. OR If one of your combat vehicles is defending a battle at a cloud sector, add one battle destiny.','\'Rather touchy, aren\'t they?\'',NULL,'5_140'),(558,961,'Dark','C','Special Edition','••Floating Refinery','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/floatingrefinery.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a cloud sector (limit one per sector). Force you activate may be drawn into hand (one per turn for each of your Floating Refineries on table). Each cloud sector or gas miner drawn in this way by this device may be revealed to retrieve 1 Force.','Refines Tibanna gas at mines like those at Cloud City. Also used for moisture collection on dry planets.',NULL,'7_216'),(559,5094,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 4','•FN-2003','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/fn2003.gif?raw=true','Character','First Order','2','2','1','3','Once per turn, if with your First Order trooper, may use 1 Force to target opponent\'s character present (free if Finn) and make FN-2003 \'hit;\' for remainder of turn, target\'s game text is canceled and target may not fire weapons.','Stormtrooper.',NULL,'204_39'),(560,5185,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 8','•FN-2199 (Nines)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/fn2199nines.gif?raw=true','Character','First Order','2','3','2','3','During battle with a stormtrooper, may cancel one opponent\'s just drawn automated or lightsaber weapon destiny. Permanent weapon is Z6 Riot Control Baton (may target a character for free; draw destiny; target hit if destiny > defense value).','Stormtrooper.',NULL,'208_31'),(561,964,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Focused Attack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/focusedattack.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Vader is present during a battle at a site, for remainder of turn, he loses his immunity to attrition, but adds ability to power (he may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny). OR During a duel, add one destiny to your total.','Not since his duel with Obi-Wan had Vader unleashed the raw power of the dark side.',NULL,'5_141'),(562,965,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Fondor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/fondor.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain -1 here. If you control, opponent may not deploy Executor.',NULL,NULL,'7_283'),(563,968,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Force Field','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/forcefield.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel an attempt to target a Dark Jedi with a character weapon.  LOST: If one of your characters was just targeted by a weapon during a battle, use 3 Force to cancel the targeting.\"','Han was fast. Vader was faster.','Blaster Deflection','5_142'),(564,5103,'Dark','C2','Virtual Set 4','•Force Freeze','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/forcefreeze.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel the game text of a character of ability < 5 present with Kylo for remainder of turn.LOST: If a battle was just initiated where there are no smugglers, take the first weapons segment action (or first two if you initiated).\"','Blank.',NULL,'204_49'),(565,4049,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•Force Field (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/forcefield.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel an attempt to use a character weapon to target your character of ability > 4.  LOST: Use 2 Force to cancel an attempt to use a [Permanent Weapon] weapon to target your character.\"','Han was fast. Vader was faster.','Blaster Deflection','200_119'),(566,969,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Force Lightning','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/forcelightning.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Target any character (even a captive) present with Emperor. Target is defense value -4 for remainder of turn.  LOST: Emperor loses immunity to attrition and is defense value -2 for remainder of turn. Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny +1 > defense value.\"','The Emperor is strong in the dark arts of the Force. He can direct pure energy to shoot forth from his outstretched fingers.',NULL,'9_136'),(567,970,'Dark','C','Death Star II','Force Pike','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/forcepike.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Royal Guard (or use 3 Force to deploy on your other warrior). Adds 1 to defense value. May target a character or creature using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value. If hit by a Royal Guard, target\'s power = 0.','Uses microscopic vibrations emitted from its tip. Cuts through stone, metal, and bone. Ceremonial weapon for most; deadly implement in the hands of an Emperor\'s Royal Guard.',NULL,'9_179'),(568,971,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Force Push','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/forcepush.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target opponent\'s Jedi with at least one combat card present with your Dark Jedi. Reveal one of target\'s combat cards (random selection). If revealed card\'s destiny > 4, place it on top of opponent\'s Reserve Deck. Otherwise, lose 1 Force. (Immune to Sense.)','A fully-trained Sith warrior has more weapons at his disposal than just a lightsaber.',NULL,'13_70'),(569,4050,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Force Push (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/forcepush.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Once per game, choose: during battle, use 2 Force to target your Dark Jedi and opponent\'s character of equal or lesser ability present. Both targets are excluded from battle. OR Exchange two cards from hand with any one card from Force Pile; reshuffle.','A fully-trained Sith warrior has more weapons at his disposal than just a lightsaber.',NULL,'200_120'),(570,972,'Dark','R','Cloud City','Forced Landing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/forcedlanding.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a docking bay. Target an opponent\'s starfighter at the related system or a related cloud sector. Target may not move away from Utinni Effect. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.','\'You will not deviate from your present course. . . Permission granted to land on platform three-two-seven.\'',NULL,'5_117'),(571,974,'Dark','F','Special Edition','<>Forest','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/forest.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : May not deploy to Bespin, Coruscant, Hoth, Kessel or Tatooine.',NULL,'Forest','7_284'),(572,973,'Dark','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','•Forced Servitude','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Dark/large/forcedservitude.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an opponent\'s location. Whenever you lose a droid from hand or Life Force, it satisfies Force loss up to its forfeit value. Once per turn, you may play Imperial Code Cylinder to cancel a Force drain where you have a droid. Effect canceled if opponent controls this location.','The Empire often uses droids for nefarious purposes. Imperials compel droids to do jobs that are repugnant to humans. An automaton has no ethical conscience.','Faithful Service','106_14'),(573,982,'Dark','U','Endor','•Freeze!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/freeze.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a Rebel just deployed or moved to a site where you have a trooper present armed with a weapon, use 1 Force. For remainder of turn, that Rebel may not battle or move and battle damage against you is limited to 4 at that location.','Despite Wicket\'s warnings, an Imperial scout got the drop on Leia.',NULL,'8_143'),(574,978,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Fozec','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/fozec.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','2','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While at a site you control, Imperials are immune to Ke Chu Ke Kukuta? at that site.','Spy for the Empire. Keeping tabs on Jabba\'s activities for the ISB. Secretly hoping to leave the Empire and pursue lucrative opportunities in the underworld.',NULL,'6_103'),(575,986,'Dark','C2','Hoth','Frostbite','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/frostbite.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Hoth system. At the end of each player\'s turn, for every character that player has present at a marker site under \'nighttime conditions,\' that player must lose 1 Force (2 if character is missing).','\'Luke! Luke! Don\'t do this. C\'mon, gimme a sign here.\'','Frostbite','3_101'),(576,990,'Dark','R1','Hoth','Frozen Dinner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/frozendinner.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s character alone at Wampa Cave. Character is power = 0 and may not move. May be canceled if opponent has a lightsaber or total ability > 4 present. If character eaten by a creature, cumulatively adds 2 to ferocity.','Freeze dried and ready to serve, a tasty, wholesome Rebel makes a nutritious meal for the whole wampa clan. They\'re Gr-r-reat!',NULL,'3_102'),(577,991,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Frustration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/frustration.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, peek at opponent\'s hand and target one non-Interrupt card you find there that has a deploy cost < total number of [Light Side] icons on table. Opponent must deploy a card of that title by the end of your next turn, or lose a card of that title from hand (if possible).','\'Rrraaaarrr!\'',NULL,'4_142'),(578,993,'Dark','U2','Premiere','Full Scale Alert','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/fullscalealert.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force. Draw Destiny. If destiny < number of Stormtroopers on the table, all opponent\'s movement is blocked for the remainder of this turn (except for smugglers and the starships they are aboard).','Imperial stormtroopers adopt strict security measures. Excellent communications and sheer numbers can hinder Rebel movement across entire territories.',NULL,'1_246'),(579,995,'Dark','R2','Hoth','Furry Fury','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/furryfury.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Wookiee Roar or Han\'s Back or Life Debt.  LOST: If Han and Chewie are in a battle together, draw two destiny. Subtract total from opponent\'s attrition and total power (cannot fall below zero).\"','\'All right, don\'t lose your temper.\' Hoth hath no fury like a Wookiee scorned.',NULL,'3_125'),(580,1000,'Dark','C2','Hoth','FX-10 (Effex-ten)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/fx10effexten.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','1','2','3','Once per turn, one of your \'hit\' non-droid characters at same or adjacent site may go to your Used Pile rather than your Lost Pile.','Standard medical droid used by Imperial field units. Enhanced programming allows FX-10 to treat a wide variety of battle wounds.','FX-7 (Effex-Seven)','3_86'),(581,996,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Fusion Generator Supply Tanks','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/fusiongeneratorsupplytanks.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your starship at a system or sector where a related docking bay is on table. Adds 1 to hyperspeed, power and maneuver.','Installed at many facilities throughout the Empire to provide power to the Imperial spacefleet. Supplies starships with energy necessary for sublight and hyperspace travel.','Fusion Generator Supply Tanks','1_203'),(582,1002,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Gaderffii Stick','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/gaderffiistick.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on any Tusken Raider. If a battle has just been initiated where present, target a character for free; draw two destiny. If total destiny > 5, target\'s weapons are \'knocked away\' (may not be used this battle).','Notorious \'gaffi\' weapon favored by Tusken Raiders. Built from scavenged metal. Intimidates and evokes fear.',NULL,'1_315'),(583,1003,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Gailid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/gailid.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','3','2','Deploys free to same site as Mosep. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While at Audience Chamber, adds 1 to your Force drains at Jabba\'s Palace sites.','Mosep\'s assistant. Accountant. Tax collector. Enjoys tending to Jabba\'s skiffs with Barada.',NULL,'6_104'),(584,1004,'Dark','C','Death Star II','•Gall','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/gall.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Immune to Revolution.',NULL,NULL,'9_148'),(585,1005,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Gamall Wironicc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/gamallwironicc.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','2','3','Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots. While Gamall is in battle, your other characters present with him may not be targeted by opponent\'s weapons. Place Gamall in Used Pile if he was just \'hit\'. Power -2 while on Tatooine.','Strange wanderer. Rumored to have sacrificed himself in battle so that his comrades could live on. Survived and now stranded on Tatooine. He misses everything he\'ll never be.',NULL,'11_56'),(586,1008,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Gamorrean Ax','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/gamorreanax.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your Gamorrean. Adds 1 to power. When present at a site, Gamorrean draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. May target a character or creature for free. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value.','Built by Snogrutt, a Gamorrean engineer. Ax head contains an ultrasonic generator. Jabba\'s Gamorrean guards sometimes switch the power off to prove their might.',NULL,'6_177'),(587,1009,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Gamorrean Guard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/gamorreanguard.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','4','1','Deploys only to Tatooine. Power -1 when not at a Tatooine site. May be sacrificed (lost) to cancel an attack just initiated by a creature present.','Big. Strong. Dumb.',NULL,'6_105'),(588,1010,'Dark','U',