er may deploy on Grievous. Once per game, Grievous may steal a lightsaber from opponent\'s Lost Pile. Unless alone, may lose 1 Force to return Grievous (and your cards on him) to hand from a site you control. Immune to attrition < 4.','Trade Federation.',NULL,'203_27'),(592,6321,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 3','•General Grievous (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Dark/large/generalgrievoush.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','6','5','7','Any stolen lightsaber may deploy on Grievous. Once per game, Grievous may steal a lightsaber from opponent\'s Lost Pile. Unless alone, may lose 1 Force to return Grievous (and your cards on him) to hand from a site you control. Immune to attrition < 4.','Trade Federation.',NULL,'203_27'),(593,5095,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 4','•General Hux','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/generalhux.gif?raw=true','Character','First Order','2','3','3','5','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys -2 aboard Finalizer. Your First Order characters and [First Order] starships are destiny +1. Once per game, may take a First Order stormtrooper into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Leader.',NULL,'204_41'),(594,6322,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 3','•General Grievous (OAI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialAI-Dark/large/generalgrievous.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','6','5','7','Any stolen lightsaber may deploy on Grievous. Once per game, Grievous may steal a lightsaber from opponent\'s Lost Pile. Unless alone, may lose 1 Force to return Grievous (and your cards on him) to hand from a site you control. Immune to attrition < 4.','Trade Federation.',NULL,'203_27'),(595,1027,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•General Tagge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/generaltagge.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','3','4','Tagge\'s forfeit +1 for each Imperial trooper, of any kind, present with him at a site.','Oversees defense operations of Death Star. Outstanding tactician. No-nonsense leader. Member of the House of Tagge, a powerful noble family and corporate conglomerate.',NULL,'1_178'),(596,5005,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 2','•General Nevar','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Dark/large/generalnevar.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','4','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots (3 if Blizzard 2). Deploys -1 to Hoth. When deployed, may peek at top card of any Reserve Deck. When a spy here is targeted by Trample, adds 1 to your destiny draw.','ISB leader.',NULL,'202_10'),(597,1029,'Dark','R1','Hoth','•General Veers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/generalveers.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','3','5','Power +1 when at same site as Admiral Ozzel. Adds 1 to power of each Imperial at same Hoth site. Adds 3 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots. On Blizzard 1, also adds 1 to armor and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','General Maximillian Veers is the model of Imperial Army officer. Cunning, loyal and ruthlessly efficient leader. In charge of the ground assault troops in Vader\'s forces.',NULL,'3_87'),(598,1030,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 0','•General Veers (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/generalveers.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','3','3','5','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots.  While piloting an AT-AT, draws two battle destiny if unable to otherwise.  While piloting a combat vehicle, its immunity to attrition is +2.','General Maximillian Veers is the model of Imperial Army officer. Cunning, loyal and ruthlessly efficient leader. In charge of the ground assault troops in Vader\'s forces.',NULL,'200_81'),(599,1034,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Ghana Gleemort','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/ghanagleemort.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','5','4','3','Your Force generation at same site is +X, where X equals the number of opponent\'s aliens at same and adjacent sites. May lose 1 Force to cancel a Force drain at an adjacent site.','Part of Jabba\'s Gamorrean security force. Negotiating with the B\'omarr monks regarding his possible defection.',NULL,'11_57'),(600,1035,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','Ghhhk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/ghhhk.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During the damage segment of a battle you lost, if you have no cards left that can be forfeited, cancel all remaining battle damage. (Immune to Sense.) OR Cancel Nightfall.','Dejarik of creature from Clak\'dor VII. Ghhhk rise with the dawn, screeching their mating calls across the jungle. Locals use their skin oils as a healing salve.','Houjix','2_132'),(601,1036,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','Ghhhk & Those Rebels Won\'t Escape Us','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/ghhhk&thoserebelswontescapeus.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Nabrun Leids  LOST: If you just forfeited all your cards that participated in a battle you lost, cancel all remaining battle damage (immune to Sense). OR Cancel Hyper Escape, Closer!?, or one \'react.\' OR During your move phase, cancel Landing Claw.\"',NULL,'Houjix & Out Of Nowhere','10_39'),(602,1041,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Giran','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/giran.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','2','Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +3 when defending a battle at a Jabba\'s Palace site. May forfeit in place of one of your alien leaders present who was \'hit\' by a weapon, restoring that leader to normal.','Kajain\'sa\'Nikto. Loyal to Jabba. Helps tend the rancor with Malakili. Hopes to snare a krayt dragon someday and pit it against the rancor.',NULL,'6_106'),(603,1043,'Dark','C','Endor','•Go For Help!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/goforhelp.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle at an exterior site with double your total power, reveal top 3 cards of your Reserve Deck. If any of those cards are scouts or speeder bikes, deploy them for free to that battle (replace others on top of Reserve Deck in same order).','When confronted with enemy troops, biker scouts are instructed to immediately call for reinforcements.',NULL,'8_144'),(604,1058,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Gragra','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/gragra.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','1','2','Once per turn, may use 1 Force to target opponent\'s card with ability just deployed to same site. Opponent must use 2 Force or return target to hand. Power +2 at Mos Espa.','Female Swokes Swokes. Lives in the city of Mos Espa and runs a street-corner market there. Seller of chuba.',NULL,'11_58'),(605,1060,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Grand Admiral Thrawn','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/grandadmiralthrawn.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','2','4','7','Adds 3 to power of any starship he pilots. When piloting a star destroyer in battle, adds one battle destiny. While no other admiral and no star cruiser on table, your Admiral\'s Order just placed in Used Pile from table, may be taken into hand instead.','The last remaining Grand Admiral. Found legendary Katana fleet of missing dreadnaughts. Military genius. Master of unorthodox tactics. Passionate collector of art. Leader.',NULL,'10_40'),(606,5155,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 7','•Grand Admiral Thrawn (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Dark/large/grandadmiralthrawn.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','4','4','7','Adds 3 to power of any starship he pilots. if a Rebel just moved from here, your Imperials present may follow that character (using landspeed). While at a battleground site, functions as a general and game text of Admiral\'s Orders is suspended.','The last remaining Grand Admiral. Found legendary Katana fleet of missing dreadnaughts. Military genius. Master of unorthodox tactics. Passionate collector of art. Leader.',NULL,'207_21'),(607,1061,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Grand Moff Tarkin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/grandmofftarkin.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','4','4','6','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When with Vader in a battle, once per battle may cancel one opponent\'s destiny just drawn.','Leader. Governor of Outer Rim Territories. Commanded Death Star. Helped disband Imperial Senate. Defined doctrine of rule by fear. Plotted to use Death Star against Emperor.',NULL,'1_179'),(608,4026,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 0','•Grand Moff Tarkin (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/grandmofftarkin.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','4','4','6','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Destiny +2 when drawn for destiny. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise (if with Vader or an Imperial leader, may add one instead). During battle, if you just drew a destiny < number of Imperials here, may cancel and redraw that destiny.','Leader. Governor of Outer Rim Territories. Commanded Death Star. Helped disband Imperial Senate. Defined doctrine of rule by fear. Plotted to use Death Star against Emperor.',NULL,'200_82'),(609,1064,'Dark','U2','Premiere','Gravel Storm','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/gravelstorm.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Strikes at Dune Sea, Jundland Wastes, Beggar\'s Canyon, Lars\' Moisture Farm, Jawa Camp, or Mos Eisley. Target opponent\'s character present at that site. Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny > ability.','Tatooine\'s twin suns cause turbulent storms that strike with little or no warning. Strong winds whip rocks through the air with enormous force.',NULL,'1_247'),(610,1065,'Dark','PM','Jedi Pack','•Gravity Shadow','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JediPack-Dark/large/gravityshadow.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent\'s starship has just begun to move through hyperspace, draw destiny. If destiny > pilot\'s ability, starship must return to original location and may not move this turn. If destiny = pilot\'s ability, starship is lost.','\'Traveling through hyperspace ain\'t like dustin\' crops, boy!\' Gravitational phenomena cast shadows in hyperspace, posing a serious threat to lightspeed navigation.',NULL,'102_8'),(611,1072,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Greeata','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/greeata.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','1','2','Other Rodians deploy -1 to same site. Once during each of your control phases, may use 1 Force to take any Rodian into hand from Reserve Deck- reshuffle. While at Audience Chamber, all your other musicians are deploy -1 and forfeit +3.','Rodian musician. In addition to her singing talents, she plays kloo horn. Befriended Sy Snootles on the luxury liner Kuari Princess.',NULL,'7_179'),(612,1073,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•Greedo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/greedo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','1',NULL,'During opponent\'s control phase, may \'threaten\' one smuggler at same site. Opponent may use all Force Pile cards to cancel threat, allowing you to activate same amount. Otherwise, draw destiny. If destiny + Greedo\'s ability > 6, smuggler lost.','Male Rodian bounty hunter. Sent by Jabba to capture Han. Arrogant, overconfident and not too bright. Trained by bounty hunters Nataz and Goa, who betrayed him to Thuku.',NULL,'2_89'),(613,5096,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 4','•Greedo (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/greedo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','3','2','4','May deploy as a \'react.\' Opponent must first use 1 Force to fire a weapon at same site. Weapons fired using Sorry About The Mess must target Greedo (if possible). Nabrun Leids may not transport characters to or from here.','Male Rodian bounty hunter. Sent by Jabba to capture Han. Arrogant, overconfident and not too bright. Trained by bounty hunters Nataz and Goa, who betrayed him to Thuku.','Cal Alder (V)','204_42'),(614,1083,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Grotto Werribee','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/grottowerribee.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','2','4','3','Deploys -1 to a docking bay. Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. While at opponent\'s docking bay, adds 2 to your Force drains there, and your vehicles and other characters there are immune to attrition < 4.','Once a junior traffic controller for an interstellar shipping corporation, Grotto brags that there is nothing about docking bay procedure that he doesn\'t know. Information broker.',NULL,'12_107'),(615,1090,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Guri','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/guri.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','6','6','7','Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. When present with Xizor, he may not be targeted by weapons. While Vader not here, opponent may draw no more than one battle destiny here. Immune to purchase, Restraining Bolt, and attrition < 5.','Human-replica droid. Programmed to function as Xizor\'s personal bodyguard and assassin. Black Sun agent. Cost 9 million credits. Worth every decicred.',NULL,'10_41'),(616,1093,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•Halt!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/halt.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During any deploy phase, target a character at same site as your battle droid. Target is landspeed = 0 for remainder of turn. OR If opponent just deployed a character to same site as your battle droid, opponent must use 1 Force or place that character in hand.','\'Coruscant?\'',NULL,'14_103'),(617,1096,'Dark','R2','Premiere','Han Seeker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/hanseeker.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploys for 1 Force to an unoccupied site. Deploys and moves like an undercover spy. When present with Han (or alien) of ability < 3, choose one to be immediately lost (treat as an \'all cards\' situation). Seeker is also lost.','Military version of a \'remote.\' Programmed to stalk specific targets or secondary targets. Heat and light sensors track with fatal accuracy. Can stow away on starships.',NULL,'1_316'),(618,1114,'Dark','C2','Hoth','He Hasn\'t Come Back Yet','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/hehasntcomebackyet.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, target any character alone at one of your exterior planet sites (except a docking bay). Draw destiny. Target is missing if destiny + 3 > ability.','\'Princess Leia is wondering about Master Luke...She doesn\'t know where he is.\' \'I don\'t know where he is.\' \'Nobody knows where he is.\'',NULL,'3_126'),(619,1115,'Dark','C','Dagobah','He Is Not Ready','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/heisnotready.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any character. Subtracts 2 from that character\'s training destiny draws. OR Deploy on an opponent\'s pilot at a site. During each of opponent\'s move phases, opponent must choose to move that character, lose that character or lose 1 Force.','\'All his live has he looked away. To the future, to the horizon. Never his mind on where he was! Hmm? What he was doing! Hm.\'',NULL,'4_123'),(620,1121,'Dark','U','Cloud City','Heart Of The Chasm','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/heartofthechasm.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your deploy phase, use X Force to rearrange all Cloud City sites, where X = total number of those sites. All cards at a given site move along with that site. OR Cancel Off The Edge. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take one Weather Vane into hand and reshuffle.','The Cloud City chasm\'s central fin was engineered with a tensile strength unsurpassed by anything in the region, save the silk of the Kashyyyk treeworm.',NULL,'5_143'),(621,1122,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Heavy Fire Zone','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/heavyfirezone.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated, deploy (for free) a vehicle weapon or starship weapon from hand (or Reserve Deck; reshuffle) on your participating vehicle or starship.','\'Heavy fire boss! Twenty-three degrees.\'','Rapid Fire','7_251'),(622,1123,'Dark','C','Death Star II','Heavy Turbolaser Battery','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/heavyturbolaserbattery.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy in your Star Destroyer (adds 2 to power) or any mobile system. May target a starship using 2 Force. Draw two destiny. Subtract 1 when targeting a capital starship. Otherwise, subtract 6. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','The ultimate in armor penetration. Relies in dense capacitor banks for massive firing charge. Capacitors regularly malfunction. Hitting maneuverable targets nearly impossible.','Heavy Turbolaser Battery','9_180'),(623,1126,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•Hem Dazon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/hemdazon.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','4','*','2','3','Once during each of your deploy phases, may place, face down, one card from hand or Force Pile under Hem, as \'salt consumption.\' If Hem lost, cards underneath also lost. *Power = 1 + number of cards underneath.','Male scout from Cona. As with many Arconas, Hem has succumbed to the power of salt, and addiction indicated by his gold eye color.',NULL,'2_90'),(624,1128,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Herat','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/herat.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','2','Deploys only on Tatooine. During your control phase may search Reserve Deck, take 1 Utinni! or Jawa into hand and reshuffle. If you have 3 or more Jawas on table, may play Utinni! to cancel a Force drain at a related site or to cancel Control.','Female Jawa shaman. Advised Wittin during his plotting with Jabba. Agreed to fan the Hutt in return for his cooperation to help usurp Kalit.',NULL,'6_107'),(625,1130,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Hermi Odle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/hermiodle.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','2','When in a battle, you may \'react\' by deploying any one non-unique blaster (for free) on Hermi from Reserve Deck. reshuffle. When present with your Advosze at a site, allows your character weapons to transfer for free there.','Baragwin assigned by Jabba to be the palace\'s master weaponsmith. Enemy of Pote Snitkin.',NULL,'6_108'),(626,1116,'Dark','R','Cloud City','He\'s All Yours, Bounty Hunter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/hesallyoursbountyhunter.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Captive Pursuit.  LOST: During your move phase, transfer an escorted captive to another bounty hunter or warrior present.\"','Once Skywalker had taken the bait, Han was of no use to the Empire.',NULL,'5_144'),(627,6349,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 11','He\'s All Yours, Bounty Hunter (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/hesallyoursbountyhunter.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: For remainder of turn, your bounty hunter draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and moves for free during your move phase. LOST: Cancel an attempt to use a weapon to target your bounty hunter escorting a captive.\"','Once Skywalker had taken the bait, Han was of no use to the Empire.',NULL,'211_13'),(628,1139,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Hidden Weapons','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/hiddenweapons.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Boba Fett, or your character with Mandalorian Armor is present during the weapons phase of a battle, target one opponent\'s character present. Draw Destiny: (0-1) no effect (2-3) character immediately captured (4-5) character is hit (6+) character immediately lost.','Boba Fett\'s Mandalorian armor was so versatile that his opponents never knew what to expect.',NULL,'6_154'),(629,1142,'Dark','R1','Hoth','•High Anxiety','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/highanxiety.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If an opponent\'s character with ability > 2 has just become missing, deploy on a Rebel with ability > 2 on same planet. Rebel may not participate in battle. Immediate Effect canceled if missing character is found or lost.','When a Rebel is missing, ranking members of the Alliance express a professional yet dispassionate concern. Some are not so dispassionate.',NULL,'3_103'),(630,1144,'Dark','U','Endor','•High-speed Tactics','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/highspeedtactics.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target two non-creature vehicles with maneuver (one yours, one opponent\'s) present at same site. Both players draw destiny, add your vehicle\'s maneuver to your total. Lowest total loses vehicle. OR You speeder bike piloted by a biker scout adds one battle destiny.','Biker scouts train relentlessly on their speeder bikes to ensure that their speed advantage is a potent weapon. This training includes highvelocity brawling.','Get Alongside That One','8_145'),(631,1146,'Dark','C','Tatooine','•His Name Is Anakin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/hisnameisanakin.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Each non-battleground docking bay generates no more than one Force for either player. Opponent\'s aliens deploy +1 on Tatooine (or +2 if non-unique or to same Tatooine site as your Dark Jedi, or +4 if both). (Immune to Alter.)','Anakin dreamt that one day he would return to Tatooine to free the slaves. His aggression will one day be felt by the entire Republic.',NULL,'11_70'),(632,1148,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Hit Racer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/hitracer.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, use 2 Force to target opponent\'s Podracer with a race total within 4 of one of your race totals. Draw destiny. If destiny > target Podracer\'s destiny number, opponent may not draw race destiny this turn and target Podracer is \'damaged.\'','Sebulba is willing to utilize a variety of \'tactics\' to maintain his lead position. Mars Guo learned this lesson the hard way.',NULL,'11_81'),(633,1150,'Dark','U','Dagobah','••HoloNet Transmission','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/holonettransmission.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Transmission Terminated.  LOST: Take one Imperial or Visage Of The Emperor into hand from Used Pile; reshuffle.\"','The Empire uses a real-time hologram communication network. Provides extensive coordination in battles, blockades and searches. Allows rapid deployment and reinforcement.',NULL,'4_143'),(634,1155,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Homing Beacon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/homingbeacon.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s starship (even if \'concealed\') if your bounty hunter or Imperial leader is on table. Your starships may move for free (and may move as a \'react\') to this location. During your move phase, may cancel Landing Claw on this starship.','\'You\'re sure the homing beacon is secure aboard their ship? I\'m taking an awful risk, Vader. This had better work.\'',NULL,'7_217'),(635,6351,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 5','•Hondo Ohnaka (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Dark/large/hondoohnaka.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','5','Draws one battle destiny in not able to otherwise. While at Audience Chamber (or stacked on your Objective), your other Weequays are deploy -1, power +1, and forfeit +2. Once per game, may deploy Aurra Sing, Slave 1, or a Kowakian from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Weequay gangster, leader, and pirate.',NULL,'205_13'),(636,1161,'Dark','C','Endor','•Hot Pursuit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/hotpursuit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If opponent\'s card present with your vehicle of landspeed > 2 has just begun to move as a \'react\', cancel that \'react\'.  LOST: Select one opponent\'s vehicle present with your vehicle of landspeed > 2 to be power = 0 for remainder of turn.\"','The mobility of speeder bikes is greatly valued by the Empire\'s advanced scout detachments.',NULL,'8_146'),(637,1162,'Dark','U2','Hoth','•Hoth','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/hoth.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, for each of your starships here, your total power is +1 in battles at Hoth sites.',NULL,'Hoth','3_143'),(638,6353,'Dark','C2','Hoth','•Hoth: Defensive Perimeter (3rd Marker)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/hothdefensiveperimeter.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your troopers are forfeit -1 here.',NULL,NULL,'3_144'),(639,1168,'Dark','U2','Hoth','•Hoth: Echo Command Center (War Room)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/hothechocommandcenterwarroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, your starship movement from Hoth sites to the Hoth system is free.',NULL,'Hoth: Echo Command Center (War Room)','3_145'),(640,1170,'Dark','U2','Hoth','•Hoth: Echo Corridor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/hothechocorridor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: :',NULL,'Hoth: Echo Corridor','3_146'),(641,1172,'Dark','C2','Hoth','•Hoth: Echo Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/hothechodockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.',NULL,'Hoth: Echo Docking Bay','3_147'),(642,5106,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 4','•Finalizer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/finalizer.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Resurgent-Class Star Destroyer','1','10','13','13','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, and 4 [First Order] starfighters. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. Deploys -4 to [Episode VII] systems and adds 1 to your Force drains there. Immune to attrition < 5.','Blank.',NULL,'204_54'),(643,6359,'Dark','R2','Hoth','•Hoth: Wampa Cave (7th Marker)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/hothwampacave.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, and Main Power Generators on table, Force drain -1 here.',NULL,NULL,'3_150'),(644,1185,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Hound\'s Tooth','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/houndstooth.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Modified Corellian Freighter','2','5','6','4','May add 1 pilot (must be smuggler or bounty hunter), 6 passengers and 1 vehicle. Immune to attrition < 4 if Bossk piloting. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. Has ship-docking capability.','Controlled by state-of-the-art-voice-activated X10-D computers. Internal sensors and security systems monitor prisoner activity. Modified for Bossk\'s Trandoshan physiology.',NULL,'4_168'),(645,1186,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•Hound\'s Tooth (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/houndstooth.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Modified Corellian Freighter','2','5','3','6','May add 1 alien pilot, 6 passengers, and 1 vehicle. Deploys (even using Combat Response) and moves like a starfighter. While Bossk piloting, adds one battle destiny and immune to attrition < 4.','Controlled by state-of-the-art-voice-activated X10-D computers. Internal sensors and security systems monitor prisoner activity. Modified for Bossk\'s Trandoshan physiology.',NULL,'200_135'),(646,1188,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Human Shield','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/humanshield.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If an opponent\'s weapon is about to \'hit\' an Imperial present with a captive being escorted, the captive is \'hit\' instead.  LOST: During the damage segment of a battle at a site, you may forfeit any captives present (once per battle per captive).\"','A shining example of Imperial honor and bravery.',NULL,'5_145'),(647,1191,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Hunting Party','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/huntingparty.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, form a search party for an opponent\'s missing character at same site. Add 1 to search party destiny draw for each bounty hunter in search party. If successful, capture the character found.','Sometimes a missing person is found by the wrong search party.',NULL,'7_252'),(648,6361,'Dark','R','Special Edition','Hunt Down And Destroy The Jedi / Their Fire Has Gone Out Of The Universe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/huntdownanddestroythejedi.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Hunt Down And Destroy The Jedi:Deploy Holotheatre and Visage Of The Emperor. May deploy Meditation Chamber and/or Epic Duel.{While} this side up, during your move phase, may use 4 Force to take Vader into hand from a location you control (cards on him go to owner\'s Used Pile). Add 4 to each player\'s destiny draw for Sense and Alter.{Flip} this card if Vader is at a battleground site and no Light Jedi or Luke is at a battleground site.{Place} out of play if you play Scanning Crew, initiate a non-Epic duel or Force drain at an Executor site.Their Fire Has Gone Out Of The Universe:{While} this side up, opponent cannot initiate battles or Force drains where opponent has a Jedi or Skywalker. You lose no Force from Visage Of The Emperor. While Vader at Meditation Chamber, subtract 2 from each of opponent\'s battle destiny draws. Opponent may not play Sense or Alter.{Flip} this card if opponent has Luke or a Jedi at a battleground site or if Vader is not on table.{Place} out of play if you play Scanning Crew, initiate a non-Epic duel or Force drain at an Executor site.',NULL,NULL,'7_297'),(649,5110,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 4','•Hunting Party (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/huntingparty.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, if your bounty hunter or Trandoshan is escorting a non-frozen captive at a battleground site you control, opponent loses 1 Force. OR If your bounty hunter or Trandoshan just captured a character, opponent loses 1 Force. (Immune to Sense.)','Sometimes a missing person is found by the wrong search party.',NULL,'204_50'),(650,1192,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Hutt Bounty','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/huttbounty.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an opponent\'s smuggler, gambler, or thief. If subsequently captured, seized by a bounty hunter and then transfered to Jabba\'s Palace Dungeon, retrieve Force equal to character\'s forfeit (+6 if Han) and lose effect. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Chissaa, picha gawanki Chewbacca. Yupon cogorato kama walpa kyess kashung kawa Wookiee.\'',NULL,'6_144'),(651,1194,'Dark','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','•Hutt Influence','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Dark/large/huttinfluence.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Opponent may not cancel or modify Force drains at each Tatooine battleground site where you have two aliens with different card titles. Also, attrition against you is reduced by 2 when two of your non-unique aliens with different card titles are in battle.','Jabba\'s criminal empire extends to all reaches of the Outer Rim.',NULL,'112_11'),(652,1195,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Hutt Smooch','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/huttsmooch.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Capture