,'If Vader just won a battle or duel against a Luke of ability < 6, deploy on Luke. During each of your move phases, opponent loses 2 Force. Also, when at same location as Vader, Luke is power and forfeit = 0 and does not add power to any starships he pilots.','\'Search your feelings, you know it to be true.\'',NULL,'5_118'),(657,5119,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 5','•I Am Your Father (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Dark/large/iamyourfather.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. [Death Star 2] Vader is deploy = 6. Once per turn, may deploy Vader\'s Lightsaber from Reserve Deck; reshuffle (or lose 1 Force to deploy from Lost Pile). Whenever a lightsaber swung by Vader \'hits\' a character, opponent loses 1 Force. Immune to NOOOOOOOOOOOO!. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Search your feelings, you know it to be true.\'','Like My Father Before Me','205_17'),(658,1204,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•I Can\'t Shake Him!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/icantshakehim.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your starship weapon aboard your starfighter was just fired during a battle, add one battle destiny. OR During your deploy phase, deploy one starship weapon or tractor beam from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','\'You\'ve picked one up... watch it!\'',NULL,'7_253'),(659,1208,'Dark','R1','Premiere','I Find Your Lack Of Faith Disturbing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/ifindyourlackoffaithdisturbing.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on one of your Dark Jedi. Opponent\'s total ability at same location is reduced by 2, unless an opponent\'s Jedi is also present.','Darth Vader ruthlessly used the Force to strike down enemies and soldiers who displeased him. He could choke victims from afar without touching them.','Affect Mind','1_217'),(660,4002,'Dark',