ah','•I Want That Ship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/iwantthatship.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one opponent\'s unique (•) starship at a location you do not occupy. When starship is targeted by any tractor beam or ion cannon, subtract 2 from maneuver. If starship is captured or lost, lose Effect and opponent must lose 3 Force (5 if Falcon).','Like nerf herders herding nerfs, Imperial commanders often use TIE fighters to drive fleeing Rebel ships into tractor beam range.',NULL,'4_124'),(667,1222,'Dark','R','Tatooine','•I Will Find Them Quickly, Master','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/iwillfindthemquicklymaster.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Opponent may deploy Amidala from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If Maul present with Amidala and opponent has no Jedi there, she is captured. Once per game may take If The Trace Was Correct into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Utilizing his \'dark eye\' probe droids and sensory equipment, Maul knew he would eventually find his target.',NULL,'11_71'),(668,5195,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 8','•I Will Finish What You Started','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/iwillfinishwhatyoustarted.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Vader is lost. Once per turn, may stack an Interrupt from hand face up here to cancel a just drawn weapon destiny at Kylo\'s site. Kylo is power +1 for each card here. Once per game, may deploy a lightsaber from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Blank.',NULL,'208_40'),(669,1239,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Iasa, The Traitor Of Jawa Canyon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/iasathetraitorofjawacanyon.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','3','2','Deploys only on Tatooin