corting Amidala at a non-Tatooine battleground site, opponent\'s Force drains at Tatooine sites are -1 and at the end of every turn, may reshuffle opponent\'s Reserve Deck.',NULL,NULL,'11_80'),(673,6376,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 11','•••IG MagnaGuard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/igmagnaguard.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','3','3','4','Grievous is defense value +2 here. While aboard Invisible Hand, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and characters here are immune to Clash Of Sabers.','Assassin. Trade Federation.',NULL,'211_60'),(674,1245,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•IG-88','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/ig88.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','1','4','5','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. May \'assassinate\' any character at same site hit by IG-88 (victim is immediately lost). May use two different weapons. May initiate battle and be battled. Immune to Restraining Bolt and purchase.','Bounty hunter. Went berserk upon activation. Murdered all designers at Holowan Mechanicals. IG-88\'s outstanding \'dismantle on sight\' warrant ignored by Darth Vader.',NULL,'4_101'),(675,1244,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•IG-2000','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/ig2000.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Trilon Aggressor','4','3','4','3','May add 1 pilot (must be a smuggler or bounty hunter) and 2 passengers. Maneuver +3 and immune to attrition < 3 if IG-88 piloting. Ion Cannon may deploy aboard.','IG-88\'s assault starfighter. Custom designed. Boasts a Kuat Galaxy-15 engine from a Nebulon-B frigate. Heavy ion cannon often used to disable starships before boarding.',NULL,'4_169'),(676,1246,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•IG-88 (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/ig88.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','1','4','4','5','Adds 2 to power of anything