nd outspoken.',NULL,'2_91'),(697,1268,'Dark','U','Cloud City','Imperial Decree','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/imperialdecree.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Whenever you control any two Rebel Base locations, or any one planet site and two systems, the effects of Revolution and all opponent\'s Force drain bonuses are canceled. (Immune to Alter.)','To Imperial command personnel: The Rebellion must be crushed! Minor acts of sedition are to be ignored. The destruction of the Alliance is your primary goal.','Menace Fades','5_120'),(698,1269,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 0','Imperial Decree (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/imperialdecree.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Whenever you lose Force (except from Force drains, battle damage, or your card), may reduce loss (to a minimum of 1) by the number of battlegrounds you occupy. During battle, may place this Effect out of play to draw one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. (Immune to Alter.)','To Imperial command personnel: The Rebellion must be crushed! Minor acts of sedition are to be ignored. The destruction of the Alliance is your primary goal.',NULL,'200_108'),(699,6394,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Imperial Detention (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Dark/large/imperialdetention.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. For opponent to deploy a character, starship, or vehicle for free (except by that card\'s own game text), opponent must first use 2 Force.',NULL,NULL,'200_98'),(700,1270,'Dark','U1','Hoth','••Imperial Domination','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/imperialdomination.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any location. Whenever you control this location during your