nd site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Opponent\'s characters require +1 Force to move from Tatooine sites using their landspeed. During your draw phase, you may retrieve one trooper.{Flip} this card if opponent controls more Tatooine sites than you.',NULL,NULL,'201_39'),(703,1272,'Dark','C2','Hoth','Imperial Gunner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/imperialgunner.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','1','1','1','Adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of anything he is aboard as a passenger.','Walker operators work in pairs, one trained to pilot the AT-AT, the other serving as gunner. Imperial gunners consider themselves the best marksmen in the Empire.',NULL,'3_88'),(704,1273,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•••Imperial Helmsman','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/imperialhelmsman.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','3','2','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting a Star Destroyer, also draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Warrant Officer Bachenkall is typical of the many graduates of the Imperial Training academy on Raithal. The sector naval school trains pilots in capital starship help tactics.',NULL,'4_102'),(705,1274,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•Imperial Holotable','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/imperialholotable.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Dejarik Rules\' in effect here. Site converted by Dejarik Hologameboard.',NULL,'Dejarik Hologameboard','2_145'),(706,1275,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','Imperial Justice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/imperialjustice.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent is generating at least 4 more Force than you, deploy on a location to cancel all Force generation at that location. OR Deploy on a location. It is now immune to Revolution.','\'There\'s