/Endor-Dark/large/itsanoldercode.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If opponent just landed a starship at an exterior site, you may deploy up to three related sites from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: Use 2 Force to \'scan\' (reveal) opponent\'s hand. You may place one starship you find there in opponent\'s Used Pile.\"','Even though Vader allowed the stolen shuttle Tydirium to land on Endor, he had a plan to deal with the Rebels.',NULL,'8_148'),(739,1345,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Jabba Desilijic Tiure','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/jabbadesilijictiure.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','5','While at Podrace Arena, once during your control phase may \'wager\'. Both players draw destiny and add 2 if they have won a Podrace. Loser (lowest total) loses 1 Force. If you just won the wager and Bib Fortuna is present, you may retrieve 1 Force.','Gangster and leader in control of Tatooine. The amount of credits Jabba earns from Podracing is said to be vast, but only Bib Fortuna knows the exact number.',NULL,'13_71'),(740,1238,'Dark','U1','Premiere','I\'ve Lost Artoo!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/ivelostartoo.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to target a starship\'s [Nav Computer] or astromech. Draw destiny. If destiny > 1, [Nav Computer] or astromech is lost. If starship\'s [Nav Computer] is lost, place Effect on starship (may add 1 astromech); otherwise, Effect lost.','\'WHAAAAAAAAAOOOOW!\'',NULL,'1_218'),(741,1346,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba The Hutt','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbathehutt.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','6','7','Deploy -2 at Tatooine or Nal Hutta. To use his landspeed requires +2 Force. May escort a captive. While at Audience Chamber, adds 1 to forfeit of all your other aliens and allows you to activate 1 Force for whenever you Force drain with an alien. Immune to attrition < 4.','Jabba Desilijic Tiure. Male heir to Zorba the Hutt. Gangster. Leader of one of the largest criminal organizations in the galaxy. Over six hundred years old.',NULL,'6_109'),(742,1353,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace: Audience Chamber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbaspalaceaudiencechamber.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, may use 4 Force to cancel Scum and Villainy. Immune to Revolution.',NULL,'Jabba\'s Palace: Audience Chamber','6_162'),(743,1237,'Dark','C2','Premiere','I\'ve Got A Problem Here','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/ivegotaproblemhere.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to target opponent\'s starfighter with maneuver at a system or sector where a battle just finished. Draw destiny. Starfighter lost if destiny > maneuver.','Debris fragments damaged Jek Porkins\' X-wing, causing a cascade of computer and flight control failures.',NULL,'1_253'),(744,1347,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•Jabba The Hutt (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/jabbathehutt.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','4','7','While with your alien leader, Jabba is immune to attrition and may not be targeted by Interrupts or weapons. May deploy one Scum And Villainy from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. During battle, may use 1 Force to double the power of one other non-[Maintenance] alien present.','Jabba Desilijic Tiure. Male heir to Zorba the Hutt. Gangster. Leader of one of the largest criminal organizations in the galaxy. Over six hundred years old.',NULL,'200_84'),(745,1344,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Jabba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/jabba.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','2','3','5','To use his landspeed requires +1 Force. Your aliens are deploy -1 to same location. While at Audience Chamber, adds 2 to forfeit of all your non-unique aliens and makes Scum and Villainy immune to Alter. Immune to attrition < 4.','Gangster. Leader. Infamous Hutt crime lord. Operates his vast empire from an ancient monastery on Tatooine. Uses mercenary pilots to smuggle spice and other contraband.',NULL,'7_182'),(746,1348,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Jabba\'s Influence','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/jabbasinfluence.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one of your gangsters or bounty hunters. Once during each of your control phases, if present with an opponent\'s smuggler or character of ability = 1, may use 3 Force. Opponent must use 5 Force or that character returns to opponent\'s hand.','Jabba makes offers one cannot refuse. Smugglers, thieves and competitors who do not acquiesce have been rumored to wake up with a bantha\'s head in their bed.',NULL,'7_231'),(747,1350,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace Sabacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbaspalacesabacc.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Requirements: Gambler, gangster, smuggler or information broker at a Jabba\'s Palace site. Wild cards (1-6): Passenger Deck and deserts. Clone cards: Aliens and Jabba\'s Palace sites (gamblers and Jabba may use clones as 4). Stakes: One character weapon or non-unique alien.\"','Jabba has won the service of many of his guards and other henchbeings through games of chance.','Jabba\'s Palace Sabacc','6_156'),(748,6435,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Jabba\'s Prize/Jabba\'s Prize','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/jabbasprizefront.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','0','0','0','0','{Deploys only at start of game if Carbon Chamber Testing is on table to Security Tower, frozen and imprisoned, (instead of a Rebel from opponent\'s Reserve Deck). If You Can Either Profit By This... is on table, opponent does not deploy Han at start of game (relocate Jabba\'s Prize to Audience Chamber, flip Carbon Chamber Testing, and you may not move or transfer Jabba\'s Prize)}. May not be placed in Reserve Deck. Jabba\'s Prize is a persona of Han only while on table. If Jabba\'s Prize leaves table, place it out of play. May not be targeted by We\'re The Bait or Someone Who Loves You. While Jabba\'s Prize is at Audience Chamber, Jabba is power +3, defense value +3, and adds 3 to his immunity to attrition. If Jabba\'s Prize was just released, opponent may replace it with any Han from hand, Used Pile, or Reserve Deck; reshuffle (if not replaced, place Jabba\'s Prize out of play).','Han Solo was frozen in carbonite to test the process Vader planned to use on Luke. When Boba Fett delivered Han to Jabba, the vile gangster called him his \'favorite decoration.\'',NULL,'10_42'),(749,1357,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace: Entrance Cavern','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbaspalaceentrancecavern.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Force drain +1 here and your aliens deploy -2 here.',NULL,'Jabba\'s Palace: Entrance Cavern','6_165'),(750,5104,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 4','•Jakku','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/jakku.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Unless your Resistance character or [Resistance] starship here, you may not draw more than one battle destiny here.',NULL,'Jakku','204_51'),(751,1362,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Sail Barge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbassailbarge.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','3','5','5','7','Deploys only on Tatooine; you may immediately deploy Passenger Deck from your Reserve Deck and reshuffle. May add 1 driver and 7 passengers. Your aliens deploy -1 aboard.','Ubrikkian sail barge. Custom built for Jabba with an armored hull and weaponry. Top speed of 100 kph. Used by the Hutt crimelord on his many trips to Mos Eisley.',NULL,'6_172'),(752,1365,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Jabba\'s Space Cruiser','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/jabbasspacecruiser.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Ubrikkian Luxury Space Yacht','2','5','5','5','Deploys and moves like a starfighter. May add 2 alien pilots and 6 passengers. Turbolaser Battery may deploy aboard as a \'react.\' When Jabba aboard, moves for free and immune to attrition.','Flying fortress of Jabba Desilijic Tiure. Reaches speeds of 800 kph in atmosphere. The crime lord installed hidden gunports as an unpleasant surprise for would-be pirates.',NULL,'7_304'),(753,5135,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 4','•Jabba\'s Sail Barge (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/jabbassailbarge.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','3','4','4','6','May add 1 alien driver and 8 passengers. Your vehicle weapons deploy free aboard. Once per turn, may deploy Passenger Deck or a skiff here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While on Tatooine with a skiff, Force drain +1 here.','Ubrikkian sail barge. Custom built for Jabba with an armored hull and weaponry. Top speed of 100 kph. Used by the Hutt crimelord on his many trips to Mos Eisley.',NULL,'204_56'),(754,1356,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace: Dungeon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbaspalacedungeon.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, may use 3 Force to release an imprisoned captive here.',NULL,NULL,'6_164'),(755,5183,'Dark','U2','Virtual Set 4','