,'https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Dark/large/jabbastrophies.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If Jabba just Force drained (or won a battle), stack top card of opponent\'s Lost Pile here; may draw top card of your Reserve Deck. If 4 or more cards here, may return this Effect and a character with Jabba at Audience Chamber to owner\'s hand. Immune to Alter.','Oola had to choose between giving in to Jabba\'s constant advances or resisting him and inciting his wrath.',NULL,'202_12'),(764,1374,'Dark','C','Coruscant','Jawa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/jawa.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','*','1','Deploys only on Tatooine. To deploy, requires 1 Force from each players\' Force Pile. Power +1 on Tatooine. While with another Jawa, if opponent just initiated a Force drain at adjacent site, may use 2 Force to reduce it by 1.','Every now and then, Jawas will pause in their scavenging duties to take in a Podrace. Many believe this is only because they want to be first to a crash scene.','Jawa (EP1)','12_108'),(765,1364,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Sail Barge: Passenger Deck','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbassailbargepassengerdeck.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your characters may enter/exit here for 4 Force each.',NULL,NULL,'6_167'),(766,5105,'Dark','C1','Virtual Set 4','•Jakku: Landing Site','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/jakkulandingsite.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: :',NULL,NULL,'204_52'),(767,1369,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Janus Greejatus','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/janusgreejatus.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','4','5','Deploys -3 to Emperor\'s site. When with Emperor at a battleground site, adds 1 to your Force drains here. Once per turn, you may use 1 Force to place a card from hand to bottom of Used Pile and draw top card of Reserve Deck. Immune to attrition < 3.','Imperial council member. Very cruel at heart. Has lusted for power his entire life. Predictable and controllable.',NULL,'9_110'),(768,1372,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Jawa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/jawa.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','*','1','To deploy, requires 1 Force from each players\' Force Pile. Cannot deploy otherwise. Deploy only on Tatooine, but may move elsewhere.','Small, rodent-like scavenger species. Refurbish and sell droids. Nest in sandcrawlers. Considered to be pests by most species.','Jawa','1_182'),(769,1360,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace: Rancor Pit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jabbaspalacerancorpit.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If your character here is \'eaten,\' opponent retrieves Force equal to character\'s forfeit.',NULL,NULL,'6_166'),(770,1376,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','Jawa Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/jawablaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Jawa. May target a character or creature for free. Draw destiny. If destiny -1 > defense value, target hit. If destiny = 0, Jawa Blaster \'explodes\' (weapon and character firing it are lost).','Built from scavenged parts, Jawa blaster are not required to adhere to any design standards. An etching on this stock warns \'datinni greb zroom.\'',NULL,'2_159'),(771,1394,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•••Jet Pack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jetpack.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on any alien (except Boba Fett or Jabba). May \'fly\' (landspeed = 3). May use 2 Force to move as a \'react\'.','Mitrinomon Z-6 jet pack. Exhaust vents are used to maneuver in midflight. Gyro-stabilizer automatically applies counterthrust when landing.',NULL,'6_140'),(772,6444,'Dark','U2','Virtual Set 9','•Jedha: Jedha City','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/jedhajedhacity.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Baze, Chirrut, and Saw deploy -1 here.',NULL,NULL,'209_49'),(773,1378,'Dark','U1','Premiere','•Jawa Pack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/jawapack.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'To deploy (on your side of table), requires 3 Force from both players\' Force Piles. Cannot deploy otherwise. All your Jawas are forfeit +1.','Jawas travel in packs for protection. They use ambush tactics against unwary droids in the canyons of the Jundland Wastes. \'Aeeeyaa!\'','Jawa Siesta','1_219'),(774,5203,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 8','•Jedha','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/jedha.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Unless Baze, Bodhi, Chirrut, or Saw here, Force drain -1 here.',NULL,NULL,'208_50'),(775,1342,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•J\'Quille','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/jquille.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','5','3','Power +2 on Hoth. At the start of a battle, may cause one opponent\'s character of ability < 3 present to be excluded from the battle. While at Audience Chamber, all your other Whipids are forfeit +2.','Whiphid spy in league with Lady Valarian. Yearns for battle. Enjoys hearing the screams of his victims. Plotting to kill Jabba.','Tanus Spijek','6_110'),(776,1395,'Dark','PM','Enhanced Jabba\'s Palace','•Jodo Kast','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedJabbasPalace-Dark/large/jodokast.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','3','4','3','When in battle, if opponent draws more than one battle destiny, may cancel one. Once per turn, when firing a rifle or blaster, may target for free and add 2 to total weapon destiny. May be targeted by Hidden Weapons. May \'fly\' (landspeeed = 3).','Bounty Hunter and scout. Perfectionist. Equipped with mandalorian armor and a jet pack. He doesn\'t mind being mistaken for Boba Fett. Occasionally works for Black Sun.',NULL,'110_9'),(777,1397,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Join Me!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/joinme.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force if Luke was just \'hit\' by a lightsaber swung by Vader. Opponent must choose: Place Luke in owner\'s Used Pile OR Luke may not be forfeited this battle and crosses to the Dark Side at the end of the turn if still on table (is no longer \'hit\').','...And together, we can rule the galaxy as father and son!\'',NULL,'11_82'),(778,1412,'Dark','C1','A New Hope','•Kashyyyk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/kashyyyk.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your starships with any Wookiee aboard are power and forfeit +2 here.',NULL,'Kashyyyk','2_146'),(779,1399,'Dark','F','Special Edition','<>Jungle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/jungle.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : May not deploy to Bespin, Coruscant, Hoth, Kessel or Tatooine. Force Drain -1 here. Your attrition against opponent is -2 here.',NULL,'Jungle','7_285'),(780,1401,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Juri Juice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/jurijuice.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any alien if Cantina, Mos Eisley or Jabba\'s Sail Barge on table. That alien may not use ability in battles (if Kabe, she also cannot \'steal\'). Utinni Effect canceled by moving that alien to one of those sites without \'driving\' a vehicle.','Popular beverage served in many cantinas and tapcafes. Has intoxicating effect on many species. Favorite drink of Kabe, Chadra-Fan thief of Mos Eisley.',NULL,'1_220'),(781,1398,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Judicator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/judicator.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','8','8','9','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Each of its weapon destiny draws is +2. Starfighters it \'hits\' are power = 0.','Incorporates latest design modifications from Kuat Drive Yards. Targeting computers outfitted with antenna locking, in-line calibration and helical-motion extrapolators.',NULL,'9_158'),(782,1421,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Keder The Black','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/kedertheblack.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','4','4','4','Deploys only to a site as an Undercover spy (-2 on Coruscant). During your control phase, may \'break cover\' to target one character with politics present. Draw destiny. If destiny +1 > target\'s politics, target and Keder are lost.','A highly paid assassin and spy, Keder has infiltrated the Senate disguised as a Coruscant Guard. The identity of his target and his employer remains a mystery to all but him.',NULL,'12_109'),(783,1426,'Dark','U2','Premiere','•Kessel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/kessel.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Total ability of 6 or more required for you to draw battle destiny here.',NULL,'Kessel','1_288'),(784,1428,'Dark','U','Special Edition','Kessel Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/kesseloperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','2','While at a Kessel site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your smuggler is on Kessel) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Kessel from Reserve Deckreshuffle.','Mercenaries that make a profit selling materials to the troops stationed on Kessel. Help the Empire prevent escape attempts by the prisoners there.',NULL,'7_184'),(785,1414,'Dark','U','Special Edition','Kashyyyk Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/kashyyykoperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','2','While at a Kashyyyk site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your Trandoshan is on Kashyyyk) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Kashyyyk from Reserve Deck- reshuffle.','Hunters who track down escaped Wookiee slaves and report on their location. The Empire and Trandoshans pay a high price for that kind of information.','Kashyyyk Operative','7_183'),(786,1430,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Ket Maliss','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/ketmaliss.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your non-warrior character (except droids) to give that character [Warrior] skill. OR Deploy on your warrior. That character is power +1. (Immune to Alter.)','Assassins are highly valued by Jabba the Hutt and other gangsters. Prince Xizor\'s \'shadow killer,\' has unknown but undoubtably lethal business in Mos Eisley.','Sai\'torr Kal Fas','1_221'),(787,1434,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•Kiffex','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/kiffex.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy with exactly 2 starships, your total power here is +2.',NULL,'Kiffex','2_147'),(788,1436,'Dark','U','Special Edition','Kiffex Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/kiffexoperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','2','While at a Kiffex site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your spy is on Kiffex) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Kiffex from Reserve Deck- reshuffle.','Couriers. Watchful for any kind of activity by the Alliance or the Empire. Sell their information to anyone willing to buy.','Kiffex Operative','7_185'),(789,1438,'Dark','C','Coruscant','•Kill Them Immediately','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/killthemimmediately.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 5 Force to reveal opponent\'s hand. If opponent has no duplicate cards there, place this Interrupt in Used Pile. OtherwiseUSED: place a revealed card in opponent\'s Used Pile.  LOST: all cards opponent has two or more of are lost. (Immune to Sense.)\"','Darth Sidious instructed Nute Gunray to dispose of the Jedi ambassadors. Rune Haako was not so confident.','Reveal Ourselves To The Jedi','12_149'),(790,1440,'Dark','C1','Premiere','Kintan Strider','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/kintanstrider.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just forfeited or lost a character, use 1 Force to regenerate one of your own characters. Retrieve the character closest to the top of your Lost Pile into your hand.','A dejarik of a ferocious creature with incredible healing abilities. Extinct on the homeworld of Kintan, but used as a guard beasts by many Hutt gangsters.',NULL,'1_254'),(791,1441,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Kir Kanos','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/kirkanos.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','5','2','3','When armed with a Force pike, adds one battle destiny. Once during each of your deploy phases, lose 1 Force or place Kanos and cards deployed on him in owner\'s Used Pile (if Emperor on table, may use 1 Force instead).','Fiercely devoted Royal Guard. Feels deeply indebted to those who risk their life for him. Unaware of the extent of Palpatine\'s atrocities and cruelty.',NULL,'10_43'),(792,5189,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 8','•Kir Kanos (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/kirkanos.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','5','3','4','When deployed, may take a Royal Guard into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If in battle with an Imperial, once per game may cancel a non-[Immune to Sense] Interrupt.','Fiercely devoted Royal Guard. Feels deeply indebted to those who risk their life for him. Unaware of the extent of Palpatine\'s atrocities and cruelty.',NULL,'208_32'),(793,1444,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Kithaba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/kithaba.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','*','4','2','Deploys only on Tatooine. Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots. Power = 1 + ability of opponent\'s highest-ability character present.','Famous Klatooinian assassin. After disposing of a few more prisoners, plans to quit the killing business and become a full-time musician. Rises to the challenges he faces.',NULL,'6_111'),(794,1445,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Kitik Keed\'kak','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/kitikkeedkak.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','8','6','2','Immediately lost if at same site as overprotective mother, Kal\'Faln C\'ndros. Cannot board starfighters or enclosed vehicles.','A female insectoid Yam\'rii. Very strong and easily angered. Known for stealth, but also has good technological aptitude. Meat eater. Loves eggs.',NULL,'1_183'),(795,1448,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Klaatu','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/klaatu.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','3','2','Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +2 when with Barada or defending a battle a a Jabba\'s Palace site. During a battle at same site, may forfeit a transport vehicle present to satisfy all remaining battle damage and attrition against you.','Kadas\'sa\'Nikto. Barada\'s main assistant. In charge of repairing Jabba\'s skiffs. Gambler. Always tries to make it back to the palace to watch the Rancor get fed.',NULL,'6_112'),(796,1450,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•Knowledge And Defense','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/knowledgeanddefense.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Insert in opponent\'s Reserve Deck. When Effect reaches top it is lost, but opponent may not initiate any battles for remainder of turn. (Immune to Alter.)','\'A Jedi uses the Force for knowledge and defense, never for attack.\'',NULL,'4_125'),(797,4042,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Knowledge And Defense (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/knowledgeanddefense.gif?raw=true','Effect','Starting','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table with up to any number of Defensive Shields from outside your deck face-down under here. Four times per game, may play a Defensive Shield from here (as if from hand). Unless canceling your Interrupt, opponent may not play Recoil In Fear until the end of your first turn.','\'A Jedi uses the Force for knowledge and defense, never for attack.\'','Anger, Fear, Aggression (V)','200_110'),(798,1452,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Krayt Dragon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/kraytdragon.gif?raw=true','Creature','Desert','1','*','7','0','Ferocity = 6 + two destiny. Habitat: deserts and Tatooine exterior sites. May not deploy to an occupied site. If defeated, opponent may draw destiny and retrieve Force equal to destiny draw.','Krayt dragons have beautiful and valuable pearls inside them as a gizzard to grind up food. Their fierceness is legendary. Up to 10 meters tall and 30 meters long.',NULL,'7_211'),(799,1453,'Dark','U1','A New Hope','•Krayt Dragon Bones','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/kraytdragonbones.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on table. Each opponent\'s destiny draw, you do the following: (0) Put top used card in hand; (1) lose 1 Force; (2) activate 1 Force; (3) lose this Effect; (4) retrieve 1 Force; (5) deploy a character for free; (6+) nothing.','Tusken Raiders, Jawas and other desert dwellers believe that krayt dragon bones possess mystical powers that can bring good or bad luck.','Tauntaun Bones','2_122'),(800,6470,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 9','•Krennic, Death Star Commandant','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/krennicdeathstarcommandant.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Once per turn, if Death Star orbiting a battleground, may peek at top two cards of your Force Pile and take one into hand. Once per game, may take a non-unique Star Destroyer into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Commander. Leader.',NULL,'209_36'),(801,1457,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Kuat','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/kuat.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy, all Star Destroyers are deploy +1 (+3 if you control). Your movement to here requires +1 Force.',NULL,NULL,'7_286'),(802,1458,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Kuat Drive Yards','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/kuatdriveyards.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Kuat system. All your Imperial-class Star Destroyers are immune to attri