lish appearance.',NULL,'1_184'),(810,6475,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 11','•Lady Proxima','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/ladyproxima.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','4','6','Lost if at an exterior site. While with two of your other aliens, adds one battle destiny. During your control phase, may reveal the top three cards of your Reserve Deck, take one alien into hand (if possible), and shuffle your Reserve Deck.','Female Grindalid. Gangster. Leader.',NULL,'211_3'),(811,1462,'Dark','C','Endor','Lambda-Class Shuttle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/lambdaclassshuttle.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Lambda-Class Shuttle','4','2','2','3','Deploy -1 if Sienar Fleet Systems on table. May add 1 pilot and 6 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Takes off and lands for free.','Manufactured by Sienar Fleet Systems. Length 20 meters. Bottom wings fold for docking and landing. Boarding ramp allows easy access to passenger and cargo areas.',NULL,'8_168'),(812,6478,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 9','•Lana Dobreed & •Sacrifice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/lanadobreedsacrifice.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your character is about to be hit, use 1 Force (free if by a [Permanent Weapon] weapon) to prevent its forfeit from being reduced for remainder of turn. OR Cancel Disarmed. (Immune to Sense.) OR Cancel a \'react\'. OR During your move phase, target any or all of your characters at one site to \'transport\' (relocate) to an exterior or battleground site. Draw destiny. Use that much Force to \'transport,\' or place Interrupt in Lost Pile.',NULL,NULL,'209_48'),(813,1463,'Dark','U','Coruscant','•Lana Dobreed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/lanadobreed.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, target any or all of your characters at one exterior site to \'transport\' (relocate) to another exterior site. Draw destiny. Use that much Force to \'transport,\' or place Interrupt in Lost Pile.','Dobreed used to have dreams of opening up his own shop in Mos Espa. Now broke from his gambling activities, he provides transportation services to pay for his urges.','Odin Nesloor','12_150'),(814,1465,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Lando Calrissian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/landocalrissian.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','2','3','Deploys only on Cloud City. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When playing Sabacc, may subtract 1 from or add 1 to your total. If present at a site, can be replaced by opponent with any Light Side Lando.','Scoundrel and gambler. Petty administrator of a small Tibanna gas mining operation. Easily coerced. Has problems of his own. Had dealings with the Tonnika sisters - twice.','Lando Calrissian','5_99'),(815,1470,'Dark','R','Dagobah','Lando System?','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/landosystem.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, use 1 Force to move any one of your [Dagobah] icon characters of ability > 1 to any [Cloud City] icon location where you have presence. If moving to a Cloud City site, this movement is free and you do not need presence.','\'Lando\'s not a system, he\'s a man.\' Regardless of where Rebels flee, dark agents are sure to follow.',NULL,'4_145'),(816,1477,'Dark','U','Coruscant','Laser Cannon Battery','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/lasercannonbattery.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your capital starship. May deploy as a \'react\'. May target a starship using X Force, where X = 0 to 3. Draw destiny. Subtract 2 if targeting a starship with maneuver. If destiny +X > defense value, target hit and opponent loses 1 Force.','Trade Federation battleships use concealed quad laser emplacements. Though their coverage is limited, the surprise factor and ferocious firing rate is often overwhelming.',NULL,'12_187'),(817,1478,'Dark','U2','A New Hope','••Laser Gate','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/lasergate.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy between any two interior mobile sites. To pass, a character must have (power + ability) > 4 or use a Lift Tube (all other vehicles are blocked). Laser Gate defense value = 3; may be targeted (as if a character) by a character weapon from either site.','Security corridors are guarded by a grid of laser emplacements which can be activated upon demand to seal off sensitive areas from intrusion.',NULL,'2_113'),(818,1479,'Dark','U2','Premiere','Laser Projector','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/laserprojector.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on an interior site. May target a seeker (use defense value = 1), character or creature for free. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny -1 > defense value. Laser Projector may be targeted by any weapon (use defense value = 1).','Laser system activated by distress signal from guards. Used at security checkpoints and detention block control rooms. Targeting guided by centralized droid controller.',NULL,'1_319'),(819,1480,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Lateral Damage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lateraldamage.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any system. Target an opponent\'s starship. Target\'s power and forfeit = 0. When target reaches Utinni Effect, target draws one destiny. Utinni Effect canceled if destiny > 2. Otherwise, draw again next move phase, etc.','Starships can become damaged in combat and rendered ineffective until they can be repaired and re-outfitted.',NULL,'1_222'),(820,1481,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Lathe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/lathe.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. If opponent has 2 or more aliens of the same title at this site, may place Lathe in Lost Pile to cause all of them to be lost. Once per turn, may use 1 Force to shuffle opponent\'s Reserve Deck.','Was one of Jabba\'s vile Nikto henchmen. Leaving Tatooine to see what the galaxy has to offer. Deep down, he loathes the slave trade. Information broker.',NULL,'11_59'),(821,1485,'Dark','C','Death Star II','•Leave Them To Me','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/leavethemtome.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. While you occupy a \'Subjugated\' planet location, operatives are forfeit = 0, operatives do not add to Force drains and your Force drains may not be reduced. At any time, you may place Effect out of play to retrieve 1 Force.','\'I will deal with them myself.\'','Let\'s Keep A Little Optimism Here','9_128'),(822,1486,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Leave Them To Me','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/leavethemtome.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. While you occupy a Subjugated planet location, operatives are forfeit = 0, operatives do not add to Force drains, and your Force drains may not be reduced. (Subjugated planet is defined on the Objective card Local Uprising.)','\'I will deal with them myself.\'','Let\'s Keep A Little Optimism Here - Defensive Shield','13_72'),(823,1496,'Dark','R2','A New Hope','Leia Seeker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/leiaseeker.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploys for 1 Force t