ns.{Flip} this card if no ISB agents are on table.',NULL,NULL,'7_299'),(833,1340,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•IT-O (Eyetee-Oh)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/ito.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','4','3','1','When at Detention Block Corridor, adds X to your Force drains there, where X = the number of captives present. Immune to Restraining Bolt.','Floating prisoner interrogation droid. Uses probes and needles to dispense truth drugs and perform \'surgery.\' Sensors determine subject\'s pain threshold and truthfulness.',NULL,'2_93'),(834,1525,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Lieutenant Endicott','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/lieutenantendicott.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Deploys -2 to any docking bay or launch bay. While he is at Death Star II: Docking Bay, you may shuttle for free between here and exterior sites related to system Death Star II orbits.','Docking bay technician. Orphan. Offered post on new Death Star when he graduated third in class from the Imperial Academy at Carida.',NULL,'9_111'),(835,1527,'Dark','U','Endor','•Lieutenant Grond','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/lieutenantgrond.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots or any swoop he drives. When in battle at an exterior site, adds 2 to attrition against opponent for each of your biker scout/trooper (non-biker scout) pairs present.','Colonel Dyer\'s aide. Coordinates scout actions. As a youth, raced swoops on homeworld of Corellia. Formerly served with Emperor\'s Demonstration Team.',NULL,'8_102'),(836,1529,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Lieutenant Hebsly','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/lieutenanthebsly.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Scythe 3, once per turn may subtract 1 from maneuver of one opponent\'s starfighter at same location for remainder of turn.','Served in Anoat sector. Uses excellent maneuverability of TIE/ln to his advantage in combat.',NULL,'9_112'),(837,1533,'Dark','R','Endor','•Lieutenant Renz','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/lieutenantrenz.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','4','Power +2 while present with a stormtrooper. You Rebel Scum target a Rebel at same site is a Used Interrupt and is immune to Sense. Immune to attrition < number of stormtroopers present.','Leader of one of the Emperor\'s finest legions of troops. His command was placed at the disposal of Colonel Dyer. Always on the lookout for Rebel activity.',NULL,'8_103'),(838,1537,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Lieutenant Sheckil','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/lieutenantsheckil.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','3','4','During your control phase, may use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one Human Shield into hand and reshuffle. When escorting a captive, captive is forfeit +2 and Sheckil is immune to attrition < 4.','Former warrant officer from Concord Dawn. Promoted due to superb performance. Specializes in transporting high-profile criminals. Twin brother of a famous mercenary.',NULL,'5_101'),(839,1538,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Lieutenant Suba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/lieutenantsuba.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','4','While at a Death Star or Executor site, your troopers deploy free there and are power and forfeit +1 there, and you may use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one Tactical Support into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.','Chief of security and political officer on Executor. Responsible for ensuring the loyalty of his fellow officers. Disapproved of Vader\'s unwillingness to simply kill Skywalker.',NULL,'4_104'),(840,1539,'Dark','U2','Premiere','•Lieutenant Tanbris','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lieutenanttanbris.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','Deploy -1 for starship weapons of any starship he pilots. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Subtracts 1 from maneuver of any starfighter he pilots.','Former fighter pilot grounded after injury. Tactical officer aboard Death Star. Competent strategist. Specializes in directing Imperial starfighters.',NULL,'1_185'),(841,1542,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Lieutenant Venka','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/lieutenantvenka.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','Power +2 when at an Executor site or same site as Tarkin or Chief Bast, or if the Death Star has been \'blown away.\' Fear Will Keep Them In Line is destiny +2 and, when it adds 1 to your power, also adds 1 to attrition against opponent.','Worked hard for a transfer to the Executor. One of the many noncommissioned personnel promoted to replace the vast number of officers lost during the Death Star disaster.',NULL,'4_105'),(842,6491,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 9','•Lieutenant Venka (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Dark/large/lieutenantvenka.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','Deploys -1 to Executor. While aboard a capital starship, adds 1 to armor and its defense value may not be reduced. While Fear Will Keep Them In Line here, when you win a battle at a related site where you have an Imperial, opponent loses 2 Force.','Worked hard for a transfer to the Executor. One of the many noncommissioned personnel promoted to replace the vast number of officers lost during the Death Star disaster.',NULL,'209_38'),(843,1543,'Dark','R','Endor','•Lieutenant Watts','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/lieutenantwatts.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots. Adds 1 to each weapon destiny draw of any combat vehicle he pilots (or 2 if on Tempest Scout 2 or if present with Marquand).','Native of Corulag. Watts\' gunnery skills produce devastating results. Temporarily assigned to Kuat Drive Yards to work on prototype AT-ST weaponry.',NULL,'8_104'),(844,1547,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Lift Tube','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lifttube.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','6','0','1','1','May carry 4 passengers. Deploy and move only at interior mobile sites. May move without presence aboard. Also, may move as a \'react\' only to a battle or Force drain (if within range).','System of enclosed high-speed vertical and horizontal transport cylinders. Used in space stations, large starships, Death Stars, etc.','Lift Tube','1_308'),(845,1551,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Light Repeating Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lightrepeatingblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior. If your power droid or fusion generator present, may target a character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value. May fire repeatedly for 2 Force each time.','BlasTech model T-21 light repeating blaster. Excellent power, good range. Carries energy for 25 shots. Unlimited firepower when attached to a power generator.',NULL,'1_320'),(846,1552,'Dark','U1','Hoth','Lightsaber Deficiency','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/lightsaberdeficiency.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel Lightsaber Proficiency. OR Target a character with ability < 4 using a lightsaber in a battle or a Force drain. Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny > ability. Lightsaber lost if destiny = ability.','\'Ah...Uh...\'',NULL,'3_129'),(847,1553,'Dark','C','Tatooine','•Lightsaber Parry','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/lightsaberparry.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If a battle was just initiated where you have a character armed with a lightsaber, characters may not be targeted by lightsabers for remainder of battle.  LOST: If opponent just initiated a duel, opponent must choose to lose 4 Force or cancel the duel.\"','Vader had to show Luke that giving in to the dark side of the Force was his only destiny.',NULL,'11_83'),(848,1555,'Dark','U2','Premiere','•Limited Resources','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/limitedresources.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If the opponent has two cards or less in hand, opponent must immediately lose 2 Force (4 Force if it is your turn). If the opponent has Fusion Generator Supply Tanks aboard a starship, loss is reduced by 2.','The Empire dominates consumption of resources. Despite being efficient, Rebel logistical and maintenance officers often are compelled to expend emergency reserves.',NULL,'1_255'),(849,1557,'Dark','C1','Premiere','LIN-V8M (Elleyein-Veeateemm)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/linv8m.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','0','2','4','At any time during your turn, may use 1 Force to \'defuse\' (lose) any one mine at same site.','Armored military droid which specializes in laying explosive mines. Originally intended to set charges inside ore and spice mines, but has also been converted for military use.','LIN-V8K (Elleyein-Veeatekay)','1_186'),(850,1558,'Dark','U2','A New Hope','•Lirin Car\'n','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/lirincarn.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','For each other musician present, adds a \'cover charge\' of 1 to the Force required to move or deploy each character to same site.','Bith mercenary. Male back-up to Kloo Horn player in Figrin D\'an\'s band. Only musician, besides Doikk, who has not lost ownership of his instrument to Figrin.',NULL,'2_94'),(851,1559,'Dark','C','Coruscant','•Little Real Power','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/littlerealpower.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During any control phase, target an opponent\'s character with politics present with your senator at Galactic Senate. For remainder of turn, target\'s game text is canceled and target is politics = 0.','\'He is mired by baseless accusations of corruption.\'',NULL,'12_151'),(852,1560,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Lobel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/lobel.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Subtracts 2 from forfeit of each opponent\'s pilot at same site. Prevents characters from moving to or from same or adjacent site using Elis Helrot or Nabrun Leids.','Powerful magnetic fields in the Lobel physiology make the operation of nearby navigation devices impossible. Pilots claim these fields also produce headaches.','Sic-Six','7_186'),(853,1561,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Lobot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/lobot.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','2','2','3','Deploys only on Cloud City. Power +2 when present at a Scomp Link. If present at a site, can be replaced by opponent with any Light Side Lobot. While present on Cloud City with your Lando, prevents replacement of Lobot and Lando.','Son of a traveling slaver. Helps run Cloud City with Administrator Lando Calrissian. Speech capability worn away by constant cyborg neural connection.','Lobot','7_187'),(854,1565,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Local Trouble','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/localtrouble.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force at the beginning of your battle phase to allow any two of your Stormtroopers in the Cantina to battle any one opponent\'s character (your choice). You may add one battle destiny. No other battles may occur in Cantina this turn.','\'Look like somebody\'s beginning to take an interest in your handiwork.\' Imperial stormtroopers coerce local residents to assist them in the apprehension of Rebel scum.',NULL,'1_256'),(855,1569,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Location, Location, Location','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/locationlocationlocation.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. At the end of each player\'s deploy phase, if they did not deploy a location, they lose 1 Force. Effect canceled if any player deploys three or more locations in a single turn.','\'Mudhole? Slimy? My home this is!\'',NULL,'4_126'),(856,1576,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Lone Pilot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lonepilot.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your pilot (or permanent pilot) is defending a battle alone at a system or sector, add one battle destiny. OR If Motti is defending a battle alone at a system or sector, add two battle destiny.','One lone TIE fighter, acting as a scout near the Death Star, suddenly encountered the Millennium Falcon.','Full Throttle','1_257'),(857,1578,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Lone Warrior','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lonewarrior.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If any warrior is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny. OR If Tagge is defending a battle alone at a site, add two battle destiny.','Though generally deployed in squads, all Imperial warriors are trained in the close combat techniques and have a reputation for ferocity when cornered.','Warrior\'s Courage','1_258'),(858,1579,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Look Sir, Droids','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/looksirdroids.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to search through the opponent\'s Used Pile and move any droids you find there to opponent\'s Lost Pile. OR Use X Force to destroy any one droid on table where X = droid\'s deploy cost.','Trooper 1124, Davin Felth, discovered droid plating dropped by R2- D2 and C-3PO when exiting escape pod.',NULL,'1_259'),(859,1580,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Lord Maul','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/lordmaul.gif?raw=true','Character','Sith','1','7','8','8','Deploys -2 to Naboo. While with Qui-Gon, your battle destinies here are each +1. When Maul wins a lightsaber combat, adds 2 to opponent\'s Force loss. Immune to Clash Of Sabers and attrition < 5 (or < 6 if armed with a lightsaber).  May not be Disarmed.','Sent by Darth Sidious to Naboo in order to assist the Trade Federation in their blockade there. His confrontation with Obi-Wan and Qui-Gon would impact history forever.',NULL,'13_74'),(860,5187,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 8','•Lord Maul With Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/lordmaulwithlightsaber.gif?raw=true','Character','Sith','1','7','6','7','Permanent weapon is •Maul\'s Lightsaber (may add 1 to Force drain where present; adds 1 to your battle destiny draws here; may target a character for free; draw two destiny; target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value).','Trade Federation.',NULL,'208_34'),(861,5188,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 8','•Lord Sidious','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/lordsidious.gif?raw=true','Character','Dark Jedi Master','1','5','6','8','Once per game, may take Always Two There Are or a Neimoidian into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If alone (or a [Theed Palace] objective on table) and opponent just initiated battle here, may exclude one character of ability < 6 present. Immune to attrition.','Leader. Trade Federation.',NULL,'208_35'),(862,1581,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Lord Vader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/lordvader.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','7','8','8','Deploys -2 to Executor, Death Star II or Endor. Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While armed with a lightsaber, adds 2 to his defense value and 1 to each of his lightsaber weapon destiny draws. Immune to Uncontrollable Fury and attrition < 6.','Forgiving administrator of Imperial policy. Emperor Palpatine\'s most trusted leader. Believes converting Skywalker is key to the Alliance\'s downfall.',NULL,'9_113'),(863,1583,'Dark','R','Dagobah','Lost In Space','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/lostinspace.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a pilot was just lost from a system or sector, deploy on that location and stack pilot here. Pilot may be rescued or captured by any capital starship present here during any move phase, and may be targeted by weapons (except during battle) as if present (treat as a starfighter with defense value = 0). Lost if no pilot here.','Congratulations on purchasing the TIE/ln starfighter by Sienar. Equipped with a jettison device and distress beacon, it should provide you with years of worry-free subjugation.',NULL,'4_127'),(864,1586,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Lott Dod','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/lottdod.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','1','2','5','Agendas: ambition, blockade, trade. While in a senate majority, once during your control phase, may search your Force Pile and take any one card there into hand; reshuffle. While at Galactic Senate, your other Neimoidians are forfeit +2.','Primary Neimoidian senator who represents the Trade Federation in the Galactic Senate. Thwarted attempts by Amidala to end the blockade of Naboo.',NULL,'12_110'),(865,1587,'Dark','C1','A New Hope','•Lt. Pol Treidum','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/ltpoltreidum.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','5','While at Docking Control Room 327, adds 2 to your total power at Docking Bay 327. Once during each of your control phases, if at same site as an Undercover spy, may draw destiny. Spy\'s \'cover is broken\' if destiny = spy\'s ability.','Gantry officer charged with maintaining magnetic field, atmosphere and security in Death Star docking bay. After mission on Ralltiir, paranoid about infiltration by Rebel spies.',NULL,'2_95'),(866,4097,'Dark','C1','Virtual Set 1','•Lt. Pol Treidum (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/ltpoltreidum.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','5','Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots. When deployed (or leaves table), may draw top card of Reserve Deck or Used Pile. During battle, attrition against you is -1 for each ISB agent here (limit -3). Your spies here (unless Undercover) are immune to Double Agent.','Gantry officer charged with maintaining magnetic field, atmosphere and security in Death Star docking bay. After mission on Ralltiir, paranoid about infiltration by Rebel spies.',NULL,'201_26'),(867,6500,'Dark','U1','Virtual Set 11','•Lt. Poldin Lehuse','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/ltpoldinlehuse.gif?raw=true','Character','First Order','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. During battle, if piloting a [First Order] TIE, may target an opponent\'s capital starship at same system. Draw destiny. If destiny > 2, choose one pilot character aboard target to be forfeit = 0 for remainder of battle.','Blank.',NULL,'211_4'),(868,1588,'Dark','U1','A New Hope','•Lt. Shann Childsen','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/ltshannchildsen.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','1','2','3','Power +2 when at Detention Block Corridor or Detention Block Control Room. Also, power +2 when an opponent\'s alien is present (+3 if alien is a Wookiee, Talz or Ewok).','Demoted after a superior blamed him for a clerical error. Considered a bully by fellow officers. Fanatically supports the New Order doctrine of alien subjugation.',NULL,'2_96'),(869,1592,'Dark','R2','Premiere','Luke Seeker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lukeseeker.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploys for 1 Force to an unoccupied site. Deploys and moves like an undercover spy. When present with Luke of ability < 4 or pilot of ability < 3, choose one to be immediately lost (treat as an \'all cards\' situation). Seeker is also lost.','Military version of a \'remote.\' Programmed to stalk specific targets or secondary targets. Heat and light sensors track with fatal accuracy. Can stow away on starships.',NULL,'1_321'),(870,1599,'Dark','U1','Premiere','•Luke? Luuuuke!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/lukeluuuuke.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any Tatooine site. Target any Rebel. Target is power and forfeit -1 (-3 if target is Luke). If Rebel\'s forfeit reaches zero, Rebel is lost. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.','\'All right. I\'ll be right there, Aunt Beru.\'',NULL,'1_223'),(871,6501,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 5','•Luke Skywalker, The Emperor\'s Prize/Luke Skywalker, The Emperor\'s Prize','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Dark/large/lukeskywalkertheemperorsprizefront.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel'