hot under the collar.',NULL,'8_149'),(878,1623,'Dark','R','Endor','•Major Hewex','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/majorhewex.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','4','Adds 1 to total power for each of your troopers present at same site. When on Endor, subtracts 1 from total for Deactivate The Shield Generator and your troopers are forfeit +1 on Endor. When at Bunker, allows Imperials to deploy there as a \'react\'.','Leader of Navy detachment assigned to guard the Endor control bunker. Liaison between Imperial technicians and command staff.',NULL,'8_105'),(879,1625,'Dark','R','Endor','•Major Marquand','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/majormarquand.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','2','3','Adds 3 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots. When piloting a combat vehicle with Watts, may add one battle destiny and, if that vehicle has immunity to attrition, adds 2 to immunity.','Directed a counterattack against the Ewoks on Endor. Formerly crewed an AT-AT assigned to Devastator. Originally from Kessel.',NULL,'8_106'),(880,1626,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Major Mianda','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/majormianda.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Adds 3 to power of any TIE he pilots. Adds 2 to total weapon destiny of any TIE/ln he pilots.','Commander of a TIE squadron assigned to defend the second Death Star during construction. Hand picked pilots to serve with him.',NULL,'9_114'),(881,1630,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Major Rhymer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/majorrhymer.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Deploys -2 aboard Scimitar 1. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting a bomber making a Bombing Run, prevents opponent\'s characters at same site from using landspeed.'