o other. When armed with a lightsaber, his opponent\'s only option is usually that of escape.',NULL,'11_99'),(900,1659,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Maul\'s Sith Infiltrator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/maulssithinfiltrator.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Sith Infiltrator','6','4','3','6','May add 2 pilots. Maul deploys -3 aboard. While Maul piloting, immune to attrition and during your move phase, may lose 2 Force to \'cloak\' (does not participate in battles) until end of next turn.','One of Sienar Advanced Projects Laboratories\' prototype designs. Equipped with advanced weaponry and a full-effect stygium-based cloaking device for invisibility on command.',NULL,'12_182'),(901,6516,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Maul\'s Sith Infiltrator (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/maulssithinfiltratorai.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Sith Infiltrator','6','4','3','6','May add 2 pilots. Maul deploys -3 aboard. While Maul piloting, immune to attrition and during your move phase, may lose 2 Force to \'cloak\' (does not participate in battles) until end of next turn.','One of Sienar Advanced Projects Laboratories\' prototype designs. Equipped with advanced weaponry and a full-effect stygium-based cloaking device for invisibility on command.',NULL,'12_183'),(902,1672,'Dark','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','Mercenary Pilot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Dark/large/mercenarypilot.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots or drives. When driving a transport vehicle, adds one battle destiny. When piloting at a cloud sector, once per turn adds one battle destiny during battle at a related exterior site.','Smugglers. Candidates who resent authority often abandon Imperial academies to sell their piloting skills to criminals. Will work for any high pay