out an anguished, sorrowful, lamenting, mournful, angst-ridden, tormented, agonizing roar.',NULL,'3_108'),(929,1524,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Lieutenant Commander Ardan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/lieutenantcommanderardan.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','3','3','If at a site, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Immune to attrition < X, where X = the number of opponent\'s aliens present.','Commander of Executor bridge pit crews. Native of Brentaal. Participated in the subjugation of Ithor, Kashyyyk, Firro, Sinton and other planets populated by non-humans.',NULL,'4_103'),(930,5186,'Dark','PM','Virtual Set 8','•Lieutenant Dopheld Mitaka','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/lieutenantdopheldmitaka.gif?raw=true','Character','First Order','6','2','0','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When drawn for destiny, use 1 Force or this card is lost. During your deploy phase, may use 3 Force to relocate Kylo from here to same site as a Resistance character.','Blank.',NULL,'208_33'),(931,1711,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','Multi Troop Transport','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/multitrooptransport.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: MTT','3','2','1','3','May add 1 pilot and 7 passengers. Your battle droids may move from this site for free. Immune to attrition < 3.','Vehicle utilized by the Trade Federation droid army. 31 meters tall. Capable of holding, transporting, and deploying up to 112 battle droids. Enclosed.',NULL,'14_122'),(932,1522,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Lieutenant Cecius','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/lieutenantcecius.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','1','2','3','Deploys free to any Executor site. Power +3 when participating in a Besieged battle. During your control phase, may use 1 Force to search your Re