d.',NULL,'13_82'),(1010,1941,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Prince Xizor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/princexizor.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','5','4','6','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When in battle at a site, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise and total ability of 6 or more required for opponent to draw battle destiny here. Immune to attrition < 5 when Vader not here.','Falleen gangster and leader. Black Sun agent. Dark Prince of the Black Sun crime syndicate. Fortifies his personal defenses with information gathered by his agents.',NULL,'10_45'),(1011,1939,'Dark','R1','Premiere','••Presence Of The Force','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/presenceoftheforce.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any location to add one [Dark Side Force] and one [Light Side Force].','A location is affected by the history of the events which occur there. The Force \'...binds the galaxy together\' and has an ebb and flow.',NULL,'1_227'),(1012,5122,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 5','Point Man (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Dark/large/pointman.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Move a trooper as a \'react\' to a battle where you have a leader. OR During any draw phase, place a card from hand under your Used Pile to take any one card into hand from Force Pile; reshuffle.  LOST: During a battle at a site, cancel Keep Your Eyes Open.\"','In a military situation, on a regional or galactic scale, commands sometimes get misinterpreted. A local commander giving orders is far more reliable.',NULL,'205_20'),(1013,1922,'Dark','U1','Premiere','•Ponda Baba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/pondababa.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Power +3 when battling at same site as Dr. Evaz