r Aryon of Tatooine. Tailed Jabba and his thugs to Docking Bay 94 when they confronted Han Solo.',NULL,'1_191'),(1035,1952,'Dark','U2','Hoth','Probe Droid Laser','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/probedroidlaser.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your probe droid. May target an artillery weapon (use 5 as defense value), character or creature for free. Draw destiny. Artillery weapon lost if destiny > defense value. Character or creature hit if destiny > defense value.','Although a probe droid\'s primary defense is stealth, many models can be equipped with a laser cannon to enhance the droid\'s combat and sabotage capabilities.',NULL,'3_161'),(1036,4030,'Dark','C2','Virtual Set 0','•Probot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/probot.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','3','4','5','Draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Power +2 if with opponent\'s smuggler or Wookiee. During your move phase, may use 1 Force to \'break cover\' of opponent\'s Undercover spy at same site. Immune to attrition < 3.','Spy.',NULL,'200_88'),(1037,1972,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Quarren','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/quarren.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','2','If present at a non-shielded site, your Imperials may deploy there (regardless of location deployment restrictions). When at a planet site, Tactical Support, Imperial Reinforcements and Full Scale Alert are Used Interrupts.','Nicknamed \'squidheads.\' Quarren share their watery homeworld with the Mon Calamari. Betrayed their planet to the Empire. Dwell on the past. Rarely look to the future.',NULL,'6_120'),(1038,1955,'Dark','U1','A New Hope','•Program Trap','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/programtrap.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on an opponent\'s droid (except R2-D2 and C- 3PO), 1 on your droid. When either player draws a destiny matching the number of characters at same site, droid \'explodes\' (all characters present are lost).','Imperial slicers imbed a secret command in a droid\'s primary performance banks. A predetermined trigger causes a power overload, destroying the droid and anything nearby.',NULL,'2_124'),(1039,1969,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Put All Sections On Alert','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/putallsectionsonalert.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Target a Rebel at a Death Star (or Executor) site. For remainder of turn, target may not use its game text and may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny. (Immune to Sense.)  LOST: Retrieve into hand up to two cards with \'Death Star\' in title.\"','\'We have an emergency alert in detention block AA-twenty three.\'',NULL,'7_259'),(1040,5160,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 7','•Punishing One (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Dark/large/punishingone.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Corellian Jm 5000','3','2','2','4','May add 1 pilot. Corellians deploy -2 aboard. When deployed, may place an Admiral\'s Order in owner\'s Used Pile. While a Corellian piloting, power + 2 and immune to attrition < 3 (<5 if Dengar).','Old Corellian Engineering Corporation starfighter. Has outdated Class Three hyperdrive, but high sublight speed capability. Easy to maintain. Owned by Dengar.',NULL,'207_29'),(1041,1978,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Quick Reflexes','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/quickreflexes.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. During your draw phase, you make use 2 Force to search through your Lost Pile. Take one Hidden Weapons into hand or take any one blaster and immediately deploy it (for free).','Boba Fett\'s helmet has infrared capabilities, a motion tracking system, a macrobinocular viewer, an internal comlink and a broadband antenna. He doesn\'t miss a thing.',NULL,'6_146'),(1042,1961,'Dark','U','Dagobah','Proton Bombs','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/protonbombs.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a bomber: When present during a Force drain, may target a related interior site. Draw destiny. Site \'collapsed\' if destiny > 4. OR May fire in a Bombing Run battle. Draw destiny. All characters, starships and vehicles with that destiny number at same site are lost.','Proton-scattering energy warheads. Especially effective against rayand energy-shielded targets. Ineffective against particle deflector.',NULL,'4_179'),(1043,1985,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Qui-Gon\'s End','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/quigonsend.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a site where Maul just defeated Qui-Gon in lightsaber combat. Place Qui-Gon out of play. While Obi-Wan at this site, his lightsaber combat total is +2 and opponent loses 1 Force at the end of each of your turns. (Immune to Control.)','While Qui-Gon spent years maintaining peace, Maul was sharpening his combat skills. Those years of training came to fruition in one fateful moment.',NULL,'13_83'),(1044,1980,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Quietly Observing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/quietlyobserving.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Aurra Sing. While Aurra is alone at a site, your total ability here = 0. During your move phase, may lose Effect to target an opponent\'s lightsaber present. Draw destiny. If destiny > 3, Aurra may \'steal\' that lightsaber.','On her assignment to kill Sharad Hett, Aurra used her patience and cunning to help track down the Jedi Master.',NULL,'11_74'),(1045,6585,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 11','•Quietly Observing (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/quietlyobserving.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Aurra, Bossk, and Cad are destiny +2. Once per game, may reveal a unique (•) alien from hand or Reserve Deck (reshuffle); for remainder of game, that card is an assassin and ignores [Reflections II] and [Theed Palace] objective deployment restrictions. [Immune to Alter.]','On her assignment to kill Sharad Hett, Aurra used her patience and cunning to help track down the Jedi Master.',NULL,'211_10'),(1046,5156,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 7','•Quiggold','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Dark/large/quiggold.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','3','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. While piloting Meson Martinet, it is defense value +2. Forfeit +2 while present with Sidon. If your Rep is a pirate (or you did not deploy an Objective), Force drain +1 here.','Gabdorin pirate.',NULL,'207_22'),(1047,1989,'Dark','C2','Premiere','R1-G4 (Arone-Geefour)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/r1g4.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','1','3','When aboard a capital starship, adds 1 to power and hyperspeed, and that starship is immune to attrition < 3. Too large to go aboard a starfighter.','Typical of the old model astromechs still used on capital starships and large freighters. Has armored Mark II reactor drone shell. R1-G4 was abandoned after owner was captured.',NULL,'1_192'),(1048,1991,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•R2-A5 (Artoo-Ayfive)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/r2a5.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','1','2','3','When in battle aboard your capital starship at a system or sector, adds 1 to total attrition against opponent for each of your piloted TIEs present in that battle.','Combat communications astromech. Coordinates starfighter attack vectors. Broadcasts target acquisition data to gunnery systems.',NULL,'7_196'),(1049,1994,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','R2-Q2 (Artoo-Kyootoo)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/r2q2.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','2','3','While aboard any starfighter, adds 1 to power, maneuver and hyperspeed. When at a Scomp link during your draw phase, may use 1 Force to peek at top three cards of your Reserve Deck.','R2 units are known for expertise in computer uplinking. R2-Q2 spent several decades serving with an Imperial reconnaissance fleet in the Expansion Region.',NULL,'2_99'),(1050,1999,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•R3-T6 (Arthree-Teesix)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/r3t6.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','1','2','3','While aboard your capital starship, adds 1 to power and 2 to hyperspeed, and that starship is immune to attrition < 4. While at Death Star: Central Core, hyperspeed of Death Star system = 2.','R3 units have larger memory and more advanced circuitry than their R1 predecessors, allowing for more efficient astrogation plots. R3-T6 served on the Death Star.','R3-T2 (Arthree-Teetoo)','2_100'),(1051,2001,'Dark','C2','Premiere','R4-M9 (Arfour-Emmnine)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/r4m9.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','1','3','While aboard a non-creature vehicle, adds 1 to power, maneuver and landspeed. May drive transport vehicles.','Typical multiple-use droid. Controls and repairs vehicles and computers. R4-M9 was once used by the Empire to pull data from Tantive IV\'s computer banks.','R4-E1 (Arfour-Eeone)','1_193'),(1052,2002,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','R5-A2 (Arfive-Aytoo)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/r5a2.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','2','3','While aboard any starship, adds 1 to power and maneuver. During your control phase, if aboard your starship damaged by an ion cannon, restores armor/maneuver and hyperspeed.','Seldom used for navigation purposes, R5 units are known for their ability to perform hull maintenance and repair damage caused by ionization.','R5-D4 (Arfive-Defour)','2_101'),(1053,2008,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Rachalt Hyst','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/rachalthyst.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. During a battle involving Rachalt, whenever opponent draws an Interrupt for destiny may use 2 Force to cause that Interrupt to be lost. While armed with a weapon at a site, Force drain +1 here.','Strange female Snivvian who frequents the cantina daily. Betrayed her loved ones, who then left her on Tatooine to die. Everything she\'s ever cared about is now gone or dead.',NULL,'11_61'),(1054,2009,'Dark','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','Racing Skiff','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Dark/large/racingskiff.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','4','1','2','3','May deploy with a driver (must be Barada, Klaatu, or a non-unique alien) as a \'react\'. May add 1 driver and 3 passengers. May move as a \'react\'. If lost, any characters aboard may \'jump off\' (disembark).','Barada and Klaatu strip down and rebuild old skiffs to race on the Dune Sea. Jabba allows the practice to continue for now.','Racing Skiff','112_18'),(1055,2013,'Dark','U','Dagobah','•Raithal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/raithal.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy, opponent\'s Raithal game text is canceled.',NULL,'Raithal','4_164'),(1056,2015,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Raithal Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/raithaloperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','2','While at a Raithal site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your gambler or tax collector is on Raithal) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Raithal from Reserve Deck- reshuffle.','Opportunists work with corrupt governments and Raithal casino operators. Keep the Empire informed of local Alliance activity, for a price.',NULL,'7_197'),(1057,2016,'Dark','C1','A New Hope','•Ralltiir','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/ralltiir.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Tantive IV is power +1 here.',NULL,'Ralltiir','2_148'),(1058,6589,'Dark','R','Special Edition','Ralltiir Operations / In The Hands Of The Empire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/ralltiiroperations.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Ralltiir Operations:Deploy Ralltiir system.{While} this side up, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy from Reserve Deck to Ralltiir one site or non-unique Imperial; reshuffle. At Ralltiir locations, each Rebel is deploy +2.{Flip} this card if Imperials control at least three Ralltiir sites and opponent controls no Ralltiir locations.{Place} out of play if Ralltiir is \'blown away.\'In The Hands Of The Empire:{While} this side up, opponent\'s Force drains are -1. At Ralltiir locations, each Rebel is deploy +2. At all locations, add X to your total battle destiny, where X = number of Ralltiir locations your Imperials occupy. Once during each of your control phases, you may use 2 Force to take any one card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.{Flip} this card if opponent controls at least two Ralltiir locations.{Place} out of play if Ralltiir is \'blown away.',NULL,NULL,'7_300'),(1059,6590,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 10','Ralltiir Operations / In The Hands Of The Empire (V','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Dark/large/ralltiiroperations.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy Ralltiir system.{For} remainder of game, spaceport sites are immune to Always Thinking With Your Stomach, He Hasn\'t Come Back Yet and Ounee Ta. Your Force generation is +1 at each Ralltiir location. {While} this side up, once per turn, may deploy a site (or non-unique Imperial) to Ralltiir from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.{Flip} this card if Imperials control at least three Ralltiir sites and opponent controls no Ralltiir locations.{While} this side up, opponent\'s Force drains are -1 at their locations. Your total battle destiny is +X, where X = number of Ralltiir locations your Imperials occupy. {Flip} this card if opponent controls at least two Ralltiir locations.',NULL,NULL,'210_42'),(1060,2021,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','Rancor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/rancor.gif?raw=true','Creature','Gigantic Predator','1','8','6','0','* Ferocity = 8 + destiny. Habitat: Rancor Pit and exterior planet sites. Deploys only to the rancor pit or to where Malakili is the only character. Moves towards another Rancor whenever possible.','Indigenous to Dathomir, but found on several dozen worlds throughout the galaxy. Vicious predator. Sometimes kept as pets by eccentrics and crime lords.',NULL,'6_139'),(1061,2025,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Rappertunie','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/rappertunie.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','2','2','Where present, adds X to Force opponent must use to initiate battle, where X = number of musicians present. May target one non-droid character resent in battle. Draw destiny. If destiny > defense balue, target is power = 0 this battle.','Shawda Ubb musician from Manpha. Plays growdi. Real name Rapotwanalantonee. When cornered in a fight, he can spit a paralyzing poison.',NULL,'7_198'),(1062,2028,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•Rayno Vaca','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/raynovaca.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','1','0','1','Your characters may move from here using their landspeed for free. During your control phase, may place Vaca in Used Pile to take Lana Dobreed into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Coruscant taxi driver who barely makes enough money to get by. Will try any trick in the book to get an extra credit from his customer.',NULL,'14_85'),(1063,2029,'Dark','U2','Premiere','Reactor Terminal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/reactorterminal.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your side of table. During your control phase, you may return any cards from your hand to the top of your Used Pile.','The Death Star has many terminals coupled to the main reactor for power distribution throughout the immense space station.','Traffic Control','1_228'),(1064,2034,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Rebel Base Occupation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/rebelbaseoccupation.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Rebel Base system if you occupy at least two related battleground sites. During each of your control phases, opponent loses 1 Force for each related battleground sit you occupy. Canceled if opponent controls this system. (Immune to Alter.)','\'General, prepare your troops for a surface attack.\'',NULL,'7_237'),(1065,2077,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Ree-Yees','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/reeyees.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','3','Thrice per battle at same site, if you just drew a battle destiny of 3, may use 3 Force to add 3 to that destiny.','Gran convicted of murder. Exiled from his homeworld. Smuggler and bounty hunter. Slowly going insane. Fond of making things explode. Plotting to kill Jabba.',NULL,'6_121'),(1066,6596,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 11','•Ree-Yees (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/reeyees.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','3','Non-[Maintenance] bounty hunters here are immune to Clash Of Sabers and Rebel Barrier. Whenever you draw a destiny of 3, may choose: activate 1 Force, draw bottom card of Used Pile, or place a card from hand on top of Used Pile.','Gran convicted of murder. Exiled from his homeworld. Smuggler and bounty hunter. Slowly going insane. Fond of making things explode. Plotting to kill Jabba.',NULL,'211_5'),(1067,2075,'Dark','U2','A New Hope','•Reegesk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/reegesk.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','3','Once during each of your control phases, may lose 1 Force to take one vehicle, droid, weapon or device from opponent\'s Lost Pile or Crash Site Memorial into hand to use as your own.','Ranat thief and scavenger from Aralia. Regularly trades with Jawas. Adept at pilfering items without alerting the owner. Willing to steal anything, even trash.',NULL,'2_102'),(1068,2079,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Release Your Anger','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/releaseyouranger.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle, you may do one of the following: Add one destiny to your total power only. OR if you have a character weapon present, select one opponent\'s character present to lose all immunity to attrition for remainder of battle.','\'Only your hatred can destroy me.\'','Dark Approach','5_150'),(1069,2080,'Dark','C','Special Edition','•Relentless Pursuit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/relentlesspursuit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your piloted starship armed with a starship weapon is in a battle, lose 1 Force to reduce the power of one opponent\'s starship in that battle to zero. OR Place one opponent\'s starship just \'hit\' in Lost Pile.','When tailed by a TIE fighter, Rebel pilots are often forced to focus on escaping the TIE\'s firing arc.','Power Pivot','7_260'),(1070,2081,'Dark','R','Endor','•Relentless Tracking','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/relentlesstracking.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s non-droid character at same or adjacent site as your scout. During each of your control phases, if your scout is at this site (and not Undercover), opponent loses 2 Force (or 3 Force if that scout is also a biker scout).','Biker scouts commonly work as a team to track enemies of the Empire. A pair of scouts on speeder bike is difficult to elude.',NULL,'8_130'),(1071,1880,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Overload','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/overload.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target any weapon (except a Gaderffii Stick or any Ewok weapon). Draw destiny. Weapon lost if destiny < weapon\'s destiny number. If destiny = 0, the character or starship carrying weapon is also lost.','Weapons like lightsabers, turbolasers and blasters run on powerful energy cells or generators. Occasionally, these cells overheat causing the weapon to unexpectedly explode.','Sabotage (V)','1_263'),(1072,1881,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Overseeing It Personally','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/overseeingitpersonally.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Emperor. While at a battleground planet site you control, at each related site where an Imperial is present, your Force drains are +1.','Though reluctant to leave Coruscant. Emperor Palpatine occasionally finds it necessary to personally put lagging Imperial operations back on schedule.',NULL,'9_130'),(1073,1865,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•OS-72-2 In Obsidian 2','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/os722inobsidian2.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','3','1','4','2','Deploy -1 and power +3 at a cloud sector. Permanent pilot is •OS-72-2, who provides ability of 2, adds 2 to power and, at a cloud sector, may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Piloted by Dodson Makraven, wingman of Cive Rashon. Experienced TIE pilot with many kills in atmospheric combat. Nicknamed \'Night Beast\' for his many curfew violations.',NULL,'7_306'),(1074,1864,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•OS-72-10','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/os7210.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if any TIE). When piloting a TIE at a cloud sector, adds one battle destiny and makes that TIE immune to attrition < 4 (< 6 if Obsidian 10).','Pilot of Obsidian 10. Has served aboard the Conquest, the Thunderflare and the Executor. Not interested in advancing his rank as it would remove him from the pilot\'s seat.',NULL,'7_194'),(1075,1863,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•OS-72-1 In Obsidian 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/os721inobsidian1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','2','2','5','3','Deploy -1 and power +3 at a cloud sector. Permanent pilot is •OS-72-1, who provides ability of 2, adds 2 to power and, at a cloud sector, may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Lead starfighter of Obsidian Squadron. Flown by Cive Rashon. Call sign \'Howlrunner.\' She served in an elite TIE squadron aboard the Star Destroyer Avenger.',NULL,'7_305'),(1076,1882,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Overwhelmed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/overwhelmed.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your deploy phase, target a system where your total power is more than double opponent\'s total power and opponent has no Jedi or starship weapon. Place all opponent\'s starships there (and cards on them) in owner\'s Used Pile.','When the Empire amasses its fleet, the only option for the Alliance is retreat.',NULL,'7_258'),(1077,1877,'Dark','C','Endor','•Outflank','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/outflank.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle, if you have weapons at at least 2 sites adjacent to that battle, add 3 to your total power and add one battle destiny. OR For remainder of turn, your biker scout at an exterior site is power +1 and adds 1 to each of that character\'s weapon destiny draws.','Commander Igar\'s defense of Endor called for the use of speeder bikes to harass any attacking Rebels.','Firefight','8_150'),(1078,1876,'Dark','R','Special Edition','Outer Rim Scout','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/outerrimscout.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','2','3','Deploy -1 to your [Independent Starship] starship. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting a [Independent Starship] starship, instead adds 3 to power and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Suspends Asteroid Sanctuary at related sector.','Smugglers and scouts employed by the ISB. Search the far reaches of the galaxy for Rebel activity and habitable worlds. Know all the smugglers\' best hiding places.',NULL,'7_195'),(1079,1885,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•OWO-1 With Backup','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/owo1withbackup.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','1','6','6','5','Requires +2 Force to use Landspeed. Power +1 for each opponent\'s Jedi present. While with a battledroid at a site, draws two battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Opponent\'s Force drains are -1 at adjacent sites.','Trade Federation battle droid leader assigned to take a squad and destroy what was left of the Jedi ambassadors. His mission went unaccomplished.',NULL,'14_84'),(1080,5120,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 5','•Overseeing It Personally (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Dark/large/overseeingitpersonally.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your leader. Opponent may not cancel or reduce Force drains at same battleground. If on Emperor, may place Effect in Lost Pile to retrieve an Imperial leader.','Though reluctant to leave Coruscant. Emperor Palpatine occasionally finds it necessary to personally put lagging Imperial operations back on schedule.','Leia Of Alderaan (V)','205_18'),(1081,1868,'Dark','U','Coruscant','•Our Blockade Is Perfectly Legal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/ourblockadeisperfectlylegal.gif?raw=true','Effect','Political','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If no senator here, you may place a senator here from hand to add 3 to any battle destiny just drawn. If a blockade agenda here, during your turn you may cancel a \'react\' or an attempt by opponent to move away from a battle.','Until it could be proven otherwise, the Trade Federation maintained that they were pursuing a legal means of protesting the taxation of outlying trade routes.',NULL,'12_138'),(1082,1869,'Dark','C2','Hoth','Our First Catch Of The Day','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/ourfirstcatchoftheday.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add 2 to a tractor beam destiny draw. OR Cancel The First Transport Is Away! or Hyper Escape.','Sir, Rebel ships are coming into our sector.\'',NULL,'3_131'),(1083,1886,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•P-59','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/p59.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','4','4','4','Permanent weapon is Twin Cannons (may target a character or vehicle for free; draw destiny; if destiny +1 > defense value, target hit and opponent loses 2 Force). Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Immune to attrition < 4.','Trade Federation destroyer droid squad leader. Charged with removing the threat posed by Qui-Gon Jinn and Obi-Wan Kenobi. Found the Jedi hard to kill, but forced their retreat.',NULL,'12_114'),(1084,1908,'Dark','C','Tatooine','Pit Droid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/pitdroid.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','1','2','While at Podracer Bay, once during each of your control phases may lose 1 Force to target your Podracer. Place target\'s top race destiny in Lost Pile, and draw one race destiny. During any control phase may use 1 Force to \'repair\' your Podracer.','Manufactured by Serv-O-Droid on Cyrillia. Collapses into a compact form when hit on the nose.',NULL,'11_60'),(1085,1901,'Dark','R','Endor','•Perimeter Patrol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/perimeterpatrol.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Bunker. While you control Bunker, each time opponent deploys a vehicle, starship or Rebel to an Endor site (except Rebel Landing Site), that card cannot move or battle for remainder of turn and opponent must lose 1 Force. (Immune to Alter.)','Heavy Imperial patrols on Endor forced the Rebels to deploy covertly. The required stealth measures created many complications.',NULL,'8_128'),(1086,1905,'Dark','U','Endor','•Pinned Down','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/pinneddown.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Opponent may not \'react\' away from a battle where you have a blaster present. Also, if you have a blaster present when opponent cancels a battle, draw destiny, opponent loses Force equal to destiny draw. (Immune to Alter.)','Heavy blaster fire hampered Han\'s attempts to open the Back Door to the Endor control bunker.',NULL,'8_129'),(1087,1912,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Planetary Subjugation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/planetarysubjugation.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. You may add up to 5 to destiny of each TIE Bomber drawn for weapon or battle destiny. You may add 1 to Proton Bomb weapon destiny draws. Asteroid Sanctuary is canceled unless present with opponent\'s starship. (Immune to Alter.)','The Empire crushes resistance with massive orbital bombardment. The coordinated attack of a TIE bomber wing reduces a planet\'s surface to rubble.',NULL,'7_235'),(1088,1887,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•P-60','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/p60.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','3','4','4','Permanent weapon is Twin Cannons (may target a character or vehicle for free; draw destiny; if destiny +2 > defense value, target hit and opponent loses 1 Force). While with a destroyer droid at a site, adds one battle destiny.','Trade Federation droideka led by unit commander P-59. Assisted in the attempt to keep the Jedi ambassadors from breaching the battleship\'s command center.',NULL,'12_115'),(1089,1896,'Dark','C','Coruscant','•Passel Argente','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/passelargente.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','1','3','3','Agendas: ambition, taxation. While in a senate majority, opponent\'s non-unique starships and non-unique vehicles are each deploy +2 and power -1. Argente is politics +X, where X = number of opponent\'s senators at same site.','A senator known for his ability to deflect blame. It is rumored that Argente receives kickbacks from a few corporations to thwart other companies\' developments.',NULL,'12_116'),(1090,1909,'Dark','C','Endor','•Pitiful Little Band','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/pitifullittleband.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your scout is battling opponent\'s scout, spy or operative, add one battle destiny. OR If you have a spy or scout at Bunker or any prison, place out of play one captured spy of ability < 3 or captured operative there. Retrieve Force equal to double that captive\'s forfeit.','The Emperor\'s defense of the forest moon of Endor appeared to work with devastating effectiveness.',NULL,'8_151'),(1091,1899,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Patrol Craft','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/patrolcraft.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','4','1','1','3','Power +1 at Coruscant or Bespin. May add 1 driver and 1 passenger. May deploy or move as a \'react.\' At cloud sectors, may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter.','Small, enclosed patrol fighter used on many worlds to help maintain order. A cheaper alternative to the Bespin Motors cloud car.','Patrol Craft','7_315'),(1092,1907,'Dark','U','Tatooine','•Pit Crews','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/pitcrews.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to reveal opponent\'s hand. All cards opponent has 3 or more of in hand are lost. OR Use 1 Force to \'repair\' your Podracer. OR Target a Podracer. Draw destiny. If destiny > Podracer\'s destiny number, target Podracer is \'damaged.\'','Pit droids are used by Podracer pilots to assist in the maintenance of their racer. While a high standard is usually maintained, sometimes things can get out of hand.',NULL,'11_84'),(1093,1904,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Physical Choke','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/physicalchoke.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cause one Rebel Trooper to be immediately lost. OR If a Dark Jedi is present at a battle you have just won, use 1 Force to attempt to choke any opposing character present. Draw destiny. If destiny > target\'s ability, target is lost.','Darth Vader often used physical means of \'persuasion\' to get information. Captain Antilles of Tantive IV chose to die rather than reveal the location of the stolen Death Star plans.',NULL,'1_264'),(1094,2123,'Dark','C','Dagobah','<>Rogue Asteroid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/rogueasteroid.gif?raw=true','Effect','Mobile','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an asteroid sector and specify starting direction. Every move phase, moves to next adjacent asteroid sector (reversing direction as necessary). Where present, adds 2 to asteroid destiny. May be targeted by starship weapons (defense value = 3).','\'We\'re gonna get pulverized if we stay out here much longer.\'','Rogue Asteroid','4_130'),(1095,6605,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Rolling, Rolling, Rolling','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/rollingrollingrolling.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take any non-unique destroyer droid into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR During your deploy phase, relocate your destroyer droid to an adjacent site.','The Colicoids from Colla IV modeled destroyer droids after themselves in that they can roll up into a ball and move swiftly into a conflict.',NULL,'14_105'),(1096,2131,'Dark','C','Special Edition','Ronto','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/ronto.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Creature','5','3','2','3','May add 2 \'riders\' (passengers). Ability = 1/4. When \'ridden\' by a Jawa, moves for free and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Beast of burden often used by Jawas. Excellent sense of smell. Poor vision. Slow moving. Tough hide. Easily startled by fast-moving speeders.','Ronto','7_316'),(1097,2133,'Dark','C','Death Star II','•Royal Escort','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/royalescort.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Each of your non-unique troopers on Endor or Death Star II is forfeit +1. When opponent just used a weapon to target your character aboard a piloted vehicle, that character may use that vehicle\'s defense value.','When away from the Imperial Palace on Coruscant, the Emperor is protected by legions of troops. Typically this force includes soldiers trained to fight in local environment.',NULL,'9_131'),(1098,2136,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•RR\'uruurrr','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/rruruurrr.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','2','Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +3 while armed with a Gaderffi Stick. Where present, each of your banthas is power and forfeit +2 unless a Weequay is at a related site. When \'riding\' a bantha, adds one battle destiny.','Tusken Raider who tends to the banthas used by URoRRuR\'R\'R\'s tribe. Expert in wielding a gaffi stick. Attacked Luke Skywalker in the Jundland Wastes.',NULL,'7_199'),(1099,2134,'Dark','C','Death Star II','Royal Guard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/royalguard.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','3','2','3','Deploys only on Coruscant or to Emperor\'s site (or related site). When armed with a Force pike and defending a battle, adds one battle destiny. Emperor may not be targeted by weapons unless all Royal Guards present with Emperor are \'hit\'.','Member of Emperor\'s Royal Guard. Completely subservient. Royal Guards must fight one of their own to the death in order to complete their training.',NULL,'9_119'),(1100,4031,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 0','•R\'tic H\'weei','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/rtichweei.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Once per game, may take one Jawa Blaster or a card with \'sandcrawler\' in title or gametext into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per turn, if present at a Tatooine battleground and there is more than 1 Force in opponent\'s Force Pile, you may use 1 Force in opponent\'s Force Pile.','Jawa',NULL,'200_89'),(1101,2139,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Rune Haako','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/runehaako.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','2','3','6','While in battle, may choose one number. If next card opponent draws for destiny this battle has a printed destiny number matching this choice, that destiny is reduced to zero. If you just initiated a battle at same or adjacent site, retrieve 1 Force.','Trade Federation settlement officer serving as legal council to Viceroy Gunray. Reputed to have one of the sharpest legal minds in all of the Republic. Neimoidian.',NULL,'12_117'),(1102,2140,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Rune Haako, Legal Counsel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/runehaakolegalcounsel.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','2','3','4','While at Theed Palce Throne Room, your attrition against opponent in battles at same and related Naboo sites is +X, where X = number of battle droids present at that site. While with a battle droid, Haako is power and defense value +2.','The Trade Federation\'s only Neimoidian leader to have ever encountered a Jedi Knight. Assumed Daultay Dofine\'s responsibilities after Dofine questioned their Sith Lord\'s plans.',NULL,'14_86'),(1103,6608,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•Rune Haako, Legal Counsel (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/runehaakolegalcounselai.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','2','3','4','While at Theed Palce Throne Room, your attrition against opponent in battles at same and related Naboo sites is +X, where X = number of battle droids present at that site. While with a battle droid, Haako is power and defense value +2.','The Trade Federation\'s only Neimoidian leader to have ever encountered a Jedi Knight. Assumed Daultay Dofine\'s responsibilities after Dofine questioned their Sith Lord\'s plans.',NULL,'14_87'),(1104,2145,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Rystall','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/rystall.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Power and forfeit +2 at a Coruscant site. May retrieve 1 Force each time your deploy a musician to same site. Once during each of your turns, may use 1 Force to \'charm\' one male of ability < 3 present- male is forfeit = 0 for remainder of turn.','Musician. Raised by Ortolans. Grew up on the streets of Coruscant. Rescued from the Black Sun crime cartel by Lando Calrissian.',NULL,'7_200'),(1105,2147,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Saber 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/saber1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Interceptor','3','3','2','4','May add 1 pilot. Fel deploys -1 aboard. When firing SFS L-s9.3 Laser Cannons, may use 1 Force to make X = 3. Immune to attrition < 5 when Fel piloting.','TIE interceptor serial number 000004. Assigned to Baron Soontir Fel of the fighting 181st. Bears the Saber Squadron bloodstripe, representing a minimum of 10 kills.',NULL,'9_162'),(1106,2148,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Saber 2','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/saber2.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Interceptor','3','3','2','3','May add 1 pilot. When Phennir piloting, immune to attrition < 4 and adds 1 to forfeit of each other Saber Squadron pilot in same battle.','TIE interceptor flown by Major Phennir. Assigned to protect Avenger at the Battle of Endor. Responsible for the logistics of Saber Squadron.',NULL,'9_163'),(1107,2149,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Saber 3','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/saber3.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Interceptor','3','3','1','3','May add 1 pilot. Cannons are deploy -2 aboard. Immune to attrition < 3 when DS-181-3 piloting.','TIE interceptor assigned to fly on the wing of Baron Fel. Often ordered to remain at a distance from Fel to give the Baron maneuvering room during combat.',NULL,'9_164'),(1108,2150,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Saber 4','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/saber4.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Interceptor','3','3','2','3','May deploy with a pilot as a \'react\' to a battle where you have a TIE (for free if TIE is in Saber Squadron). May add 1 pilot. Immune to attrition < 4 when DS-181-4 piloting.','TIE interceptor often assigned to fly in a reserve position during battle. The bloodstripe of the 181st denotes the 10 kills scored by DS-181-4.',NULL,'9_165'),(1109,2154,'Dark','F','Special Edition','•Sacrifice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sacrifice.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Reduce your battle damage by 5 by losing from hand a starship, vehicle or character. OR If your character\'s forfeit was just reduced to 0, restore it to normal. (Immune to Sense.)','Jabba\'s minions could be expected to be sacrificed to save the Hutt, to destroy one of the Hutts enemies or to provide the Hutt and his minions with a good laugh.','First Aid','7_261'),(1110,2159,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Salacious Crumb','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/salaciouscrumb.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','1','3','Opponent may initiate battle at same site for free. At same or adjacent site, whenever an opponent draws a card for battle destiny, if it is: Even, opponent must use 1 Force (if possible); Odd, destiny card is lost. (AH-hahahahaha!)','Male Kowakian. Prankster. Humiliates others for Jabba\'s amusement. His life depends on making Jabba laugh at least once per day.',NULL,'6_122'),(1111,2160,'Dark','R2','Premiere','Sandcrawler','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/sandcrawler.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','2','3','3','5','Deploys only to a Tatooine site. May add 1 driver and 7 passengers. Cannot move to mobile sites. Adds 1 to forfeit of each Jawa at same exterior site.','Warren-like enclosed homes for Jawa tribes. Protect against Tusken Raiders, krayt dragons, etc. 36 meters longs, 17 meters tall. Originally mining vehicles. No two look alike.','Sandcrawler','1_309'),(1112,2164,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•••Sandcrawler: Droid Junkheap','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/sandcrawlerdroidjunkheap.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your characters may enter/exit here for 1 Force each. \'Nighttime conditions\' here.',NULL,'Sandcrawler: Loading Bay','2_149'),(1113,2166,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Sando Aqua Monster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/sandoaquamonster.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Cancels Colo Claw Fish. While no card here, you may draw destiny and place it face-up here. If you are about to draw a card for weapon or battle destiny, you may instead use card here, then place it in Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','Huge creature that is feline in nature and moves on its hind legs. Slow movement makes it difficult for the monster to feed but whenever a confrontation arises it always wins.','Sando Aqua Monster','13_85'),(1114,2169,'Dark','F','Special Edition','Sandtrooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sandtrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Deploys only to Tatooine or any desert. Immune to Sandwhirl. Power -1 when not on Tatooine.','Equipped for harsh, high-temperature environments. Primarily assigned to search-and-destroy missions, but sometimes beaks up local disputes or recover stolen droids.',NULL,'7_201'),(1115,2170,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','<>Sandwhirl','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/sandwhirl.gif?raw=true','Effect','Mobile','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Desert. Specify starting direction. All characters (except Jawas and Tusken Raiders) present at same non-interior site are missing. During your control phase, moves to next adjacent site (reversing directions as necessary), but lost if at an interior site.','Called \'Teeth Of The Wind\' by Tusken Raiders. Only those familiar with Tatooine\'s vast deserts can navigate successfully during its furious onslaught.','Sandwhirl','6_148'),(1116,2172,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Sarlacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sarlacc.gif?raw=true','Creature','Ancient Desert','2','*','4','0','* Ferocity = 4 + destiny. Habitat: Great Pit Of Carkoon. If Sarlacc eats a captive, may retrieve 1 Force for each of your aliens here. Anything eaten by Sarlacc is placed out of play.','Very patient predator in the Dune Sea. Tentacles can grab prey up to four meters away. Digests victims for 1000 years. Often fed prisoners by Jabba the Hutt.',NULL,'7_214'),(1117,5157,'Dark','F','Virtual Set 7','Savage Opress','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Dark/large/savageopress.gif?raw=true','Character','Sith','1','8','8','5','Deploys -1 for each other Sith character here (limit - 4). Once per game, may exchange a card in hand with a Sith character in Lost Pile. Immune to attrition < 3.','Dathomirian assassin.',NULL,'207_23'),(1118,2176,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Scanning Crew','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/scanningcrew.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to glance at the cards in the opponent\'s hand for 10 seconds. You may move any one Rebel you find there to the top of opponent\'s Used Pile.','Imperials use sensitive equipment to search captured ships for shielded compartments. Scanning crew BT-445 planned to search the Millennium Falcon.',NULL,'1_266'),(1119,2177,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Scimitar 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/scimitar1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SA','2','1','2','4','May add 1 pilot. Power +3 during a Bombing Run battle. When proton bombs aboard \'collapse\' a site, opponent loses 1 Force for each rebel just lost.','Scimitar bombing group TIE bomber. Equipped with advanced targeting system to increase damage during planetary bombardment.',NULL,'9_166'),(1120,2178,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Scimitar 2','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/scimitar2.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SA','2','1','2','4','May add 1 pilot. Power +3 during a Bombing Run battle. Once per game, you may deploy one Proton Bombs from Reserve Deck on this starfighter; reshuffle.','TIE bomber repaired after being struck by an asteroid in the Anoat system. Stationed aboard second Death Star battle station.',NULL,'9_167'),(1121,2179,'Dark','C','Death Star II','•••Scimitar Squadron TIE','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/scimitarsquadrontie.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SA','2','1','2','4','Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. Power +3 during a Bombing Run battle. Cumulatively adds 1 to total weapon destiny of your other TIE/sa present firing Concussion Missiles.','Bombers typically assigned to attack secondary targets and provide cover during bombing runs. Targeting systems calibrated to track fast-moving Rebel starfighters.',NULL,'9_168'),(1122,2181,'Dark','C','Endor','Scout Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/scoutblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your biker scout, or use 2 Force to deploy on your other warrior. May deploy as a \'react\'. May target a character or creature using 1 Force (for free if fired by your spy or scout). Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value.','Hold-out blaster utilized by Imperial scouts. Small size limits range, but concealability is often an asset.',NULL,'8_179'),(1123,2182,'Dark','C','Endor','•Scout Recon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/scoutrecon.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add 1 to landspeed of your scout at an exterior planet site for remainder of turn. OR If Igar is with Grond or Dyer in battle, draw one destiny and subtract if from opponent\'s attrition against you.','Familiarity with native terrain is essential to a scout garrison. Imperial command can also put this type of information to effective use.',NULL,'8_152'),(1124,2187,'Dark','R2','Hoth','Scruffy-Looking Nerf Herder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/scruffylookingnerfherder.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Solo Han or Warrior\'s Courage or I Know.  LOST: If Han and Leia are in a battle together, draw two destiny. Subtract that amount from opponent\'s attrition and total power (cannot fall below zero).\"','\'But you didn\'t see us alone in the south passage. She expressed her true feelings for me.\' \'My...Why you stuck-up, half-witted, scruffy-looking NERF HERDER!\'',NULL,'3_133'),(1125,2188,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Scum And Villainy','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/scumandvillainy.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Audience Chamber. While all your ability on table is provided by aliens and independent starship pilots, your aliens and starships deploy -1 and you retrieve 2 Force whenever you initiate battle. (Immune to Alter if you control at least three Jabba\'s Palace sites.)','A relief in Nal Hutta sandstone. Hand-carved by slaves of the great Hutt artist Dreyba. Commissioned by Jabba to illustrate his vast influence. Titled \'Ne Ganna Dateel Jabba.\'',NULL,'6_149'),(1126,2190,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Scythe 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/scythe1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','4','1','2','3','May add 1 pilot. Once during each of your move phases, may fire one starship weapon aboard (\'hit\' targets are lost) and/or make an additional move. Immune to attrition < 4 when Mianda piloting.','TIE fighter garrisoned aboard second Death Star. Part of Scythe Squadron, a TIE group with upgraded SFS Pw702 maneuvering jets to increase performance in tight quarters.',NULL,'9_169'),(1127,2191,'Dark','U','Death Star II','•Scythe 3','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/scythe3.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','4','1','2','3','May add 1 pilot. Hebsly deploys -2 aboard. Once during each of your move phases, may fire one starship weapon aboard (\'hit\' targes are lost). Immune to attrition < 4 when Hebsly piloting.','Heavily modified TIE/ln. Cannons upgraded to destroy small asteroids while serving in Anoat system. P-w702 maneuvering jets added by Death Star technicians.',NULL,'9_170'),(1128,2192,'Dark','C','Death Star II','•••Scythe Squadron TIE','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/scythesquadrontie.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','4','1','4','3','Deploy -2 to Death Star II or Endor. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2 add adds 1 to power and maneuver.','Scythe Squadron TIE fighters are modified TIE/lns assigned to defend the second Death Star during construction. Their pilots fly frequent training missions within the Death Star.',NULL,'9_171'),(1129,2193,'Dark','U','Endor','•Search And Destroy','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/searchanddestroy.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Biker scouts are forfeit +1. During every draw phase, unless opponent\'s character of destiny < 4 occupies a battleground site, opponent loses 1 Force. Effect canceled unless your characters of destiny < 4 occupy two battleground sites.','Imperial troops searched the forests of Endor to flush the Rebels out.','I Hope She\'s All Right','8_131'),(1130,2194,'Dark','R','Tatooine','•Sebulba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/sebulba.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','5','Once per battle may use 1 Force to target opponent\'s character of ability < 3 at same site; target is power -3 for remainder of turn. If present with Jar Jar, during your control phase may use 3 Force to place Jar Jar out of play.','Bad tempered Dug from Pixelito. He was about to turn Jar Jar into orange goo, until Anakin intervened.',NULL,'11_62'),(1131,6620,'Dark','R','Tatooine','•Sebulba (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/sebulbaai.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','5','Once per battle may use 1 Force to target opponent\'s character of ability < 3 at same site; target is power -3 for remainder of turn. If present with Jar Jar, during your control phase may use 3 Force to place Jar Jar out of play.','Bad tempered Dug from Pixelito. He was about to turn Jar Jar into orange goo, until Anakin intervened.',NULL,'11_63'),(1132,6622,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 11','•Sebulba (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/sebulba.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys free to Mos Espa. While on Tatooine, attrition against opponent is +1 here and your Force generation is +1. When You\'re A Slave? places a card in your Used Pile, may draw top card of your Reserve Deck.','Bad tempered Dug from Pixelito. He was about to turn Jar Jar into orange goo, until Anakin intervened.',NULL,'211_6'),(1133,6624,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 11','•Sebulba (V) (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/sebulbaai.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','3','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys free to Mos Espa. While on Tatooine, attrition against opponent is +1 here and your Force generation is +1. When You\'re A Slave? places a card in your Used Pile, may draw top card of your Reserve Deck.','Bad tempered Dug from Pixelito. He was about to turn Jar Jar into orange goo, until Anakin intervened.',NULL,'211_61'),(1134,2195,'Dark','R','Tatooine','•Sebulba\'s Podracer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/sebulbaspodracer.gif?raw=true','Podracer',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Adds 3 to each of your race destinies here. If you and your opponent have the same race total, may use 2 Force. Opponent draws no race destiny for remainder of turn (may only be used once for any race total).','Some hidden modifications mean Sebulba\'s Podracer doesn\'t conform to race specifications. The duplicitous Dug has equipped it with a flame emitter that can fry other Podracers.',NULL,'11_97'),(1135,2197,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Secret Plans','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/secretplans.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. If opponent is about to retrieve X Force, opponent must first use X Force or that retrieval is canceled. (X is equal to the full amount of Force allowed to be retrieved, regardless of the number of cards in opponent\'s Lost Pile.)','Imperial computer systems are equipped with complex algorithms designed to prevent access by unauthorized users.','Aim High - Defensive Shield','13_86'),(1136,2196,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Secret Plans','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/secretplans.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Once during each of your control phases, may take one Shocking Revelation into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Also, whenever opponent retrieves X cards, opponent must first use X Force or that retrieval is canceled. (Immune to Alter.)','Imperial computer systems are equipped with complex algorithms designed to prevent access by unauthorized users.','Aim High','7_240'),(1137,2200,'Dark','C','Coruscant','Security Battle Droid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/securitybattledroid.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','2','2','3','Opponent\'s characters require +1 Force to move from same site using their landspeed. While with another battle droid at a site, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.','Manufactured by the Baktoid Combat Automata, battle droids are used by the Trade Federation throughout the galaxy in order to secure and protect sites of strategic importance.',NULL,'12_118'),(1138,2202,'Dark','R','Endor','•Security Precautions','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/securityprecautions.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a location. Your Force generation is +1 here. Also, if you \'probe\' opponent\'s \'Hidden Base\' system, opponent loses X Force, where X = 15 - number of systems on table. You take no battle damage where you have a \'probe\' card. (Immune to Alter.)','\'I think I got it.\'',NULL,'8_132'),(1139,5162,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 7','•Security Precautions (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Dark/large/securityprecautions.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a location. Your Force generation is +1 here. Once per game, you may restore a just \'hit\' starship to normal. Unless opponent occupies a battleground site, Corellian Engineering Corporation is suspended. (Immune to Alter.)','\'I think I got it.\'',NULL,'207_26'),(1140,2209,'Dark','U1','Hoth','Self-Destruct Mechanism','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/selfdestructmechanism.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Lose a droid to cancel all attrition against you at same site this turn. OR Re-target an opponent\'s weapon to one of your droids at same site. If droid is \'hit\', use original target\'s forfeit number.','\'\'Fraid there\'s not much left...I didn\'t hit it that hard. It musta had a self-destruct.\'','This Is All Your Fault','3_134'),(1141,2211,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','Senate Hovercam','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/senatehovercam.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Galactic Senate. While you have a senate majority, your Force generation here is +3, and your Force generation at Coruscant locations is immune to This Place Can Be A Little Rough. Place Effect in Lost Pile if opponent controls this location.','Used to monitor and record events inside the Galactic Senate. By law, hovercams are required to be present in every Senate session, a law Senator Palpatine opposed.','Senate Hovercam','14_100'),(1142,2214,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Send A Detachment Down','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/sendadetachmentdown.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on any Tatooine site (except docking bay). Target any trooper on Death Star. When target reaches Utinni Effect, attrition +1 against opponent in all Tatooine battles as long as target remains at same site as Utinni Effect.','Vader sent Imperial stormtroopers to the surface of Tatooine in search of the stolen Death Star plans. \'There\'ll be no one to stop us this time.\'',NULL,'1_229'),(1143,2220,'Dark','U','Coruscant','Sense','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/sense.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just played an Interrupt (or just initiated a \'react\'), target one of your characters on table. Draw destiny. If destiny < ability of target, that Interrupt (or \'react\') is canceled. OR Cancel Alter.','A Sith Lord can use the Force to reach out and find what he seeks.','Sense (EP1)','12_157'),(1144,2216,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Sense','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/sense.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel one Interrupt (or one \'react\') by drawing a destiny < ability of your highest-ability character on table. OR Cancel one Alter card just played.','\'I sense something. A presence I\'ve not felt since...\'','Sense','1_267'),(1145,2219,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','Sense & Uncertain Is The Future','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/sense&uncertainisthefuture.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Target your highest-ability character and one just-played Interrupt. Draw destiny. If destiny < ability of target character, cancel target Interrupt.  LOST: Use 3 Force. Each player places hand onto Reserve Deck (if possible), then places Used Pile onto Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Each player then draws cards from Reserve Deck equal to the number of cards just placed from hand onto Reserve Deck (if any).\"',NULL,'Sense & Recoil In Fear','10_46'),(1146,2223,'Dark','F','Special Edition','Sentinel-Class Landing Craft','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sentinelclasslandingcraft.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Sentinel-Class Landing Craft','2','3','3','4','May add 1 pilot, 4 passengers and 2 speeder bikes. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Any starship cannon may deploy here. Takes off and lands for free.','Modified light freighter. Length 20 meters. Heavily armored for a landing craft. Has ion cannon mounts. Often carries speeder bikes for reconnaissance purposes.',NULL,'7_307'),(1147,2224,'Dark','R','Endor','•Sergeant Barich','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/sergeantbarich.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (or 3 to any speeder bike). When in a battle with your other biker scout, may draw one battle destiny and subtract that amount from opponent\'s attrition and total power.','Wakeelmui native. Former employee of Sienar Fleet Systems missile division. Stormtrooper biker scout with dreams of transferring to 181st Imperial Fighter Group.',NULL,'8_111'),(1148,2229,'Dark','U','Endor','•Sergeant Elsek','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/sergeantelsek.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','1','1','3','Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots. When in battle with Avarik, adds 2 to your total battle destiny. When forfeited at same site as your other biker scout, also satisfies all remaining attrition and battle damage against you.','Stormtrooper biker scout. Kuat native. Avarik\'s partner since graduation from Corulag academy. Often forced to cover for partner\'s rash decisions.',NULL,'8_112'),(1149,2231,'Dark','R','Endor','•Sergeant Irol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/sergeantirol.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','2','3','May deploy -1 as a \'react\' to any forest, jungle or exterior Endor site. Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots. When vehicle he drives or pilots is targeted by High-speed Tactics or Get Alongside That One, adds 2 to your destiny draw.','Cocky stormtrooper from an Outer Rim forest planet. Confident biker scout and hunter. Relies on superior balance and strength to operate his speeder bike.',NULL,'8_113'),(1150,2233,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Sergeant Major Bursk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sergeantmajorbursk.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','3','2','3','When in a battle on Hoth, immune to attrition < 3 and adds 2 to attrition against opponent. Your snowtroopers are deploy -1 to same Hoth site. Power -1 when not on Hoth.','Leader of most brutal snowtrooper plotoon in the battle of Hoth. Cunning planner. Coordinates attacks and manages troop movements.',NULL,'7_202'),(1151,2235,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Sergeant Major Enfield','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sergeantmajorenfield.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','3','When in a battle with another Death Star trooper, adds one battle destiny. Your Death Star troopers are deploy -1 to same Death Star site. Trooper Charge targeting at same or related site is a Used Interrupt. Power -1 when not on Death Star.','Commander of a platoon of Death Star troopers. Maintains security around the detention block area. Often serves as Lt. Shann Childsen\'s attache.',NULL,'7_203'),(1152,2236,'Dark','U','Special Edition','•Sergeant Merril','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sergeantmerril.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','2','Deploys for free on Cloud City if your Lando is at a related location. Power +2 on Cloud City. When in battle at a Cloud City site, adds 1 to your total battle destiny for each of your other Cloud City troopers in that battle.','Tyrannical squad commander on Cloud City. Treats his fellow Cloud City troopers with disdain. Enemy of Utris M\'Toc.',NULL,'7_204'),(1153,2237,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Sergeant Narthax','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sergeantnarthax.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','3','2','3','While on Hoth, makes all your snowtroopers immune to Ice Storm. When in battle on Hoth with another snowtrooper, adds one battle destiny. Precise Attack targeting at same or related site is a Used Interrupt. Power -1 when not on Hoth.','Commanded a squad of snowtroopers in the Battle of Hoth. Trains snowtroopers in extreme-weather survival tactics. Originally from Ukio.',NULL,'7_205'),(1154,6632,'Dark','C1','Virtual Set 11','•Sergeant Narthax With E-web Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/sergeantnarthaxwithewebblaster.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','3','3','4','Permanent weapon is E-web Blaster (may target a character, landed starfighter, or vehicle for free; if targeting a starfighter or vehicle, add one destiny to attrition; otherwise, subtract 3 from target\'s immunity to attrition (if any) until end of turn).','Snowtrooper.',NULL,'211_7'),(1155,2238,'Dark','U','Endor','•Sergeant Tarl','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/sergeanttarl.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','While Tarl is the trooper targeted by Spice Mines of Kessel, that Utinni Effect is immune to Alter and Tarl adds 4 to Force retrieved when completed. Subtracts 3 from Force opponent retrieves with Noble Sacrifice.','Took part in the capture of the Rebel Blockade Runner Tantive IV. Stormtrooper trained on Corulag. Corellia native.',NULL,'8_114'),(1156,2239,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Sergeant Torent','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/sergeanttorent.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','2','Deploys -2 on Death Star. When in battle, adds 1 to your total battle destiny for each of your Death Star troopers present. While on Death Star, adds 1 to each of your Force drains at a battleground related to system Death Star orbits.','Senior watch trooper at Death Star\'s command center. Monitors external sensor data, scanning for Rebel activity. Vigilant in his duties.',NULL,'7_206'),(1157,2242,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Set For Stun','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/setforstun.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to target one opponent\'s character. Draw destiny. If destiny > character\'s ability, character immediately returns to opponent\'s hand. (Also, any cards deployed on character return to owners\' hands.)','\'...bring me the passengers. I want them alive!\' Imperial soldiers use blaster stun settings to intimidate or to capture prisoners for questioning and interrogation.',NULL,'1_268'),(1158,2240,'Dark','R','Endor','•Sergeant Wallen','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Dark/large/sergeantwallen.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','May deploy for free to a battle you just initiated at a battleground site.','Stormtrooper assigned to Colonel Dyer\'s command. His unit was recommended to Commander Igar by Governor Yount of the Wakeelmui garrison.',NULL,'8_115'),(1159,6635,'Dark','PM','Third Anthology','Set Your Course For Alderaan / The Ultimate Power In The Universe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ThirdAntholo