/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/slaveisymboloffear.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Firespray-class Attack Ship','3','3','3','5','May add 2 pilots and 2 passengers. Power +1 for each opponent\'s starship here. While Jango or Boba Fett piloting, immune to attrition < 5.','Originally designed as a planetary defense craft. Uses restricted jamming technology, allowing it to appear out of nowhere. Contains many hidden armaments.',NULL,'201_40'),(1195,6649,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 1','•Slave I, Symbol Of Fear (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialAI-Dark/large/slaveisymboloffear.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Firespray-class Attack Ship','3','3','3','5','May add 2 pilots and 2 passengers. Power +1 for each opponent\'s starship here. While Jango or Boba Fett piloting, immune to attrition < 5.','Originally designed as a planetary defense craft. Uses restricted jamming technology, allowing it to appear out of nowhere. Contains many hidden armaments.',NULL,'201_40'),(1196,2281,'Dark','C','Dagobah','Sleen','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/sleen.gif?raw=true','Creature','Swamp','3','*','2','0','Ferocity = destiny - 3. Habitat: planet sites (except Hoth and Tatooine) and Dark Waters. Cumulatively absorbs (temporarily cancels) one [Light Side Force] icon present. Parasite: None.','Slow, omnivorous swamp forager. Eats insects. Seeks damp, dark environments strong with the Force.','Nudj','4_111'),(1197,2283,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Slip Sliding Away','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/slipslidingaway.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Relocate a card from the top of any Deck or Pile to the bottom (without looking). OR if you have a droid at a Scomp link on Cloud City, cancel Into The Ventilation Shaft, Lefty. OR use 3 Force to cause a character at Weather vane to be lost.','Luke