r/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/sniper&darkstrike.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just targeted with a lightsaber, add 3 to your total weapon destiny. OR During your control phase, fire one of your weapons. Any \'hit\' targets are immediately lost. OR Lose 1 Force to place opponent\'s just \'hit\' character in Lost Pile',NULL,'Sorry About The Mess & Blaster Proficiency','10_47'),(1202,2293,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','•Snoova','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/snoova.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','6','5','4','Deploys -3 to same site as any smuggler or bounty. During your deploy phase, a Vibro-Ax may deploy for free on Snoova from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. When Snoova excludes a target with a Vibro-Ax, he may capture target instead.','Perhaps the only true Wookiee bounty hunter in the galaxy. Even high ranking members of the Alliance fear him. Favors a vibro-ax for his personal weapon.',NULL,'10_48'),(1203,2295,'Dark','C3','Hoth','Snowtrooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/snowtrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','2','2','3','Deploys only on Hoth. Power -1 when not at a Hoth site.','Cold Assault troopers are specially trained and equipped to operate in frozen environments. Blizzard Force snowtroopers often work in tandem with AT-ATs.',NULL,'3_91'),(1204,2296,'Dark','C1','Hoth','•••Snowtrooper Officer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/snowtrooperofficer.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','3','3','Deploy only on Hoth, but may move elsewhere. Snowtroopers are deploy -1 to same site. Your troopers may move to same Hoth site as a \'react.\'','Elite snowtrooper offers, like all Imperial Army officers, are well versed in Rebel tactics. They serve as infantry liaisons to AT-ATs.',NULL,'3_92'),(1205,2302,'Dark','C','Dagobah','Something Hit Us!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/somethinghitus.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle, lose 1 Force. Cumulatively adds 1 to attrition against opponent.','\'That was no laser blast...\'',NULL,'4_148'),(1206,2303,'Dark','C','Death Star II','•Something Special Planned For Them','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/somethingspecialplannedforthem.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. For opponent to move a starship from same location as your Star Destroyer requires +2 Force. Also, when opponent has just retrieved Force using an Interrupt or Utinni Effect card, that card is placed out of play. (Immune to Alter.)','The high command of the Emperor\'s fleet is selected as much for loyalty and obedience as for martial skills. A wise admiral knows better than to question Palpatine.',NULL,'9_132'),(1207,4044,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 0','•Something Special Planned For Them (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Dark/large/somethingspecialplannedforthem.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per game, if opponent just played an Interrupt, may stack it here. To play any new Interrupt of same name, players must first stack it here. May place this Effect in Lost Pile (place cards here in owners\' Used Pile) to retrieve a starship. (Immune to Alter.)','The high command of the Emperor\'s fleet is selected as much for loyalty and obedience as for martial skills. A wise admiral knows better than to question Palpatine.','Strikeforce (V)','200_112'),(1208,2306,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Sonic Bombardment','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/sonicbombardment.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Search your Reserve Deck, take any one prison into hand and reshuffle.  LOST: If you have an opponent\'s alien captive at a prison, opponent loses 3 Force.\"','Ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui.',NULL,'5_155'),(1209,5198,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 8','•Sonic Bombardment (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Dark/large/sonicbombardment.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Take any one Downtown Plaza or prison into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: Search your Reserve Deck, take any one unqiue (•) bounty into hand; reshuffle. OR Target an alien. For remainder of turn, target is power and forfeit -1 (-3 if Chewie).\"','Ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui ooui.',NULL,'208_45'),(1210,2312,'Dark','U','Dagobah','<>Space Slug','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/spaceslug.gif?raw=true','Creature','Space','4','*','2','0','* Ferocity = two destiny. Habitat: Big One (Cave is now Belly). Attacks starfighters (defeated cards are eaten or relocated to Belly, opponent of victim chooses). Once per turn, may open or close mouth.','Gigantic silicon-based lifeform. Exists in the vacuum of space. Devours small vessels whole. Has difficulty keeping its modified light freighters down.','Space Slug','4_112'),(1211,2314,'Dark','F','Special Edition','<>Spaceport City','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/spaceportcity.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If your thief or scout present, Force drain +1 here. May not deploy to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth, Kashyyyk or Yavin 4.',NULL,'Spaceport City','7_288'),(1212,2316,'Dark','F','Special Edition','<>Spaceport Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/spaceportdockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','S