our senators at Galactic Senate. (Immune to Sense.) OR Take one senator (or Coruscant Guard) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','To simply be a sitting member of the Galactic Senate consumes a lot of time and energy. The opposition that is arrayed against you does not make it any easier.',NULL,'12_159'),(1221,2335,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•SSA-1015','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/ssa1015.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','3','3','While with an opponent\'s Jedi, your other battle droids present are power +1. Opponent\'s Jedi are deploy +4 to same site. While with another battle droid at a site, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.','Security battle droid whose programming assured him a Jedi could be subdued. Supposed to be designated SSA-101, but a mistake in production pushed him back to 1015.',NULL,'14_89'),(1222,2336,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•SSA-306','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/ssa306.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','3','3','At same site, opponent\'s spies and smugglers are deploy +4 and may not apply their ability toward drawing battle destiny. While with another battle droid at a site, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.','Security battle droid was assigned guard duty at Theed Palace. His shift can only be ended by a blaster shot.',NULL,'14_90'),(1223,2337,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•SSA-719','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/ssa719.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','3','3','While with another battle droid, power +3. If with a battle droid on Naboo and you just verified opponent\'s Reserve Deck, may lose 2 Force to search that Reserve Deck and place one card you find there out of play.','Security battle droid assigned to quell uprisings before they have a chance to gather momentum. Believes the best form of defense is offense.',NULL,'14_91'),(1224,2339,'Dark','R1','Hoth','•Stalker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/stalker.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','8','8','9','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Probe droids deploy free to sites related to same system.','Originally assigned to search the Outer Rim for new worlds to subjugate. Launched the probe droid that found Echo Base. Later reassigned to Death Squadron.',NULL,'3_152'),(1225,2340,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 1','•Stalker (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/stalker.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','8','8','9','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1.  If opponent\'s starship just moved from here, Stalker may follow it as a regular move (if within range).','Originally assigned to search the Outer Rim for new worlds to subjugate. Launched the probe droid that found Echo Base. Later reassigned to Death Squadron.',NULL,'201_41'),(1226,2341,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','STAP Blaster Cannons','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/stapblastercannons.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Vehicle','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your STAP. Vehicle is power +3. May target a character, creature or vehicle for free. Draw two destiny and choose one. Target hit if destiny +2 > defense value.','Standard weapon equipped on a Single Trooper Aerial Platform. STAP laser cannons can be devastating due to the high speed of the STAP itself.',NULL,'14_129'),(1227,2343,'Dark','C','Dagobah','•••Star Destroyer: Launch Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/stardestroyerlaunchbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Starships