ormtroopergarrison.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','4','8','6','4','Imperial leaders present may not be targeted by weapons. While with an Imperial leader, adds one battle destiny. While at an opponent\'s site, Force drain +1 here (or +2 if also a Rebel Base). End of your turn: Use 1 Force to maintain OR Lose 1 Force to place in Used Pile OR Place out of play.','The Imperial Navy\'s ruthless shock troops. The distinctive white armor of the stormtrooper is recognized throughout the galaxy as a feared occupational force.',NULL,'13_87'),(1241,5099,'Dark','U2','Virtual Set 4','•••Stormtrooper Patrol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Dark/large/stormtrooperpatrol.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','3','3','3','4','May deploy as a \'react\' to a site. Each other stormtrooper present is power +1. Rebels are deploy +1 to same site.','Imperial stormtroopers adopt strict security measures. Excellent communications and sheer numbers can hinder Rebel movement across entire territories.',NULL,'204_44'),(1242,2360,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Stormtrooper Utility Belt','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/stormtrooperutilitybelt.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on any Imperial or alien. Character\'s power and forfeit are +1. If on Death Star, power and forfeit are +2.','Standard Imperial issue for stormtroopers. Contains grappling hook, rope, and other miscellaneous emergency tools. Rebels have been known to steal and use them.',NULL,'1_207'),(1243,2362,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Strategic Reserves','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/strategicreserves.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Once per turn, you may cancel a Force drain by placing here from hand any non-unique Imperial. Imperials may deploy from here as if from hand (if Effect cance