e leaders for interrogation. Stun effects wear off, requiring efficient action.','Blast The Door, Kid!','2_140'),(1247,2369,'Dark','U','Dagobah','Sudden Impact','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/suddenimpact.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any Effect or Utinni Effect (except those immune to Alter). During each of owner\'s draw phases, if you occupy an asteroid sector, owner must choose to either lose 1 Force or voluntarily cancel that Effect or Utinni Effect. (Immune to Alter.)','An asteroid looming in one\'s path can force a quick decision. One must choose, but choose wisely. This pilot chose poorly.','Ineffective Maneuver','4_132'),(1248,2371,'Dark','C','Death Star II','•Sullust','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/sullust.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Immune to Revolution.',NULL,'Sullust','9_150'),(1249,2373,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Sunsdown','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/sunsdown.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any planet system to cause \'nighttime conditions\' at related sites. During battles there, both sides add one destiny to power only. Spies deploy free to sites under \'nighttime conditions.\'','When the twin suns of Tatooine set. \'Sand People or worse\' become a threat, and battles are more dangerous. On Hoth, temperatures drop to deadly extremes.','Nightfall','1_230'),(1250,2374,'Dark','PM','Reflections II','Sunsdown & Too Cold For Speeders','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Dark/large/sunsdown&toocoldforspeeders.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any planet system. At related sites: nighttime conditions are in effect; non-creature vehicles are power = 0, maneuver = 0, and landspeed = 0; spies deploy -1; and in battles there both sid