,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any male character. Target a female character on table. Target is power -2. Utinni Effect canceled when present with target.','\'Why, I guess you don\'t know everything about women yet.\'',NULL,'3_112'),(1350,2575,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','•This Is Not Good','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/thisisnotgood.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: For remainder of turn, subtract 2 from any attempt to \'blow away\' Blockade Flagship.  LOST: During any deploy phase, use 3 Force to target any starship at same system as your battleship. Target is hyperspeed = 0 until end of turn.\"','\'Everything\'s overheated.\'',NULL,'14_108'),(1351,2576,'Dark','U','Coruscant','•This Is Outrageous!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/thisisoutrageous.gif?raw=true','Effect','Political','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If no senator here, you may place a senator here from hand to cancel an opponent\'s Force drain. If a trade agenda here, once during your turn, you may place a card from hand in Lost Pile, shuffle that pile, and take top card into hand.','\'I recommend a commission be sent to Naboo to ascertain the truth!\'',NULL,'12_142'),(1352,2577,'Dark','U1','A New Hope','This Is Some Rescue!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/thisissomerescue.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel I\'m Here To Rescue You, Plastoid Armor, Out Of Commission, Alternatives To Fighting, Cell 2187 or Ewok Rescue.','\'When you came in here, didn\'t you have a plan for getting out?\'',NULL,'2_141'),(1353,2578,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•This Is Still Wrong','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/thisisstillwrong.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated where opponent has a female targeted by This Is Just Wrong, add one battle destiny. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take one This Is Just Wrong into hand and reshuffle. OR Cancel This Is More Like It.','Han: 2. Luke: 2. Chewie: 0.',NULL,'5_157'),(1354,2579,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Thok & Thug','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/thok&thug.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','5','8','7','5','Deploys -2 to a Jabba\'s Palace site.  If opponent just initiated battle at same site, may use X Force (limit 2) to add twice X to power. Your alien leaders present may not be targeted by weapons. End of your turn: Use 2 Force to maintain OR Lose 1 Force to place in Used Pile OR Place out of play.','Jabba the Hutt knew that having a big, strong, dumb guard was good, but having lots of them is better.',NULL,'13_92'),(1355,2580,'Dark','C','Dagobah','Those Rebels Won\'t Escape Us','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/thoserebelswontescapeus.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Nabrun Leids.  LOST: During your move phase, cancel Landing Claw. OR Cancel Hyper Escape, Closer?! or one \'react.\'\"','\'I don\'t know how we\'re gonna get out of this one.\'',NULL,'4_150'),(1356,2584,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Through The Corridor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/throughthecorridor.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated battle against Maul where opponent has two Jedi, cancel that battle and you may relocate one of those Jedi (your choice) to any adjacent site. That Jedi may not move for remainder of turn. (Immune to Sense.)','Obi-Wan was anxious, Qui-Gon was patient, and Maul was angry.',NULL,'13_93'),(1357,2589,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Thul Fain','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/thulfain.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','2','3','Deploys free to your [Independent Starship] starship. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When with Lieutenant Tanbris in a battle at a system, adds 2 to each of your battle destiny draws.','Gambler who bets on how long the Rancor\'s victims will last. Formerly an Imperial pilot who worked with Lieutenant Tanbris. Now a smuggler for Jabba.',NULL,'6_125'),(1358,2590,'Dark','R','Death Star II','•Thunderflare','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/thunderflare.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','9','7','7','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1. Turbolaser Batteries deploy and fire free here.','Overpowered Star Destroyer. Energy is transferred from hyperdrive to weapons. Patrol duties in the Core Worlds make it a common first assignment for junior officers.',NULL,'9_174'),(1359,2591,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Tibanna Gas Miner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/tibannagasminer.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','2','When at a site, adds 1 to your Force drains at related cloud sectors. Also, during your activate phase, if at a Cloud City site and you control Bespin: Cloud City, may cumulatively activate 1 Force for every cloud sector on Bespin.','One of the many Cloud City miners who are willingly employed by greedy corporations exploiting planetary atmospheres. Unconcerned with environmental repercussions.','Tibanna Gas Miner','5_102'),(1360,2595,'Dark','U2','Premiere','TIE Advanced x1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/tieadvancedx1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Advanced x1','3','2','2','3','Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','TIE advanced x1 fighter boasting improved power plant, stronger shields, armored hull and enhanced weapons. Deployed to elite Imperial Navy pilots.',NULL,'1_303'),(1361,2596,'Dark','U1','A New Hope','TIE Assault Squadron','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/tieassaultsquadron.gif?raw=true','Starship','Squadron: TIE/LN','3','3','*','6','* Replaces 3 TIE/lns at one location (TIE/lns go to Used Pile). Permanent pilots provide total ability of 3.','Imperial strategy relies on quantity over quality. Although many of their pilots have low motivation, this is compensated by \'wolfpack\' group tactics.',NULL,'2_153'),(1362,2597,'Dark','C','Dagobah','TIE Avenger','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/tieavenger.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/AD','3','2','3','2','Deploy -1 to same system as any Imperial capital starship. May add 1 pilot. Boosted TIE Cannon may deploy aboard.','Design based on Lord Vader\'s prototype Advanced x1. Manufactured until replaced by the more economical TIE Interceptor. Equipped with deflector shields and a hyperdrive.',NULL,'4_172'),(1363,2598,'Dark','U','Dagobah','TIE Bomber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/tiebomber.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SA','0','1','2','2','Power +2 during a Bombing Run battle. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1. At any time during your turn, may use 1 Force to \'diffuse\' (lose or return to hand) any one Orbital Mine present.','Because fleet orbital bombardment often destroyed entire cities, the double-pod TIE surface assault starfighter was developed to allow more precise and controlled targeting.',NULL,'4_173'),(1364,2599,'Dark','F','Special Edition','TIE Defender Mark I','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/tiedefendermarki.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Defender Mark I','3','3','3','3','May deploy as a `react\'. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Any starship cannon may deploy aboard. Power - 2 while opponent has a starfighter present with higher maneuver.','First production run of TIE defender design. Powerful P-sz9.7 sublight engines. Fire-linked laser cannons. Aft blind spot exploited by maneuverable enemy starfighters.',NULL,'7_308'),(1365,2600,'Dark','C2','Premiere','TIE Fighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/tiefighter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/LN','1','1','1','2','Deploy -1 to same system as any Imperial capital starship. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','TIE or Twin Ion Engine. TIE/ln model is Empire\'s most common fighter. Quick and maneuverable. Solar-panel wings supplement power generator. Built by Sienar Fleet Systems.',NULL,'1_304'),(1366,2601,'Dark','C','Death Star II','TIE Interceptor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Dark/large/tieinterceptor.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Interceptor','2','3','2','3','Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Power +1 when present with an X-wing. During each battle, may fire one starship weapon aboard twice.','Advanced TIE design. Assigned to elite squadrons, such as the 181st. Developed with enhanced weapons and maneuverability to defeat the Incom X-wing design.',NULL,'9_175'),(1367,2602,'Dark','C2','Premiere','TIE Scout','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/tiescout.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SR','4','1','2','3','May add 1 pilot and 1 passenger, or 2 passengers. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','Limited production, light reconnaissance starship. Minimal armor and weapons. Long-range sensor and communications array. Scouts for Rebel activity.',NULL,'1_305'),(1368,2603,'Dark','C','Cloud City','•TIE Sentry Ships','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/tiesentryships.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a Force drain at a system, cloud sector or asteroid sector, you may \'react\' by deploying TIEs and pilots to that location (at normal use of the Force).','Several TIEs were assigned to patrol Cloud City prior to the Imperial occupation of Bespin. Their instructions were to herd any vessels attempting to escape toward the Executor.',NULL,'5_158'),(1369,4104,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 1','•TIE Sentry Ships (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/tiesentryships.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If you just drew a starship for destiny, take that starship into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny.  LOST: Use 3 Force to retrieve a starship into hand.','Several TIEs were assigned to patrol Cloud City prior to the Imperial occupation of Bespin. Their instructions were to herd any vessels attempting to escape toward the Executor.','Starship Levitation (V)','201_36'),(1370,2604,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','TIE Vanguard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/tievanguard.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/RC','3','1','2','3','Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. You may deploy cards to same system or sector as a \'react\'.','Reconnaissance starfighter. Often deployed first to gather detailed information on enemy starship movement before full fleet engagement.',NULL,'2_154'),(1371,2608,'Dark','C','Coruscant','•Tikkes','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/tikkes.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','2','3','6','Agenda: wealth. While in a senate majority, your Force generation is +2 at battlegrounds you control, and Honor Of The Jedi is suspended. Once during your deploy phase, may draw bottom card of your Force Pile into hand.','Quarren senator elected by the people of Mon Calamari. Has amassed considerable wealth through a multitude of political deals, but still moves to gain more.',NULL,'12_122'),(1372,2609,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Timer Mine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/timermine.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s side at same site as one of your mining droids. \'Explodes\' at beginning of your next turn. Draw destiny. That number of opponent\'s characters there are immediately lost (owner\'s choice). Timer Mine is also lost.','A timer-activated explosive device designed to be placed by a mining droid. Originally used in ore and spice mines for demolition. Altered for military use.','Timer Mine','1_322'),(1373,2613,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Tonnika Sisters','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/tonnikasisters.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','2','2','Twice during each of your control phases, may use 2 Force to draw 2 destiny for 2 chances at a destiny = 2. If successful, may steal or destroy up to 2 weapons or 2 devices present.','Twins. Thieves. Con artists. Spies. Swindlers. Double agents. Brea and Senni use their natural charm to sway the unwary on the fringe of society.',NULL,'1_195'),(1374,2615,'Dark','U1','Hoth','Too Cold For Speeders','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/toocoldforspeeders.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your side of table. Non-creature vehicles at marker sites under \'nighttime conditions\' are power = 0, maneuver = 0 and landspeed = 0.','\'We\'re having some trouble adapting them to the cold.\'',NULL,'3_113'),(1375,2616,'Dark','U','Coruscant','•Toonbuck Toora','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/toonbucktoora.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','3','Agendas: ambition, taxation, wealth. While in a senate majority, once per turn may add 1 to your total attrition in battle for each character with an ambition agenda at Galactic Senate.','Female senator and member of her planet\'s ruling class. Her original optimism in the political process has been eroded by witnessing bribery, corruption and petty bickering.',NULL,'12_123'),(1376,2438,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•Tatooine: Bluffs','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/tatooinebluffs.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Bluff Rules\' in effect here.',NULL,NULL,'2_150'),(1377,2439,'Dark','R2','Premiere','•Tatooine: Cantina','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/tatooinecantina.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your aliens here are each forfeit +1.',NULL,'Tatooine: Cantina','1_290'),(1378,2442,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','•••Tatooine: Desert','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/tatooinedesert.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your character movement from here (except for scouts) requires +1 landspeed.',NULL,'Tatooine: Desert','6_169'),(1379,2444,'Dark','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','•Tatooine: Desert Heart','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Dark/large/tatooinedesertheart.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your character movement from here (except for Jawas) requires +1 landspeed.',NULL,NULL,'112_20'),(1380,2445,'Dark','R','Tatooine','•Tatooine: Desert Landing Site','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/tatooinedesertlandingsite.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If Amidala at a battleground site (or captive), opponent may not Force drain here.',NULL,NULL,'11_92'),(1381,2622,'Dark','R','Coruscant','<>Trade Federation Droid Control Ship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/tradefederationdroidcontrolship.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Trade Federation Battleship','2','5','6','6','May add 4 pilots, 4 passengers, 2 vehicles, and 4 starfighters. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. While a droid starfighter here, adds one battle destiny.','These heavily modifed battleships are used to control and direct the Trade Federation\'s automated army. Easily identified by its array of sensors and antennae.',NULL,'12_185'),(1382,2623,'Dark','C','Theed Palace','Trade Federation Landing Craft','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/tradefederationlandingcraft.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Trade Federation Landing Craft','2','2','1','3','May add 2 pilots and 6 vehicles. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. While at a site, once during your deploy phase may take an MTT into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','C-9979 landing craft designed to transport and unload Multi Troop Transports and its battle droid cargo as rapidly as possible.',NULL,'14_119'),(1383,2624,'Dark','U','Theed Palace','•Trade Federation Tactics','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/tradefederationtactics.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to target a starship at same system as your [Trade Federation] starship armed with a weapon. Target is forfeit = 0 until end of turn. OR During battle, add X to your total power, where X = armor of one of your [Trade Federation] starships in that battle.','Organizations as wealthy as the Trade Federation can afford large amounts of military hardware, all purchased under the guise of protecting their commercial interests.',NULL,'14_109'),(1384,6709,'Dark','U','Virtual Set 11','•Trade Federation Tactics (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/tradefederationtactics.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel an attempt to use a weapon to target your capital starship. LOST: Re-target On Target to an opponent\'s capital starship armed with a weapon. OR Take Blockade Support Ship or Invisible Hand into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.\"','Organizations as wealthy as the Trade Federation can afford large amounts of military hardware, all purchased under the guise of protecting their commercial interests.',NULL,'211_14'),(1385,2627,'Dark','R1','Hoth','Trample','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/trample.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a piloted AT-AT or AT-ST present at a site, target opponent\'s character, \'crashed\' vehicle or unpiloted vehicle without armor present. Draw destiny. Character lost if destiny > ability. Vehicle lost if destiny < 7.','The enormous feet of a walker are designed for mobility on many types of terrain. They also can be used by merciless pilots to crush the Rebellion.',NULL,'3_138'),(1386,2628,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Trandoshan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/trandoshan.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','2','Power and Forfeit +1 at same site as a Wookiee or while Bossk at Audience Chamber. When in battle at same site as a bounty, adds 1 to attrition against opponent.','Trandoshans refer to themselves as T\'doshok. Hate Wookiees. Many have come to work for Jabba, attempting to emulate the success of Bossk.',NULL,'6_126'),(1387,2630,'Dark','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Trap Door','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/trapdoor.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have no characters at Rancor Pit at the end of your deploy phase, target a character (even a captive) at Audience Chamber. Draw destiny. If destiny +2 > ability, target relocated to Rancor Pit, and, if captive, released to the Light Side of Rancor Pit (not Used Pile).','\'Boscka!\'',NULL,'6_159'),(1388,2633,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Trooper Assault','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/trooperassault.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated at a site, each of your troopers present is power +2 and immune to attrition for remainder of turn.','An assault of stormtroopers caused Leia, Chewie and Lando to retreat. When working together, the troopers\' powerful onslaught can appear unstoppable.',NULL,'5_159'),(1389,2632,'Dark','U1','Premiere','Trinto Duaba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/trintoduaba.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If there are cards in the opponent\'s Used Pile during your battle phase, draw one destiny. All cards there with the same destiny number are lost.','A Stennes Shifter, a near-human race. Have ability to blend unnoticed into crowds. Trinto profits from turning lawbreakers over to Imperial authorities.',NULL,'1_273'),(1390,2634,'Dark','U2','Premiere','Trooper Charge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/troopercharge.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Select one of your troopers in a battle to make a \'charge.\' If that trooper is a Death Star Trooper, it is power +3 this battle. If any other trooper, power +2. However, that trooper must be forfeited at end of battle.','Imperial troopers are fearless and totally indoctrinated. Backed by the most powerful weapons and starships in the galaxy, they tend to consider themselves invincible.',NULL,'1_274'),(1391,2635,'Dark','R2','A New Hope','•Trooper Davin Felth','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/trooperdavinfelth.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','2','2','1','3','While he is on Tatooine, Local Trouble and Look Sir, Droids are Used Interrupts. Opponent may select target when using Friendly Fire at same site as Felth.','Dispatched to Tatooine to apprehend renegade droids fleeing the Tantive IV. Suspected to have misgivings about Imperial methods. Allegedly shot his commander in the back.',NULL,'2_106'),(1392,2637,'Dark','U','Cloud City','•Trooper Jerrol Blendin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/trooperjerrolblendin.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','0','3','Deploys only on Cloud City, but may move elsewhere. Power +2 when participating in a battle you initiate. Opponent may use 2 Force to \'bribe\' (exclude) Blendin from battle.','Corrupt captain of the Cloud City Wing Guard. Began working during the administration of Baron Raynor. Easily bribed. Keeps the peace through intimidation.',NULL,'5_103'),(1393,2638,'Dark','F','Special Edition','•Trooper Sabacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/troopersabacc.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Requirements: A gambler or trooper at a site. Wild cards (2-7): Imperial and Rebel leaders. (Troopers may use weapons as wildcards.) Clone cards: Locations and droids. Stakes: One transport vehicle without armor or one character weapon.\"','Sabacc is a popular game for off-duty Imperial stormtroopers throughout the galaxy.','Trooper Sabacc','7_267'),(1394,2641,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•TT-6','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/tt6.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: MTT','4','2','2','4','May add 7 passengers. Once per turn, may deploy a battle droid leader to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if your AAT or STAP present).','Primary command liaison transport. Contains the majority of officer battle droids. Has priority to unload as soon as the area is secured. Enclosed.',NULL,'14_124'),(1395,2642,'Dark','R','Theed Palace','•TT-9','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Dark/large/tt9.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: MTT','4','2','2','4','May add 4 passengers and 3 STAPs. Once per turn, may deploy a STAP to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if your AAT or STAP present).','Auxiliary mobilization supply transport. Coordinates with the Droid Control Ship to determine whether additional STAPs are needed in any given area. Enclosed.',NULL,'14_125'),(1396,2645,'Dark','C1','Hoth','Turn It Off! Turn It Off!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/turnitoffturnitoff.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel any attempt to place a \'hit\' starship, vehicle or droid in the Used Pile rather than the Lost Pile. OR Cancel Han\'s Toolkit.  LOST: Cancel Crash Site Memorial.\"','\'Turn it off! Turn it off! Off! TURN IT OFF!\'',NULL,'3_139'),(1397,2644,'Dark','R2','Premiere','Turbolaser Battery','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/turbolaserbattery.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on your Star Destroyer or any mobile system. May target a starship using 2 Force. Draw two destiny. Subtract 2 if targeting a capital starship. Otherwise, subtract 5. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','High-powered blasters. Require power generators, cryogenic cooling units and large crews. More effective against capital starships than starfighters.',NULL,'1_323'),(1398,4105,'Dark','C1','Virtual Set 1','Turn It Off! Turn It Off! (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Dark/large/turnitoffturnitoff.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Play a Defensive Shield from under your Starting Effect. OR If opponent just deployed a [Maintenance] card, it may not battle for remainder of turn. OR Cancel Out Of Commission (if attempting to place a card out of play). (Immune to Sense.)','\'Turn it off! Turn it off! Off! TURN IT OFF!\'',NULL,'201_37'),(1399,2649,'Dark','C','Coruscant','Tusken Raider','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/tuskenraider.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','2','While at Podrace Arena, if opponent just placed race destiny on their Podracer, once per turn may use 3 Force to \'shoot\' (no other Tusken Raiders may \'shoot\' this turn.) Draw destiny. If destiny > 3, place race destiny in opponent\'s hand.','Tusken Raiders are constantly taking bets to see who can hit the most Podracers on the Boonta Eve racetrack.',NULL,'12_124'),(1400,2648,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Tusken Raider','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/tuskenraider.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','1','Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +1 if another non-unique Tusken Raider present. If you have four or more non-unique Tusken Raiders present, your total power here is +2.','\'Sand People.\' Ride banthas. Wield gaderffi (gaffi) sticks. Wear eye protectors and breath masks. Violent, nomadic, desert survival experts. \'Urrrg! Ur Ur Uur!\'',NULL,'1_196'),(1401,2650,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Tusken Scavengers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/tuskenscavengers.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to draw destiny. If destiny < the number of Tusken Raiders on table, you may scavenge (search through) the opponent\'s Used Pile. All vehicles, weapons or devices you find there are lost.','\'Sand People always ride single file to hide their numbers.\' They frequently attack strangers as they scavenge for useful equipment. Looted Luke\'s landspeeder.',NULL,'1_275'),(1402,2651,'Dark','C','Jabba\'s Palace','•Twi\'lek Advisor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/twilekadvisor.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Starting','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Use 3 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one Effect of any kind into hand; reshuffle.  STARTING: Deploy from your Reserve Deck one Effect which has no deploy cost; reshuffle. Place Interrupt in the Lost Pile.\"','\'He\'s no Jedi.\'','The Signal','6_160'),(1403,6715,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 11','•Twi\'lek Advisor (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/twilekadvisor.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Audience Chamber on table, deploy Passenger Deck or a pit from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Deploy an alien leader or Twi\'lek to Audience Chamber from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','\'He\'s no Jedi.\'',NULL,'211_15'),(1404,6716,'Dark','R','Demo Deck','Twin Suns Of Tatooine / Well Trained In The Jedi Arts','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DemoDeck-Dark/large/twinsunsoftatooine.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Twin Suns Of Tatooine:Deploy Tatooine system and a non-Jabba\'s Palace Tatooine battleground site. {For} remainder of game, you may not deploy Jabba\'s Palace sites or Sandwhirl. {While} this side up, once per turn, may use 1 Force to deploy a Tatooine battleground site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. {Flip} this card if you control two Tatooine battleground sites (at least one with a Dark Jedi) and occupy Tatooine system, and opponent controls no Tatooine sites.Well Trained In The Jedi Arts:{While} this side up, once per game,may deploy Tatooine Occupation from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once during your control phase, may peek at the top two cards of your Reserve Deck; take one into hand and shuffle Reserve Deck. For opponent to move a character or vehicle from same site as your Dark Jedi requires +1 Force. {Flip} this card if opponent controls more Tatooine sites than you.',NULL,NULL,'301_4'),(1405,2657,'Dark','R1','Hoth','•Tyrant','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Dark/large/tyrant.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Imperial-Class Star Destroyer','1','8','7','9','May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1. When using Tractor Beam, adds 1 to destiny draw.','Assigned to Admiral Ozzel\'s Death Squadron. Attempted to capture Rebel starships fleeing the Hoth system.',NULL,'3_153'),(1406,2659,'Dark','R1','A New Hope','•U-3PO (Yoo-Threepio)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/u3po.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','3','3','Deploy on opponent\'s side as an Undercover spy (except that if present during a battle at a site, adds its power to Light Side). If spy\'s \'cover is broken,\' the above game text is canceled and Light Side may use as if stolen.','This protocol droid served in the House of Alderaan\'s Diplomatic Corps. Imperials altered its programming for espionage, making the droid an unwitting spy for the Empire.',NULL,'2_107'),(1407,2660,'Dark','C2','Premiere','Ubrikkian 9000 Z001','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/ubrikkian9000z001.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','2','2','2','4','May add 1 driver and 2 passengers. May move as a \'react.\'','Enclosed repulsorlift landspeeder. Micro-thrusters placed around spherical hull. Seats three. Extremely maneuverable. Top speed of 160 km per hour.',NULL,'1_310'),(1408,2661,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Ugloste','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/ugloste.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','3','Power +2 at Trash Compactor, Droid Junkheap, Incinerator or Carbonite Chamber. Functions as a leader if present with another Ugnaught. Where present, other Ugnaughts are forfeit +2 and double their bonus to Carbon-Freezing destiny.','Ugnaught assigned to determine how to use carbon-freezing on humans. Placed in charge or the Ugnaught workers on Cloud City. Formerly enslaved by humans.',NULL,'5_104'),(1409,2662,'Dark','C','Cloud City','Ugnaught','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/ugnaught.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','2','When at Carbonite Chamber, cumulatively adds 1 to each Carbon- Freezing destiny draw. During your control phase, may lose 1 Force from hand to search your Lost Pile and take one weapon or device into hand.','Cheap manual labor from Gentes in the Anoat system. Make up Cloud City\'s second largest population. Responsible for maintenance and menial chores throughout the city.',NULL,'5_105'),(1410,2668,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Umpass-stay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/umpassstay.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','3','4','2','Power +2 at a Jabba\'s Palace site. Each of your other musicians at same site is power +2 and immune to attrition < 3. Immune to attrition < 4.','Klatooinian born into slavery to Desilijic Hutt clan on Shawti. Musician. Works as a spy for Jabba at his desert fortress while playing drums for visiting bands.',NULL,'7_209'),(1411,2669,'Dark','C','Dagobah','Uncertain Is The Future','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/uncertainisthefuture.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force. Each player places hand onto Reserve Deck (if possible), then places Used Pile onto Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Each player then draws cards from Reserve Deck equal to the number of cards just placed from hand onto Reserve Deck (if any).','Even a Jedi cannot always foresee future events.',NULL,'4_151'),(1412,2672,'Dark','C2','A New Hope','Undercover','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/undercover.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your spy at a site and cross spy to opponent\'s side. Spy is now Undercover. During your deploy phase, may voluntarily \'break cover\' (lose Effect) if at a site. (Immune to Alter.)','The Empire maintains a network of spies attempting to infiltrate the Rebel Alliance or misinform their operatives.','Undercover','2_129'),(1413,2677,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Unexpected Interruption','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/unexpectedinterruption.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one Interrupt into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.','\'Sir! Sir! I\'ve isolated the reverse power flux coupling!\'',NULL,'4_152'),(1414,2680,'Dark','PM','Reflections III','•Unsalvageable','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Dark/large/unsalvageable.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your turn, target an opponent\'s unpiloted starship present at a system, or an opponent\'s unpiloted vehicle. Target is lost (along with any cards aboard it). OR Cancel Hyper Escape, Power Pivot, or Out Of Commission.','With mounting pressure from superior forces, the Rebellion sometimes has to abandon its crippled equipment in order to simply get its personnel out alive.',NULL,'13_94'),(1415,2683,'Dark','U2','A New Hope','•URoRRuR\'R\'R','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/urorrurrr.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','4','Deploys only on on Tatooine. When at same site as another Tusken Raider, may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Leader of a Tusken Raider tribe. Unafraid of machines. Skilled hunter and marksman. Raids moisture farms for water. Roams the Jundland Wastes in search of unwary travelers.',NULL,'2_108'),(1416,2685,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•URoRRuR\'R\'R\'s Bantha','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/urorrurrrsbantha.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Creature','3','2','1','4','May add 2 \'riders\' (passengers). Ability = 1/2. Adds 1 to power of each of your Tusken Raiders and other banthas present. When ridden by URoRRuR\'R\'R, adds one battle destiny.','Raised by RR\'uruurr for personal use by URoRRuR\'R\'R. Alpha male of his bantha herd. Has trampled many Jawas. Nicknamed \'Rrr\'ur\'R.',NULL,'7_317'),(1417,2687,'Dark','U1','A New Hope','•URoRRuR\'R\'R\'s Hunting Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Dark/large/urorrurrrshuntingrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on URoRRuR\'R\'R or Chief Bast, 3 on your non-droid character. May target a character or creature using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Subtract 1 if targeting a character. Add 2 if targeting a creature. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Owning a hunting rifle is an important status symbol in Tusken culture. URoRRuR\'R\'R scavenged this weapon from a starship wreck near Anchorhead.',NULL,'2_162'),(1418,2681,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Ur\'Ru\'r','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/urrur.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','2','Deploys only on Tatooine. While at Tusken Canyon, Jundland Wastes or same Tatooine site as UroRRuR\'R\'R, adds 2 to each of your battle destiny draws at Tatooine sites where you have a Tusken Raider.','Fierce Tusken Raider. Ransacks homes and moisture farms on the borders of Mos Espa.',NULL,'7_210'),(1419,2688,'Dark','R1','Premiere','Utinni!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/utinni.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your Jawas is at the same location as any Utinni Effect, \'steal\' that Utinni Effect into your hand, to use or lose as your own. OR Cancel any Interrupt or Effect with \'Jawa\' in the card name.','The Jawa who shot R2-D2 with an ionization gun called to his companions, \'Utinni!\', the Jawa word for \'come here!\'','Utinni!','1_276'),(1420,2693,'Dark','PM','Premiere Introductory Two Player Game','•Vader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/PremiereIntroductoryTwoPlayerGame-Dark/large/vader.gif?raw=true','Character','Imperial','1','4','7','5','Must deploy on Death Star, but may move elsewhere. May not be deployed if two or more of opponent\'s unique (•) characters on table. If in a losing battle, draw destiny. If destiny > 4, \'choke\' (lose) one Imperial present (your choice).','Sought to extinguish all Jedi. Former student of Obi-Wan Kenobi. Seduced by the dark side of the Force.',NULL,'101_5'),(1421,2695,'Dark','C','Tatooine','•Vader\'s Anger','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Dark/large/vadersanger.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Add 1 to your just-drawn lightsaber weapon destiny draw.  LOST: If a duel was just initiated, place the top card of your Used Pile on top of your Reserve Deck.\"','Anger and aggression fuel the dark side of the Force.',NULL,'11_89'),(1422,6725,'Dark','C','Virtual Set 11','•Vader\'s Anger (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Dark/large/vadersanger.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'For remainder of turn, opponent may not cancel your lightsaber weapon (or \'choke\') destiny draws. OR If Vader in battle alone, your total battle destiny is +1 for each character in battle. OR Cancel It\'s A Trap!','Anger and aggression fuel the dark side of the Force.',NULL,'211_16'),(1423,2697,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Vader\'s Bounty','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/vadersbounty.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Rebel of ability > 2. If subsequently captured, seized by a bounty hunter and then transferred to a prison where Vader is present, retrieve Force equal to character\'s forfeit (+4 if Luke) and lose Effect. (Immune to Alter.)','\'We would be honored if you would join us.\'',NULL,'5_125'),(1424,2699,'Dark','R','Cloud City','•Vader\'s Cape','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Dark/large/vaderscape.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on one of your Imperials or aliens. Immune to attrition < 5. When in battle, adds 1 to each of your battle destiny draws.','A symbol of the Dark Lord of the Sith, and of the seductive power of the dark side.',NULL,'5_126'),(1425,2700,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Vader\'s Custom TIE','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/vaderscustomtie.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Advanced x1','2','2','2','4','May add 1 pilot. If Vader is pilot, Custom TIE is immune to attrition < 4.','TIE advanced x1 prototype. First of a limited production run leading to the development of the TIE Interceptor. At Vader\'s insistence a hyperdrive was installed.',NULL,'1_306'),(1426,5143,'Dark','R1','Virtual Set 6','•Vader\'s Custom TIE (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual6-Dark/large/vaderscustomtie.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE Advanced x1','2','2','2','5','May add 1 pilot. Vader deploys -2 aboard. While Vader piloting, immune to attrition < 5, and during battle, may cancel game text of a passenger (or pilot of ability < 4) here.','TIE advanced x1 prototype. First of a limited production run leading to the development of the TIE Interceptor. At Vader\'s insistence a hyperdrive was installed.',NULL,'206_14'),(1427,2701,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Vader\'s Eye','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/vaderseye.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Vader is defending a battle alone at a site, add 1 to power and add one battle destiny. OR If any other Imperial with ability > 2 is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny.','Darth Vader\'s armored mask and life-support system provide him with extraordinary physical protection in duels and battles, in addition to his Dark Jedi combat skill.',NULL,'1_277'),(1428,2702,'Dark','R1','Premiere','•Vader\'s Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Dark/large/vaderslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Vader. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.','Custom-built by Darth Vader. After the Clone Wars, he wielded this weapon while hunting down the last of the Jedi. Cuts through almost anything except another lightsaber blade.',NULL,'1_324'),(1429,2703,'Dark','PM','Premiere Introductory Two Player Game','•Vader\'s Obsession','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/PremiereIntroductoryTwoPlayerGame-Dark/large/vadersobsession.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, if Vader moves to Luke\'s site from an adjacent site, begin a duel between them. Each adds two destiny to power. Winner retrieves lost Force equal to the difference. Loser loses same amount of Force, plus the character.','Vader sought to hunt down and destroy all Jedi. After completing the circle with Obi-Wan, he turned his attention to the young Skywalker.',NULL,'101_6'),(1430,2704,'Dark','R','Special Edition','•Vader\'s Personal Shuttle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Dark/large/vaderspersonalshuttle.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Lambda-Class Shuttle','3','2','2','4','May add 1 pilot and 4 passengers. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 2. Moves for free. While Vader a