as ship-docking capability.  Permanent pilot provides ability of 1.','Outfitted to chart unknown expanses of Outer Rim. Staff includes galactic cartography contingent. Considered a joke assignment by most lower-ranked Naval officers.',NULL,'9_176'),(1448,2721,'Dark','R','Dagobah','•Visage Of The Emperor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Dark/large/visageoftheemperor.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Lose 2 Force to deploy on Executor: Holotheatre or Death Star: Conference Room. At the end of each player\'s turn, each player must lost 1 Force. Effect canceled if opponent controls this site. (Immune to Alter.)','Palpatine\'s hologram. Imposing. Ominous. Intimidating. Instrument for the evil Emperor\'s sinister reach across the galaxy. Used on a secret frequency of the Imperial HoloNet.',NULL,'4_135'),(1449,2724,'Dark','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Vizam','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Dark/large/vizam.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','3','3','Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +3 when defending a battle. If with your Advosze during your control phase, may search Reserve Deck, take one vehicle weapon into hand and reshuffle. Your vehicle weapons deploy free at same site.','Kajain\'sa\'Nikto. Keeps Jabba\'s vehicles and starships well armed. Has hidden several weapon caches on board Jabba\'s sail barge.',NULL,'6_129'),(1450,2726,'Dark','R','Coruscant','•Vote Now!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Dark/large/votenow.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, draw destiny. If destiny > 2, draw up to X cards (maximum 4) from Reserve Deck, where X = your total politics at Galactic Senate minus opponent\'s total politics at Galactic Senate.','With enough political support, any number of devious plans can be put into motion.','Vote Now!','12_162'),(1451,4408,'Dark','R','Virtual Set 0','•