cter of equal or lesser ability. [Immune to Alter.]','Blank.',NULL,'209_16'),(1544,16,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•A Close Race','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/acloserace.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. If you just lost a Podrace, your Force loss is limited to half the difference between the winning race total and your highest race total (round up). While you occupy three battlegrounds, Watto\'s Box is suspended.','\'Poodoo!\'',NULL,'13_1'),(1545,24,'Light','C2','Premiere','A Few Maneuvers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/afewmaneuvers.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add 2 to hyperspeed and maneuver of any starfighter for the remainder of this turn. (Interrupt may even affect the result immediately after a destiny draw targeting the starfighter\'s maneuver.)','\'...I know a few maneuvers. We\'ll lose them.\' Boosted shields and fancy flying are necessary to escape Imperial weapon fire until hyperspace jump can be made.','Dark Maneuvers','1_70'),(1546,25,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•A Gift','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/agift.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just moved a droid to Audience Chamber, deploy on the droid. Droid is an Undercover spy. Wherever opponent has an alien, opponent\'s battle destiny draws are -2 and Force drains are -1. Immediate Effect canceled if droid leaves Tatooine. (Immune to Control.)','\'As a token of my good will, I present to you a gift: these two droids. Both are hardworking and will serve you well.\'',NULL,'6_52'),(1547,4079,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 0','•A Good Blaster At Your Side','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/agoodblasteratyourside.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Non-lightsaber weapons carried by your non-Jedi characters may not be stolen. During your control phase, opponent loses 1 Force for each battleground site you control with a non-[Permanent Weapon] blaster present. Rebel Artillery is a Lost interrupt. (Immune to Alter.)','\'I\'ve been looking forward to this for a long time.\' \'Yes, I\'ll bet you have.\' Han abruptly ended his conversation with Greedo and flipped Wuher a credit to pay for the cleanup.',NULL,'200_34'),(1548,26,'Light','C','Tatooine','•A Jedi\'s Concentration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/ajedisconcentration.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If a battle was just initiated where you have a character armed with a lightsaber, characters may not be targeted by lightsabers for remainder of battle.  LOST: If opponent just initiated a duel, opponent must choose to lose 4 Force or cancel the duel.\"','Luke\'s experience on Dagobah gave him great skill in using the Force. Vader had to keep his focus on Luke at all times, or face the consequences.',NULL,'11_26'),(1549,27,'Light','C','Tatooine','•A Jedi\'s Focus','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/ajedisfocus.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If you have a character with a lightsaber in battle, all opponent\'s aliens at same site are power -1 for remainder of turn ( -2 if alien is non-unique).  LOST: If a duel was just initiated, add the destiny number of the top card of your Lost Pile to your total.\"','Vader was surprised at how far the \'young apprentice\' had come in his training.',NULL,'11_27'),(1550,28,'Light','C','Tatooine','•A Jedi\'s Patience','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/ajedispatience.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If your character armed with a lightsaber is defending a battle, adds 2 to your total power in that battle.  LOST: During a duel, cancel one of your duel destiny draws to cause a re-draw.\"','Early on in his duel with Vader, Luke took his time in trying to sense his opponent\'s weaknesses.',NULL,'11_28'),(1551,29,'Light','U','Tatooine','•A Jedi\'s Resilience','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/ajedisresilience.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just lost a duel opponent initiated (before duel has any result) lose 1 Force to cancel the duel and return Interrupt (if any) used to initiate duel to owner\'s hand. OR If you just lost a character armed with a lightsaber, take that character into hand.','Luke wasn\'t going to let Vader dispose of him too quickly.',NULL,'11_29'),(1552,30,'Light','U','Dagobah','A Jedi\'s Strength','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/ajedisstrength.gif?raw=true','Jedi Test #2',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an unoccupied Dagobah site. At the beginning of each of your move phases, opponent may relocate this Jedi Test to an adjacent site. Target a mentor on Dagobah and an apprentice who has completed Jedi Test #1. Apprentice may move only by using personal landspeed. Attempt when apprentice is present at the beginning of your control phase. Draw training destiny. If destiny + apprentice\'s ability > 13, test completed: Place on apprentice. Apprentice is power +1 and may move normally. Total ability of 6 or more is required for opponent to draw battle destiny.',NULL,NULL,'4_75'),(1553,32,'Light','PM','Third Anthology','•A New Secret Base','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ThirdAnthology-Light/large/anewsecretbase.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on 1st marker. Yavin 4 locations do not count for Imperial Decree. S-foils and your \'insert\' cards are canceled. Once during each of your turns, may take up to two site