ces force it to consider the wisdom of any military encounter. In many cases, retreat or deception is a preferable recourse.',NULL,'2_44'),(1597,104,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Ambush','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/ambush.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your turn, target a site where your total power is more than double opponent\'s total power. Unless opponent has a Dark Jedi or character weapon there, place each opponent character, vehicle and starship there (and cards on them) in owner\'s Used Pile.','\'Well done. Hold them in the security tower, and keep it quiet. Move.\'',NULL,'5_31'),(1598,5337,'Light','R','Virtual Set 10','•Ambush (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/ambush.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Lose 1 Force to take up to three troopers into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Once per game, target three related battlegrounds occupied by your clones. Your Force drains at same and related battlegrounds this turn are +1.','\'Well done. Hold them in the security tower, and keep it quiet. Move.\'',NULL,'210_2'),(1599,105,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Amidala\'s Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/amidalasblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Amidala. May target a character or creature for free. Draw destiny. Character is power and forfeit = 0 if destiny > defense value. Creature lost if destiny +2 > defense value.','Amidala\'s ability as a warrior is underestimated by those who encounter her. With her weapon of choice, she often uses this fact to her advantage.',NULL,'14_62'),(1600,107,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•An Unusual Amount Of Fear','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/anunusualamountoffear.gif?raw=true','Effect','Starting','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Before any starting cards are revealed, deploy on table with up to 10 cards from outside your deck face-down under here. Cards under here do not count toward your deck limit. Three times per game, may play a Defensive Shield from here, as if from hand.','The peacekeepers of the galaxy are not to be taken lightly.','Fear Is My Ally','13_5'),(1601,108,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Anakin Skywalker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/anakinskywalker.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke is about to be lost from table and Vader is present, shuffle Reserve Deck and draw destiny. Add 6 if Emperor present. If total destiny > 12, Vader instead crosses to Light Side, Luke is not lost, opponent loses 6 Force, and Emperor (if present) is lost. (Immune to Sense.)','\'You were right about me. Tell your sister ... you were right.\'',NULL,'9_48'),(1602,4065,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Anakin Skywalker, Padawan Learner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/anakinskywalkerpadawanlearner.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','5','5','8','Adds 3 to the power of anything he pilots. Deploys -2 aboard Azure Angel. Adds 2 to maneuver of anything he pilots. Players may initiate battles here for free. During battle, your battle destiny draws and Anakin\'s weapon destiny draws are +1. Immune to attrition < 4.','Blank.',NULL,'200_2'),(1603,5340,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Anakin Skywalker, Padawan Learner (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialAI-Light/large/anakinskywalkerpadawanlearner.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','5','5','8','Adds 3 to the power of anything he pilots. Deploys -2 aboard Azure Angel. Adds 2 to maneuver of anything he pilots. Players may initiate battles here for free. During battle, your battle destiny draws and Anakin\'s weapon destiny draws are +1. Immune to attrition < 4.','Blank.',NULL,'200_2'),(1604,109,'Light','R1','Hoth','•Anakin\'s Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/anakinslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Skywalker of ability > 3. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.','Constructed by Anakin Skywalker. Kept by Obi-Wan Kenobi until given to Luke.',NULL,'3_71'),(1605,5343,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 10','•Anakin\'s Lightsaber (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/anakinslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Anakin, Luke, or Rey. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.','Constructed by Anakin Skywalker. Kept by Obi-Wan Kenobi until given to Luke.',NULL,'210_3'),(1606,110,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Anakin\'s Podracer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/anakinspodracer.gif?raw=true','Podracer',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Draws 2 race destiny instead of 1. During your draw phase, if opponent has a higher race total than Anakin\'s Podracer, draw 3 race destiny next turn and choose 2. Once per game may take I Did It! into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Built from Radon-Ulzer racing engines that Watto regarded as too burned-out to be of any use. New fuel injection subsystem created by Anakin radically increases thrust.',NULL,'11_47'),(1607,5344,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 10','•Ancient Watering Hole','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/ancientwateringhole.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Maz and your Rep are immune to attrition. While you have alien characters of five different species on table: your Force drains are +1, your total battle destiny is +1 (+2 if Maz or your Rep in battle), and your aliens are forfeit +1. (Immune to Alter.)','Blank.',NULL,'210_7'),(1608,111,'Light','C','Dagobah','•Anger, Fear, Aggression','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/angerfearaggression.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Insert in opponent\'s Reserve Deck. When Effect reaches top it is lost, but opponent must initiate a battle by the end of opponent\'s next battle phase or lose 4 Force. (Immune to Alter.)','\'The dark side of the Force are they. Easily they flow, quick to join you in a fight.\'',NULL,'4_16'),(1609,4080,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Anger, Fear, Aggression (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/angerfearaggression.gif?raw=true','Effect','Starting','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table with any number of Defensive Shields from outside your deck face-down under here. Four times per game, may play a card from here (as if from hand). Unless canceling your Interrupt, opponent may not play Uncertain Is The Future until the end of your first turn.','\'The dark side of the Force are they. Easily they flow, quick to join you in a fight.\'','Knowledge And Defense (V)','200_35'),(1610,113,'Light','U','Dagobah','•Anoat','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/anoat.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If opponent initiates a battle here, your starships may move as a \'react\' to or from nearest related asteroid sector.',NULL,'Anoat','4_80'),(1611,4115,'Light','U','Virtual Set 1','•Anoat (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/anoat.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force loss from Security Precautions is reduced by 4.',NULL,NULL,'201_16'),(1612,115,'Light','C','Special Edition','Anoat Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/anoatoperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','3','While at an Anoat site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is forfeit +1 (and power +1 if your smuggler or Ugnaught is on Anoat) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Anoat from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Independent H\'nemthe merchants at Anoat coordinate the shipping of supplies to Rebel bases throughout the galaxy.','Anoat Operative','7_2'),(1613,116,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Another Pathetic Lifeform','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/anotherpatheticlifeform.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once during each of opponent\'s turns, if you occupy a battleground site, may activate 1 Force. While opponent has a non-unique alien or non-unique starfighter in battle, opponent may not draw more than two battle destiny. (Immune to Alter.)','Young Obi-Wan has much to learn about the living Force. Patience with others is also high on that list.',NULL,'12_39'),(1614,117,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Another Pathetic Lifeform','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/anotherpatheticlifeform.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. While opponent has a non-unique alien or non-unique starfighter in battle, opponent may not draw more than two battle destiny.','Young Obi-Wan has much to learn about the living Force. Patience with others is also high on that list.','Wipe Them Out, All Of Them - Defensive Shield','13_6'),(1615,118,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Antilles Maneuver','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/antillesmaneuver.gif?raw=true','Interrupt'