NULL,'6_49'),(1619,127,'Light','C2','A New Hope','•••Arcona','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/arcona.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','2','Power +1 under \'nighttime conditions.\' May move away from a battle at same site as a \'react.\'','Unut Poll is a typical male Arcona. Unlike many other Arcona, he has avoided salt. Scout known to cooperate with Alliance operatives.',NULL,'2_1'),(1620,128,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Ardon \'Vapor\' Crell','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/ardonvaporcrell.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','4','2','2','2','Deploys free on Tatooine. While on Tatooine, your Force drains are +1 at exterior sites where you have a Vaporator or Hydroponics Station (+2 if both). While present with a Vaporator, each of your characters present is immune to attrition < 3.','Representative from the Moisture Farmers of Tatooine (local 253). Pays Jabba for protection from Sand People.',NULL,'6_2'),(1621,129,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Are You Brain Dead?!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/areyoubraindead.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Target your [Episode I] Jedi defending a battle. Target is immune to attrition for rest of turn (unless Dark Jedi present).  LOST: In a battle you lost, place a Jedi Council Member you just forfeited in Used Pile to cancel all battle damage and attrition against you.\"','\'I\'m not going in there with two Jedi!\'',NULL,'12_55'),(1622,5074,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 4','•Are You Okay?','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/areyouokay.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Subtract 2 from a just drawn destiny targeting the ability or defense value of your non-Jedi [Episode VII] character. OR If you just forfeited a character from a Jakku site during your turn, use 1 Force to deploy that character from Lost Pile to same site for free.','Blank.',NULL,'204_17'),(1623,131,'Light','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','•Arleil Schous','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Light/large/arleilschous.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','4','5','When deployed, you may take one non-unique alien into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Your aliens deploy -1 to same or adjacent Tatooine site.','One of the Rebellion\'s main contacts on Tatooine. Widely regarded as a leader in the Mos Eisley alien community. Aging male Defel. Has lost the ability to warp light.',NULL,'106_1'),(1624,132,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Armament Dismantled','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/armamentdismantled.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force (or 1 Force if Obi-Wan is armed with a lightsaber) to deploy on table if Maul present with Obi-Wan. (Obi-Wan may not move that turn.) Maul\'s lightsaber may add only 1 to Force drains, and may be \'swung\' only once per battle. (Immune to Alter.)','Divide and conquer.',NULL,'13_7'),(1625,133,'Light','U','Cloud City','Armed And Dangerous','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/armedanddangerous.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle or duel was just initiated at a site, deploy (for free) a unique matching weapon on one of your participating characters from hand or Reserve Deck; reshuffle (if from Reserve Deck).','The ability to retrieve his weapon by use of the Force was now second nature to Luke.',NULL,'5_32'),(1626,135,'Light','R2','Hoth','Artillery Remote','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/artilleryremote.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on any warrior. Your artillery weapons anywhere on same planet may fire without a warrior present. Also, once each turn during your control phase, one of your artillery weapons on same planet may be fired (at normal use of the Force).','Although artillery weapons have a manual firing mechanism, this optional device allows weapons operation from a remote location. Uses coded signals.',NULL,'3_28'),(1627,136,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Artoo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/artoo.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid',NULL,'1','4','5','During each of your control phases, may take one Hero Of A Thousand Devices or A Gift into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If at a battleground site with C-3PO, may subtract 1 from each opponent\'s battle destiny at same and related sites.','Counterpart to C-3PO. Spy. Obstinate, headstrong and always full of surprises. R2-D2 was an integral part of Luke Skywalker\'s rescue plans.',NULL,'6_3'),(1628,137,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Artoo & •Threepio','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/artoo&threepio.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','2','3','6','May pilot only Falcon. All droids may be battled. Any player that has no ability in a battle takes no battle damage. Once per turn, may take on card with \'Bad Feeling\' in title into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Bad Feeling Have I is suspended.','Threepio\'s extensive experience \'talking\' to the Falcon\'s computer allowed him to pilot the freighter while on Coruscant. Artoo, an R-unit droid, provided moral support.',NULL,'10_2'),(1629,138,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Artoo, Brave Little Droid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/artoobravelittledroid.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','6','1','4','4','While aboard any starfighter, adds 2 to its power and hyperspeed. While in battle at a system, may place Artoo in Used Pile to cancel a just-drawn battle destiny. Cancels Lateral Damage targeting a starship at same system.','Starship maintenance droid within the Naboo droid pool. Personally responsible for saving Amidala\'s starship and getting her to Tatooine.',NULL,'14_3'),(1630,5352,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Artoo, Brave Little Droid (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/artoobravelittledroidai.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','6','1','4','4','While aboard any starfighter, adds 2 to its power and hyperspeed. While in battle at a system, may place Artoo in Used Pile to cancel a just-drawn battle destiny. Cancels Lateral Damage targeting a starship at same system.','Starship maintenance droid within the Naboo droid pool. Personally responsible for saving Amidala\'s starship and getting her to Tatooine.',NULL,'14_4'),(1631,139,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Artoo, Come Back At Once!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/artoocomebackatonce.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Search your Reserve Deck, take one Hero Of A Thousand Devices into hand and reshuffle.  LOST: If R2-D2 is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve him. OR Use 3 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take R2-D2 into hand and reshuffle.\"','\'You haven\'t finished with me yet!\'',NULL,'5_33'),(1632,140,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Artoo, I Have A Bad Feeling About This','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/artooihaveabadfeelingaboutthis.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you are about to draw a battle destiny, instead use the destiny number of one of your droids in that battle. OR Add 1 to attrition against opponent for each droid you have in that battle. OR If R2-D2 and C-3PO are in battle together, opponent draws no battle destiny.','\'He says our instructions are to give it only to Jabba himself. I\'m terrible sorry. I\'m afraid he\'s ever so stubborn about these sort of things.\'',NULL,'6_60'),(1633,141,'Light','PM','Third Anthology','•Artoo-Detoo In Red 5','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ThirdAnthology-Light/large/artoodetooinred5.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: X-Wing',NULL,'3','4','5','May add 1 pilot. Permanent astromech aboard is *R2-D2, who adds 2 to power, maneuver and hyperspeed. Luke of ability < 5 deploys free aboard. Immune to attrition < 5 when Luke piloting.','R2-D2 saved Luke and his starfighter more times than the young pilot could count.',NULL,'111_2'),(1634,142,'Light','C','Cloud City','As Good As Gone','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/asgoodasgone.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, use 2 Force to return one of your smugglers, gamblers or thieves on table (unless captured or missing) to your hand.','Han\'s habit of leaving during a crisis was offset by his tendency to return when his friends needed him the most.',NULL,'5_34'),(1635,143,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Ascension Guns','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/ascensionguns.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, target any number of your characters at Theed Palace Hallway. Draw destiny. If destiny +2 > number of characters targeted, relocate those characters to one other interior Naboo site. Otherwise targets are lost.','Modified S-5 security blasters can be used for a wide array of purposes',NULL,'14_40'),(1636,4113,'Light','U','Virtual Set 1','•Ascension Guns (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/ascensionguns.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your deploy phase, use X Force (minimum 1) to relocate X of your characters at an interior Theed Palace site to Theed Palace 