, opponent loses X Force, where X = total number of asteroid sectors at same system that are not occupied by opponent. Effect canceled if opponent controls this location.','Smugglers and other criminals sometimes hide in asteroids to avoid capture. The larger the asteroid field, the more resources have to be devoted to the pursuit.',NULL,'4_17'),(1641,151,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Asteroids Do Not Concern Me','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/asteroidsdonotconcernme.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any asteroid sector. Target one opponent\'s capital starship. Pilots aboard target may not use ability to draw battle destiny. Subtract 4 from asteroid destiny when targeting that starship. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.','The personal fears of Vader\'s minions do not affect his priorities.',NULL,'4_18'),(1642,155,'Light','C','Dagobah','Astromech Translator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/astromechtranslator.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any starfighter. While an astromech character is aboard: If not piloted, starfighter may move and may use power, maneuver and hyperspeed. OR if piloted, starfighter is immune to attrition < 3 (< 6 if matching pilot aboard).','Standard technology found on hyperdrive-capable starfighters. Many manufacturers. Converts electronic impulses and high-density electronic languages into readable text.',NULL,'4_8'),(1643,157,'Light','R','Dagobah','•At Peace','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/atpeace.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any apprentice at the beginning of your turn. Apprentice \'rests\' (may not attempt Jedi Tests) until end of your next turn, then relocate Immediate Effect to Jedi Test. When attempting this test, that apprentice adds 3 to training destiny. (Immune to Control.)','To recover from the strenuous Jedi training routine and revitalize the mind and body, an apprentice must rest to be calm and at peace.',NULL,'4_19'),(1644,161,'Light','U2','Hoth','Atgar Laser Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/atgarlasercannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Artillery','5',NULL,'2','2','Deploy on an exterior planet site. Your warrior present may target a vehicle at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target crashes if destiny +2 > armor. Target hit if destiny +1 > maneuver.','Atgar 1.4 FD P-tower anti-vehicle cannon. Adapted to operate with minimal performance loss in the extremes of a cold environment.',NULL,'3_72'),(1645,167,'Light','U1','Hoth','Attack Pattern Delta','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/attackpatterndelta.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated at a site, identify your lead T-47 there. For remainder of this turn, all other T-47s at same site are power +1, are immune to attrition and cannot be targeted by weapons.','Snowspeeder attack plan devised by Commander Skywalker and Rebel tactician Beryl Chifonage. Single-file formation protects the squadron as the leader draws fire.',NULL,'3_40'),(1646,169,'Light','R2','A New Hope','•Attack Run','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/attackrun.gif?raw=true','Epic Event',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2_42'),(1647,170,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Attark','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/attark.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','3','2','When at a site you control, allows your Seekers to deploy free there. Attark also allows your Seekers to move for free and to ignore any or all potential target(s) whenever you choose.','From a mysterious species known as Hoovers. Possesses tremendous technical abilities. Small size allows him to easy manipulate detailed electronic equipment.','Velken Tezeri','6_4'),(1648,174,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Aved Luun','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/avedluun.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','2','Deploys only on Tatooine. During your control phase, may search Reserve Deck, take one Utinni! or Jawa into hand and reshuffle. If you have 3 or more Jawas on table, may play Utinni! to cancel a Force drain at a Tatooine site or to cancel Control.','Shaman of her Jawa tribe. Mate of Kalit. Suspects betrayal from her mate\'s rival, Wittin.',NULL,'6_5'),(1649,177,'Light','U','Dagobah','•Away Put Your Weapon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/awayputyourweapon.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If a lightsaber was just used to enhance a Force drain, place it in Owner\'s Used Pile.  LOST: Place any or all of your devices and character weapons on table in your Used Pile.\"','\'I mean you no harm.\'','Weapon Of An Ungrateful Son','4_45'),(1650,5017,'Light','C','Virtual Set 2','•Azure Angel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Light/large/azureangel.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified Delta-7 Interceptor','2','3','3','6','May add one pilot and one astromech. During battle, if Anakin or R2-D2 aboard, may lose 1 Force to cancel a non-[Immune to Sense] interrupt. While Anakin or R2-D2 aboard, immune to attrition < 5 (< 6 if both).','Blank.',NULL,'202_7'),(1651,5366,'Light','C','Virtual Set 2','•Azure Angel (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialAI-Light/large/azureangel.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified Delta-7 Interceptor','2','3','3','6','May add one pilot and one astromech. During battle, if Anakin or R2-D2 aboard, may lose 1 Force to cancel a non-[Immune to Sense] interrupt. While Anakin or R2-D2 aboard, immune to attrition < 5 (< 6 if both).','Blank.',NULL,'202_7'),(1652,340,'Light','F','Special Edition','B-wing Attack Fighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/bwingattackfighter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: B-Wing','3','4','3','4','Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. May fire 2 or more weapons during battle. Each of its destiny draws is +1. During your turn, may use 1 Force to \'defuse\' (lose) an Orbital Mine present.','First models designed in Roche asteroid field by Admiral Ackbar\'s team of Verpine engineers. Early design equipped to detect and neutralize Imperial orbital mines.',NULL,'7_140'),(1653,341,'Light','R','Death Star II','B-wing Attack Squadron','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/bwingattacksquadron.gif?raw=true','Starship','Squadron: B-Wing','3','12','*','12','* Replaces 3 B-Wings at one location (B-wings go to Used Pile). Permanent pilots provide total ability of 3. Each of its weapon destiny draws is +1.','Utilizes dense formations on attack mission to concentrate firepower. This tactic is particulary effective in defeating deflector shields.',NULL,'9_65'),(1654,342,'Light','C','Death Star II','B-wing Bomber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/bwingbomber.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: B-Wing','3','4','3','4','May add 1 pilot (suspends permanent pilot). Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. May fire two or more weapons during battle. Each of its ion cannon weapon destiny draws is +3.','Carries weapon systems capable of taking on escort frigates and capital starships. Armed with high-powered ion cannon used to disable deflector shields.',NULL,'9_66'),(1655,184,'Light','R2','Hoth','•Bacta Tank','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/bactatank.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',