attle Plan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/battleplan.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. For either player to initiate a Force drain, that player must first use 3 Force unless that player occupies a battleground site and a battleground system.','Even though the landing of the stolen shuttle was successful, the Rebel strike team on Endor was forced to rethink their plans when Leia disappeared.','Battle Order - Defensive Shield','13_8'),(1663,213,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Battle Plan & •Draw Their Fire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/battleplan&drawtheirfire.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. You may initiate battles for free. During a battle you initiate, each time opponent plays an interrupt, opponent must first use 1 Force. For either player to initiate a Force drain, that player must first use 3 Force unless that player occupies a battleground site and a battleground system. (Immune to Alter.)',NULL,'Battle Order & First Strike','12_41'),(1664,5316,'Light','C','Virtual Set 9','•Admiral Raddus','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/admiralraddus.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','0','4','Your capital starships here are power +1. Once per game, may take Rogue One, a Hammerhead corvette, or a non-unique corvette into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Mon Calamari leader.',NULL,'209_1'),(1665,5213,'Light','C','Virtual Set 8','•Admiral U.O. Statura','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/admiraluostatura.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','3','2','3','5','At same location, Resistance characters and [Resistance] starships are each defense value and forfeit +1. While at an [Episode VII] location with a Resistance leader, adds one battle destiny.','Leader.',NULL,'208_1'),(1666,64,'Light','U1','A New Hope','Advance Preparation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/advancepreparation.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Place out of play any one of the following from your hand: Attack Run, You\'re All Clear Kid, Death Star: Trench or Rebel Tech. Retrieve 1 Force.  LOST: Use 3 Force to retrieve Attack Run.\"','Early warning and careful planning allow the Rebels to achieve maximum readiness while still maintaining optimal flexibility.',NULL,'2_43'),(1667,68,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Affect Mind','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/affectmind.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on one of your Jedi. Unless a Dark Jedi is also present, opponent\'s total ability at same location is reduced by 2.','\'What was that?\' The Jedi power known as \'affect mind\' is often used to create minor distractions, allowing Jedi to elude enemies rather than engage them in battle.','I Find Your Lack Of Faith Disturbing','1_43'),(1668,66,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Advantage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/advantage.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'f an opponent\'s character of ability > 3 was just lost in a battle or duel you won, deploy on one of your warriors involved. Warrior is power +2. During each of opponent\'s move phases, opponent loses 1 Force (2 if character was a Dark Jedi). (Immune to Control.)','With only a few Jedi remaining in the galaxy, each confrontation between them has far reaching consequences.',NULL,'5_16'),(1669,217,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Beldon\'s Eye','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/beldonseye.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Bespin: Cloud City. Your Tibanna Gas Miners deploy free to Cloud City sites and double the Force they activate.','Symbol for the Cloud City Miner\'s Guild (not affiliated with the Galactic Miner\'s Guild). Named after the beldons, giant creatures who generate Tibanna gas.',NULL,'5_18'),(1670,5376,'Light','R','Virtual Set 11','•Beldon\'s Eye & •All My Urchins','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/beldonseyeallmyurchins.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per game, if Quiet Mining Colony on table, may search your hand and/or Reserve Deck and reveal an [Independent] starfighter and matching pilot; place both in hand, reshuffle; they each deploy -1 this turn. Once per game, if a battle just initiated at Bespin system with Executor there, may cancel that battle unless opponent uses 15 Force. [Immune to Alter.]',NULL,NULL,'211_31'),(1671,218,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Beldon\'s Eye (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/beldonseye.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your [Independent Starship] starships are defense value +2 at Bespin locations. Once per game, if Quiet Mining Colony on table, may simultaneously deploy a unique (•) [Independent Starship] starfighter and matching pilot (for -1 Force each) from your hand and/or Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Symbol for the Cloud City Miner\'s Guild (not affiliated with the Galactic Miner\'s Guild). Named after the beldons, giant creatures who generate Tibanna gas.',NULL,'200_36'),(1672,219,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Ben Kenobi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/benkenobi.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','5','5','9','Deploys only on Tatooine. When in a duel, adds 2 to your total. Once per turn, if a battle just ended here, may \'revive\' (place here from Lost Pile) your character forfeited from same site this turn. Immune to attrition < 5.','Served Bail Organa during the Clone Wars. Saved Anakin\'s lightsaber until he was able to give it to Luke. Hasn\'t gone by the name Obi-Wan for a long time.',NULL,'7_4'),(1673,221,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Beru Lars','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/berulars.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','1','1','3','Forfeit +2 when at same site as Owen Lars or a Hydroponics Station. If lost from table during opponent\'s turn, Luke is power +3 until the end of your next turn.','Wife of Owen Lars and guardian of Luke Skywalker. Quietly lobbied Owen to allow Luke to attend Academy. Maintains Lars\' farm hydroponics labs.',NULL,'1_2'),(1674,222,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Beru Stew','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/berustew.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Each player must immediately activate 2 Force. Also, you may activate 1 additional Force for each Beru Lars, Owen Lars or Hydroponics Station on table.','Moisture farmers grow enough food to sustain Tatooine\'s population. Beru Lars has devised many dishes using herbs and roots naturally found in Tatooine\'s desert.',NULL,'1_72'),(1675,226,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Bespin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/bespin.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, opponent\'s characters and vehicles deploy +1 to Cloud City locations',NULL,NULL,'5_76'),(1676,229,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Bespin: Cloud City','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/bespincloudcity.gif?raw=true','Location','Sector','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, for each of your starships or vehicles here, your total power is +1 in battles at Cloud City sites.',NULL,'Bespin: Cloud City','5_77'),(1677,230,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•BG-J38','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/bgj38.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','2','2','May add 2 to the destiny of each of your holograms and dejariks drawn for battle destiny or weapon destiny. While at a site you control, adds 1 to power of each of your dejariks and holograms at a holosite.','Roche J9 worker drone. Undefeated hologame player. Kept by Jabba as a source of entertainment. Hoping for escape or termination.',NULL,'6_7'),(1678,234,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•Big Boomers!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/bigboomers.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If there is more than 1 card in opponent\'s Force Pile, opponent must use 1 Force. OR Take a Fambaa or Booma into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If you just drew weapon destiny for your Booma, cancel that destiny to cause a re-draw.','Gungan weaponry can be quite sophisticated. Sometimes its users are not.',NULL,'14_41'),(1679,236,'Light','U','Dagobah','<>Big One','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/bigone.gif?raw=true','Location','Sector','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Asteroid Rules\' in effect here. If you control, Force drain +1 here for each Asteroid Field at same system.',NULL,'Big One','4_82'),(1680,238,'Light','U','Dagobah','<>Big One: Asteroid Cave Or Space Slug Belly','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/bigoneasteroidcaveorspaceslugbelly.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Cave Rules\' in effect here. If you control, may cancel Force drains at system Related to Big One.',NULL,'Big One: Asteroid Cave or Space Slug Belly','4_83'),(1681,239,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Biggs Darklighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/biggsdarklighter.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Red 3, also adds 1 to maneuver and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Piloted Red 3 at Battle of Yavin. Childhood friend of Luke. Led mutiny on Rand Ecliptic and theft of Ecliptic from shipyards on Bestine. Ecliptic Evaders emblem on helmet.',NULL,'1_3'),(1682,244,'Light','R','Cloud City','Bionic Hand','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/bionichand.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on a Disarmed character. Cancels the disarming card. Character is power +1 and adds 1 to weapon destiny when firing character weapons. Device lost if character Disarmed again (otherwise, may not be removed).','Uses state-of-the-art digital processors. Although Luke had lost his hand, the Alliance could rebuild it. They had the technology. They could make it better, stronger, faster.',NULL,'5_12'),(1683,255,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Blast The Door, Kid!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/blastthedoorkid.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated at an interior site, use 1 Force; for remainder of battle, all characters of ability > 2 and all leaders (on both sides) are simultaneously excluded from that battle.','When Vader turned his attention to the escaping Rebels, Han immediately offered Luke some sage advice.','Stunning Leader','2_45'),(1684,256,'Light','C','Endor','BlasTech E-11B Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/blasteche11bblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your scout warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value. May fire repeatedly for 2 Force each time.','Modified by Alliance armorers who defected from the BlasTech corporation. Expensive cooling system incorporated to allow higher fire rate.',NULL,'8_85'),(1685,258,'Light','C','Dagobah','•Blasted Varmints','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/blastedvarmints.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to cause all Mynocks or Vine Snakes to detach from one starfighter or character. OR Cause one Mynock attached to any starfighter to be lost. OR After creature has selected a target character, cancel that selection and select again.','\'I just got this bucket back together. I\'m not gonna let something tear it apart.\'',NULL,'4_46'),(1686,259,'Light','C2','Premiere','Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/blaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value.','A Merr-Sonn Model 44 blaster pistol. Uses power packs and highenergy blaster gases to shoot bolts of explosive coherent light energy.','Imperial Blaster','1_152'),(1687,260,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Blaster Deflection','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/blasterdeflection.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel an attempt to use a character weapon to target your character of ability > 4.  LOST: If your character of ability > 4 with a lightsaber was just targeted by a blaster, use 3 Force to re-target that blaster to an opponent\'s character present.\"','A Jedi can anticipate the actions of his opponent and let the Force control his actions, causing him to effortlessly deflect an opponent\'s attacks.','Force Field','6_61'),(1688,261,'Light','C','Cloud City','•Blaster Proficiency','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/blasterproficiency.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If you just targeted with a blaster, add 3 to your weapon destiny.  LOST: Lose 1 Force to cause one opponent\'s character just \'hit\' to be immediately placed in Lost Pile. OR Cancel Levitation Attack.\"','Some people think that hokey religions and ancient weapons are no match for a good blaster at your side.','Dark Strike','5_35'),(1689,265,'Light','C1','Premiere','Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/blasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.','BlasTech E-11 blaster rifle. Standard issue for Imperial forces. So numerous that many have been stolen by Rebels. Extendable stock. Carries energy for 100 shots.','Blaster Rifle','1_153'),(1690,4095,'Light','C1','Virtual Set 0','Blaster Rifle (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/blasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Republic warrior; warrior is power +1. May target a character, creature, or vehicle for free. Draw destiny; add 1 if targeting a character, 2 if a vehicle. Target hit, and may not be used to satisfy attrition, if total destiny > defense value.','BlasTech E-11 blaster rifle. Standard issue for Imperial forces. So numerous that many have been stolen by Rebels. Extendable stock. Carries energy for 100 shots.',NULL,'200_69'),(1691,278,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Blockade Flagship: Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/blockadeflagshipdockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : This site may not be converted.',NULL,'Blockade Flagship: Docking Bay','14_48'),(1692,5386,'Light','R','Virtual Set 9','•Blue 11','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/blue11.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: U-Wing','4','4','4','6','May add 1 pilot and 2 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. Once per turn, may deploy a non-pilot Rebel of ability < 5 aboard from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 4.','Enclosed.',NULL,'209_32'),(1693,282,'Light','C2','A New Hope','•Blue Milk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/bluemilk.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Select a player to activate 1 Force.  LOST: Cancel Juri Juice or Hypo.\"','Nutrient-rich beverage common in moisture farm communities. Rumored to have medicinal qualities. Popular in cantinas among those who can\'t hold their juri juice.',NULL,'2_46'),(1694,5387,'Light','U','Virtual Set 10','•Blue Squadron 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/bluesquadron1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: X-Wing','2','3','3','5','May add 1 pilot. Snap deploys free aboard. While Snap piloting, immune to attrition < 5 and, once per turn, may use 1 Force to cancel a Force drain at another system within 1 parsec of Snap.','Blank.',NULL,'210_5'),(1695,283,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Blue Squadron 5','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/bluesquadron5.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: B-Wing','2','4','2','4','May add 1 pilot. May fire two or more weapons during battle. Each of its weapon destiny draws is +2. Immune to attrition < 4 when Ten Numb piloting.','Blue Squadron B-Wing. Ordered to lead attack on Executor. Drew enemy fighters away from strike force led by General Calrissian and Commander Antilles.',NULL,'9_63'),(1696,284,'Light','R','Death Star II','•••Blue Squadron B-wing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/bluesquadronbwing.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: B-Wing','3','4','5','4','Deploy -2 to Roche. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2 and adds 1 to power. May fire two or more weapons during battle. Each of its weapon destiny draws is +2.','B-wings ordered to attack Imperial command starships at Battle of Endor. Armed with armor-penetrating missiles. Maintained by Verpine mechanics.',NULL,'9_64'),(1697,285,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Bo Shuda','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/boshuda.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Audience Chamber. If you have an alien here, no battles or Force drains may take place here and your aliens cannot be targeted by Trap Door. Effect canceled if opponent occupies this site without an alien. (Immune to Alter.)','In order to remain a successful crime lord, Jabba must ensure the safety of all those who seek to do business with him.',NULL,'6_54'),(1698,5146,'Light','C','Virtual Set 6','•Bodhi Rook','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual6-Light/large/bodhirook.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots, 3 if Rogue One or a stolen starship. May be deployed simultaneously with a piloted starship from hand to a system even without presence or Force icons. If about to be lost, your Rebel or Rebel starship at a related location may make a regular move.','Gambler and spy.',NULL,'206_1'),(1699,297,'Light','C','Dagobah','Bog-wing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/bogwing.gif?raw=true','Creature','Avian','5','*','2','0','* Ferocity = destiny -1. Habitat: Dagobah. Parasite: Character (that can move). Relocate Bog-wing and host up to two sites away (opponent of victim chooses). Bog-wing then detaches.','Large, flying jungle predator. One to five meters long, including tail. Swoops down and grasps victims in its claws. Young are born in mid-flight, as the mother drops from extreme altitude.','Bog-wing','4_3'),(1700,183,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','•••B\'omarr Monk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/bomarrmonk.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','0','3','4','While at a site, adds Force icons to equalize them for both sides. Cancels opponent\'s Jabba\'s Palace game text where present. Can not use vehicles, starships, weapons, or devices. Participates only in defensive battles. Lost if not on Tatooine.','Members of a mysterious religious sect. Resentful of their monastery being taken over by Jabba. Shed their bodies and have their brains encased in a walking automaton.',NULL,'6_8'),(1701,300,'Light','C','Theed Palace','Booma','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/booma.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Vehicle','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Fambaa. Twice during battle may draw destiny. If destiny < total number of opponent\'s characters and vehicles present, one of them is lost (opponent\'s choice).','Launched from fambaa-mounted catapults. Gungan \'energy balls\' are used to disable a variety of mechanized threats. Effectiveness is enhanced by the skill of the user.',NULL,'14_63'),(1702,302,'Light','R','Tatooine','Boonta Eve Podrace','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/boontaevepodrace.gif?raw=true','Epic Event',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Once per game, either player may initiate a Podrace: During opponent\'s control phase, each player may draw one race destiny. Each player may place any drawn race destiny on their Podracer (or on Podrace Arena if they have none) or in their Used Pile. During any move phase, winner is any player with a race total > 24 and greater than opponent\'s highest race total. Winner retrieves 6 Force and loser loses 6 Force. Place all race destiny cards in owner\'s Used Piles and all Podracers are lost.',NULL,'Boonta Eve Podrace','11_24'),(1703,4087,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Booster In Pulsar Skate','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/boosterinpulsarskate.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Baudo-Class Star Yacht','2','4','4','4','May add 1 pilot and 6 passengers.  Permanent pilot is •Booster, who provides ability of 3. Once per game, may deploy Mirax here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to Lateral Damage and attrition < 5.','Owned by legendary Terrik family of smugglers. Used to chase down the pirates who killed Wedge\'s parents. On Corellian Security\'s most wanted list. 37.5 meters long.',NULL,'200_60'),(1704,305,'Light','U1','Premiere','•BoShek','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/boshek.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','2','4','3','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. May make a Kessel Run in place of a smuggler. Immune to attrition < 3.','Rogue pilot. Outlaw starship tech. Has secret lab in Mos Eisley. He bragged about beating Han Solo\'s Kessel Run record. Left fringe life behind after meeting Obi-Wan Kenobi.',NULL,'1_4'),(1705,5391,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 10','•BoShek (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/boshek.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','3','5','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. BoShek\'s deploy cost may not be increased. During battle, may use 1 Force to subtract 1 from opponent\'s just drawn destiny or cancel an attempt to cancel and redraw a destiny. Immune to attrition < 3.','Rogue pilot. Outlaw starship tech. Has secret lab in Mos Eisley. He bragged about beating Han Solo\'s Kessel Run record. Left fringe life behind after meeting Obi-Wan Kenobi.',NULL,'210_6'),(1706,307,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Boss Nass','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/bossnass.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','3','6','While at an underwater site and all of your characters on Naboo are Gungans: add one battle destiny in battles at Naboo sites and once during your deploy phase may deploy a Gungan or Steady, Steady from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Ankura Gungan who is the leader of his people. Prone to nervous tics. Personally responsible for uniting the Ankura and Otolla races together.',NULL,'14_5'),(1707,5393,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Boss Nass (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/bossnassai.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','3','6','While at an underwater site and all of your characters on Naboo are Gungans: add one battle destiny in battles at Naboo sites and once during your deploy phase may deploy a Gungan or Steady, Steady from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Ankura Gungan who is the leader of his people. Prone to nervous tics. Personally responsible for uniting the Ankura and Otolla races together.',NULL,'14_6'),(1708,313,'Light','C','Special Edition','Bothan Spy','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/bothanspy.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','May be targeted (instead of a droid) by Death Star Plans. When targeted by Death Star Plans, makes that Effect immune to Alter and adds one destiny to Force retrieved with Death Star Plans. May not be targeted by Nabrun Leids.','Bothans operate the most complex spy network in the galaxy. Discovered the location of the second Death Star. Ambitious. Resourceful. Furry. Tend to die in large numbers.',NULL,'7_5'),(1709,314,'Light','F','Special Edition','•Bothawui','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/bothawui.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your spies deploy -1 here and at related sites. If you control, characters targeted by Undercover are immune to Hutt Smooch.',NULL,NULL,'7_110'),(1710,315,'Light','C','Special Edition','Bothawui Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/bothawuioperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','3','While at a Bothawui site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is forfeit +1 (and power +1 if your Bothan is on Bothawui) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Bothawui from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Gran pacifists responsible for maintaining contact with the Bothans. Some are stationed on the Bothan homeworld to help monitor sensitive information.',NULL,'7_6'),(1711,317,'Light','PM','Enhanced Jabba\'s Palace','•Boushh','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedJabbasPalace-Light/large/boushh.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','6','7','Deploys only to a site (-2 on Tatooine or Coruscant) as an Undercover Spy. While undercover at an opponents site, prevents opponent from modifying or cancelling your Force Drains at opponent\'s related sites. Immune to Attrition < 3.','Leia obtained the armor of a notorious mercenary to sneak onto Coruscant. She later assumed the same role to spy on Jabba. Fearless and inventive. Jabba\'s kind of scum.',NULL,'110_1'),(1712,318,'Light','R2','A New Hope','Bowcaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/bowcaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use X Force to deploy on your warrior, where X = (7 - warrior\'s power). X cannot fall below 1. May target a character or creature using X Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a character, 2 if targeting a creature. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Hand-crafted weapon of choice among Wookiees. Fires explosive \'quarrels\' (which look like blaster bolts). Requires great strength to use. Extra ammo carried on bandoleers.',NULL,'2_77'),(1713,319,'Light','R1','A New Hope','•Brainiac','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/brainiac.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien',NULL,'*',NULL,NULL,'* Power = v(3(X-Y)+2(A-B)+ p) (minimum power =1). X = Dark Side hand cards; Y = Light Side hand cards; A = total number of Dark icons in play; B = total number of Light icons in play; p?= 3.141592653589793238462643383...','BoShek nicknamed this male Siniteen \'Brainiac\' due to his ability to calculate hyperspace coordinates in his head. \'He\'s the brains, sweetheart!\'',NULL,'2_2'),(1714,321,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Bravo 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/bravo1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: N-1 Starfighter','3','2','1','3','Deploys -1 to Naboo. May add 1 pilot. While Ric piloting, immune to attrition < 4 and draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.','Ric Olie\'s starfighter at the battle of Naboo. Conrtol configuration modified by Ric himself.',NULL,'14_53'),(1715,322,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Bravo 2','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/bravo2.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: N-1 Starfighter','2','2','1','3','Deploys -1 to Naboo. May add 1 pilot. While Dolphe piloting, immune to attrition < 4. While at Naboo system, your Bravo Squadron pilots at same system are forfeit +2.','Starfighter assigned to Officer Dolphe at the battle of Naboo. Damaged when the Trade Federation first invaded his planet, but Dolphe was able to make the necessary repairs.',NULL,'14_54'),(1716,323,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Bravo 3','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/bravo3.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: N-1 Starfighter','2','2','1','3','Deploys - 1 to Naboo. May add one pilot. While Arven piloting, immune to attrition < 4. While at Naboo system, opponent\'s battle destiny draws are - 1 here.','Arven Wendik\'s starfighter at the Battle of Naboo. Oldest starfighter in the Naboo corps.',NULL,'1