hip with no character piloting. Draw destiny. If destiny > defense value, target hit. Immune to attrition < 3.','Flown by an unknown pilot who likes to spin a lot. Played the deciding role in the attack against the Droid Control Ship.',NULL,'200_61'),(1721,329,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Bren Quersey','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/brenquersey.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to anything he pilots. When piloting Red 8 during battle, adds one destiny to total power only. When at Raithal system, adds 1 to each of your Force drains there.','Piloted Red 8 at the Battle of Yavin. Dreamed of attending the prestigious Raithal Academy. Trained on X-wings by Wedge Antilles.',NULL,'7_7'),(1722,332,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Bright Hope','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/brighthope.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Transport','3','1','3','5','May add 1 pilot and 6 passengers. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','Modified medium transport. Well armored. Has expanded passenger capacity to facilitate evacuation. The last transport to escape Hoth. Nearly destroyed by the Stalker.',NULL,'5_86'),(1723,5052,'Light','R','Virtual Set 3','•Bright Hope (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/brighthope.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Transport','3','1','3','5','May add 2 pilots and 6 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. If in battle with another Rebel capital starship, may draw destiny. Subtract that amount from opponent\'s attrition and total power.','Modified medium transport. Well armored. Has expanded passenger capacity to facilitate evacuation. The last transport to escape Hoth. Nearly destroyed by the Stalker.',NULL,'203_20'),(1724,335,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Brisky Morning Munchen','