y not use its game text for remainder of turn).','Information broker and spy.',NULL,'208_2'),(1728,345,'Light','U2','Hoth','•Cal Alder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/calalder.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','3','Power +1 at Defensive Perimeter. Your vehicles move for free if moving toward same site as Cal.','An expert Scout originally from Kai\'Shebbol in the Kathol sector. Served with Bren Derlin for many years. Patrols the outer perimeter of Echo Base.',NULL,'3_2'),(1729,5147,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 6','•Cal Alder (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual6-Light/large/calalder.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','May deploy as a \'react\'. Deploys -1 to same site as a Rebel leader. Unless with Luke, opponent must first use 1 Force to fire a weapon at same site. Elis Helrot may not transport characters to or from here.','An expert Scout originally from Kai\'Shebbol in the Kathol sector. Served with Bren Derlin for many years. Patrols the outer perimeter of Echo Base.','Greedo (V)','206_2'),(1730,346,'Light','C','Tatooine','•Caldera Righim','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/calderarighim.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','3','Unless Great Warrior on table, opponent must have total ability < 8 to initiate a battle at same site. Also, whenever a battle is initiated at same site both players may draw up to 2 cards from top of their Reserve Deck.','Male Talz. Somewhat of a pacifist, Caldera has always been an opponent to violence in the cantina. Personal friend of Wuher.',NULL,'11_1'),(1731,348,'Light','U2','Premiere','Caller','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/caller.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Rebel or Jawa. During your control phase, may steal one droid at same site if it is controlled by a 