ther Gungans at same site. Opponent\'s characters may not move to underwater sites. Once per turn, if you just drew a Gungan for battle destiny, may deploy that Gungan for free to cancel that destiny and re-draw.','Gungan leader of the forces that patrol and protect the city of Otoh Gunga. Consistantly placed in the top ten of the Big Nasty Free-For-All.',NULL,'14_7'),(1743,372,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•Captain Tarpals\' Electropole','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/captaintarpalselectropole.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploys on Captain Tarpals. May \'throw\' (place in Used Pile) to target a character, creature or vehicle for free. Draw destiny. If destiny +3 > defense value, target is landspeed = 0 and power - 3 for remainder of turn.','Tarpals\' electropole is nearly as old as he is. Used to enforce the laws of Otoh Gunga.',NULL,'14_64'),(1744,373,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Captain Verrack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/captainverrack.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','4','Allows your starship weapons at same location to fire and deploy for 1 less Force. While aboard your capital starship, adds 1 to each of its weapon destiny draws (2 when targeting a capital starship).','Mon Calamari computer technician. Expert in power systems. His skills are desperately needed by Rebel fleet. Gunner.',NULL,'9_7'),(1745,375,'Light','U','Endor','•Captain Yutani','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/captainyutani.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','3','2','3','Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one artillery weapon or Portable Fusion Generator to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. May move Medium Repeating Blaster Cannon by himself (for free).','Scout and heavy weapons specialist. Carries custom repulsorlift compensators to allow fluid movement with light artillery weapons.',NULL,'8_1'),(1746,4068,'Light','C1','Virtual Set 0','•Captain Yutani With Blaster Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/captainyutaniwithblastercannon.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','3','3','4','Artillery weapons here are \'powered.\'  Permanent weapon is Blaster Cannon (may target a character, creature, or vehicle at same or adjacent site for free; draw destiny; target \'hit,\' and its forfeit = 0, if destiny +1 > defense value).','Scout.',NULL,'200_4'),(1747,376,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Captive Fury','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/captivefury.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Force drain bonus from IT-O this turn.  LOST: During your battle phase, any of your escorted captives at same site may initiate and participate in one battle (they may not use weapons or devices and you may not voluntarily forfeit or relocate them).\"','Chewie\'s life debt to Han forced him to act, retaliating unexpectedly against his captors.',NULL,'5_36'),(1748,377,'Light','C','Cloud City','Captive Pursuit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/captivepursuit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If a battle was just initiated at a site, target a captive present. Captive released if you win battle.  LOST: Cancel Aiiii! Aaa! Aggggggggggggg!, Sonic Bombardment, Interrogation Array, This Is Some Rescue or Special Delivery.\"','Han could have used a hand. Fortunately, Luke still had one to give.',NULL,'5_37'),(1749,381,'Light','C','Endor','•Careful Planning','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/carefulplanning.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Starting','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If a battle was just initiated, draw destiny and activate up to that much Force.  START