=true','Character','Alien','4','1','2','2','Power and forfeit +2 while Kabe at Audience Chamber. During your control phase, may glance at one card randomly selected from opponent\'s hand; if that card is a character weapon, may \'steal\' it into your hand.','Short, intelligent and selfish. Their enhanced vision and smell make them outstanding Thieves. Communicate with pheromones and high-pitched squeaks.',NULL,'6_9'),(1754,389,'Light','U','Endor','•Chandrila','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/chandrila.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy with a capital starship, Force generation +2 for you here. Mon Mothma deploys -2 at any Chandrila location.',NULL,NULL,'8_67'),(1755,390,'Light','C','Tatooine','•Changing The Odds','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/changingtheodds.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just drew battle destiny (or destiny for Watto\'s Chance Cube), subtract one from that destiny. OR If you just verified opponent\'s Reserve Deck, search that Reserve Deck and place one Interrupt found there out of play.','Qui-Gon used his Jedi abilities to insure that there was no \'chance\' involved with the use of Watto\'s chance cube.',NULL,'11_31'),(1756,392,'Light','U','Cloud City','Chasm','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/chasm.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If a unique (•) card is drawn for destiny and a duplicate is on table, destiny card is lost (destiny = 0). If duplicated card is a character, it loses immunity to attrition for rest of turn and player must lose 2 Force or lose that character. (Immune to Alter.)','At Cloud City, Luke came face to face with his own destiny. Looking into the abyss, he made his decision.','Abyss','5_19'),(1757,394,'Light','R2','A New Hope','•Chewbacca','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/chewbacca.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien/Rebel','1','6','4','6','Power +1 at same location as Han. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Falcon, also adds 1 to maneuver. Your vehicles, starships, and droids at same site that are \'hit\' and about to be lost go to Used Pile instead.','Wookiee smuggler from Kashyyyk. Over 200 years old. Top-notch mechanic and pilot. Jabba has large bounty on this \'walking carpet.\' Friends call him Chewie...or Fuzzball.',NULL,'2_3'),(1758,396,'Light','R','Endor','•Chewbacca Of Kashyyyk','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/chewbaccaofkashyyyk.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','6','6','7','Deploys -2 on Endor. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When targeted by a weapon, may \'roar\' (defense value = 4). When on Endor during your deploy phase, may deploy Lumat and/or Wuta for free here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Wookiee scout. Volunteered for Han\'s Endor strike team. Keeps his distance, but doesn\'t look like he\'s keeping his distance. Always thinks with his stomach.',NULL,'8_2'),(1759,397,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Chewbacca, Protector','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/chewbaccaprotector.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','6','5','6','Deploys -3 to same site as Leia. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if Falcon). Once per turn, may target opponent\'s character at same site who has power < 4 and cancel target\'s game text for remainder of turn.','Chewie honored his life debt to Han by protecting Leia. Posed as the mercenary Snoova while on Coruscant. Smuggler. Wookiee.',NULL,'10_3'),(1760,399,'Light','R','Endor','•Chewbacca\'s Bowcaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/chewbaccasbowcaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Chewie, or use 4 Force to deploy on your other Wookiee. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 3 Force (for free if Chewie firing). Draw two destiny. Target hit if total destiny > defense value. If hit by Chewie, target\'s forfeit = 0.','Specially modified by Chewbacca. Fires larger bolts with more accuracy. Superior targeting at long distances.',NULL,'8_86'),(1761,5164,'Light','C','Virtual Set 7','•Baze Malbus With Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/bazemalbuswithcannon.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','4','4','5','If about to be lost, may fire Baze\'s Cannon. Permanent weapon is •Baze\'s Cannon (may target a character for free; draw destiny;  add 1 if targeting a character of ability < 3; target hit, and it\'s forfeit = 0, if destiny +1 > defense value).',NULL,NULL,'207_1'),(1762,5088,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 4','•BB-8 (Beebee-Ate)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/bb8.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','Pi or 2Pi','1','2','4','If just forfeited from a site, opponent may capture BB-8. While a captive, adds 1 to Force drains at same site. During your control phase, if at a battleground site and present with a Resistance character, opponent loses 1 Force.','Blank.',NULL,'204_1'),(1763,5373,'Light','U','Virtual Set 11','•BB-8 In Black Squadron 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/bb8inblacksquadron1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: X-wing',NULL,'4','3','5','May add 1 pilot. Permanent astromech aboard is •BB-8. If Poe piloting, may lose 1 Force to cancel a just drawn weapon destiny targeting this starship. Immune to attrition < 4.','Blank.',NULL,'211_28'),(1764,215,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Beggar','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/beggar.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on any exterior Tatooine site (free at Beggar\'s Canyon). You may use any amount of Force in the opponent\'s Force Pile during your turns. However, if you use more than 1 of the opponent\'s Force in a turn, Beggar is lost.','Many Mos Eisley citizens, once swindled and robbed, become destitute. Unable to afford off-planet passage, they live in the streets and do odd jobs or beg.',NULL,'1_44'),(1765,403,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Chewie, Enraged','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/chewieenraged.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','9','6','6','X = number of Imperials present. While with Han or Leia, adds 2 to your battle destiny draws here. During your turn, target one Imperial pr power < 5 present. Target\'s game text canceled for remainder of turn. End of your turn: Use 2 Force to maintain OR Lose 1 Force to place in Used Pile OR Place out of play.','Smuggler. Very few people need to be told that angry Wookiees should be given a wide berth.',NULL,'13_9'),(1766,404,'Light','R','Endor','•Chewie\'s AT-ST','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/chewiesatst.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: AT-ST','4','3','2','5','Deploy only to Endor or same site as Chewie or opponent\'s AT-ST. May add 2 pilots or passengers. Subtracts 1 from power of other AT-STs at same site. Immune to attrition < 4 when Chewie piloting.','Enclosed Chewie\'s daring capture of an Imperial AT-ST helped turn the tide in the Battle of Endor.',NULL,'8_81'),(1767,407,'Light','R','Endor','•Chief Chirpa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/chiefchirpa.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','0','3','2','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one non-unique Ewok to same Endor site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Leader of Wicket\'s Ewok tribe for 42 seasons. Head of the Council of Elders. Decided to spare Han\'s Rebels and join their fight against the Empire.',NULL,'8_3'),(1768,5165,'Light','C','Virtual Set 7','•Chirrut Imwe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/chirrutimwe.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','4','4','5','If a battle was just inititaed here, may peek at the top card of any Reserve Desk; return it or place it on top of owner\'s Force Pile. If just lost, may take into hand from reserve deck; reshuffle or retrieve Baze. Once per game, you may re-circulate.',NULL,NULL,'207_2'),(1769,411,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Choke','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/choke.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, cancel the game text of one unique (•) alien for remainder of turn. OR If you just forfeited an alien, cancel all remaining attrition against you.','Reaching out with the Force, Luke rendered Ortugg unconscious without doing the Gamorrean any actual harm.',NULL,'6_62'),(1770,5421,'Light','PM','Demo Deck','City In The Clouds / You Truly Belong Here With Us','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DemoDeck-Light/large/cityintheclouds.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'City In The Clouds:Deploy Bespin system and a Cloud City battleground site. {While} this side up, once per turn may use 1 Force to deploy a Cloud City battleground site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. {Flip} this card if you control two Cloud City battleground sites and occupy Bespin system, and opponent controls no Cloud City sites.You Truly Belong Here With Us:{While} this side up, once per game, may deploy Cloud City Celebration from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once during your control phase, may use 2 Force to take one Interrupt into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per turn, may move your character as a \'react\' to a battle or Force drain at a Cloud City site. {Flip} this card if opponent controls more Cloud City sites than you.',NULL,NULL,'301_2'),(1771,414,'Light','C','Cloud City','•Civil Disorder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/civildisorder.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s side of table. At the end of opponent\'s deploy phase, if they did not deploy a card with ability, opponent loses 2 Force. Effect lost if opponent has more cards with ability on table than you. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Attention. This is Lando Calrissian. The Empire has taken control of the city. I advise everyone to leave before more Imperial troops arrive.\'','Ability, Ability, Ability','5_20'),(1772,415,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Civil Disorder (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/civildisorder.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. You may not play Rebel Barrier. Senators are deploy +2. Whenever you initiate a battle, may retrieve your topmost non-[Permanent Weapon], non-[Maintenance] character. May place the top card of your Reserve Deck in Lost Pile to place a combat card in owner\'s Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Attention. This is Lando Calrissian. The Empire has taken control of the city. I advise everyone to leave before more Imperial troops arrive.\'','Ability, Ability, Ability (V)','200_37'),(1773,416,'Light','R2','A New Hope','•Clak\'dor VII','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/clakdorvii.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy, each Bith character is destiny +2.',NULL,NULL,'2_60'),(1774,417,'Light','U','Special Edition','Clak\'dor VII Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/clakdorviioperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','3','While at a Clak\'dor VII site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is forfeit +1 (and power +1 if your musician is on Clak\'dor VII) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Clak\'dor VII from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Hired by the Alliance after the ecological disaster on Clak\'dor VII. Brought food supplies and medicine to the Bith, securing their loyalty to the Rebellion.',NULL,'7_10'),(1775,418,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Clash Of Sabers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/clashofsabers.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to target a character present with your warrior with a lightsaber. Target cannot move or battle until the end of your next turn. OR Use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one Uncontrollable Fury into hand and reshuffle. OR Cancel Presence Of The Force.','Weooww - bzzzzt - bzt - weoww - bzzzt - weoww - weow - bzt - bzt - bzt - weow - bzzzzzt!','You Are Beaten','5_38'),(1776,419,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Clinging To The Edge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/clingingtotheedge.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent\'s Dark Jedi with at least one combat card just initiated lightsaber combat against your Jedi with none, draw 3 destiny and choose 2 to use for lightsaber combat destiny. You may take other card into hand, or return it to top of Reserve Deck.','There are some times, more than others, when you should not look down.',NULL,'13_10'),(1777,5428,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 10','•••Clone Squad Leader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/clonesquadleader.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','3','3','4','Your other clones present are each forfeit +1. Once during battle with your clone, may cancel and redraw your just drawn battle destiny. When moving with a \'squad\' of up to three other clones, they all move simultaneously for 1 Force.','Clone trooper.',NULL,'210_8'),(1778,5430,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 10','Clone Trooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/clonetrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','3','Deploys free to same site as your [Clone Army]: general, leader, or Padawan. Once during battle, if firing a blaster, may cancel and redraw your just drawn weapon destiny. While with your clone, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.',NULL,NULL,'210_9'),(1779,5432,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 11','•Cloning Cylinders','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/cloningcylinders.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on table. During your draw phase, may stack a non-unique clone from your Lost Pile here face down. At the start of your turn, turn all cards here face up. You may deploy any face up card stacked here (as if from hand). [Immune to Alter.]','Blank.',NULL,'211_53'),(1780,420,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Close Air Support','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/closeairsupport.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. While your Z-95 occupies a system or cloud sector, once per turn your scout at a related exterior site may add one battle destiny (if Z-95 is Tala 1 or Tala 2, may also add one destiny to total power only).','Attack plans for General Madine\'s commandos often require coordinated air support. A number of Z-95 headhunters have been modified to operate in this role.',NULL,'9_32'),(1781,424,'Light','U','Dagobah','•Closer?!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/closer.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, use 1 Force to relocate one of your starships from a planet system to any related asteroid sector (or vice versa). This movement is free if a smuggler is on board. OR Cancel Rogue Asteroid or Close Call.','\'I\'m going in closer to one of those big ones.\' \'Closer?!\' \'Closer?!\' \'Graarg?!\'',NULL,'4_47'),(1782,426,'Light','C','Cloud City','Cloud Car','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/cloudcar.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: Twin-Pod Cloud Car','2','2','2','3','May add 1 pilot or passenger. At cloud sectors, power +1, may deploy as a \'react\' and may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','Enclosed high altitude vehicle designed by Bespin Motors. Top speed of 1,500 kph. Repulsorlift drives and ion engines allow it to reach the upper atmosphere.','Cloud Car','5_88'),(1783,428,'Light','C','Cloud City','Cloud City Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/cloudcityblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior at a Cloud City site. May target a character or creature using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit (and may not be used to satisfy attrition) if destiny > defense value.','Black market ties make it possible for the Cloud City quartermaster to acquire powerful weapons such as this. Low refraction index provides minimal beam dispersion.','Cloud City Blaster','5_89'),(1784,429,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Cloud City Celebration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/cloudcitycelebration.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Bespin system if you occupy at least two Cloud City battleground sites. During each of your control phases, retrieve 1 Force for each Cloud City battleground you occupy. Canceled if opponent controls this system. (Immune to Alter.)','The merchants on Cloud City fear Imperial occupation. Many on the floating station long for the day that the Empire is overthrown.',NULL,'7