n-Light/large/dantooinebaseoperations.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Dantooine Base Operations:Deploy Dantooine system.{While} this side up, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy from Reserve Deck to Dantooine one site or non-unique Rebel; reshuffle. At Dantooine locations, each Imperial is deploy +2.{Flip} this card if Rebels control at least three Dantooine sites and opponent controls no Dantooine locations.{Place} out of play if Dantooine is \'blown away.\'More Dangerous Than You Realize:{While} this side up, opponent\'s Force drains are -1. At Dantooine locations, each Imperial is deploy +2. Your squadrons may deploy to Dantooine (deploy cost = squadron\'s power -3), are immune to attrition < 4 and may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Your Force drains are +1 at systems where you have a squadron present.{Flip} this card if opponent controls at least two Dantooine locations.{Place} out of play if Dantooine is \'blown away.\'',NULL,NULL,'7_135'),(1877,612,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Dark Approach','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/darkapproach.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle, you may do one of the following: Add one destiny to power only. OR If you have a character weapon present, select one opponent\'s character present to lose all immunity to attrition for remainder of battle.','\'The Force is with you, young Skywalker. But you are not a Jedi yet.\'','Release Your Anger','5_42'),(1878,615,'Light','R1','Hoth','Dark Dissension','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/darkdissension.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Dark Collaboration or Lone Pilot.  LOST: If two Imperials each with ability > 2 are in a battle together, use 2 Force to draw two destiny. Subtract that amount from opponent\'s attrition and total power (cannot fall below zero).\"','The huge Imperial officers corps, with its high rate of turnover, is ripe with competitiveness and ambition. Advancement comes at the expense of another\'s career.',NULL,'3_41'),(1879,627,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Darklighter Spin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/darklighterspin.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle at a system or sector, if you are about to draw a card for battle destiny, you may instead use the maneuver number of your starfighter in that battle.','Biggs improvised this maneuver shortly after joining the Alliance. By spinning his starfighter while firing all four cannons, he was able to destroy multiple incoming targets.','Watch Your Back!','7_85'),(1880,632,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Darth Maul\'s Demise','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/darthmaulsdemise.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your [Episode I] Jedi just defeated Maul in lightsaber combat, draw destiny. Add 2 if Qui-Gon out of play. If total > 6, place Maul out of play and you may search your Lost Pile and take any one card into hand. (Immune to Sense.)','Despite coming face to face with the first Sith to be seen in a millennia, the young Padawan was still a force to be reckoned with.',NULL,'13_12'),(1881,640,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Dash','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/dash.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to increase a character\'s or creature vehicle\'s landspeed by 1 for remainder of turn. OR Use 3 Force to move one of your characters as a \'react\' (free if character is a scout).','See Luke run. Run Luke, run!',NULL,'5_43'),(1882,4118,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 1','•Dash in Rogue 10','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/dashinrogue12.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: T-47 Snowspeeder','2','5','3','5','May add 1 pilot. Permanent pilot is •Dash, who provides ability of 3. During battle, if with another T-47 and about to draw battle destiny, may draw two and choose one. Immune to attrition < 4.','Enclosed.',NULL,'201_20'),(1883,641,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Dash Rendar','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/dashrendar.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','5','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Outrider, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise, and once per battle, may reduce power of one opponent\'s starship in same battle by power of Outrider for remainder of battle.','Emperor banished Rendar family from Coruscant. Became gambler and smuggler. Brought down AT-AT at the Battle of Hoth. Works for Rebel Alliance from time to time. Corellian.',NULL,'10_6'),(1884,5477,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 10','•Dash Rendar (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/dashrendar.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','3','5','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. May move as a \'react\'. When in battle with Leebo (or opponent\'s gangster, [Permanent Weapon] card, or [Maintenance] card), may draw one destiny; subtract that amount from opponent\'s total power and attrition.','Emperor banished Rendar family from Coruscant. Became gambler and smuggler. Brought down AT-AT at the Battle of Hoth. Works for Rebel Alliance from time to time. Corellian.',NULL,'210_12'),(1885,644,'Light','R','Endor','•Daughter Of Skywalker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/daughterofskywalker.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','7','8','Deploys -3 on Tydirium, Endor or Dagobah. May be deployed instead of Luke by Mind What You Have Learned (that card then targets Leia instead of Luke for remainder of game). While at any exterior site, adds one Light side icon. Immune to attrition < 4.','Scout. Leader. Made friends with Wicket. Negotiated an alliance with the Ewoks. Leia found out the truth about her father from Luke in the Ewok village.',NULL,'8_8'),(1886,4067,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Daughter Of Skywalker (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/daughterofskywalker.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','5','8','If in hand, may place her under Reserve Deck. May be targeted instead of Luke by Mind What You Have Learned (that card then targets Leia instead of Luke for remainder of game). May deploy Reflection from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 4.','Scout. Leader. Made friends with Wicket. Negotiated an alliance with the Ewoks. Leia found out the truth about her father from Luke in the Ewok village.',NULL,'200_9'),(1887,646,'Light','R','Endor','Deactivate The Shield Generator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/deactivatetheshieldgenerator.gif?raw=true','Epic Event',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Bunker. Once during your control phase, if you control Bunker with a Rebel, you may attempt to \'blow away\' Bunker as follows: Charges! Come On, Come On!: Draw two destiny. Add 3 to total for each Explosive Charge on Bunker. Move! Move! Move!: If total destiny > 12, your characters here may relocate to Back Door for free, Bunker and Landing Platform (if on table) are \'blown away,\' opponent loses 8 Force and this card is lost.',NULL,NULL,'8_43'),(1888,655,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Death Star','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/deathstar.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Deploy if Death Star Plans completed and and Death Star system not on table. If \'blown away,\' Dark Side loses 8 Force.',NULL,'Death Star','7_117'),(1889,664,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Death Star Plans','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/deathstarplans.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any Death Star site(except docking bay). Target one of your droids(not on Death Star). When target reaches Utinni Effect, \'steal\' plans. If target then moves to any Yavin 4 site, draw 3 destiny. Retrieve that much lost Force. Lose Utinni Effect.','\'What\'s so important? What\'s he carrying?\' \'The technical readouts of that battle station. I only hope that when the data is analyzed, a weakness can be found.\'',NULL,'1_46'),(1890,672,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Death Star: Detention Block Control Room','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/deathstardetentionblockcontrolroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Force Drain +1 here and all imprisoned characters on Death Star are released.',NULL,'Death Star: Detention Block Control Room','1_123');
INSERT INTO `Card` VALUES (1891,674,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Death Star: Detention Block Corridor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/deathstardetentionblockcorridor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain +1 here. Whenever you release a captive here, retrieve 1 Force (4 if Leia).',NULL,'Death Star: Detention Block Corridor','7_118'),(1892,676,'Light','C2','Premiere','•Death Star: Docking Bay 327','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/deathstardockingbay327.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.',NULL,'Death Star: Docking Bay 327','1_124'),(1893,679,'Light','PM','Premiere Introductory Two Player Game','•Death Star: Level 6 Core Shaft Corridor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/PremiereIntroductoryTwoPlayerGame-Light/large/deathstarlevel6coreshaftcorridor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Luke and Obi-Wan are power +2 on Death Star.',NULL,NULL,'101_1'),(1894,680,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Death Star: Trash Compactor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/deathstartrashcompactor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : You may deploy here without presence. If you control, Force drain +1 here.',NULL,NULL,'1_125'),(1895,681,'Light','R2','A New Hope','•Death Star: Trench','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/deathstartrench.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Trench Rules\' in effect and each of your starfighters is maneuver - 2 here.',NULL,NULL,'2_62'),(1896,683,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Debnoli','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/debnoli.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','3','3','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When firing a character weapon, adds 1 to total weapon destiny and characters he \'hits\' are forfeit=0. Immune to attrition < 2 (< 5 while armed with a blaster).','Good-natured patron of Mos Eisley cantina, until the Empire impounded his starship. Expert marksman. Seeking revenge on the Empire.',NULL,'7_14'),(1897,691,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Defiance','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/defiance.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Mon Calamari Star Cruiser','1','8','9','10','May add 5 pilots, 6 passengers, 1 vehicle and 3 starfighters. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 2. Each of it\'s weapon destiny draws are +2. Capital starships it hits are power -5.','Fleet rear guard. Weapon batteries hard-wired to central targeting processor. Coordinates vicious crossfire against enemy captial starships.',NULL,'9_67'),(1898,694,'Light','R1','A New Hope','•Dejarik Hologameboard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/dejarikhologameboard.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Dejarik Rules\' in effect here.',NULL,'Imperial Holotable','2_63'),(1899,695,'Light','R2','Premiere','Demotion','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/demotion.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on any Imperial except Vader, Emperor or a stormtrooper. That Imperial is power -2 and its game text is canceled.','Repercussions for failure are severe in the Imperial military. Many officers prefer demotion to \'alternative\' punishment from Darth Vader.',NULL,'1_47'),(1900,699,'Light','U','Tatooine','•Deneb Both','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/denebboth.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','3','5','When deployed, draw up to 2 cards from top of Reserve Deck. Unless Graak on table, while at a battleground and opponent is losing Force from Force drains at same or adjacent site, lost Force must come from Force Pile, if possible.','Shy Ithorian forester. She seeks to leave Tatooine for a better life. Firm adherent to Ithorian philosophy of planting two trees for every one harvested.',NULL,'11_2'),(1901,706,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Depa Billaba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/depabillaba.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','2','4','4','6','Deploys only to Jedi Council Chamber. While at Jedi Council Chamber, immune to attrition and once per turn may use 1 Force to peek at the top card of any Reserve Deck and place that card on top of owner\'s Reserve Deck or Used Pile.','Chalactan Jedi Master who was rescued by Mace Windu from space pirates when she was six months old. Jedi Council member who is reknowned for her insights.',NULL,'12_4'),(1902,5166,'Light','R','Virtual Set 7','•Depa Billaba (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/depabillaba.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','2','4','4','6','If at least two [Light Side] icons here, once during your control phase may draw top card of Reserve Deck. If at least two [Dark Side] icons here, may forfeit in place of your hit non-Jedi character present with Depa (forfeit = 0), restoring that character to normal.','Chalactan Jedi Master who was rescued by Mace Windu from space pirates when she was six months old. Jedi Council member who is reknowned for her insights.',NULL,'207_3'),(1903,707,'Light','U1','Hoth','•Derek \'Hobbie\' Klivian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/derekhobbieklivian.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Power +2 when at same site as Biggs. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if a Star Destroyer is at same location). When piloting Rogue 4, also adds 2 to maneuver.','Defected from the Empire with Biggs Darklighter. Aided in mutiny aboard the transport Rand Ecliptic. Served in the Ecliptic Evaders. Luke\'s wingman at the Battle of Hoth.',NULL,'3_5'),(1904,4072,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 0','•Derek \'Hobbie\' Klivian (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/derekhobbieklivian.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting Rogue 4 (or any X-wing), draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Permanent weapon is Rogue Blaster (may target a character or creature for free; draw destiny; target hit and its forfeit = 0, if destiny + 1 > defense value).','Defected from the Empire with Biggs Darklighter. Aided in mutiny aboard the transport Rand Ecliptic. Served in the Ecliptic Evaders. Luke\'s wingman at the Battle of Hoth.',NULL,'200_10'),(1905,708,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Descent Into The Dark','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/descentintothedark.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your turn, if either player just placed a card in a Used Pile, deploy on table. All Used Piles are immediately re-circulated. When any player places one or more cards in a Used Pile, Immediate Effect canceled.','Jedi training is a journey into the depths of an apprentice\'s subconscious, where one must learn to use the Force wisely. \'A Jedi\'s strength flows from the Force.\'',NULL,'4_20'),(1906,711,'Light','F','Special Edition','<>Desert','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/desert.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your Jawas may deploy here. Sandwhirl here moves only if on Tatooine. May not be deployed to Bespin, Coruscant, Dagobah, Hoth, Kessel or Naboo.',NULL,'Desert','7_119'),(1907,717,'Light','U','Cloud City','Desperate Reach','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/desperatereach.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, relocate one of your characters (unless Disarmed) from Weather Vane to any Cloud City site. Character may not move for remainder of turn. OR Cancel Imperial Barrier or The Shield Doors Must Be Closed.','If only someone had given Luke a hand.',NULL,'5_44'),(1908,718,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Desperate Tactics','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/desperatetactics.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your vehicle weapon was just fired during a battle, add one battle destiny. OR During a battle at a site where you have an artillery weapon or vehicle weapon, cancel all opponent\'s immunity to attrition for remainder of battle.','Members of the Rebel Alliance are willing to make a perilous frontal attack for their cause.',NULL,'7_86'),(1909,719,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Desperate Times','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/desperatetimes.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle where your opponent has more characters participating than you, fire (for free) one blaster that cannot fire repeatedly, even if that blaster was already fired this battle. Add 1 to your total weapon destiny.','Han\'s best tactic when outnumbered? Shoot first and don\'t worry about asking questions later.',NULL,'13_13'),(1910,722,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Devaronian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/devaronian.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','2','Power +2 at Mos Eisley, any mobile site or any docking bay. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When playing sabacc, may use clone cards to \'clone\' his own destiny number.','Adept at sneaking through corridors and alleyways. Devaronians frequently surprise opponents. Regarded as drunkards, gamblers and fools by many species.',NULL,'6_10'),(1911,730,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Dice Ibegon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/diceibegon.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','4','3','If present where an opponent\'s character just fired a weapon, may use 1 Force to utilize Dice\'s poison stinger (once per turn). Target that character and draw destiny. If destiny = ability, target is \'hit\'.','Female companion of Lak Sivrak. A Florn lamproid. Dangerous predator with a poison stinger. Rumored to have mysterious time-shifting attunement to the Force.',NULL,'1_7'),(1912,5167,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 7','•Dice Ibegon (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/diceibegon.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','5','Power +2 at a Jabba\'s Palace or Endor site. If just lost, place Dice in Used Pile. if opponent is about to draw destiny for an Interrupt targeting your character here, opponent must first lose 1 Force then shuffle their Reserve Deck.','Female companion of Lak Sivrak. A Florn lamproid. Dangerous predator with a poison stinger. Rumored to have mysterious time-shifting attunement to the Force.',NULL,'207_4'),(1913,5487,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 3','Diplomatic Mission To Alderaan / A Weakness Can Be Found','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/diplomaticmissiontoalderaan.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Diplomatic Mission To Alderaan:Deploy Tatooine system (with Tantive IV, non-[Reflections II] R2-D2, and Stolen Data Tapes there) and Dune Sea.{For} remainder of game, you may not deploy Sandwhirl or [Episode I] Jedi.{While} this side up, your Force drains at Tatooine system are -1. Once per turn, may deploy Alderaan or a Tatooine battleground site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Until the start of your turn, Tantive IV may be forfeited to satisfy all battle damage against you.{Flip} this card if Stolen Data Tapes \'delivered\' and Rebels control two battlegrounds (a site and a system).A Weakness Can Be Found:{While} this this side up, your total battle destiny is +X, where X = number of battlegrounds occupied by Rebels of ability < 4. Once per turn, may deploy Alderaan or a Tatooine battleground site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per turn, if you just won a battle, may retrieve 1 Force.{Flip} this card if you do not occupy a battleground site and a battleground system (or you do not control any locations).',NULL,NULL,'203_19'),(1914,732,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Direct Assault','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/directassault.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a piloted starship armed with a starship weapon, select one opponent\'s starship present to lose all immunity to attrition for remainder of turn. OR Cancel Dark Maneuvers.','\'I got \'im! I got \'im!\'',NULL,'7_87'),(1915,735,'Light','R1','Premiere','Disarmed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/disarmed.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If both players have a character with a weapon present at same site, deploy on that opponent\'s character during any control phase. Character loses all weapons, is power -1 and may no longer carry weapons. (Immune to Alter.)','When Dr. Evazan and Ponda Baba confronted Luke in the Cantina, Obi-Wan pointed out, \'This little one isn\'t worth the effort.\' A brawl ensued.','Disarmed','1_48'),(1916,736,'Light','R1','Hoth','Disarming Creature','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/disarmingcreature.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a character with a weapon at same site as any creature (except Space Slug), deploy on that creature during any deploy phase, Creature is Disarmed (each time ferocity is calculated, draw destiny, subtract that amount). (Immune to Control.)','Luke\'s defensive maneuver put him out of arm\'s way.',NULL,'3_33'),(1917,737,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Dismantle On Sight','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/dismantleonsight.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on a droid with armor (free on IG-88). At end of any opponent\'s turn, droid is immediately lost if present with an Imperial (or with a bounty hunter if droid is IG-88).','After losing control of several extremely powerful and deadly assassin droids, the Empire issued a decree ordering their immediate destruction.',NULL,'5_22'),(1918,739,'Light','F','Special Edition','Disruptor Pistol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/disruptorpistol.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior (1 on your non-unique warrior). May target a character or creature using 2 Force (for free if on your non-unique warrior). Draw Destiny. Target lost if destiny > defense value.','llegal weapon easily purchased by Rebel suppliers on the black market. Rechargeable energy packs make it a cost-effective weapon.','Disruptor Pistol','7_157'),(1919,740,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Diversionary Tactics','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/diversionarytactics.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your starfighter with a pilot character aboard is in a battle, target an opponent\'s starfighter present that has no characters aboard. For remainder of battle, both starfighters are power = 0, and target starfighter is forfeit = 0. (Immune to Sense.)','Rebel pilots understand that what they lack in numbers, they must make up for in strategy. They often use diversions to remove dangerous opponents from a conflict.',NULL,'13_14'),(1920,745,'Light','C','Dagobah','•Do, Or Do Not','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/doordonot.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Sense and Alter are now Lost Interrupts. Also, when and player makes a destiny draw for Sense or Alter, and that destiny draw is successful, that player loses 2 Force. (Immune to Alter.)','A Jedi may choose to intervene in the natural course of events, but must accept responsibility for the consequences.',NULL,'4_21'),(1921,746,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Do, Or Do Not','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/doordonot.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Sense and Alter are now Lost Interrupts. When any player makes a destiny draw for Sense or Alter, and that destiny draw is successful, that player loses 2 Force.','A Jedi may choose to intervene in the natural course of events, but must accept responsibility for the consequences.','There Is No Try - Defensive Shield','13_15'),(1922,747,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Do, Or Do Not & •Wise Advice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/doordonot&wiseadvice.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Sense and Alter are now Lost Interrupts. When any player makes a destiny draw for Sense or Alter, and that destiny draw is successful, that player loses 2 Force. Your Immediate Effects may deploy for free. Whenever opponent cancels your card with Sense or Alter, place that canceled card in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',NULL,NULL,'10_7'),(1923,748,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Docking And Repair Facilities','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/dockingandrepairfacilities.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on your sid