onent\'s destiny draws.',NULL,NULL,'4_76'),(1927,755,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Don\'t Do That Again','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/dontdothatagain.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Once per game may take any Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While opponent occupies no battleground systems, Mobilization Points is suspended.','The Jedi won\'t tolerate silly behavior for very long.','Fanfare - Defensive Shield','13_16'),(1928,754,'Light','C','Tatooine','•Don\'t Do That Again','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/dontdothatagain.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per game may take any Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While opponent occupies no battleground systems, Mobilization Points is suspended. (Immune to Alter.)','The Jedi won\'t tolerate silly behavior for very long.',NULL,'11_17'),(1929,5492,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Don\'t Do That Again (Tatooine) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/dontdothatagaintatooine.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Once per game, may take an Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While opponent occupies no battleground systems, Mobilization Points is suspended. \'Missing\' on Always Thinking With Your Stomach is treated as \'landspeed = 0 for remainder of turn.\'','The Jedi won\'t tolerate silly behavior for very long.',NULL,'13_16'),(1930,4404,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Don\'t Do That Again (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/dontdothatagain.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Once per game, may take an Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While opponent oc