adonme.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Starting','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Use 1 Force to deploy an Effect that deploys for free on table (or on your side of table) and is always Immune to Alter from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  STARTING: When drawing your starting hand, draw up to 12 cards instead of 8. Place this Interrupt in Reserve Deck.','Han did not take kindly to Jabba\'s posturing.','Surface Defense (V)','200_51'),(1935,761,'Light','C1','Premiere','Don\'t Underestimate Our Chances','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/dontunderestimateourchances.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If an opponent has just initiated a battle, triple the resulting battle damage for the eventual loser. OR Triple the result of You Overestimate Their Chances.','\'Stand-by alert. Death Star approaching. Estimated time to firing range, fifteen minutes.\'','You Overestimate Their Chances','1_77'),(1936,5001,'Light','U','Virtual Set 0','•Dorme\'','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/dorme.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','4','2','2','3','Once per turn, if Amidala at another location, may activate 1 Force. During your move phase, may target an opponent\'s Undercover spy here and draw two destiny. Choose one (take the other into hand). Target \'breaks cover\' if destiny +1 > target\'s ability.','Spy and handmaiden.',NULL,'200_11'),(1937,762,'Light','R2','A New Hope','Double Agent','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/doubleagent.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If both players have a spy at same site, draw destiny. Add 2 if opponent\'s spy is Undercover. Opponent\'s spy is lost if destiny > 2. OR Opponent\'s Tonnika Sisters present at a site cross to your side.','Typical of impersonators, Shada double-crossed everyone. Her true affiliations still remain a mystery.','Nevar Yalnal','2_48'),(1938,766,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Down With The Emperor!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/downwiththeemperor.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If no Dark Jedi is on table, deploy on Death Star system. If Death Star \'blown away,\' relocate to opponent\'s side of table: each Imperial and Imperial starship is deploy +8 and loses immunity to attrition. Canceled if a Dark Jedi is deployed. (Immune to Alter.)','News of Imperial defeat inspires the citizens of the galaxy. A major loss seriously undermines the Empire\'s ability to function.','A Day Long Remembered','7_59'),(1939,767,'Light','U','Virtual Set 0','•Down With The Emperor! (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/downwiththeemperor.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. All immunity to attrition is -3. You may not fire [Permanent Weapon] weapons. If opponent just lost a Dark Jedi or a battle, they lose 1 Force. During your draw phase, use 3 Force or place this Effect in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','News of Imperial defeat inspires the citizens of the galaxy. A major loss seriously undermines the Empire\'s ability to function.','A Day Long Remembered (V)','200_38'),(1940,772,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Draw Their Fire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/drawtheirfire.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Whenever a battle is initiated, player initiating battle retrieves 1 Force and defender loses 1 Force. Also, during a battle you initiate, each time opponent plays an interrupt, opponent must first use 1 Force. (Immune to Alter.)','\'I\'m going to cut across the axis and try and draw their fire.\'','First Strike','7_60'),(1941,776,'Light','C','Endor','Dresselian Commando','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/dresseliancommando.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','3','2','Power +1 when at a forest, jungle or exterior Endor site. When in battle at an exterior site against a non-unique alien, adds one destiny to power only, prevents opponent from drawing more than one battle destiny and is immune to attrition < 4.','Dresselians combat their homeworld\'s subjugation with supplies provided by Bothans. The Alliance uses their talents as resistance fighters. These scouts prefer to work alone.',NULL,'8_9'),(1942,778,'Light','C','Special Edition','•••Droid Merchant','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/droidmerchant.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','3','Spaceport Speeders may be played at same site. Once per game, may do one of the following: activate 1 Force when you deploy a droid OR retrieve 1 Force when you deploy an astromech to a starfighter.','Careful manipulator of funds and Imperial taxation codes. Buys droids from Jawas and sells them to the Alliance.',NULL,'7_15'),(1943,780,'Light','U','Dagobah','Droid Sensorscope','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/droidsensorscope.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one of your R-unit droids. During any control phase, you may use 1 Force to peek at the top card of opponent\'s Reserve Deck. Also, if on Dagobah, droid may move for free.','Full-spectrum transceiver for R-unit droids including electro-photo receptors, DERs and heat and motion detectors. Data is routed directly to droids Intellex IV internal computer.',NULL,'4_9'),(1944,781,'Light','C2','Premiere','Droid Shutdown','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/droidshutdown.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel an attempt by opponent to target your droid to be stolen, \'hit,\' lost or captured. Droid is protected from all such attempts for remainder of turn.','If low on energy and unable to recharge, a droid can shutdown active systems to conserve power.',NULL,'1_78'),(1945,784,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Droopy McCool','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/droopymccool.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Power +2 at any desert or Tatooine site. Immune to Gravel Storm, Sandwhirl and desert landspeed requirements. While at Audience Chamber, all your other Kitonaks are forfeit +2. Immune to attrition < number of your musicians on table.','Kitonak musician. Lead jizz wailer. Searching for other Kitonak rumored to be living on Tatooine. Rarely uses his real name, Snit.',NULL,'6_11'),(1946,793,'Light','U1','Hoth','Dual Laser Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/duallasercannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Vehicle','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your T-47. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Subtract 1 if targeting a character or creature. Add 2 if targeting a vehicle. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Sund x2-100 laser cannon. Popular among outlaw organizations because it is both cheap and powerful. Frequently mounted on T-47 airspeeders.',NULL,'3_74'),(1947,797,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Dune Sea Sabacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/duneseasabacc.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Requirements: A Jawa at a Tatooine site. Wild cards (0-7): Sandcrawler sites, Magnetic Suction Tube, Jawa Siesta and Jawa Pack. Clone cards: Tatooine locations, sandcrawlers, Jawa weapons, and Utinni! Stakes: One device or droid with out armor.','R\'kik D\'nec remains undefeated in this version of sabacc. Or at least there are no witnesses to the contrary.','Dune Sea Sabacc','6_65'),(1948,799,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Dutch','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/dutch.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','2','2','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Gold 1, also adds 1 to maneuver and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Adds 1 to forfeit of each other Gold Squadron pilot at same location.','Jon \'Dutch\' Vander. Gold Squadron leader at Battle of Yavin. Prefers Y-wing fighters. Previously led squadron at Renforra Base. Emblem of Specter Squadron on his helmet.',NULL,'1_8'),(1949,5501,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 10','•Dutch (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/dutch.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if Gold 1). While piloting a Y-Wing, for each Y-wing you have in a battle, attrition against opponent is +1 and attrition against your is -1. Y-wing pilots are fofeit +1 here.','Jon \'Dutch\' Vander. Gold Squadron leader at Battle of Yavin. Prefers Y-wing fighters. Previously led squadron at Renforra Base. Emblem of Specter Squadron on his helmet.',NULL,'210_13'),(1950,804,'Light','PM','Third Anthology','•Echo Base Garrison','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ThirdAnthology-Light/large/echobasegarrison.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Rogue T-47s are immune to attrition < 4 (or < 6 if matching pilot aboard). Once during each of your turns, may take one maintenance droid, Bacta Tank, Lone Rogue, [Hoth] Luke, [Special Edition] Wedge, Zev or Hobbie into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','\'All troop carriers will assemble at the North Entrance. The heavy Transport ships will leave as soon as they\'re loaded.\'',NULL,'111_3'),(1951,805,'Light','R2','Hoth','•Echo Base Operations','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/echobaseoperations.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Main Power Generators if 