round wreckage of the colony ship Dowager Queen. The wreck remains as a monument where residents leave junk for Jawa scavengers.',NULL,'1_45'),(1955,586,'Light','C','Coruscant','•Credits Will Do Fine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/creditswilldofine.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on table. If you just initiated a Force drain (or won a battle) at Watto\'s Junkyard, opponent loses 1 Force (cannot be reduced) and stacks lost card here face down. (Immune to Alter.)','\'No, they won\'t!\'',NULL,'12_42'),(1956,587,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Critical Error Revealed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/criticalerrorrevealed.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a leader at your war room, peek at the top card of opponent\'s Reserve Deck. You may place it on bottom of that Reserve Deck.','Hologram technology allows effecient communication of complex intelligence during war room briefings.',NULL,'9_49'),(1957,814,'Light','R','Dagobah','Effective Repairs','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/effectiverepairs.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Limited Resources.  LOST: Use 3 Force to retrieve into hand one Effect of any kind.\"','When the nav computer maintenance program failed to auto-repair the hyperdrive, Han decided to take matters into his own hand.',NULL,'4_49'),(1958,5503,'Light','R','Virtual Set 9','Effective Repairs & Starship Levitation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/effectiverepairsstarshiplevitation.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Broken Concentration, Lateral Damage, or Limited Resources. OR Place a card just stacked on Droid Racks or Strategic Reserves in opponent\'s Lost Pile. (Immune to Sense) OR If you just drew a starship for destiny, take that starship into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny.  LOST: Use 3 Force to retrieve an Effect of any kind or a non-[Maintenance] starship into hand.\"',NULL,NULL,'209_19'),(1959,815,'Light','C1','Hoth','EG-4 (Eegee-Four)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/eg4eegeefour.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','*','0','1','3','Adds 1 to power of each of your droids present, except power droids. * Destiny equals zero, but if drawn as a battle destiny where you have less power than opponent, your total power present is doubled (once per battle).','Very popular droid on inhospitable worlds. Rugged design. Modified top-mounted power sockets. Donated to the Alliance by the Bothan underground.','EG-6 (Eegee-Six)','3_8'),(1960,817,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Egregious Pilot Error','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/egregiouspiloterror.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During opponent\'s control phase, if opponent has two or more capital starships at a system or sector together, draw destiny. If destiny -1 < number of those starships, they may not move or participate in battle until end of your next turn.','Details of the notorious \'Incident at Anoat\' are required reading at the Imperial Academy of Raithal, where the pilots\' names are posthumously displayed.',NULL,'4_50'),(1961,818,'Light','U','Tatooine','•Either Way, You Win','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/eitherwayyouwin.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Opponent chooses: opponent may activate up to 2 Force and you may activate up to 4 Force, or opponent retrieves 1 Force and you retrieve 3 Force.','\'Deal!\'',NULL,'11_32'),(1962,819,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Eject! Eject!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/ejecteject.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to target a starfighter having one or more permanent pilots. Draw destiny. If destiny > 2, deploy on starfighter to remove all permanent pilots (otherwise, Effect is lost). May add 1 pilot for each permanent pilot removed. (Immune to Alter.)','The Guiderhouser ejection seat has saved many pilots from their exploding starships. However, system malfunctions have sometimes caused spontaneous ejection.','Come With Me','2_32'),(1963,821,'Light','C2','Premiere','Electrobinoculars','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/electrobinoculars.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on any warrior. At any time, you may peek at the top card of your Reserve Deck by using 2 Force. You may choose to move that card to the top of your Force Pile.','Enhances distant targets using a computer-assisted zoom technology. Provides range information. Works in low-light. Rugged case protects the internal systems.',NULL,'1_35'),(1964,822,'Light','C','Theed Palace','Electropole','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/electropole.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Gungan. May target a character for free. Draw destiny. If destiny > defense value, character is power -4 for remainder of turn. At the end of battle here, may place this electropole on top of Reserve Deck.','Gungan weapon that is very similar to the Force pike. Used to control crowds, wild animals, and the occasional battle droid.',NULL,'14_65'),(1965,5218,'Light','C','Virtual Set 8','•Ello Asty','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/elloasty.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting an X-wing alone, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and all immunity to attrition here is canceled. Once during your control phase, may take Sabotage into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Abednedo.',NULL,'208_5'),(1966,826,'Light','C2','Premiere','Ellorrs Madak','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/ellorrsmadak.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your non-pilot character (except droids) to give that character [Pilot] skill. Adds 2 to power of anything that character pilots. OR Deploy on your pilot. Adds 1 to power of anything that character pilots. (Immune to Alter.)','Like many Duros, Madak has natural piloting and navigation skill. Former scout. Freelance instructor. Makes runs to important trade worlds Celanon, Byblos and Yaga Minor.','Baniss Keeg','1_49'),(1967,5508,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 3','•Ellorrs Madak, Pilot Instructo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/ellorrsmadakpilotinstructor.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3',NULL,NULL,'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Adds 2 to the hyperspeed of any freighter he pilots. During your move phase, may use 1 Force to \'break cover\' of opponent\'s Undercover spy at same site. Cancels Lateral Damage targeting your starship at same or related system.','Duros scout and smuggler.',NULL,'203_4'),(1968,828,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Elom','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/elom.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','4','1','3','3','Power +3 at same site as an Imperial. For remainder of game, Plastoid Armor is an Effect, is not unique, is immune to Alter while on table, and it deploys only on a Rebel or alien at same mobile site as Elom (character is now \'disguised\').','Many Elom commit sabotage and theft against the Empire to avenge the invasion of their homeworld. Experts in adapting stolen equipment for use by the Rebellion.',NULL,'6_12'),(1969,829,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Elyhek Rue','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/elyhekrue.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Red 7 during battle, adds one destiny to total power only. When at Ralltiir system, adds 1 to each of your Force drains there.','Piloted Red 7 at the Battle of Yavin. Part of the Griffon flight wing, a Rebel squadron sent to fight the Imperial subjugation of Ralltiir.',NULL,'7_16'),(1970,838,'Light','C','Dagobah','<>Encampment','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/encampment.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on any exterior planet site where you have a Rebel or alien. You may deploy characters at this site, even without presence, regardless of location deployment restrictions.','Pirates, smugglers and Rebels operate from tiny camps which can be set up quickly and relocated at a moment\'s notice. A surprise visitor made Luke an unhappy camper.',NULL,'4_22'),(1971,840,'Light','R','Tatooine','•End Of A Reign','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/endofareign.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Overseeing It Personally. OR Use 4 Force to cancel Vader\'s game text for remainder of turn.  LOST: If Emperor just lost from table, draw destiny. Opponent must lose Force equal to the destiny draw.\"','The turning of Vader and the loss of Palpatine was the beginning of a new era for the entire galaxy.',NULL,'11_33'),(1972,843,'Light','U','Endor','•Endor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endor.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain -1 here. To move your starship here from Sullust, Rendezvous Point or Haven requires -1 Force.',NULL,'Endor','8_68'),(1973,5066,'Light','U','Virtual Set 4','\"•Endor (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/endor.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you have no Rebels on Endor, Force drain -1 here. If you control, each of opponent\'s biker scouts is forfeit -1.',NULL,'Endor','204_24'),(1974,844,'Light','R','Endor','•Endor Celebration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorcelebration.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel Tatooine Occupation, Cloud City Occupation or Rebel Base Occupation. (Immune to Sense.) OR During your activate phase, activate 1 Force for each Endor battleground you occupy.','The Rebel presence on Endor meant that the Ewoks would be able to live free from the Empire\'s tyranny.',NULL,'8_46'),(1975,5037,'Light','R','Virtual Set 3','•Endor Commando Team','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/endorrcommandoteam.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','8','5','5','Deploys -1 to Endor. During battle, your other Rebels here may not have their forfeit reduced unless this card \'hit.\' Each time this character is \'hit,\' it is cumulatively power -2 until end of turn.','General Solo\'s strike team was made up of the Alliance\'s finest ground troops. Scout trooper.',NULL,'203_5'),(1976,848,'Light','C','Endor','Endor Scout Trooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorscouttrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','3','Power -1 while not on Endor. While Endor Scout Trooper is on Endor, Lieutenant Page and each of your Rebel scouts of ability < 3 at same and adjacent exterior sites are immune to attrition < 2.','Rebel troopers receive Scout training that helps them to survive combat in harsh environments. Often protect \'specialists\' while they accomplish mission tasks.',NULL,'8_10'),(1977,852,'Light','U','Endor','•Endor: Back Door','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorbackdoor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : During your move phase, you may move from Back Door to Bunker (or vice versa).',NULL,'Endor: Back Door','8_69'),(1978,854,'Light','U','Endor','•Endor: Bunker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorbunker.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain +1 here. If you initiate a battle here, add one battle destiny.',NULL,'Endor: Bunker','8_70'),(1979,5067,'Light','U','Virtual Set 4','•Endor: Bunker (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/endorbunker.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Unless you occupy Bunker (or Back Door), your characters may not deploy here.',NULL,'Endor: Bunker','204_25'),(1980,855,'Light','R','Endor','•Endor: Chief Chirpa\'s Hut','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorchiefchirpashut.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your Ewoks are deploy -1 here. Chief Chirpa deploys free here.',NULL,NULL,'8_71'),(1981,858,'Light','C','Endor','•Endor: Dense Forest','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endordenseforest.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : No starships or vehicles here except speeder bikes, AT-STs, Ewok gliders and creature vehicles.',NULL,'Endor: Dense Forest','8_72'),(1982,860,'Light','U','Endor','•Endor: Ewok Village','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorewokvillage.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : No starships or vehicles here. Ewok devices and Ewok weapons deploy -1 here.',NULL,'Endor: Ewok Village','8_73'),(1983,5236,'Light','U','Virtual Set 8','•Endor: Ewok Village (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/endorewokvillage.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : While a Skywalker here, Prophecy Of The Force may not relocate from here.',NULL,NULL,'208_23'),(1984,863,'Light','C','Endor','•••Endor: Great Forest','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorgreatforest.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your character movement from here (except for Ewoks and scouts) requires +1 landspeed.',NULL,'Endor: Great Forest','8_74'),(1985,864,'Light','U','Endor','•Endor: Hidden Forest Trail','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorhiddenforesttrail.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : During your move phase, your scouts may move between here and any exterior Endor site.',NULL,NULL,'8_75'),(1986,866,'Light','C','Endor','•Endor: Landing Platform (Docking Bay)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorlandingplatformdockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force.',NULL,'Endor: Landing Platform (Docking Bay)','8_76'),(1987,867,'Light','R','Endor','•Endor: Rebel Landing Site (Forest)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/endorrebellandingsiteforest.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your starfighters land here for free. Your droids and [Endor] Rebels are deploy -1 here.',NULL,NULL,'8_77'),(1988,870,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Energy Walls','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/energywalls.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, deploy on Theed Palace Generator Core. No more than one character may deploy to here each turn, and characters may not move to or from here. Immediate Effect lost at end of opponent\'s turn.','Theed security protocol proved to be a deciding variable in the duel of the fates.','Energy Walls','13_18'),(1989,871,'Light','C','Death Star II','Enhanced Proton Torpedoes','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/enhancedprotontorpedoes.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your X-wing, Y-wing or B-wing. May target a starship for 1 Force. Add 1 if targetting a capital starship. Otherwise, subtract 1. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Often modified by Rebel technicians. Heavy warhead provides increased armor penetration. Decreased maneuverability and effectiveness against starfighters.',NULL,'9_88'),(1990,5126,'Light','C3','Virtual Set 5','Ensign Chad Hilse','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/ensignchadhilse.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','3','During battle, if present at a site with a stormtrooper (or Rebel leader), may add one destiny to total power only. Once per turn, may subtract 1 from a destiny draw of an opponent\'s Interrupt or weapon targeting a non-Jedi Rebel here.','Corellian Corvette trooper Ensign Chad Hilse, an Alderaanian, typifies the loyal Rebel volunteers dedicated to defeating the Empire. Trained in starship and ground combat.',NULL,'205_2'),(1991,874,'Light','U','Tatooine','•Entering The Arena','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/enteringthearena.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Once per game may take Podracer Bay into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: During a battle at Podracer Bay, add one battle destiny.\"','\'What\'d he mean by that?\' \'I\'ll tell you later.\'',NULL,'11_34'),(1992,875,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Entrenchment','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/entrenchment.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Once per turn, you may cancel a Force drain by placing here from hand any non-unique Rebel. Rebels may deploy from here as if from hand (if Effect canceled by opponent, any Rebels here may immediately deploy for free.)','As the Empire advances, Rebels retreat to fortified positions to marshal their resources and redeploy the troops.','Strategic Reserves','7_61'),(1993,877,'Light','C','Tatooine','Eopie','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/eopie.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Creature','5','1','1','3','May add 2 \'riders\' (passengers). Ability = 1/4.Moves for free. While \'ridden\' by Amidala in battle, adds one battle destiny.','Herd animal native to Tatooine. Adults are used as beasts of burden, while the young and elderly eopies are useful for consuming desert weeds.',NULL,'11_48'),(1994,882,'Light','U2','Premiere','Escape Pod','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/escapepod.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Save all characters, weapons, and devices aboard any just-lost capital starship. Relocate them to any planet site.','Capital starships have emergency escape pods. Equipped with food, water, flares, medpacs, hunting blaster and tracking beacon (R2-D2 deactivated this one\'s beacon).',NULL,'1_79'),(1995,5073,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 4','Escape Pod & We\'re Doomed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/escapepodweredoomed.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to take a dejarik into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR For remainder of turn, you lose no Force to Cloud City Occupation, Rebel Base Occupation, Tatooine Occupation, That Thing\'s Operational, or You May Start Your Landing.','Blank.',NULL,'204_18'),(1996,883,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 1','Escape Pod (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/escapepod.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to take a dejarik or holosite into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Cancel a Force drain at a holosite. OR If opponent is about to place your character our of play, place that character in your Lost Pile instead.','Capital starships have emergency escape pods. Equipped with food, water, flares, medpacs, hunting blaster and tracking beacon (R2-D2 deactivated this one\'s beacon).','Masterful Move','201_12'),(1997,889,'Light','U1','Hoth','Evacuation Control','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/evacuationcontrol.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your war room. Once during each of your move phases, your Planet Defender Ion Cannon at same planet may fire. Also, each of your medium transports at same planet is hyperspeed +2, is immune to attrition < 3 and may move for free.','\'Give the evacuation code signal...and get to your transports!\'',NULL,'3_35'),(1998,890,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 0','Evacuation Control (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/evacuationcontrol.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table; shuffle your Reserve Deck, peek at top three cards, and stack them face-up here. During battle, may take a card here into hand to prevent all battle destiny draws from being modified or canceled (each player may draw no more than one battle destiny). (Immune to Alter.)','\'Give the evacuation code signal...and get to your transports!\'','Imperial Justice (V)','200_39'),(1999,893,'Light','U','Tatooine','•Eventually You\'ll Lose','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/eventuallyyoulllose.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If a battle was just initiated, place the top card of your Used Pile on top of your Reserve Deck.  LOST: Use 3 Force to cause opponent to reveal hand. All cards opponent has 3 or more of in hand are lost.\"','In the end, Watto finally came to understand the agony of defeat.',NULL,'11_35'),(2000,895,'Light','C','Endor','•Ewok And Roll','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewokandroll.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent\'s creature vehicle or AT-ST just deployed or moved to where your Ewok is present, draw destiny. Creature vehicle lost if destiny > defense value. AT-ST crashed if destiny +2 > armor. OR If your Ewok is defending a battle, add 2 to your total power.','Even an All Terrain Scout Transport cannot stand on all terrain.',NULL,'8_47'),(2001,896,'Light','C','Endor','Ewok Bow','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewokbow.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your Ewok. May target a character or creature using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 for each other Ewok present who is armed with an Ewok Bow. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Primitive weapon. Effective in large volleys. Imperial troops are not prepared for such simple tactics.',NULL,'8_87'),(2002,897,'Light','U','Endor','Ewok Catapult','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewokcatapult.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Artillery','7',NULL,'2','4','Deploy on an exterior Endor site. Does not require a power source. Your Ewok present may target a vehicle with armor at same or adjacent site for free. Draw destiny. Add 1 for each Ewok present. Target crashes if total destiny > defense value.','Crowning achievement of Chirpa\'s engineers. Heavy stones from these weapons distracted Imperial AT-ST walkers.',NULL,'8_88'),(2003,898,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Ewok Celebration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/ewokcelebration.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. At Endor sites where you have an Ewok, your characters are forfeit and defense value +1 (+3 if you have two Ewoks at that site.) In battles at Endor sites where all your ability is provided by Ewoks, add one battle destiny. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Na na, beecha na noooooooooooooooowa.\'',NULL,'13_19'),(2004,899,'Light','C','Endor','Ewok Glider','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewokglider.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','5','1','1','2','May add 1 driver (must be an Ewok). Once per turn, when in battle, may target a character or creature present. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny -1 > defense value.','Primitive flying vehicle used by Ewoks. Used to drop rocks on Imperial troops during the Battle of Endor.',NULL,'8_82'),(2005,900,'Light','C','Endor','•Ewok Log Jam','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewoklogjam.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent\'s transport vehicle or AT-ST just deployed or moved to an Endor site, draw destiny. Add 1 for each of your Ewoks present. Vehicle lost if total destiny -1 > defense value. OR Lose 1 Force to take into hand a card you just drew for battle or weapon destiny.','Any problem can be solved by the proper application of the principles of mass and velocity.',NULL,'8_48'),(2006,901,'Light','C','Endor','Ewok Rescue','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewokrescue.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your Ewok is present with an escorted captive, draw destiny. Add 2 if Ewok is a scout. If total destiny > escort\'s defense value, captive is released. OR If your Ewok is defending a battle, up to three of your Ewoks at one exterior site may move as a \'react\' (for free).','Ewoks used superior knowledge of Endor\'s forested terrain to free commandos captured by Imperial stormtroopers.',NULL,'8_49'),(2007,902,'Light','C','Endor','Ewok Sentry','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewoksentry.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','1','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. May deploy as a \'react\'. May move as a \'react\' (for free) to a battle where you have a unique (•) Ewok.','Ewok sentries scout the perimeter of their domain. Their watchful eyes search for both predatory animals and invading stormtroopers.',NULL,'8_11'),(2008,903,'Light','C','Endor','Ewok Spear','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewokspear.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your Ewok (free on Ewok Spearman). Adds 1 to power. May target a character or creature using 1 Force. Both players draw destiny. Target\'s power or ferocity for remainder of turn = 0 if your destiny + Ewok\'s power > opponent\'s destiny.','Chosen weapon of most Ewok warriors. Pointed tip made of stone or animal horn.',NULL,'8_89'),(2009,904,'Light','C','Endor','Ewok Spearman','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewokspearman.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. When on Endor and present with any other Ewok, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Ewok fighters train with primitive weapons. Their bravery and careful aim helped defeat the Imperial troops during the Battle of Endor.',NULL,'8_12'),(2010,905,'Light','C','Endor','Ewok Tribesman','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ewoktribesman.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','1','1','Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. When forfeited at same site as your Ewok of ability > 1, may satisfy all remaining attrition against you.','Members of Chief Chirpa\'s Ewok tribe are courageous in battle. They seek to impress older members of the tribe. Deploys only on Endor.',NULL,'8_13'),(2011,915,'Light','U','Endor','Explosive Charge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/explosivecharge.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an interior site you occupy. Immune to Overload. Place in Used Pile if opponent controls this site. If you just lost a battle opponent initiated here, may draw destiny. All cards (except Effects) here are lost if destiny > 4 (otherwise, Charge lost).','Standard explosive charge carried by Rebel commandos. When used in multiple, these charges have the explosive capacity to level a heavily armored structure.',NULL,'8_90'),(2012,917,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Eyes In The Dark','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/eyesinthedark.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy beside either player\'s Lost Pile. That pile is turned face down. Cards from that player\'s Life Force may not be viewed when they are lost.','\'I don\'t like the look of this.\'','Your Eyes Can Deceive You','1_50'),(2013,5520,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 10','•Ezra Bridger','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/ezrabridger.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','4','5','Power +1 for each Dark Jedi or Jedi on table. At start of opponent\'s turn, if at opponent\'s site, opponent chooses: their Force generation is -X this turn, or you may activate up to X Force, where X = number of [Dark Side Force] icons here.','Padawan. Spy.',NULL,'210_14'),(2014,919,'Light','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','•Faithful Service','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Light/large/faithfulservice.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an opponent\'s location. Whenever you lose a droid from hand or Life Force, it satisfies Force loss up to its forfeit value. Once per turn, you may play Scomp Link Access to cancel a Force drain where you have a droid. Effect canceled if opponent controls this location.','Unlike the Empire, the Alliance treats their droids with respect. Many droids volunteered to share the risk of battle and aid the Rebellion\'s assault on the Death Star.','Forced Servitude','106_3'),(2015,920,'Light','C2','Hoth','Fall Back!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/fallback.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle at an exterior site with more than double your total power, use 1 Force to cancel the battle and have all your characters there move away to an adjacent site (for free) where the opponent has no presence.','\'K-one zero...all troops disengage.\'',NULL,'3_42'),(2016,921,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Fall Of A Jedi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/fallofajedi.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your Jedi was just defeated in lightsaber combat, you may either: Reveal a Dark Jedi\'s combat cards and place one in opponent\'s Lost Pile (return others). OR Place Qui-Gon out of play and take [Episode I] Obi-Wan into hand from Lost Pile or Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','The blow, when it came, was lightning swift and fatal. But Qui-Gon\'s death gave new life to his former Padawan.',NULL,'13_20'),(2017,922,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Fall Of The Empire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/falloftheempire.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'At the end of a battle that you won at an interior site where you have a character of ability > 3 present, relocate one opponent\'s character present to an adjacent site. (If on Cloud City, character may be relocated to Weather Vane instead.)','\'Aaaaah!\'',NULL,'5_46'),(2018,923,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Fall Of The Legend','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/fallofthelegend.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just lost a character during a battle or duel at a Cloud City site, use 2 Force to relocate that character to Weather Vane instead of your Lost Pile. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take one Weather Vane into hand and reshuffle.','Luke had a falling out with his estranged father.',NULL,'5_47'),(2019,924,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Fallen Portal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/fallenportal.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target one creature or up to two characters present that just initiated an attack or battle against you at Back Door, Rancor Pit, Tatooine: Jabba\'s Palace or any docking bay. Draw destiny. Target(s) immediately lost if destiny +2 > total defense value.','Jabba ordered the two-meter thick door to keep the rancor in. He never thought it would be the instrument of the rancor\'s demise.',NULL,'6_66'),(2020,925,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•••Fambaa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/fambaa.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Creature','5','5','4','5','May add 2 \'riders\' (passengers). Ability + 1/2. Requires +1 Force to use landspeed. May not be attacked by creatures.','Pack animal domesticated by Gungan warriors. Able to bear heavy loads, even during the heat of combat.',NULL,'14_59'),(2021,928,'Light','F','Special Edition','<>Farm','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/farm.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : During your deploy phase, Hydroponics Station or Vaporator may deploy here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. May not be deployed to Bespin, Coruscant, Dagobah, Hoth, Kessel.',NULL,NULL,'7_120'),(2022,942,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Figrin D\'an','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/figrindan.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','4','Once each turn during your control phase, you may use 1 Force to make a \'wager.\' Draw three destiny. Opponent draws two destiny. Player with highest total may randomly select one card to be retrieved from that player\'s Lost Pile.','A male Bith. Musician who leads the Mos Eisley Cantina band, Figrin D\'an and the Modal Nodes. Expert gambler and card shark.',NULL,'1_9'),(2023,5084,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•Finn','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/finn.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','1','4','3','6','Adds 3 to power of any starship or enclosed vehicle he is aboard as a passenger. May deploy as a \'react\' to same location as your pilot (free if Poe or Rey). Once per game, may take Blaster Proficiency into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 4.','Gunner. Stormtrooper.',NULL,'204_6'),(2024,943,'Light','U2','A New Hope','Fire Extinguisher','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/fireextinguisher.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your astromech droid. Cancels an \'exploding\' Program Trap here. Any starship it is aboard is immune to Lateral Damage and ion cannons. If deployed on R2-D2, may lose Fire Extinguisher to cancel a battle just initiated where present at a site.','Among the various special devices on droids like R2 units are gasbased fire extinguishers. Effective against electrical fires and can cause confusion during battle.',NULL,'2_25'),(2025,944,'Light','C','Endor','Firefight','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/firefight.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle, if you have weapons at at least 2 sites adjacent to that battle, add 3 to your total power and add one battle destiny. OR For remainder of turn, your scout at an exterior site is power +1 and adds 1 to each of that character\'s weapon destiny draws.','Lieutenant Page effectively deployed his detachment of Rebel commandos during the attack at the control bunker.','Outflank','8_50'),(2026,947,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Firin Morett','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/firinmorett.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','4','Subtracts 2 from deploy cost of each of your starfighters to same docking bay. Once during each of your control phases, may take one Advanced Preparation, Rebel Planners or docking bay into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Engineer responsible for preparing Red and Gold Squadron starships for battle. Has final launch authority in the Yavin 4 docking bay.',NULL,'7_17'),(2027,948,'Light','F','Special Edition','•First Aid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/firstaid.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your character\'s forfeit was just reduced to 0, restore it to normal. OR Reduce your battle damage by 5 by losing from hand a starship, vehicle or character. (Immune to Sense.)','The Alliance used stolen medical droids to help carry on the battle against the Empire.','Sacrifice','7_89'),(2028,949,'Light','R','Death Star II','•First Officer Thaneespi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/firstofficerthaneespi.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','3','5','Deploys -2 to Home One. Adds 3 to power of any capital starship she pilots. When piloting a Star Cruiser with another Mon Calamari pilot aboard, unless opponent has total ability > 6 piloting here, may reset opponent\'s total battle destiny here to 0.','Mon Calamari deck officer. Brilliant tactical analyst. One of several brave leaders of Mon Calamari refugees from Imperial invasion of her planet.',NULL,'9_12'),(2029,957,'Light','U','Dagobah','•Flash Of Insight','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/flashofinsight.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. At any time, you may use 3 Force to draw the top card of your Reserve Deck into your hand. If that card is a space creature, you may immediately deploy it for free.','Occasionally Han was capable of such feats, even without Threepio there to tell him these things.',NULL,'4_23'),(2030,962,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','•••Florn Lamproid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/flornlamproid.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','2','May deploy as a \'react\' to any jungle or forest site. Power and forfeit +2 while Dice Ibegon at Audience Chamber. Poison stinger cumulatively adds 1 to attrition against opponent in battles at same site.','Aggressive, serpent-like colonizers. Found on many jungle and forest planets. Have poison stinger that they use when defending themselves.',NULL,'6_13'),(2031,963,'Light','R','Endor','•Fly Casual','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/flycasual.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Early Warning Network or It\'s An Older Code. OR During your deploy phase, deploy one starship (deploy -1) and/or one pilot to a system even without presence or Force icons.  LOST: Take one Tydirium or Tantive IV into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.\"','As a smuggler, Han had years of experience at avoiding Imperial detection. He chose the approach to Endor\'s moon as the time to pass some of that knowledge on to Chewie.',NULL,'8_51'),(2032,966,'Light','PM','Jedi Pack','•For Luck','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JediPack-Light/large/forluck.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If Counter Assault is played, may use 1 Force to add one destiny to your total. If Sense or Alter just played, may use X Force to exclude X Dark Jedi from being the \'highest-ability character.\'','Before swinging across the treacherous abyss, Leia gave Luke a kiss for luck. Despite an incessant storm of laserblasts, they made it.','Dark Forces','102_1'),(2033,967,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•For Luck (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/forluck.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once during your control phase, if opponent occupies a non-battleground location, may peek at top two cards of your Reserve Deck and take one into hand. (Immune to Alter.)','Before swinging across the treacherous abyss, Leia gave Luke a kiss for luck. Despite an incessant storm of laserblasts, they made it.',NULL,'200_40'),(2034,5016,'Light','U','Virtual Set 2','•Force Levitation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Light/large/forcelevitation.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take a device (except Landing Claw) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Target one opponent\'s droid present with your Jedi in battle. For remainder of turn, target is power -1 and may not fire weapons.','Blank.',NULL,'202_6'),(2035,5527,'Light','U','Virtual Set 11','•Force Projection','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/forceprojection.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If [Episode VII] Luke at a site, target all your characters at one other site. They are defense value = 5 this turn.  LOST: Once per game, if opponent just drew battle destiny and Luke is out of play, draw destiny and subtract that amount from opponent\'s total battle destiny.\"','Blank.',NULL,'211_51'),(2036,975,'Light','F','Special Edition','<>Forest','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/forest.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your characters present here are immune to attrition. May not be deployed to Bespin, Coruscant, Hoth, Kessel or Tatooine.',NULL,'Forest','7_121'),(2037,976,'Light','U','Dagobah','Found Someone You Have','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/foundsomeoneyouhave.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a character of ability > 4 on table, use 3 Force to find one of your missing characters (your choice). OR During any control phase, examine the top card of your Lost Pile. If that card is a character of ability < 3, take that character into hand.','\'I\'m looking for someone.\' \'Looking? Found someone you have I would say.\'',NULL,'4_51'),(2038,977,'Light','U','Virtual Set 0','Found Someone You Have (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/foundsomeoneyouhave.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Find one of your missing characters. OR Retrieve the topmost character of your Lost Pile into hand.','\'I\'m looking for someone.\' \'Looking? Found someone you have I would say.\'',NULL,'200_52'),(2039,980,'Light','U','Endor','•Free Ride','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/freeride.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you control a location where opponent has a speeder bike, AT-ST or skiff, steal that vehicle (any characters aboard are lost). OR Peek at one card randomly selected from opponent\'s hand. If that card is a speeder bike, AT-ST or skiff, steal it into hand.','To prevent biker scouts from reaching their base, Luke and Leia \'borrowed\' some nearby transportation.',NULL,'8_52'),(2040,981,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Free Ride & •Endor Celebration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/freeride&endorcelebration.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel Tatooine Occupation, Cloud City Occupation, Rebel Base Occupation. (Immune to Sense.) OR Peak at one card randomly selected from opponent\'s hand. If that card is a speeder bike, AT-ST, or skiff, steal it into hand.',NULL,NULL,'12_58'),(2041,984,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Freon Drevan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/freondrevan.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','3','2','4','Cancels game text of opponent\'s accountants and tax collectors at same or adjacent site. While in a battle at a site, your battle destiny draws may not be canceled, and you may not draw more than two battle destiny.','Xexto who had his business license revoked when his partner siphoned away his credits, fled the system, and left him with the tax debt.',NULL,'12_5'),(2042,985,'Light','C2','Premiere','Friendly Fire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/friendlyfire.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'An accident occurs at the beginning of a battle at any site where opponent has at least two characters and one weapon. Draw destiny. If destiny < number of opponent\'s characters at that site, one is lost. (Opponent\'s choice.)','Overcrowding in heavy fire zones increases chances of accidentally shooting one\'s own comrades. Stormtroopers never let accuracy get in the way of victory.','Collateral Damage','1_80'),(2043,987,'Light','C2','Hoth','•Frostbite','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/frostbite.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Hoth system. At the end of each player\'s turn, for every character that player has present at a marker site under \'nighttime conditions,\' that player must lose 1 Force (2 if character is missing).','\'Then I\'ll see you in hell!\'','Frostbite','3_36'),(2044,989,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Frozen Assets','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/frozenassets.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. At every site where there is a \'frozen\' captive, your Rebels deploy -2 and are power +2 in battle. OR Deploy on top of opponent\'s Force Pile. Force below this card may not be drawn or used. Effect lost at end of opponent\'s next turn.','Molten carbonite is released into the chamber and then flash frozen, releasing a blast of air. The subject is instantly covered in the newly solidified material.',NULL,'5_23'),(2045,994,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Full Throttle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/fullthrottle.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your pilot (or permanent pilot) is defending a battle alone at a system or sector, add one battle destiny. OR If Luke is defending a battle alone at a system or sector, add 1 to power and add one battle destiny.','Rebel pilots use visual scanning to supplement sensors for an edge against Imperial fighter pilots. Natural instincts allow lone Rebels to overcome superior numbers.','Lone Pilot','1_81'),(2046,997,'Light','C2','Premiere','Fusion Generator Supply Tanks','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/fusiongeneratorsupplytanks.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your starship at a system or sector where a related docking bay is on table. Adds 1 to hyperspeed, power and maneuver.','Uses standard fusion technology. Provides starships with energy for hyperspace travel. Installed at docking bays and throughout the Outer Rim Territories.','Fusion Generator Supply Tanks','1_36'),(2047,1001,'Light','C2','Hoth','FX-7 (Effex-Seven)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/fx7effexseven.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','0','2','3','Once per turn, one of your \'hit\' non-droid characters at same or adjacent site may go to your Used Pile rather than your Lost Pile. Cumulatively subtracts 2 from X on your Bacta Tank.','Model nicknamed \'Fixit\' by Rebels at Echo Base. Though obsolete in advanced hospitals, FX-7 droids still operate at many Rebel outposts as assistant surgeons.','FX-10 (Effex-ten)','3_9'),(2048,5533,'Light','R','Virtual Set 9','•Galen Erso','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/galenerso.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','3','3','4','Once per game, may place a non-[Immune to Alter] Effect in owner\'s Used Pile. If both players just drew one battle destiny here, may use 2 Force (free if with an Imperial) to switch numbers. Opponent must first lose 2 Force to fire a superlaser.','Information broker, leader, and spy.',NULL,'209_4'),(2049,1006,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Gambler\'s Luck','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/gamblersluck.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If any gambler is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny (draw two destiny, and choose one). OR if your Lando is defending a battle alone at a site, add two battle destiny (draw three and choose two).','Works every time.',NULL,'5_48'),(2050,1012,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Garon Nas Tal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/garonnastal.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','While at Audience Chamber, all your other Saurins are forfeit +2 and all your characters trained by Sai\'torr Kal Fas are power and forfeit +1.','Saurin combat expert. Hired by Jabba to train his Gamorrean guards. Regrets taking the job. Dislikes Jabba and his henchbeings. Plotting to kill Jabba.',NULL,'6_14'),(2051,807,'Light','C3','Hoth','Echo Base Trooper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/echobasetrooper.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','3','Deploy only on Hoth, but may move elsewhere. Power -1 when at a site other than a Hoth site.','The personnel assigned to protect Echo Base are veteran warriors. Troopers such as Jess Allashane are trained to counter Imperial tactics in cold environment.',NULL,'3_6'),(2052,808,'Light','C1','Hoth','•••Echo Base Trooper Officer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/echobasetrooperofficer.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','3','3','Deploy only on Hoth but may move elsewhere. Echo Base Troopers deploy -1 to same site. Your troopers may move to same Hoth site as a \'react.\'','Like many Rebel specialists, Trey Callum defected from the Imperial officer corps. Trooper officers are masters at stretching the meager resources of the Rebellion.',NULL,'3_7'),(2053,810,'Light','C','Special Edition','Echo Base Trooper Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/echobasetrooperrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on your warrior (Free on your Echo Base trooper). May target a character, creature or vehicle at same or adjacent site using 2 Force (1 if fired by an Echo Base trooper). Draw Destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.','BlasTech A295 blaster rifle. Standard-issue longarm at Echo Base. Highly accurate with good range. Favored by marksmen and snipers in a hostile environment.',NULL,'7_158'),(2054,811,'Light','C2','Hoth','Echo Trooper Backpack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/echotrooperbackpack.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your trooper. May use any number of weapons and devices. Trooper is immune to attrition < 3 when at a planet site.','Rebels carry a variety of equipment to be fully prepared for enemies and the elements. Weather-resistant backpacks keep gear protected and operational.','Stormtrooper Backpack','3_29'),(2055,4071,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•General Airen Cracken','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/generalairencracken.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','3','3','4','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Opponent may not add destiny draws to power or attrition here. While all your ability here is provided by scouts and/or spies, adds one battle destiny and once during your turn may peek at top card of opponent\'s Force Pile.','Leader, scout, and information broker.',NULL,'200_12'),(2056,1017,'Light','R','Death Star II','•General Calrissian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/generalcalrissian.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','4','7','Deploy -2 aboard Falcon. Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting a freighter, adds 1 to maneuver and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. When he attempts to \'blow away\' Death Star II, adds 2 to total.','Leader. Gambler. Fair pilot. Lando was given the rank of General for \'a little maneuver\' at the Battle of Taanab. Willing to lead Rebel starfighters in a crazy attack.',NULL,'9_13'),(2057,1018,'Light','R2','Hoth','•General Carlist Rieekan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/generalcarlistrieekan.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','2','3','5','Each Rebel present with him at a Hoth site is power +1. May use 1 Force to cancel Death Squadron. While at an Echo site, opponent must occupy an additional Hoth site to cancel Echo Base Operations.','One of the original founders of the Rebel Alliance. Former civilian strategist with the House of Organa. Somber leader of Echo Base.',NULL,'3_10'),(2058,5217,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 8','•General Carlist Rieekan (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/generalcarlistrieekan.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','2','3','5','Deploys -1 to a war room. While at a war room, your capital starships at Rebel Base systems may not be targeted by weapons and your Rebels and T-47s at same and related Rebel Base locations move for free to same or related locations.','One of the original founders of the Rebel Alliance. Former civilian strategist with the House of Organa. Somber leader of Echo Base.',NULL,'208_6'),(2059,1020,'Light','R','Endor','•General Crix Madine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/generalcrixmadine.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','6','Once during each of your deploy phases, may take one scout of ability < 3 into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While at your war room or aboard your capital starship, adds 1 to immunity to attrition of all your scouts who have immunity.','Military advisor to Mon Mothma. Leader of commando project. Corellian native. Defected to the Alliance shortly after the Battle of Yavin. Rescued by Rogue Squadron.',NULL,'8_14'),(2060,1021,'Light','U1','Premiere','•General Dodonna','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/generaldodonna.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','3','5','Increases Rebel Planners by 1, doubles if at same site. May use 1 Force to cancel Wrong Turn. Each Rebel present with him at a Yavin 4 site is power +1.','Skilled tactician and natural leader. Planned attack on Death Star after analyzing technical readouts provided by Princess Leia. Star Destroyer captain during Old Republic.',NULL,'1_10'),(2061,5540,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 9','•General Dodonna (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/generaldodonna.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','3','3','5','Once per game, if at a war room, may take a related battleground (or a Y-wing) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While present at a war room, opponent\'s spies may not deploy here and your Epic Event destiny draws are +1.','Skilled tactician and natural leader. Planned attack on Death Star after analyzing technical readouts provided by Princess Leia. Star Destroyer captain during Old Republic.',NULL,'209_5'),(2062,1023,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•General Jar Jar','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/generaljarjar.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','2','4','Once per game may take Brisky Morning Munchen into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per battle, may use 1 Force to target an opponent\'s droid present. Both players draw destiny. If your destiny + 1 > opponent\'s destiny, target lost.','After uniting the Gungans and the Noboo, Boss Nass promoted Jar Jar Binks to General. He\'s still a bit clumsy.',NULL,'14_10'),(2063,5541,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•General Jar Jar (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/generaljarjarai.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','4','2','4','Once per game may take Brisky Morning Munchen into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per battle, may use 1 Force to target an opponent\'s droid present. Both players draw destiny. If your destiny + 1 > opponent\'s destiny, target lost.','After uniting the Gungans and the Noboo, Boss Nass promoted Jar Jar Binks to General. He\'s still a bit clumsy.',NULL,'14_11'),(2064,5542,'Light','U','Virtual Set 9','•General Kenobi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/generalkenobi.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','6','6','9','During battle, if alone or with a clone, may activate 1 Force or add 1 to a just drawn destiny. Once per game, may take a clone or [Reflections III] lightsaber into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 6.','Jedi Council member. Leader.',NULL,'209_6'),(2065,5168,'Light','R','Virtual Set 7','•General Leia Organa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/generalleiaorgana.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','1','4','4','8','While at a war room or battleground, game text of Admiral\'s Orders is suspended and whenever you initiate a battle with a Resistance character, retrieve 1 Force (2 if initiating against a First Order character). Immune to attrition < 4.','Leader.',NULL,'207_5'),(2066,1024,'Light','R','Special Edition','•General McQuarrie','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/generalmcquarrie.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','3','While McQuarrie is on Hoth, your Hoth Sentry is not unique (•), is doubled, deploys free, applies all of its modifiers and is immune to Alter. Power -1 when not on Hoth.','Commander from Ralltiir. Fled from his homeworld after its occupation by the Empire. Was instrumental in the establishment of the new Rebel base on Hoth.',NULL,'7_18'),(2067,1025,'Light','R','Endor','•General Solo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/generalsolo.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','6','8','Deploys -2 on Falcon, Tydirium or Endor. Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When in battle with Chewie (or another of your scouts at an exterior site), may use 2 Force to cancel one opponent\'s battle destiny just drawn. Immune to attrition < 3.','Scout. Leader of the Rebel strike team on Endor. Needed the cleverness of a Corellian to destroy the Endor control bunker. Discovered the truth about Luke and Leia.',NULL,'8_15'),(2068,1026,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•General Solo (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/generalsolo.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','4','8','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. During battle, may use 1 Force to play an Interrupt from your Reserve Deck (then place that card out of play). Once per turn, may take a non-Interrupt card with \'door\' in game text into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Scout. Leader of the Rebel strike team on Endor. Needed the cleverness of a Corellian to destroy the Endor control bunker. Discovered the truth about Luke and Leia.',NULL,'200_13'),(2069,1031,'Light','U','Death Star II','•General Walex Blissex','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/generalwalexblissex.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','1','2','3','Deploys -2 aboard your Star Cruiser or to same location as your Admiral. Adds 1 to the power of anything he pilots. Adds 1 to the power and forfeit ofeach of your A-wings at same and related locations.','Engineer who worked with Jan Dodonna to design the A-wing starfighter. Given honorary rank due to his service to the Rebellion.',NULL,'9_14'),(2070,5546,'Light','U','Virtual Set 9','•General Walex Blissex (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/generalwalexblissex.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','1','2','3','While at a war room, at systems where you have two piloted snub fighters, opponent may draw no more than one battle destiny (you may not cancel those destiny draws) and opponent must use +1 Force to move an Imperial starship away.','Engineer who worked with Jan Dodonna to design the A-wing starfighter. Given honorary rank due to his service to the Rebellion.',NULL,'209_7'),(2071,1032,'Light','U','Endor','•Get Alongside That One','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/getalongsidethatone.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target two non-creature vehicles with maneuver (one yours, one opponent\'s) present at same site. Both players draw destiny; add your vehicle\'s maneuver to your total. Lowest total loses vehicle. OR Your speeder bike piloted by Luke or a scout adds one battle destiny.','Versatility is key to the Rebellion. The Rebels\' ability to adapt to any situation is well-known.','High-speed Tactics','8_53'),(2072,1033,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•Get To Your Ships!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/gettoyourships.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once during your deploy phase, may reveal an unpiloted starfighter from hand to take its matching pilot character from Reserve Deck (or vice versa) and deploy both simultaneously; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','The Queen\'s plan called for the remnants of Bravo Flight to eliminate the Droid Control Ship. Not an easy task.',NULL,'14_31'),(2073,1037,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Ghoel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/ghoel.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','4','0','2','4','Deploys only at interior sites. Cannot move. During a battle at same site, may target one character present. Draw destiny. If destiny +3 > ability, target may not use ability toward drawing battle destiny this turn.','Wol Cabbasshite. Immobile. Species evolved from parasites. Mistakenly left in Jabba\'s palace. No one suspects its intelligence. Often tries to lick passersby.',NULL,'6_16'),(2074,5178,'Light','U','Virtual Set 7','•Ghost','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/ghost.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified VCX Feighter','2','4','3','6','May add 2 pilots, 3 passengers, and Phantom. Has ship-docking capability. May deploy Phantom here from reserve deck; reshuffle. While Hera piloting, immune to attrition < 5 (may not be canceled).','Phoenix Squadron',NULL,'207_17'),(2075,1038,'Light','C','Theed Palace','Gian Speeder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/gianspeeder.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','2','2','2','3','May add 1 driver and 3 passengers. May move as a \'react\' to Naboo sites. Your battle destiny draws are +1 for each of your Royal Naboo Security present. (Limit +3.)','Military repulsorlift armed with three light repeating blasters. With a top speed of 160 kilometers per hour, they have the ability to out-flank an opponent in battle.',NULL,'14_60'),(2076,1039,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Gift Of The Mentor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/giftofthementor.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke and Obi-Wan or Yoda are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny. OR Use 1 Force to search through your Reserve Deck and take any one lightsaber into your hand. Shuffle deck, cut and replace.','Luke relied on Obi-Wan\'s knowledge and advice to learn the ways of the Force. Obi-Wan continued to counsel Luke long after the old Jedi\'s apparent \'death.\'','Maul Strikes','1_82'),(2077,1040,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Gimme A Lift!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/gimmealift.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Relocate Jar Jar to a battle just initiated at an adjacent site. OR Increase Jar Jar\'s landspeed by 1 for remainder of turn. OR If Jar Jar on Brisky Morning Munchen, take him into hand.','Jar Jar Binks\'s courage on the battlefield put quite a thorn in the Trade Federation\'s side. Many believed it wasn\'t actually courage.',NULL,'14_42'),(2078,1042,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Glancing Blow','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/glancingblow.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a character with a lightsaber present in a battle with Vader, lose 1 Force to reduce Vader\'s power to zero. OR If you have a character with a lightsaber in a duel, cancel one opponent\'s destiny draw immediately after it is revealed.','It had been decades since Vader had felt the sting of an enemy\'s blade.',NULL,'5_49'),(2079,1045,'Ligh