rret-mounted laser cannons.',NULL,'3_75'),(2083,1049,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Gold 4','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/gold4.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Y-Wing','3','2','1','3','If deployed to Anoat, may retrieve 1 Force. May add 2 pilots or passengers. SW-4 Ion Cannon deploys and fires free aboard. Immune to attrition < 4 when matching pilot aboard.','Point starfighter for Gold Squadron during the approach to the Death Star. Impact scars on its hull caused by small asteroids.',NULL,'7_142'),(2084,1050,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Gold 5','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/gold5.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Y-Wing','4','2','1','3','May add 2 pilots or passengers, and 1 astromech.','Flown by the veteran Rebel fighter pilot Pops during the Battle of Yavin. He personally supervised all repairs and maintenance.',NULL,'1_142'),(2085,1051,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Gold 6','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/gold6.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Y-Wing','3','2','1','3','If deployed to Kashyyyk, may retrieve 1 Force. May add 2 pilots or passengers. SW-4 Ion Cannon deploys and fires free aboard. Immune to attrition < 4 when matching pilot aboard.','Led an attack on an Imperial outpost at Kashyyyk. Disabled the outpost\'s shields with ion cannons. Flown by Hol Okand during the Battle of Yavin.',NULL,'7_143'),(2086,5552,'Light','PM','Rebel Leader Pack','•Gold Leader In Gold 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/RebelLeader-Light/large/goldleaderingold1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Y-Wing','2','2','5','4','May add 1 pilot or passenger. Permanent pilot aboard is •Dutch, who provides ability of 2, adds 2 to power and may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','At the Battle of Yavin, Dutch led his squadron of out