ue','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just played an Interrupt, use 1 Force to deploy on table. That Interrupt is played out but is then \'grappled\' (placed here but is out of play). Any new Interrupts of the same name are now unique (•). (Immune to Control.)','Stormtrooper utility belts contain basic tools such as a grappling hook to grab onto protrusions. The hook can also be used to ensnare escaping targets.','Tentacle','2_33'),(2095,1069,'Light','C','Death Star II','•••Gray Squadron Y-wing Pilot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/graysquadronywingpilot.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','3','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. When piloting a Y-wing, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. When a starship he pilots fires an ion cannon, once per turn, may draw two weapon destiny and choose one.','Veteran pilots of the reliable Koensayr starfigher were assigned by Ackbar to a key role at Endor. Both the pilots and their venerable Y-wings were up to the task.',NULL,'9_15'),(2096,1057,'Light','R','Endor','•Graak','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/graak.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','2','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. When opponent is losing Force from Force drains at same or adjacent Endor site, lost Force must come from Reserve Deck if possible.','Cunning Ewok. Led successful attacks, encircling enemies and cutting off their retreats.',NULL,'8_16'),(2097,1075,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Green Leader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/greenleader.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Green Squadron 1, draws on battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Adds 3 to total weapon destiny of any starfighter he pilots firing at a starfighter with lower maneuver.','Leader. Assigned to fly fighter screen for General Calrissian at Endor.',NULL,'9_16'),(2098,1067,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Gray Squadron 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/graysquadron1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Y-Wing','3','2','2','3','May add 2 pilots or passengers. Ion cannons may fire free aboard. Each of its ion cannon destiny draws is +2. Immune to attrition < 4 when Salm or Kian piloting.','Y-wing flown by Colonel Salm at the battle of Endor. Ordered to disable capital starships between the Death star and General Calrissian.',NULL,'9_69'),(2099,1078,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Green Squadron 3','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/greensquadron3.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: A-Wing','3','3','2','3','May add 1 pilot. Power -1 when opponent has a starfighter present with higher maneuver. Maneuver +2 at a Death Star II sectors. Immune to attrition < 4 when Tycho Celchu piloting.','Flown by Tycho Celchu at the Battle of Endor. Modified canopy improves pilot vision in tight confines. Assigned to fly top cover for Millennium Falcon.',NULL,'9_72'),(2100,1076,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Green Squadron 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/greensquadron1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: A-Wing','3','3','2','4','May add 1 pilot. Power -1 when opponent has a starfighter present with higher maneuver. Immune to attrition < 4 when Green Leader piloting.','Constructed at Chardaan Shipyards, a zero-gravity facility. Typically used as an escort for Y-wings or B-wings on critical attack missions.',NULL,'9_71'),(2101,4117,'Light','C','Virtual Set 1','•Green Leader In Green Squadron 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/greenleaderingreensquadron1.gif?raw=true','Starship',