ngans spend years studying the art of war in the depths of Otoh Gunga. Only at the Battle of Naboo were these Gungans able to exercise that knowledge. Leader.',NULL,'14_12'),(2109,1084,'Light','U','Dagobah','Grounded Starfighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/groundedstarfighter.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a landed starship (not at a docking bay). Starship may not move. OR Deploy on a starship or vehicle on Dagobah. Starship or vehicle may not move. At the start of your next control phase, starship or vehicle \'sinks\' to bottom of the Lost Pile.','\'If you\'re saying coming here was a bad idea. I\'m beginning to agree with you.\'',NULL,'4_24'),(2110,1089,'Light','C','Coruscant','Gungan Warrior','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/gunganwarrior.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Deploys -1 to a Naboo site opponent occupies. While with another Gungan, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Power +3 while armed with an electropole.','Residing in the underwater city of Otoh Gunga, the Gungans established an alliance with the Naboo to fight the Trade Federation\'s forceful occupation of their planet.',NULL,'12_7'),(2111,1100,'Light','PM','Enhanced Premiere','•Han With Heavy Blaster Pistol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedPremiere-Light/large/hanwithheavyblasterpistol.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','4','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Adds one battle destiny if with Luke or Chewie. Permanent weapon is •Han\'s Heavy Blaster Pistol (may target a character or creature for free; draw destiny; target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if destiny +1 > defense value).','Scoundrel, smuggler, gambler and risk taker. \'Everything\'s going to be fine. Trust me.\'',NULL,'108_1'),(2112,5131,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 5','•Han, Chewie, And The Falcon (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/hanchewieandthefalcon.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Heavily Modified Light Freighter','2','7','5','8','Permanent pilots are •Han and •Chewie: provide ability of 5. Attempts here to \'blow away\' any Death Star are +2. Immue to Come With Me, Lateral Damage, Life Debt and attrition < 6.','Although tempermental, this trusty hunk of junk always seems to perform for its proud owner and his Wookie co-pilot when needed the most.',NULL,'205_7'),(2113,1102,'Light','U2','Premiere','Han\'s Back','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/hansback.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Han is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve him from the Lost Pile. OR Use 3 Force to search through your Reserve Deck and take Han into your hand. Shuffle deck, cut and replace.','\'Didn\'t we just leave this party?\'',NULL,'1_83'),(2114,1101,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Han, Chewie, And The Falcon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/hanchewieandthefalcon.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Heavily Modified Light Freighter','2','4','6','8','Permanent pilots are •Han and •Chewie: provide ability of 5, add one battle destiny, and add 5 to power. Immune to attrition < 6, Come With Me, and Lateral Damage. End of your turn: Use 3 Force to maintain OR Place out of play.','Although tempermental, this trusty hunk of junk always seems to perform for its proud owner and his Wookie co-pilot when needed the most.',NULL,'13_21'),(2115,1108,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Han\'s Toolkit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/hanstoolkit.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on one of you characters, vehicles or starships (free on Falcon or Han). While aboard a vehicle or starship, you may use 1 Force to cancel any Interrupt or Effect of any kind (except those immune to Alter or Control) which targets that vehicle or starship.','Experienced pilots keep a well equipped toolkit. Horizontal boosters, alluvial dampers and hydrospanners aid in performing high-tech repairs aboard starships.',NULL,'4_10'),(2116,1106,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Han\'s Heavy Blaster Pistol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/hansheavyblasterpistol.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on Han, or 3 on your warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value. If hit by Han, target\'s forfeit = 0.','BlasTech DL-44 heavy pistol. Short range, but relatively powerful. Carries energy for 25 shots. Illegal or restricted on most systems.',NULL,'1_154'),(2117,1104,'Light','C2','Premiere','Han\'s Dice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/hansdice.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your characters of ability > 2 is in a battle, use 1 Force to draw another battle destiny instead of the one you just drew.','A pair of dice dangling above Millennium Falcon\'s cockpit, for luck. \'I\'ve never seen anything to make me believe there\'s one, all-powerful Force controlling everything.\'',NULL,'1_84'),(2118,1109,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Harc Seff','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/harcseff.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Power +1 at a swamp. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While at a battleground site, whenever you must lose Force from a Force drain at an adjacent site, may reduce the loss by X by using X Force.','Ishi Tib accountant. Experienced administrator. Freelance consultant. Worked for many planetary governors. Knows how to get the most out of any taxation scheme.',NULL,'7_20'),(2119,1110,