ere), Ewok Village, and I Feel The Conflict.{For} remainder of game, you may not deploy [Episode I] Jedi (except Yoda) or [Episode I] padawans. Luke may not be captured by Bring Him Before Me unless there are 2 or more cards stacked on Insignificant Rebellion during any move phase.(While) this side up, you may initiate battles for free.{Flip} this card if Luke (or a Jedi) at a battleground site and opponent has no characters of ability > 4 at battleground sites.He Will Bring Balance:{While} this side up, once during your control phase, may peek at up to X cards from the top of your Reserve Deck, where X = number of battlegrounds you occupy; take one into hand and shuffle your Reserve Deck. During your draw phase, may retrieve any one card; opponent may stack a card from hand on I Feel The Conflict to place that out of play instead.{Flip} this card (unless Vader crossed over) if opponent\'s character of ability > 4 at a battleground site or you do not have Luke (or a Jedi) at a battleground site.',NULL,NULL,'208_25'),(2123,1125,'Light','R1','Premiere','Help Me Obi-Wan Kenobi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/helpmeobiwankenobi.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Obi-Wan is at a site you control, he may apply any amount of his ability toward drawing a battle destiny at any other location. Ability he uses this way cannot be used again this turn. OR One Rebel may move as a \'react\' to an adjacent battle site.','Leia sent a hologram plea, \'General Kenobi, years ago you served my father in the Clone Wars. Now he begs you to help him in his struggle against the Empire.\'',NULL,'1_86'),(2124,4018,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 1','Hear Me Baby, Hold Together (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/hearmebabyholdtogether.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Play a Defensive Shield from under your Starting Effect. [Immune to Sense] OR Cancel Counter Attack, [Virtual Set 0] Defensive Fire or Hidden Weapons. OR Make a just drawn Overload destiny = 1/2.  LOST: Cancel Cease Fire! or I Have You Now.\"','Smuggler and Rebel starships use black market armor plating and deflector shields to withstand enemy fire. Expensive but life-saving modifications.','Cold Feet (V)','201_13'),(2125,1113,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•He Can Go About His Business','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/hecangoabouthisbusiness.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Cancels Responsibility Of Command and You Overestimate Their Chances. While Brangus Glee on table, once per turn you may search opponent\'s Lost Pile and place all docking bays found there out of play.','\'You can go about your business.\'',NULL,'13_22'),(2126,5182,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 7','Help Me Obi-Wan Kenobi (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/helpmeobiwankenobi.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During battle, target an opponent\'s characterof ability of < 2 present with your Jedi;  target is excluded from battle. OR Cancel a \'react\'. OR If Obi-Wan is at a battleground site, and your Rebel of Republic character (or Leia) is in battle at another location, add one battle destiny.','Leia sent a hologram plea, \'General Kenobi, years ago you served my father in the Clone Wars. Now he begs you to help him in his struggle against the Empire.\'',NULL,'207_12'),(2127,1129,'Light','R','Endor','•Here We Go Again','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/herewegoagain.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle that opponent initiated just ended, initiate a new battle at same location. \'Reacts\' are allowed only for opponent, but cards may not \'react\' away or hide from battle. Loser ignores battle damage. If your droid present there, add one battle destiny (two if C-3PO).','C-3PO had been through enough battles that many of the Rebels in the strike team considered him a good luck charm. That isn\'t what Han considers him.','Counterattack','8_54'),(2128,1134,'Light','U','Special Edition','Heroic Sacrifice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/heroicsacrifice.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just forfeited a Rebel of ability > 2 from a battle at a battleground, deploy on that location; place that Rebel out of play and retrieve 2 Force for each Heroic Sacrifice on table. Immediate Effect canceled if opponent controls this location. (Immune to Control.)','The Alliance lost many fine soldiers at conflicts such as the Battle of Hoth. The Rebel High Command is aware of the cost of freedom from Imperial tyranny.',NULL,'7_63'),(2129,5576,'Light','R','Special Edition','Hidden Base / Systems Will Slip Through Your Fingers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/hiddenbase.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Hidden Base:Deploy Rendezvous Point. Place a planet system (with a parsec number from 1 to 8) from outside your deck face down on your side of table (not in play); that card indicates the planet where your \'Hidden Base\' is located.{While} this side up, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one system from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Opponent loses no more than 1 Force from each of your Force drains at systems and sectors.{Flip} this card any time after you have deployed five battleground systems and your \'Hidden Base\' system.Systems Will Slip Through Your Fingers:{While} this side up, to draw a card from Force Pile, opponent must first use 1 Force. For each battleground system you control, you may cancel one opponent\'s Force drain (limit twice per turn). You may not deploy any systems. At each system opponent occupies during any deploy phase, opponent may \'probe\' there by placing one card from hand face down beneath that system.{Place} out of play if \'Hidden Base\' system is \'probed.\' Dark side places \'probe\' cards in Used Pile (and may retrieve 1 Force for each Probe Droid used to \'probe\').',NULL,NULL,'7_136'),(2130,1136,'Light','U2','A New Hope','•Het Nkik','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/hetnkik.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','*','1','* Deploys only on Tatooine for 2 Force from each player\'s Force Pile. Het is power +1 for each Stormtrooper at same site, unless Reegesk is present.','Jawa scout. Wants to avenge deaths of relatives killed in stormtrooper assault on sandcrawler. Reegesk pilfered the powerpack from his blaster at a critical moment.',NULL,'2_9'),(2131,1014,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Geezum','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/geezum.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','2','During your control phase, if at an exterior planet site, may use 2 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take a related site into hand and reshuffle. While at Audience Chamber, all your other Snivvians are forfeit +2.','Snivvian scout. Enjoys exploring new planets and charting difficult terrain. Paid very well by Jabba to do so. Unsure of his employer\'s motivations.',NULL,'6_15'),(2132,1140,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Hiding In The Garbage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/hidinginthegarbage.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your side of table. At any time, you may declare a card type. Use Force one by one, revealing each card used, until a card of that type is revealed (take it into hand) or Force Pile is depleted.','Rebels often exploit loopholes in Imperial procedures to gain an advantage.',NULL,'4_25'),(2133,1138,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','Hidden Compartment','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/hiddencompartment.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any R-unit droid. At start of a battle, you may \'react\' by deploying one character weapon (at normal use of the Force) from Reserve Deck on a warrior present; reshuffle.','Standard astromech internal cargo area measures 20 centimeters by 8 centimeters. Some models have a custom compressed (AI)r launcher for shooting flares.',NULL,'6_50'),(2134,1154,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Home One: War Room','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/homeonewarroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: :While you control with a Rebel here, Home One is deploy -5 and power +3.',NULL,NULL,'9_58'),(2135,1153,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Home One: Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/homeonedockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here is free. If you occupy, opponent may not move to this site.',NULL,NULL,'9_57'),(2136,1163,'Light','U2','Hoth','•Hoth','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/hoth.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, for each of your starships here, your total power is +1 in battles at Hoth sites.',NULL,'Hoth','3_55'),(2137,1156,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Honor Of The Jedi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/honorofthejedi.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Unless opponent occupies three battlegrounds, each time you must lose Force (except from your card, battle damage or a Force drain at a battleground), reduce the loss by 2. (Immune to Alter while you occupy any battleground).','The final act of Luke\'s ascension to Jedi Knighthood was sending off his father, draped in the garb of Vader.',NULL,'9_33'),(2138,1157,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Hopping Mad','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/hoppingmad.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one of your droids. During your control phase, may use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one Droid Shutdown, The Professor, We\'re Doomed, Scomp Link Access, This Is All Your Fault or Shocking Information into hand and reshuffle.','\'I\'m standing here in pieces and you\'re having delusions of grandeur!\'',NULL,'5_27'),(2139,1152,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Home One','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/homeone.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Mon Calamari Star Cruiser','1','9','12','12','May add unlimited pilots, passengers, vehicles and starfighters. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilots provide total ability of 4. Immune to attrition < 8 (< 10 when Ackbar piloting).','Command ship of the Rebel fleet. 1200 meters long. Masterpiece of aesthetic form. Most heavily armed and armored ship in the fleet. Admiral Ackbar\'s personal flagship.',NULL,'9_74'),(2140,1013,'Light','U2','A New Hope','•Garouf Lafoe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/garouflafoe.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','2','Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots. Adds 1 to forfeit of each of your characters at same Tatooine site. Subtracts 1 from forfeit of each of opponent\'s characters at same Hoth site. Game text suspended if at same site as a tax collector.','Free-trader who imports ice chunks from rings of Ohann and Adriana, outer planets in Tatoo system. Sales remain cold...due to steep Imperial taxes and bribes.',NULL,'2_8'),(2141,1160,'Light','C','Coruscant','•Horox Ryyder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/horoxryyder.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','1','2','4','Agendas: order, taxation, peace. While in a senate majority, opponent may not draw more than one battle destiny at battleground systems, and you may not cancel opponent\'s battle destiny draws at systems.','Anx senator. Known for his patience, Horox exhibits unique insight into many complicated Senate issues.',NULL,'12_8'),(2142,1164,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Hoth Sentry','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/hothsentry.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy at any Hoth site. Declare one of the following to affect that site and adjacent sites while \'sentry\' present: Opponent\'s deploy +1. OR Opponent\'s ability required for battle destiny +1. OR Your total power +1.','\'Reroute all power to the energy shield. We\'ve got to hold them till all transports are away.\'',NULL,'7_64'),(2143,1169,'Light','U2','Hoth','•Hoth: Echo Command Center (War Room)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/hothechocommandcenterwarroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, with X leaders here, your total power is +X in battles at Hoth locations.',NULL,'Hoth: Echo Command Center (War Room)','3_57'),(2144,1171,'Light','C2','Hoth','•Hoth: Echo Corridor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/hothechocorridor.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, once per turn, may use 4 Force to raise a converted Hoth site to the top.',NULL,'Hoth: Echo Corridor','3_58'),(2145,1174,'Light','C2','Hoth','•Hoth: Echo Med Lab','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/hothechomedlab.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Once per turn, when you deploy a medical droid, it is deploy -2.',NULL,NULL,'3_60