Vaporator on table, the second Force you activate may also be drawn into hand.','Grows fruits and vegetables. Very efficient water use. Often underground. Feeds moisture farm families, but excess vegetables are often sold at markets.',NULL,'1_37'),(2151,1184,'Light','PM','Reflections II','Houjix & Out Of Nowhere','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/houjix&outofnowhere.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If opponent just initiated a battle at a system or sector where you have a starship with maneuver > 3, use 1 Force to add one battle destiny.  LOST: If you just forfeited all your cards that participated in a battle you lost, cancel all remaining battle damage. (Immune to Sense.)\"',NULL,'Ghhhk & Those Rebels Won\'t Escape Us','10_8'),(2152,1187,'Light','U2','Premiere','How Did We Get Into This Mess?','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/howdidwegetintothismess.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your droids is at the Dune Sea or where there is a Scomp link, use 1 Force to discard your entire hand to your Used Pile. Draw the same number of cards from your Reserve Deck. Draw one extra card if droid is C- 3PO or R2-D2.','Stranded in the Dune Sea, R2-D2 insisted on heading into rocky canyons where he thought settlements were likely to exist. Threepio had other ideas.',NULL,'1_87'),(2153,1203,'Light','C','Tatooine','•I Can\'t Believe He\'s Gone','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/icantbelievehesgone.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Obi-Wan was just placed out of play, use 1 Force to deploy Immediate Effect on table. If a battle was just initiated at a site, may use 1 Force to increase your total power by 5. (Immune to Control.)','Even though Luke felt the pain of losing his mentor, Obi-Wan continued to give him strength and guidance through the Force.',NULL,'11_19'),(2154,1197,'Light','C2','Premiere','Hyper Escape','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/hyperescape.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated at any system or sector, move all your starships and vehicles there away.','\'We\'ll be safe enough once we make the jump to hyperspace.\' A starship in hyperspace cannot be tracked unless a homing beacon has been hidden aboard.',NULL,'1_88'),(2155,1183,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Houjix','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/houjix.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During the damage segment of a battle you lost, if you have no cards left that can be forfeited, cancel all remaining battle damage. (Immune to Sense.) OR Cancel Sunsdown.','Dejarik creature. These ferocious-looking beasts are gentle, loyal, and often domesticated as guard animals or pets on Kinyen, the Gran homeworld. Incendiary.','Ghhhk','2_50'),(2156,1133,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Heroes Of Yavin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/heroesofyavin.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke, Chewie and Han are in a battle together, draw destiny and subtract that amount from opponent\'s attrition and total power. OR If Red 5 and Falcon are in a battle together, add one battle destiny.','The three Rebels proved to be a deadly combination time and time again.',NULL,'7_91'),(2157,1214,'Light','C2','A New Hope','I Have A Very Bad Feeling About This','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/ihaveaverybadfeelingaboutthis.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just deployed four or more characters to same location this turn, prevent all of those characters from battling this turn. OR If opponent just \'reacted\' to a battle, cancel the battle.','\'Look at him, he\'s heading for that small moon.\' Luke became apprehensive when Obi-Wan informed him, \'That\'s no moon. It\'s a space station.\'','Ng\'ok','2_51'),(2158,1207,'Light','U','Death Star II','•I Feel The Conflict','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/ifeeltheconflict.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on table. Each time you win a battle or duel, opponent loses 1 Force (cannot be reduced) and stacks lost card here face down. When attempting to cross Vader over, add 3 to total destiny for each card in stack. (Immune to Alter.)','\'I know there is good in you. The Emperor hasn\'t driven it from you fully.\'','Insignificant Rebellion','9_34'),(2159,1212,'Light','R','Dagobah','I Have A Bad Feeling About This','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/ihaveabadfeelingaboutthis.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force: Retarget an Interrupt or Utinni Effect which specifies a target to another appropriate target on the same side of the Force. OR Relocate any Effect (except those immune to Alter) deployed on a location to another appropriate location.','\'This grounds sure feels strange. Doesn\'t feel like rock. I don\'t know...\'','Surprise','4_52'),(2160,1213,'Light','C','Endor','•I Have A Really Bad Feeling About This','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ihaveareallybadfeelingaboutthis.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle where opponent has more than double your power, target your highest-ability character in that battle. Draw destiny. If destiny < target\'s ability, deploy one character there from hand (for free).','\'I\'m rather embarrassed, General Solo, but it appears you are to be the main course at a banquet in my honor.\'',NULL,'8_55'),(2161,1220,'Light','R1','Hoth','I Thought They Smelled Bad On The Outside','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/ithoughttheysmelledbadontheoutside.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Sacrifice (lose) your creature vehicle to protect one character present from Exposure, Ice Storm, Frostbite and Gravel Storm for remainder of turn. (Two characters may be protected if sacrificing a ronto.) OR Double Tzizvvt\'s power until he moves.','\'Hang on, kid. This may smell bad, kid...but it\'ll keep you warm...until I can get the shelter built...\'',NULL,'3_43'),(2162,1241,'Light','U1','Hoth','•Ice Storm','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/icestorm.gif?raw=true','Effect','Mobile','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy at outermost marker. All characters present at same exterior site are missing. Each turn, during your control phase, storm moves to next marker, reversing direction at innermost marker. Mobile Effect lost when moved beyond outermost marker.','The intensity of a Hoth ice storm is exacerbated by its speed and erratic movement across the frozen planet.','Ice Storm','3_37'),(2163,1229,'Light','U1','A New Hope','I\'m Here To Rescue You','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/imheretorescueyou.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a spy present at the Detention Block Corridor, target a captive there. Draw destiny. If destiny + ability of spy > ability of captive, target is released. Otherwise, spy is captured. OR Cancel Spice Mines Of Kessel (releasing targeted captive).','\'Huh?\'',NULL,'2_52'),(2164,1223,'Light','U','Coruscant','•I Will Not Defer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/iwillnotdefer.gif?raw=true','Effect','Political','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If no senator here, you may place a senator here from hand to add 2 to your next Force drain at a battleground this turn. If a peace agenda here, once per turn you may activate up to 2 Force when opponent initiates battle.','\'I\'ve come before you to resolve this attack on our sovereignty now.\'',NULL,'12_43'),(2165,1217,'Light','R','Endor','•I Know','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/iknow.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Leia and Han are in a battle together, add two battle destiny. OR If opponent just initiated a battle against Han, you may \'react\' by deploying there (for free) Leia and/or her matching weapon from hand and/or Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Han and Leia chose unusual times to express their true feelings for each other.',NULL,'8_56'),(2166,1233,'Light','R','Death Star II','•I\'m With You Too','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/imwithyoutoo.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Luke if That\'s One and Count Me In are on table. When Han, Chewie, Leia and Luke are involved in the same battle, you may double your total battle destiny and Han, Chewie, Leia, and Luke are immune to attrition. Don\'t Get Cocky is a Used Interrupt.','Luke completes the legendary foursome.',NULL,'9_35'),(2167,1218,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•I Must Be Allowed To Speak','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/imustbeallowedtospeak.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Jabba\'s Palace site. Luke may deploy at this site regardless of presence or location deployment restrictions. When he is deployed here, relocate Effect to Luke, he is immune to attrition while on Tatooine. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Jedi mod spienko eek.\'',NULL,'6_55'),(2168,1219,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•I Must Be Allowed To Speak (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/imustbeallowedtospeak.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per character, when you deploy Chewie, Lando, Leia, or Luke to a Tatooine site, may take any one card from Used Pile into hand; reshuffle. While Han is frozen, Rebels are immune to None Shall Pass. Once per game, may deploy a farm from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','\'Jedi mod spienko eek.\'',NULL,'200_41'),(2169,1296,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Incom Corporation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/incomcorporation.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Rebel Base interior site. Your ability-1 permanent pilots aboard T-16s, T-47s, Z-95s and X-wings (except squadrons) are replaced by ability-2 permanent pilots who add 1 to power. Canceled if opponent controls this site. (Immune to Alter.)','Incom\'s core design team defected to the Alliance with the plans for the famed X-wing fighter. Once with the Alliance, many former Incom test pilots flew for the Rebellion.',NULL,'7_66'),(2170,1302,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Independence','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/independence.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Mon Calamari Star Cruiser','1','8','9','10','May add 5 pilots, 6 passengers, 1 vehicle and 3 starfighters. Has shipdocking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 4 when a Rebel leader aboard).','Communications starship. Often hosts first assignment for top prospects from among newly commissioned officers.',NULL,'9_75'),(2171,1303,'Light','U','Dagobah','Ineffective Maneuver','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/ineffectivemaneuver.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any Effect or Utinni Effect (except those immune to Alter). During each of owner\'s draw phases, if you occupy an asteroid sector, owner must choose to either lose 1 Force or voluntarily cancel that Effect or Utinni Effect. (Immune to Alter.)','To succeed in the Imperial Navy, an officer must be willing to take risks. Difficult choices must be made.','Sudden Impact','4_26'),(2172,1297,'Light','C','Special Edition','Incom Engineer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/incomengineer.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','1','2','3','At same and related locations, adds 2 to your total battle destiny where your X-wing, T-47, T-16 and Z-95 is present and makes those vehicles and starships immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if he is present with your maintenance droid).','After narrowly escaping the nationalization of Incom by the Empire, many former employees joined the Rebellion. They spent long hours maintaining X-wings and T-47s.',NULL,'7_22'),(2173,1321,'Light','R2','Premiere','Into The Garbage Chute, Flyboy','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/intothegarbagechuteflyboy.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Trash Compactor is on table, cancel any battle just initiated at another Death Star site by moving (for free) all your characters involved to the Trash Compactor.','Leia led an unorthodox escape into a \'garbage masher\' on the detention level. \'What an incredible smell you\'ve discovered!\'',NULL,'1_89'),(2174,1325,'Light','F','Special Edition','Intruder Missile','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/intrudermissile.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your B-wing, Z-95, YT-1300 Transport, or Falcon. May target a capital starship for free. Draw destiny. Add 3 if that capital starship was targeted by another weapon this turn. Target hit if total destiny > defense value. After firing, place Missile in Used Pile.','Prototype missile developed by Slayn & Korpil. Ionizing warhead disrupts onboard systems. Capable of destroying capital starships by overloading shield generators.','Intruder Missile','7_159'),(2175,1323,'Light','R','Cloud City','Into The Ventilation Shaft, Lefty','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/intotheventilationshaftlefty.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Relocate one of your characters from a Cloud City site to Weather Vane (if \'hit,\' character is first restored to normal). May be played even after a battle has just been initiated.','\'Aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa . . .\'',NULL,'5_54'),(2176,1330,'Light','C2','Hoth','•It Can Wait','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/itcanwait.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to place an opponent\'s just deployed character, starship, vehicle, weapon, or device in opponent\'s hand. On opponent\'s next turn, that card (or one card of same title) may deploy for free.','\'Sir, might I suggest that you - It can wait.\'','I\'d Just As Soon Kiss A Wookiee','3_44'),(2177,1329,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','•••Ishi Tib','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/ishitib.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','2','Power +1 at any swamp. During your draw phase, may place one card from your hand on bottom of Used Pile to draw a card from Reserve Deck.','Extremely efficient organizers. Sought after by transgalactic corporations. Spend a large part of their life underwater. Protected by rough, thick skin.',NULL,'6_19'),(2178,1313,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Innocent Scoundrel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/innocentscoundrel.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If your gambler was just targeted by a weapon, opponent must choose to select a new target or lose 2 Force.  LOST: Cancel any Effect (except those immune to Alter) deployed on Han or your Lando.\"','\'Well, that 