lotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/holokand.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Gold 6 during battle, adds one destiny to total power only. When at Kashyyyk system, adds 1 to each of your Force drains there.','Piloted Gold 6 at the Battle of Yavin. Flew as Dutch\'s wingman during an attack on an Imperial supply outpost at Kashyyyk. Befriended by Chewbacca before leaving Yavin 4.',NULL,'7_21'),(2183,1147,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Hit And Run','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/hitandrun.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Just after the weapons segment of a battle, you may move any or all of your starships there away. (\'Hit\' cards must still be lost.)','Many pilots for the Rebellion learned their skills using modified T- 47s and other airspeeders. Being able to weave in and out of combat has become second nature to them.',NULL,'7_92'),(2184,1242,'Light','U2','A New Hope','•Ickabel G\'ont','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/ickabelgont.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Opponent must use X Force when Force draining at any adjacent site, where X = the number of other musicians present with Ickabel.','Male Bith musician. His favorite cantina song is \'Tears of Aquanna\' (mainly because it features him on Fanfar).',NULL,'2_11'),(2185,1377,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Jawa Ion Gun','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/jawaiongun.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your Jawa, 3 on your warrior. May target a character using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Targeted droid stolen if destiny +1 > forfeit. Targeted non-droid character excluded from battle if destiny = defense value.','Cobbled-together weapon built from salvaged power cells, droid restraining bolts and an ion accelerator. Fires a stream of ion energy that stuns droids and irritates others.',NULL,'2_78'),(2186,1386,'Light','U1','Premiere','Jedi Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/jedilightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use X Force to deploy on your warrior where X = (7 - warrior\'s ability). May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature by using X Force. Draw two destiny. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Elegant sword of pure energy. \'This is the weapon of a Jedi Knight. Not as clumsy or as random as a blaster. A lightsaber can be dangerous to an unskilled user.\'','Dark Jedi Lightsaber','1_155'),(2187,1392,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Jerus Jannick','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/jerusjannick.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','4','3','3','Deploys - 2 to same site as Amidala. While in a battle with Amidala or Leia, your leaders present may not be targeted by weapons, and Jerus may be forfeited to satisfy all battle damage and attrition against you.','Part of Amidala\'s Royal Naboo Security Forces, Jerus has been trained as a protector of royalty, and is determined that his responsibility be carried out professionally.',NULL,'14_14'),(2188,1389,'Light','R1','Premiere','Jedi Presence','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/jedipresence.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your Jedi is present during any battle, use 1 Force to cause all other Rebels there to battle at double power.','Jedi Knights inspired allies on the battlefield through bravery and heroism. Obi-Wan\'s presence encouraged the Rebels and gave them a chance to escape the Death Star.','Dark Jedi Presence','1_92'),(2189,5627,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 10','•Jedi Business','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/jedibusiness.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Non-[Episode I] Jedi are lost. Qui-Gon is deploy -1. Unless with Anakin or Vader, Mace is immune to attrition. Once per turn, may choose: deploy an [Episode I] lightsaber from Reserve Deck (reshuffle), or once per game, deploy Malastare, Mos Espa, or Night Club from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter)','The peacekeepers of the galaxy are not to be taken lightly.',NULL,'210_17'),(2190,1400,'Light','F','Special Edition','<>Jungle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/jungle.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your aliens and creature vehicles are each power +1 here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Coruscant, Hoth, Kessel or Tatooine.',NULL,'Jungle','7_122'),(2191,1380,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Jawa Siesta','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/jawasiesta.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'To deploy (on your side of table), requires 3 Force from both players\' Force Piles. Cannot deploy otherwise. All your Jawas are forfeit +1.','Three Jawas take a cool, energy-saving nap in the noon-day suns at Mos Eisley.','Jawa Pack','1_51'),(2192,1385,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','Jedi Levitation (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/jedilevitation.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If you just drew a character for destiny, take that card into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny.  LOST: Use 3 Force to retrieve a non-[Maintenance] character into hand.\"','A Jedi can adjust the Force within and around an object, causing it to move as the Jedi wills.','Sith Fury (V)','200_54'),(2193,1393,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jess','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/jess.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','1','3','3','May retrieve 1 Force each time you deploy a musician to same site. During your turn, may use 1 Force to \'charm\' one male alien of ability < 3 present; that male is forfeit = 0 for remainder of turn.','Popular musician. Often seen with Bib Fortuna. Captivates those around her. Hoping to join a band and leave Jabba\'s palace.',NULL,'6_21'),(2194,1383,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Jedi Leap','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/jedileap.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your deploy phase, lose 1 Force to relocate [Episode I] Obi- Wan to an adjacent Naboo site. OR Raise your converted interior Theed Palace site to the top.','Obi-Wan\'s youth combined with his Jedi training meant that he was not to be dispatched easily.',NULL,'13_26'),(2195,1405,'Light','C','Theed Palace','Kaadu','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/kaadu.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Creature','4','1','1','3','May add 1 \'rider\' (passenger). Ability = 1/2. Moves for free. While \'ridden\' by a Gungan, may move as a \'react.\' While at a swamp, adds 1 to your Force drains there.','Used by many Gungan warriors due to their fearless nature. Kaadu lay large numbers of eggs to compensate for those eaten by predators.',NULL,'14_61'),(2196,5150,'Light','F','Virtual Set 6','•K-2SO (Kay-Tuesso)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual6-Light/large/k2so.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','4','4','4','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. While with Cassian, attrition against opponent is +1 here. If just lost, place out of play; if lost from a site, opponent may not move from there for remainder of turn.','Spy.',NULL,'206_5'),(2197,1390,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Jek Porkins','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/b