olotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/keirsantage.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','4','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. When at a system, sector, or docking bay, once during each of your deploy phases, may subtract 2 from deploy cost of your unique (•) X-wing deploying here.','Rescued from an Imperial detention center by Wedge Antilles. Rogue Squadron veteran. Assigned to Red Squadron at the Battle of Endor. Coordinates with Rebellion procurement.',NULL,'9_19'),(2206,5038,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 3','•Kanan Jarrus','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/kananjarrus.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','4','4','6','Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots. While present with an Imperial (or two Rebels), all immunity to attrition here is canceled.','Padawan.',NULL,'203_6'),(2207,5060,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•Jakku','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/jakku.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If [Episode VII] Falcon here, Force drain +1 here.',NULL,'Jakku','204_26'),(2208,1352,'Light','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','•Jabba\'s Palace: Antechamber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Light/large/jabbaspalaceantechamber.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Creatures cannot attack here. While no Rebels present, your total power here is +2.',NULL,NULL,'112_2'),(2209,1235,'Light','C','Coruscant','•I\'ve Decided To Go Back','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/ivedecidedtogoback.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: During your move phase, take one of your characters with politics at Galactic Senate into hand.  LOST: If you have a Republic character with politics in battle at a site, add one battle destiny; that character is power and politics = 0 until end of turn.\"','\'This is your arena. I feel I must return to mine.\'',NULL,'12_60'),(2210,5616,'Light','R','Virtual Set 10','•It\'s True, All Of It','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/itstrueallofit.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just played an Interrupt, use 2 Force to deploy on table and stack that card here. If opponent just drew destiny (or played an Interrupt) with the same card title as card here, they lose 1 Force. (Immune to Control)','The heroes of the Rebellion know that where there is life, there is hope.',NULL,'210_16'),(2211,5064,'Light','C1','Virtual Set 4','•Jakku: Starship Graveyard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/jakkustarshipgraveyard.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you just deployed a scavenger here, may retrieve a device, droid, or weapon.',NULL,NULL,'204_30'),(2212,5062,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•Jakku: Ravager Crash Site','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/jakkuravagercrashsite.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : At the start of your turn, may stack top card of Lost Pile face down on Graveyard Of Giants.',NULL,NULL,'204_28'),(2213,1334,'Light','U','Cloud City','•It\'s A Trap!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/itsatrap.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Sniper or Blasted Droid. LOST: Use 3 Force to cancel any battle just initiated at a site. (Immune to Sense.)\"','Luke\'s decision to ignore Leia\'s warning about the trap cost him an arm and a. . . well, just a hand actually.',NULL,'5_55'),(2214,1370,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Jar Jar Binks','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/jarjarbinks.gif?raw=true','Character