t/large/landoswristcomlink.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a character. When at a Cloud City site, Lobot and your Cloud City troopers may deploy or move here as a \'react.\'','Easily concealed device used by Lando to remain in contact with his subordinates. Directly connected to Cloud City\'s central computer.',NULL,'5_14'),(2219,5063,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•Jakku: Rey\'s Encampment','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/jakkureysencampment.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Once per game, may deploy Rey here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Rey deploys -2 here.',NULL,NULL,'204_29'),(2220,1371,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Jar Jar\'s Electropole','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/jarjarselectropole.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploys on Jar Jar. May \'throw\' (place in Used Pile) to target a character, creature or vehicle. Draw destiny. If destiny +2 > defense value, target is landspeed = 0 and power -2 for remainder of turn.','Jar Jar had to be instructed on how to use an electropole prior to the battle on the great grass plains. It\'s not his weapon of choice.',NULL,'13_25'),(2221,5065,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•Jakku: Tuanul Village','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/jakkutuanulvillage.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Lor San Tekka is power +4 and defense value -2 here.',NULL,'Jakku: Tuanul Village','204_31'),(2222,1351,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace Sabacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/jabbaspalacesabacc.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Requirements: A Gambler, gangster, smuggler or information broker at a Jabba\'s Palace site. Wild cards (1-6): Passenger Deck and deserts. Clone cards: Aliens and Jabba\'s Palace sites (gamblers and Jabba may use clone cards as 4\'s.) Stakes: One character weapon or non-unique alien.','Jabba could lick anyone at sabacc.','Jabba\'s Palace Sabacc','6_67'),(2223,1358,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace: Entrance Cavern','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/jabbaspalaceentrancecavern.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Force drain +1 here.',NULL,'Jabba\'s Palace: Entrance Cavern','6_82'),(2224,1382,'Light','C','Tatooine','•Jedi Escape','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/jediescape.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a duel against one of your non-captive Jedi at a site, use 1 Force to cancel the duel and you may relocate any number of your characters there to an adjacent site.','Qui-Gon escaped with his friends from Tatooine, barely getting away from the clutches of Darth Maul.',NULL,'11_36'),(2225,5631,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 11','Jedi Lightsaber (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/jedilightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your character of ability > 4 or Padawan. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and may not be used to satisfy attrition, if total destiny > defense value.','Elegant sword of pure energy. \'This is the weapon of a Jedi Knight. Not as clumsy or as random as a blaster. A lightsaber can be dangerous to an unskilled user.\'',NULL,'211_33'),(2226,5614,'Light','F','Special Edition','•It\'s Not My Fault!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/itsnotmyfault.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle at a site, use X Force