s-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/insertionplanning.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your scout is in battle at an exterior planet site, subtract 3 from opponent\'s total battle destiny. OR Target opponent\'s character aboard an open vehicle moving to your scout\'s site. Draw destiny. If destiny +2 > ability, target goes to Used Pile.','The Rebellion employees every advantage it has over Imperial machines. A corps of well-trained scouts can elude detection in proper terrain.',NULL,'9_52'),(2242,1433,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Ki-Adi-Mundi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/kiadimundi.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','5','5','6','Deploys +3 if not to Jedi Council Chamber. While at a battleground site, if opponent just initiated a battle at same or adjacent site, opponent must lose top card of their Reserve Deck (if possible). Immune to attrition < 5 while at Jedi Council Chamber.','Cerean Jedi trained by Yoda since the age of four. Only Jedi Council member who is a Jedi Knight. Freed his homeworld from a group of rogues without any bloodshed.',NULL,'12_10'),(2243,1118,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Head Back To The Surface','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/headbacktothesurface.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your piloted unique (•) starfighter is present with opponent\'s piloted starfighter during your move phase at a non-cloud sector, relocate both to related system. OR Target your starfighter in battle. During this battle, your other starships may not be targeted by weapons.','\'And see if you can get a few of those TIE fighters to follow you.\'',NULL,'9_50'),(2244,1406,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Kabe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/kabe.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','During your control phase, may target one opponent\'s weapon or device at same site. Draw destiny. If destiny < target\'s destiny number, Kabe \'steals\' device to use, or weapon to hold and transfer (for free) to a warrior at same site.','Young female Chadra-Fan. Thief. Guardian is Muftak. Abandoned on Tatooine by slavers. Loves intoxicating juri juice. Once robbed Jabba the Hutt\'s dwelling in Mos Eisley.',NULL,'1_14'),(2245,1068,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Gray Squadron 2','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/graysquadron2.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Y-Wing','3','2','1','2','May add 2 pilots or passengers. Immune to attrition < 3 when Lieutenat Telsij or Karie Neth piloting (when both immune to attrition < 5 and adds one destiny to power only).','Flown by Lieutenant Telsij as Colonel Salm\'s wingman. Part of gray squadron at the battle of Endor.',NULL,'9_70'),(2246,1333,'Light','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','•It\'s A Hit!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Light/large/itsahit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel a Force drain at a site related to a system you control.  LOST: Cancel Counter Assault, It\'s Worse, Elis Helrot, Tallon Roll, Limited Resources or Scanning Crew. OR Use 3 Force to search your Lost Pile and take one non-unique starfighter into hand.\"','Red Leader fired the first shot in the Death Star trench, causing massive internal damage. The spectacular near-miss inspired Red Squadron to double their efforts.','Tarkin\'s Orders','106_5'),(2247,1482,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Laudica','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/laudica.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','When in a battle, you may \'react\' by deploying any one non-unique blaster (for free) on Laudica from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. When present with your non-unique Corellian at a site, allows your character weapons to transfer for free there.','Corellian gun-runner. Skilled markswoman. Friends with Brindy Truchong and the Tonnika sisters. Romantically involved with Rayc Ryjerd, against her better judgment.',NULL,'6_25'),(2248,1489,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Leesub Sirln','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/leesubsirln.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','4','1','3','3','Once each turn during your control phase, may use 1 Force to guess a card type and point to a card in opponent\'s hand. Card must be shown. If guessed correctly, card is lost.','Leesub is a Qiraash (near-human). Enslaved as child. Limited precognition. Selected by Imperial High Inquisitor Tremayne as Force adept. Escaped and hiding in Mos Eisley.',NULL,'1_16'),(2249,1088,'Light','C','Theed Palace','Gungan Guard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/gunganguard.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','0','2','2','Your Gungan leaders present may not be targeted by weapons. While defending a battle on Naboo, Power +4 and, whenever you draw a Gungan for battle destiny, add 3 to that destiny. Requires +2 Force to use landspeed.','Equipped with portable Gungan shields, these front line troops provide a secondary defense against blaster fire.',NULL,'14_13'),(2250,1484,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Launching The Assault','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/launchingtheassault.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any system. Once per game, may take Home One into from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Your Force drains are +1 at battleground systems where you have a Star Cruiser piloted by a character. Effecte canceled when Rendezvous Point on table. (Immune to Alter.)','By recruiting the Mon Calamari, a race of master shipwrights, the Rebel starfleet gained capital starships rivaling the dreaded Imperial Star Destroyers.',NULL,'9_36'),(2251,1490,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Legendary Starfighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/legendarystarfighter.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just lost a starship in a battle you won, deploy on your participating starfighter. Once during each of opponent\'s move phases, opponent loses 1 Force (2 if starfighter is Falcon or Red 5). Also, that starfighter is power +2 (Immune to Control.)','The Millennium Falcon\'s well-known reputation is favorable not only for its captain and first mate, but for the Alliance as well.','Pride Of The Empire','7_68'),(2252,4073,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 0','•Leesub Sirln (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/leesubsirln.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','4','2','3','3','Once during your control phase, may use 1 Force to name a card type. Reveal top card of opponent\'s Reserve Deck. If that card matches the named card type, it is lost. Otherwise, replace it or move it to opponent\'s Used Pile. Immune to attrition < 3.','Leesub is a Qiraash (near-human). Enslaved as child. Limited precognition. Selected by Imperial High Inquisitor Tremayne as Force adept. Escaped and hiding in Mos Eisley.',NULL,'200_17'),(2253,5011,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 2','•Leia Organa (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Light/large/leiaorgana.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','6','Agenda: rebellion. May not be \'choked.\' Gains [Republic] at Galactic Senate. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise (if with an Imperial leader, may add one destiny to total power or attrition instead). \'Diplomatic\' immunity to attrition < 3.','Strong-willed princess from Alderaan. Youngest Imperial Senator ever. Used diplomatic immunity to spy for Rebels. Led relief effort on Ralltir. Natural leader.',NULL,'202_1'),(2254,5129,'Light','R','Virtual Set 5','•Leia Of Alderaan (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/leiaofalderaan.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Rebel leader. Opponent may not cancel or reduce Force drains at same battleground. If on Leia, she is a general, power +2 and, once per turn, may cancel the immunity to attrition of a character (or game text of a [Jabba\'s Palace] alien) here for remainder of turn.','The face that launched a thousand starships.',NULL,'205_5'),(2255,1498,'Light','PM','Enhanced Premiere','•Leia With Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedPremiere-Light/large/leiawithblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','4','6','Adds 1 to power of anything she pilots. Adds one battle destiny if with Han. Permanent weapon is •Leia\'s Blaster Rifle (may target a character or creature for free; draw destiny; target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if destiny +1 > defense value).','Spirited leader. \'I am not a committee!\'',NULL,'108_2'),(2256,1493,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Leia Of Alderaan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/leiaofalderaan.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Leia. While at any Rebel Base site, your Rebels, except unique (•) Rebels, are deploy -2 and power +2 at same and adjacent sites. While at any system, your starfighters, except unique (•) starfighters, are deploy -2 there.','The face that launched a thousand starships.',NULL,'5_28'),(2257,1500,'Light','U2','Premiere','Leia\'s Back','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/leiasback.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Leia is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve her from the Lost Pile. OR Use 3 Force to search through your Reserve Deck and take Leia into your hand. Shuffle deck, cut and replace.','\'It\'s not over yet!\'',NULL,'1_94'),(2258,1519,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Lieutenant Arven Wendik','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/lieutenantarvenwendik.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting Bravo 3 at same system as a battleship, adds one destiny to attrition only.','Bravo Squadron pilot who assisted in the attack at the battle of Naboo. Tactical expert of capital starship shield capabilities.',NULL,'14_15'),(2259,1492,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Leia (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/leia.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','5','While at opponent\'s Galactic Senate, Leia\'s game text may not be canceled and may lose 1 Force to place Leia and any character present out of play. During battle, may cancel game text of a leader of ability < 5 with Leia for remainder of turn.','Adopted daughter of the Viceroy and First Chairman of Alderaan. Became a political leader at a young age. The injustices of the New Order led her to join the Rebellion.',NULL,'200_18'),(2260,5171,'Light','U','Virtual Set 7','•Kin Kian (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/kinkian.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','4','Matching pilot for any snub fighter. While piloting a snub fighter, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and opponent may not substitute battle destiny draws here.','Rogue Squadron pilot. Assigned as gunner aboard Colonel Salm\'s Y-wing at Battle of Endor, as part of Gray Squadron. Former member of Aggressor Squadron.',NULL,'207_6'),(2261,1442,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Kirdo III','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/kirdoiii.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy, once per turn, may search Reserve Deck and take any Desert, Kitonak, or Sandwhirl into hand; reshuffle.',NULL,NULL,'6_84'),(2262,5652,'Light','R','Virtual Set 10','•Kit Fisto','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/kitfisto.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','5','6','7','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys -1 to an [Episode I] site (-2 if underwater). Landspeed = 2. Once per turn, may use 1 Force (or place your combat card here in Used Pile) to draw top card of Reserve Deck. Immune to attrition < 5.','Nautolan Jedi Council member.',NULL,'210_19'),(2263,1507,'Light','R1','A New Hope','•Let The Wookiee Win','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/letthewookieewin.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle at a holosite, add one battle destiny. OR Target an opponent\'s character of ability < 5 present with your Wookiee that just participated in a battle you lost; character is Disarmed (power -1 and may no longer carry weapons). Stack on that character.','\'It\'s not wise to upset a Wookiee.\' \'But sir, nobody worries about upsetting a droid.\' \'That\'s cause a droid don\'t pull people\'s arms out of their sockets when they lose.\'',NULL,'2_53'),(2264,5654,'Light','C','Virtual Set 9','•Knights Of The Old Republic','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/knightsoftheoldrepublic.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If present with a Dark Jedi or [Episode I] Jedi, your Padawan is power +2 for remainder of turn. OR Deploy one [Episode I] lightsaber from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.LOST: Once per game, retrieve a Padawan or [Episode I] lightsaber.\"','A Jedi seeks nonviolent solutions to problems, but may fight to preserve the existence of life. An apprentice must learn which battles to fight and which to avoid.',NULL,'209_20'),(2265,1451,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Koensayr Manufacturing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/koensayrmanufacturing.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Ralltiir system. Once during each of your control phases, you may retrieve one Y-wing. Also Special Modifications is not unique (•) and makes its target immune to attrition < 4. Suspended while opponent controls Ralltiir. (Immune to Alter.)','Company responsible for design of the rugged Y-wing snub fighter. Maintains sales offices on many planets. Koensayr parts often find their way into a variety of ships.',NULL,'7_67'),(2266,1455,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Krayt Dragon Howl','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/kraytdragonhowl.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Obi-Wan is defending a battle alone at a site, add 1 to power and add one battle destiny. OR If any other Rebel with ability > 2 is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny.','Using Jedi skill, Obi-Wan Kenobi imitated perfectly the mournful howl of the dangerous krayt dragon to scare Tusken Raiders away from Luke Skywalker.',NULL,'1_93'),(2267,1464,'Light','R','Dagobah','••Landing Claw','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/landingclaw.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one of your starfighters. During any control phase, may target one opponent\'s capital starship present. Starfighter attaches to target (automatically moves with target and is \'concealed\'). May detach at any time (even as target begins to move).','Special modification for starfighters. Size may vary depending on mass of starship. Allows a stable connection to a spacedock, uneven terrain or even another starship.',NULL,'4_11'),(2268,1512,'Light','U','Dagobah','Levitation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/levitation.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Silence Is Golden or Shut Him Up Or Shut Him Down.  LOST: Search your Used Pile and take any one droid, device or Stone Pile you find there into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.\"','Telekinesis is one of the powers awakened during a Jedi\'s apprenticeship. Using this ability, a student of the Force can learn to levitate objects.',NULL,'4_54'),(2269,5660,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 9','•Lak Sivrak','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/laksivrak.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','4','4','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. May move as a \'react\' for free. While at opponent\'s battleground, may not be targeted by opponent\'s Interrupts and your Force drains here may not be canceled or reduced by opponent.','Lak Sivrak is a typical Shistavanen male. Ferocious, but not aggressive. Often trained as scouts at Imperial academies, but they despise the ambitions of the New Order.',NULL,'209_8'),(2270,1469,'Light','PM','Enhanced Cloud City','•Lando In Millennium Falcon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedCloudCity-Light/large/landoinmillenniumfalcon.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified Light Freighter','2','3','5','6','May add 1 pilot and 2 passengers. Permanent pilot is •Lando, who provides ability of 3 and adds 3 to power. May not be piloted by Han unless he won a hand of sabbac this game. Immune to attrition < 5.','Heavily modified Corellian YT-1300 freighter. \'She\'s the fastest hunk of junk in the galaxy.\'',NULL,'109_2'),(2271,1472,'Light','PM','Enhanced Cloud City','•Lando With Blaster Pistol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedCloudCity-Light/large/landowithblasterpistol.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','4','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Adds one battle destiny if with your other alien on Cloud City. Permanent weapon is blaster pistol (may target a character for free; draw destiny; target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if destiny +1 > defense value).','Smuggler, gambler and leader. \'Yeah, I\'m responsible these days. It\'s the price you pay for being successful.\'',NULL,'109_3'),(2272,1443,'Light','C','Special Edition','Kirdo III Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/kirdoiiioperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','3','While at a Kirdo III site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is forfeit +1 (and power +1 if your Kitonak is on Kirdo III) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Kirdo III from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Some traders who run convoys to Kirdo III relay secret information from the Rebel population of Kirdo III. These traders have extensive experience with the Kitonak.',NULL,'7_27'),(2273,1468,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Lando Calrissian, Scoundrel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/landocalrissianscoundrel.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','5','6','5','7','Adds one battle destiny. If opponent initiates battle at same location, retrieve 1 Force and add its destiny number to Lando\'s power, or power of Falcon he is piloting. End of your turn: Use 1 Force to maintain OR Lose 2 Force to place in Used Pile OR Place out of play.','With a silvery tongue or a rapid-fire blaster, Lando prides himself on being able to get out of tight situations. Is at his best when cornered.',NULL,'13_27'),(2274,1474,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Lando\'s Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/landosblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Lando or use 3 Force to deploy on your other warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 1 Force. If Lando targeting a character, target is power -2 for remainder of turn. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.','Standard-issue Imperial blaster rifle appropriated by Lando from a stormtrooper. Used by Calrissian to pin down stormtroopers as he made his escape from Cloud City.',NULL,'7_160'),(2275,1563,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Lobot (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/lobot.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','2','2','5','Deploys free to Cloud City or a site with a scomp link. If a battle was just initiated at same site, may deploy an alien here (free if Lando) as \'react\' from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. May deploy Cyborg Construct on Lobot from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Former criminal. Fitted with a cybernetic device. Now repays his debt to society by ensuring the smooth running of Cloud City. Becomes disoriented when not with a computer.',NULL,'200_19'),(2276,1427,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Kessel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/kessel.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Force drain +1 here.',NULL,'Kessel','1_126'),(2277,1572,'Light','U2','A New Hope','•Logistical Delay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/logisticaldelay.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on opponent\'s side of table. All opponent\'s TIEs are deploy +1.','The Empire\'s tremendous military machine requires extensive coordination at every level. Slight errors in any step can quickly escalate supply delays.',NULL,'2_34'),(2278,5695,'Light','PM','Empire Strikes Back Introductory Two Player Game','Lone Rogue','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EmpireStrikesBackIntroductoryTwoPlayerGame-Light/large/lonerogue.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your pilots is at an exterior Hoth site, use 2 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one T-47 into hand. OR If your piloted T-47 is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny.','The pilots at the Rebel Base on Hoth are trained to respond quickly to the Empire\'s forces. Many Rebels feel that they could take on the whole Empire themselves.',NULL,'104_2'),(2279,1495,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Leia Organa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/leiaorgana.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','6','Adds 1 to power of each Rebel present with her at a Death Star site. \'Diplomatic\' immunity to attrition < 2.','Strong-willed princess from Alderaan. Youngest Imperial Senator ever. Used diplomatic immunity to spy for Rebels. Led relief effort on Ralltir. Natural leader.',NULL,'1_17'),(2280,1447,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','•••Kitonak','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/kitonak.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','2','Power +1 at a Tatooine site, or power +2 at any desert. Immune to Gravel Storm, Sandwhirl and desert landspeed requirements. Immune to attrition < the number of your musicians present.','Natives of Kirdo III, a desert world, Kitonak possess tough, leathery skin. Many become musicians. Very patient. Thousands have been enslaved by the Empire.',NULL,'6_23'),(2281,5083,'Light','C1','Virtual Set 4','•Lor San Tekka','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/lorsantekka.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','3','1','3','5','If you just deployed BB-8 or a Resistance leader to same or related location, may draw top card of Reserve Deck. During your control phase, one of your other Resistance characters present may make a regular move.','Information broker. Leader.',NULL,'204_7'),(2282,1584,'Light','R','Endor','•Lost In The Wilderness','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/lostinthewilderness.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel a Force drain at an exterior planet site where opponent has no vehicles or starships. Draw destiny. If destiny > number of opponent\'s characters at that site, choose one of those characters to be missing.','Survival training becomes essential when an Imperial Scout trooper is separated from his speeder bike.','Always Thinking With Your Stomach','8_57'),(2283,1589,'Light','U1','Hoth','Lucky Shot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/luckyshot.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add X to one weapon destiny (before weapon destiny is drawn) when targeting a combat vehicle. USED: X = 1.LOST: X = 3.\"','AT-ATs are nearly impervious to infantry fire, but occasionally a blaster bolt hits between the plating. It\'s one shot in a million, but such odds are a familiar to the Rebellion.','Direct Hit','3_45'),(2284,5691,'Light','R','Special Edition','Local Uprising / Liberation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/localuprising.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Local Uprising:Deploy any planet system and one <> site to that system. This system is the Subjugated planet.{While} this side up, once during each of your deploy phases, you may deploy one <> site to the Subjugated planet from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.{Flip} this card if your matching operatives control at least three battleground sites related to the Subjugated planet.Liberation:{While} this side up, opponent\'s Force drains are -1. You may retrieve 1 Force whenever you deploy a matching operative to the Subjugated planet. Your matching operatives on that planet are each forfeit +2 and, when at the same site as an Imperial or AT-AT, are each power +2. When you have at least one matching operative in a battle on the Subjugated planet, you may add one battle destiny.{Flip} this card if you do not occupy at least two battleground sites related to the Subjugated planet.',NULL,NULL,'7_137'),(2285,1585,'Light','C','Dagobah','Lost Relay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/lostrelay.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target one opponent\'s starfighter present with one of your starships at an asteroid sector, before asteroid destiny is drawn this turn. If target lost this turn due to asteroid destiny, opponent also loses Force equal to target\'s forfeit value.','Asteroid fields require starfighters to act as comm relays, forwarding orders to the squadron via subspace AE-35 Transceivers. If ships are lost, communications break down.',NULL,'4_56'),(2286,1516,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Liana Merian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/lianamerian.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','1','2','5','Agendas: peace, trade. While in a senate majority, once during opponent\'s turn, target an opponent\'s just drawn battle destiny; opponent must use or lose 2 Force or that battle destiny = 0.','Alderaanian senator. Known for her efforts to promote peace throughout the Republic by using her homeworld as an example.',NULL,'12_11'),(2287,1517,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Liberty','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/liberty.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Mon Calamari Star Cruiser','2','7','8','9','May add 5 pilots, 6 passengers, 1 vehicle, and 3 starfighters. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. May go to Used Pile instead of Lost Pile when forfeited (unless \'hit\').','Winged star cruiser. Military transport for techinical units. Afforced special care by the Alliance\'s top engineers.',NULL,'9_76'),(2288,1594,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 0','•Luke Skywalker (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/lukeskywalker.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','7','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. If piloting lead starfighter, Attack Run total is +3. During your control phase, if piloting at a battleground, may take Darklighter Spin into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle or retrieve 1 Force.','Son of Anakin Skywalker. Student of Obi-Wan Kenobi. Honed piloting skills while bullseyeing womp rats in Beggar\'s Canyon aboard T-16 skyhopper.',NULL,'200_20'),(2289,1536,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Lieutenant s\'Too Vees','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/lieutenantstoovees.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','3','2','3','When in battle at a site with Lando or Marmor, adds one destiny to total power only. When he is at a docking bay, once during each of your deploy phases, you may deploy one starship weapon from Reserve Deck on your starfighter present; reshuffle.','Dock mechanic. Installs starfighters cannons. Gambler. Followed Lando from Cloud City. Turned down assignment in rear guard to work on General Calrissian\'s starship.',NULL,'9_22'),(2290,1520,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Lieutenant Blount','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/lieutenantblount.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Tala 2, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. While he occupies any Coruscant location, Empire\'s Sinister Agents is flipped and ISB Operations may not be flipped.','Wingman of Colonel Cracken. Spy and scout. Former agent of the Imperial Security Bureau. Defected and joined Rebel Intelligence. Seasoned combat veteran.',NULL,'9_21'),(2291,1540,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Lieutenant Tarn Mison','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/lieutenanttarnmison.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','1','2','4','Deploys -1 aboard your unique (•) Rebel starfighter. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When starfighter he pilots fires a starship weapon, characters aboard target are forfeit = 0 for remainder of turn.','Former Imperial pilot. Joined the Alliance shortly after the Battle of Yavin. Flew cover for Bright Hope during the evacuation of Hoth. Expert marksman.',NULL,'7_30'),(2292,1546,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Life Debt','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/lifedebt.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Han and Chewie are in a battle together, add two battle destiny. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take Falcon into hand, and reshuffle. OR If Han is defending a battle alone, you may \'react\' by deploying Chewie there (for free) from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','\'I\'m all right, pal. I\'m all right.\'',NULL,'6_70'),(2293,1545,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Lieutenant Williams','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/lieutenantwilliams.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting Radiant VII and you have no other starships at same system, unless opponent has total ability > 6 piloting here, opponent\'s total battle destiny here is -3.','Pilot of the Radiant VII. Was personally requested by Captain Madakor to assist in the transportation of the Jedi ambassadors.',NULL,'12_12'),(2294,1535,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Lieutenant Rya Kirsch','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/lieutenantryakirsch.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While aboard Bravo 4, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise, and opponent\'s droid starfighters are deploy +2 at same system.','Became a member of Bravo Flight after embarrassing himself in front of Amidala as a guard. Has redeemed himself by becoming an expert in defense aviation tactics.',NULL,'14_17'),(2295,1562,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Lobot','https://github.com/swcc