M (Elleyein-Veeateemm)','1_18'),(2299,1505,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Leslomy Tacema','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/leslomytacema.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','2','Adds 3 to power of anything she pilots. While at Audience Chamber, adds 2 to the power bonus provided by Ellorrs Madak.','Female Duros. Expert pilot. Helps run the docking facilities in Mos Eisley. Friends with Ellorrs Madak. Approves all cargo manifests. Forgiving of minor transgressions.',NULL,'6_26'),(2300,1554,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Lightsaber Proficiency','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/lightsaberproficiency.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your character with ability > 2 and a lightsaber. That character is power +3 in battles or may add 1 to Force drain where present. Effect is lost if character loses lightsaber.','A Jedi learns not only to wield a lightsaber, but how to channel the Force to increase skill and control the lightsaber\'s damage.',NULL,'1_54'),(2301,5015,'Light','U','Virtual Set 2','•Like My Father Before Me','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Light/large/likemyfatherbeforeme.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If an Endor site on table, deploy on table. [Death Star II] Luke is deploy = 6 and may not be Disarmed. If Luke is at a battleground (even as a captive), your battle destiny draws are +1 there and, once during your turn, may / Luke\'s Lightsaber or place a card from hand on Force Pile. [Immune to Alter.]','The final act of Luke\'s ascension to Jedi Knighthood was sending off his father, draped in the garb of Vader.',NULL,'202_5'),(2302,1550,'Light','R','Dagobah','Light Maneuvers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/lightmaneuvers.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel Dark Maneuvers,