=true','Character','Rebel','2','3','3','4','Adds 1 to each of your battle destiny draws when with Derlin, Cracken or Madine at a site (or when with at least two of your other scouts at an exterior planet site). Your Rebel scouts deploy -1 to same exterior site (except Rebel Landing Site).','Scout who served under General Veers\' command. Defected and was recruited by General Madine\'s commando organization. Works closely with Colonel Cracken.',NULL,'8_19'),(2307,1439,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Kin Kian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/kinkian.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','4','Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots. While aboard your starship, adds 2 to each of its weapon destiny draws. While aboard a unique (•) Gray Squadron Y-wing at a system or sector, adds 1 to each of your Force drains there.','Rogue Squadron pilot. Assigned as gunner aboard Colonel Salm\'s Y-wing at Battle of Endor, as part of Gray Squadron. Former member of Aggressor Squadron.',NULL,'9_20'),(2308,5632,'Light','R','Virtual Set 10','•Jedi Mind Trick (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/jedimindtrick.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If opponent just initiated a battle or Force drain, they must use 2 Force, or it is canceled.  LOST: If your Jedi in battle (unless with a Dark Jedi, Hutt, or Toydarian), \'wave had at\' (add or subtract 2 from) an opponent\'s just drawn destiny.\"','\'You will bring Captain Solo and the Wookiee to me.\'',NULL,'210_18'),(2309,1473,'Light','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','•Lando With Vibro-Ax','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Light/large/landowithvibroax.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','4','6','6','Deploys -2 on Tatooine. When at a Tatooine site, adds one battle destiny. Permanent weapon is vibro-ax (may target character for free; both players draw destiny; target excluded from battle if your destiny +4 > target\'s power + opponent\'s destiny).','Gambler. Spy in Jabba\'s Court. Has walked the palace\'s passageways and overheard many details of Jabba\'s operations on Tatooine.',NULL,'112_3'),(2310,5039,'Light','R','Virtual Set 3','•Leslomy Tacema (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/leslomytacema.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Adds 3 to power of anything she pilots. Smuggler. Adds 1 to hyperspeed of any freighter she pilots. Your total ability at same docking bay or system may not be reduced. Once per game, may deploy a card with \'Ellorrs\' in title here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Female Duros. Expert pilot. Helps run the docking facilities in Mos Eisley. Friends with Ellorrs Madak. Approves all cargo manifests. Forgiving of minor transgressions.',NULL,'203_7'),(2311,1511,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Let\'s Keep A Little Optimism Here','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/letskeepalittleoptimismhere.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. While you occupy a Renegade planet location, operatives are forfeit = 0, operatives do not add to Force drains and your Force drains may not be reduced. (Renegade planet is defined on the Objective card Imperial Occupation.)','The heroes of the Rebellion know that where there is life, there is hope.','Leave Them To Me - Defensive Shield','13_30'),(2312,5618,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 8','•I\'ve Got A Bad Feeling About ...','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/ivegotabadfeelingabout.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take one security droid into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR During your control phase, if K-2SO controls opponent\'s site, opponent loses 1 Force. OR If a battle was just initiated where K-2SO i