1503,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Leia\'s Sporting Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/leiassportingblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on Leia, or 2 on your warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle for free. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny -1 > defense value. If hit by Leia, target\'s forfeit = 0.','Defender sporting blaster, made by Drearian Defense Conglomerate. Intended for personal defense or small-game hunting. Short range. Low power. Carries energy for 50 shots.',NULL,'1_156'),(2338,5058,'Light','R','Virtual Set 4','•Masanya (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/masanya.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Corellian Corvette','2','5','4','8','Deploys -2 to same system as any Star Cruiser. May add 3 pilots and 4 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. Weapon destinies targeting your starships here are -2.','Frequently escorts Mon Calamari star crusiers. Personally assigned by Ackbar to main Rebel fleet. Advanced scanners continuosly disrupt target acquistion signals.',NULL,'204_33'),(2339,1641,'Light','C','Special Edition','Maneuvering Flaps','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/maneuveringflaps.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Once during each of your control phases, may use 1 Force: your combat vehicles and shuttle vehicles are power and forfeit +2, maneuver +1 and landspeed=0 until start of your next turn. (Immune to Alter if Luke or Zev on table.)','Enhanced steering mechanisms on Rebel T-47s provide increased maneuverability in planetary atmospheres.',NULL,'7_69'),(2340,1649,'Light','PM','Enhanced Jabba\'s Palace','•Master Luke','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedJabbasPalace-Light/large/masterluke.gif?raw=true','Character',