ore of opponent\'s unique (•) characters on table. Your warriors at same site as Luke, or adjacent sites are forfeit +1.','Raised by guardians Owen and Beru Lars on a moisture farm on Tatooine, where Owen wanted him to stay. Nicknamed \'Wormie\' by childhood friends Camie and Fixer.',NULL,'101_2'),(2348,1600,'Light','U2','Premiere','Luke\'s Back','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/lukesback.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve him from the Lost Pile. OR Use 3 Force to search through your Reserve Deck and take Luke into your hand. Shuffle deck, cut and replace.','\'It looks like I\'m going nowhere.\'',NULL,'1_95'),(2349,1595,'Light','UR','Death Star II','•Luke Skywalker, Jedi Knight','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/lukeskywalkerjediknight.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','6','6','8','9','Deploys -3 to Home One or Endor. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Power +2 when armed with a lightsaber. Subtracts 3 from any attempt to cross him over (even if captured). Immune to attrition < 5 (< 6 if alone or armed with a lightsaber, < 7 if both).','Scout trained in the ways of the Force. Key figure for both the Alliance and the Empire. Desired by Vader as an ally, by Palpatine as a servant and by the Alliance as its savior.',NULL,'9_24'),(2350,1602,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Luke\'s Backpack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/lukesbackpack.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any character. May carry and use any number of devices. May also carry Yoda, Kabe or any one Jawa or Ewok (as if riding a creature vehicle). Adds 1 to training destiny when carrying the Mentor.','Made on Dantooine. Luke used the many pockets in his gundark-skin backpack to carry supplies while on patrol.',NULL,'4_12'),(2351,1605,'Light','R1','A New Hope','•Luke\'s Cape','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/lukescape.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on a Rebel or alien. If Luke\'s Cape is not at a Tatooine location, your total Force generation is +1. That character is immune to attrition < 3.','A symbol of the adventurous pilot and the awakening of his destiny. \'You\'ve taken your first step into a larger world.\'',NULL,'2_35'),(2352,1603,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Luke\'s Blaster Pistol','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/lukesblasterpistol.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on Luke, 3 on your other warrior. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force (if targeted by Luke, target loses immunity to attrition for remainder of turn.) Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a character or creature. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Merr-Sonn Model 57. Part of an arms lot purchased for the Alliance from a black market dealer on Ord Mantell. Carried by Luke as a backup for his father\'s lightsaber.',NULL,'5_90'),(2353,1606,'Light','U1','A New Hope','•Luke\'s Hunting Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/lukeshuntingrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on Luke or Owen Lars, 3 on your non-droid character. May target a character or creature using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Subtract 1 if targeting a character. Add 2 if targeting a creature. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Czerka 6-2Aug2. Extended barrel provides long-range targeting without expensive laser sight. Sturdy construction, but no match for a Tusken Raider\'s gaderffi stick.',NULL,'2_79'),(2354,1690,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Momaw Nadon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/momawnadon.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','During your control phase, may snare (steal) one Bantha, Dewback, Wampa, Rancor, Bubo, or Dragonsnake present at same site.','Male Ithorian, from a tree-loving race derogatorily nicknamed, \'Hammerheads.\' Master of animal husbandry and horticulture. Former herd ship leader. Rebel spy.',NULL,'1_20'),(2355,1593,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Luke Skywalker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/lukeskywalker.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','7','While Luke is not on Tatooine your total Force generation is +1. Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Red 5, also adds 2 to maneuver. Immune to attrition < 3.','Son of Anakin Skywalker. Student of Obi-Wan Kenobi. Honed piloting skills while bullseyeing womp rats in Beggar\'s Canyon aboard T-16 skyhopper.',NULL,'1_19'),(2356,1705,'Light','R2','A New Hope','Motti Seeker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/mottiseeker.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploys for 1 Force to an unoccupied site. Deploys and moves like an undercover spy. When present with Motti (or pilot) of ability < 3, choose one to be immediately lost (treat as an \'all cards\' situation). Seeker also lost.','Military version of a \'remote.\' Programmed to stalk specific targets or secondary targets. Heat and light sensors track with fatal accuracy. Can stow away on starships.',NULL,'2_80'),(2357,1695,'Light','R','Endor','•Mon Mothma','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/monmothma.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','2','5','8','While at your war room, subtracts 1 from each opponent\'s battle destiny at all system locations and adds 2 to forfeit of all non-unique rebels. During your deploy phase, may deploy one non-unique Rebel from Reserve Deck and reshuffle.','Native of Chandrila. Leader of the Alliance. A former member of 