','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on an exterior site. Target an opponent\'s combat vehicle at a related site. Target\'s power and forfeit = 0. When target reaches Utinni Effect, target draws one destiny. Utinni Effect canceled if destiny > 2. Otherwise, draw again next move phase, etc.','The massive war machines of the Empire require tremendous effort to maintain combat readiness.',NULL,'7_70'),(2366,4085,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Nar Shaddaa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/narshaddaa.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Force drain +1 here. Once per game, if your control, may take Han\'s Toolkit into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',NULL,NULL,'200_58'),(2367,1667,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Menace Fades','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/menacefades.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. While you control any three Coruscant, Death Star and/or Death Star II locations, or any battleground site and one battleground system, all opponents Force drain bonuses everywhere are canceled. (Immune to Alter.)','As the Executor crashed into the Death Star, hope surged throughout the ranks of the outmanned Rebel fleet.','Imperial Decree','9_38'),(2368,1740,'Light','C','Coruscant','•Naboo: Theed Palace Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/nabootheedpalacedockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.',NULL,'Naboo: Theed Palace Docking Bay','12_82'),(2369,1747,'Light','C','Coruscant','•Naboo: Theed Palace Throne Room','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/nabootheedpalacethroneroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : While you occupy, opponent\'s [Presence] droids require 