sent, may choose one opponent\'s character of ability < X to move away for free (or that character is lost), where X = number of your musicians present.','Disciple of Davrilat, a complicated religion based on the sanctity of harmonics. Originally from the desert planet Tocoya. Strong protective instincts.',NULL,'7_34'),(2374,1660,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Max Rebo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/maxrebo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','3','2','Power +2 on Hoth. If at same site as another of you musicians, you may play Bith Shuffle to cancel a Force drain at an adjacent site. While at Audience Chamber, all your other musicians are deploy -1 and forfeit +3.','Ortolan musician and gambler. Leader of The Max Rebo Band. Signed a lifetime contract to Jabba in exchange for unlimited food.',NULL,'6_28'),(2375,1752,'Light','U2','A New Hope','•Nalan Cheel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/nalancheel.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','After using Bith Shuffle, peek at top X cards of pile or deck just shuffled, where X = number of other musicians at same site. May reshuffle without peeking.','Male Bith musician. Though he enjoys playing his Bandfill in Figrin D\'an\'s band, he misses the bubblink pink swamps of his homeworld, Clak\'dor VII.',NULL,'2_13'),(2376,5766,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Obi-Wan Kenobi, Padawan Learner (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/obiwankenobipadawanlearnerai.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','6','6','8','Deploys -2 to Tatooine. If opponent just initiated a battle at a related Tatooine site, may use 2 Force to relocate Obi-Wan to that site. Immune to attrition < 4.','Qui-Gon Jinn\'s Padawan. Stayed behind to protect Queen Amidala when Qui-Gon left to explore Mos Espa, but was in constant communication should he be needed.',NULL,'11_7'),(2377,1775,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Nick Of Time','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/nickoftime.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. During a battle, you may place out of play from hand a copy of any unique (•) card participating in that battle to reduce attrition against you by that card\'s forfeit value. (Immune to Alter while you occupy a battleground.)','Luke barely escaped being crushed by the AT-AT\'s massive footpad during the Battle of Hoth.',NULL,'7_72'),(2378,1808,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Obi-Wan\'s Apparition','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/obiwansapparition.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on any site if opponent is generating at least 3 Force more than you. At that site, adjacent sites and same sites as Obi-Wan, players activate Force only if they have presence.','\'Luminous beings are we, not this crude matter.\' The inner consciousness of a Jedi can transcend even death.','Image Of The Dark Lord','4_29'),(2379,1805,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Obi-Wan Kenobi, Jedi Knight','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/obiwankenobijediknight.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','6','7','8','Deploys -2 to Naboo. Power +2 if Maul present. If Qui-Gon is participating in lightsaber combat and Obi-Wan is present, Qui-Gon may use Obi-Wan\'s combat cards. Immune to Sniper and attrition < 5.','Padawan learner promoted to Jedi Knight after his encounter with Darth Maul. Has sworn to train Anakin Skywalker, even if the Jedi Council forbids it.',NULL,'13_33'),(2380,1871,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Our Only Hope','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/ouronlyhope.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If your Rebel of ability > 2 just won a battle or duel, randomly take into hand one card stacked on Insignificant Rebellion. (Immune to Sense.)  LOST: If Luke is in battle (except with Vader), subtract 2 from each of opponent\'s battle destiny draws.\"','\'The Emperor knew, as I did, if Anakin were to have any offspring, they would be a threat to him.\'',NULL,'9_53'),(2381,1814,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Obi-Wan\'s Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/obiwanslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on [Episode I] Obi-Wan. May add 1 to Force drain if present at a Naboo battleground. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Add 1 if targeting a Dark Jedi. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.','Constructed by Obi-Wan himself, this Padawan\'s lightsaber was responsible for tearing an ancient Sith weapon in half.',NULL,'13_34'),(2382,5729,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Master Qui-Gon (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/masterquigonai.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','8','9','Deploys -2 on Coruscant. If opponent\'s Dark Jedi on table, during your move phase may use 4 Force to return Qui-Gon (and all cards on him) to owner\'s hand. Immune to attrition and You Are Beaten.','Jedi Master currently not on the Council. Although he serves the Council well, there have been times when he has defied their wishes to pursue a path he believes is right.',NULL,'12_17'),(2383,1839,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Only Jedi Carry That Weapon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/onlyjedicarrythatweapon.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. For opponent to steal a weapon from target character using a non-[Episode I] card, must first draw destiny. If destiny +1 > target\'s ability, weapon stolen. Otherwise, attempt fails and stealing card is placed out of play.','An elegant weapon for a more civilized age.','Weapon Of A Sith - Defensive Shield','13_35'),(2384,1681,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Mirax Terrik','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/miraxterrik.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','5','Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. When piloting Pulsar Skate, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Once per turn, may use 1 Force to place a card from hand on bottom of Used Pile and draw top card of Reserve Deck.','Called \'Myra\' by childhood friend Wedge Antilles. Corellian smuggler. Captain of the Pulsar Skate. Responsible for starship repairs and upgrades. Information Broker.',NULL,'10_12'),(2385,1763,'Light','U','Death Star II','Nebulon-B Frigate','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/nebulonbfrigate.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Nebulon-B Frigate','3','4','5','6','May add 4 pilots, 4 passangers, and 2 starfighters. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Turbolaser batteries and laser cannons may deploy aboard for free.','Product of Imperial Kuat Drive Yards. Several captured by Alliance. Imperial crews promptly defected. Can be outfitted for a variety of missions requiring mid-size capital starships.',NULL,'9_80'),(2386,5732,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Master Qui-Gon (V) (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/masterquigonai.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','7','7','Deploys -1 to [Episode I] locations. If you just lost Force from an opponent\'s Effect, may take an [Episode I] Interrupt (except Control) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle, or place a card from hand under Credits Will Do Fine. May not be Disarmed. Immune to You Are Beaten and attrition.','Jedi Master currently not on the Council. Although he 