pt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle with more than double your total power, search your Reserve Deck. Any one character you find there may deploy as a \'react\' (at normal use of the Force). Reshuffle.','When the ghost-like image of Obi-Wan failed to appear, another came out of the light to rescue Luke.',NULL,'5_61'),(2391,1860,'Light','R','Endor','•Orrimaarko','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/orrimaarko.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','5','4','When Orrimaarko is in a battle you just won against an Imperial, opponent must lose 2 Force. Immune to attrition < 3 (or < 4 when present at a forest, jungle or exterior Endor site).','Dresselian Scout and resistance leader. Worked tirelessly to combat the subjugation of his homeworld before Bothans brought him into contact with the Alliance.',NULL,'8_23'),(2392,1888,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Padme Naberrie','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/padmenaberrie.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','3','2','5','Twice per game may deploy Qui-Gon or Obi-Wan here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While present with your Jedi at a site, opponent may not target Amidala with weapons.','Queen Amidala posed as one of her own handmaidens for added safety as well as to keep an eye on her Jedi protectors. Was to be protected by the Jedi at all times.',NULL,'11_8'),(2393,1872,'Light','U2','A New Hope','Out Of Commission','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/outofcommission.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, use 2 Force to release a starship held by any Tractor Beam. (Not effective on Death Star Tractor Beam if Central Core in play.) OR Randomly select one card from opponent\'s Lost Pile or Blaster Rack and place out of play.','\'I hope that old man got the tractor beam out of commission or this is gonna be a real short trip.\'',NULL,'2_54'),(2394,1828,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Old Pirates','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/oldpirates.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated involving Han and any Lando, the eventual loser of the battle may not lose cards from Life Force to satisfy battle damage while that player has any cards in hand. OR Cancel Double-Crossing, No-Good Swindler.','\'How you doing, you old pirate? So good to see you.\'',NULL,'5_60'),(2395,1742,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Naboo: Theed Palace Generator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/nabootheedpalacegenerator.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your Jedi are power +2 here.',NULL,'Naboo: Theed Palace Generator','13_31'),(2396,5042,'Light','R','Virtual Set 3','•Padme Naberrie (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/padmenaberrie.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','3','4','7','Cancels Vader\'s game text here. If with a Skywalker, may add one destiny to attrition. Immune to attrition < 3.','Queen Amidala posed as one of her own handmaidens for added safety as well as to keep an eye on her Jedi protectors. Was to be protected by the Jedi at all times.',NULL,'203_10'),(2397,1836,'Light','U1','Hoth','•One More Pass','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/onemorepass.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you are about to draw power harpoon weapon destiny, add ability of one pilot aboard same vehicle.','\'Cable out. Let \'er go!\'',NULL,'3_47'),(2398,1736,'Light','C','Coruscant','•Naboo: Swamp','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/nabooswamp.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your gungans are each power +1 and deploy -1 here.',NULL,'Naboo: Swamp','12_80'),(2399,1889,'Light','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','Palace Raider','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Light/large/palaceraider.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (or 3 to power of anything he drives). When driving a transport vehicle, it moves for free and he adds one battle destiny.','Smugglers from many worlds are hunted by the Empire for providing arms and supplies to the Alliance. The Outer Rim is their refuge.',NULL,'112_5'),(2400,1892,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Panaka\'s Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/panakasblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Panaka. May target a character, creature, or vehicle for free. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +2 > defense value. When this blaster hits a character or vehicle in battle, your total power here is +3 for remainder of battle.','Naboo blaster personally modified by Captain Panaka. Boosted by extra power packs that allow it to maintain sustained fire in tense situations.',NULL,'12_96'),(2401,1833,'Light','C','Special Edition','•On Target','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/ontarget.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a piloted capital starship armed with a starship weapon, use 2 Force to target an opponent\'s starship present. Until the end of your next turn, target cannot move and its pilots may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny.','Some Imperial starfighters are equipped with sensors, informing the pilot when an enemy craft has targeted him. The pilot\'s evasive maneuvers cost him time, but save his life.','They\'ve Shut Down The Main Reactor','7_96'),(2402,1874,'Light','U2','Premiere','Out Of Nowhere','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/outofnowhere.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle at a system or sector where you have a starship with maneuver > 3, use 1 Force to add one battle destiny.','Black market sensor-stealth arrays can be used to hide starships from enemy sensor scans. Stellar interference can naturally shield a starship for surprise attacks.',NULL,'1_102'),(2403,5794,'Light','U','Virtual Set 10','•Paploo (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/paploo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','2','While on Endor, Perimeter Patrol is suspended. Once per game, if in battle with a speeder bike (or two scouts), may relocate Paploo and one opponent\'s character of ability < 4 present with him (unless either are \'hit\') to an adjacent site.','Ewok scout. Son of Warok. Brave, adventurous thief. Stole an Imperial speeder bike to create a diversion. \'Not bad for a little furball.\'',NULL,'210_22'),(2404,1893,'Light','U1','Premiere','Panic','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/panic.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle where opponent has more than double your power, reveal up to 3 cards from your Reserve Deck. Of those 3, deploy anywhere (for free) any characters, starships, vehicles, devices or weapons. Any others are lost.','Cornered by Imperial troops, Han\'s gambler reflexes led him to do what comes naturally - attack! Surprise assaults work...sometimes.','Emergency Deployment','1_103'),(2405,1898,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Path Of Least Resistance & •Revealed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/pathofleastresistance&revealed.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Place one opponent\'s Undercover spy in opponent\'s Used Pile. OR If opponent has no presence or Force icons, return spy to hand. Any Force used to deploy spy remains used and that card may not deploy this turn. OR Relocate one of your characters at an interior mobile site to a related interior mobile site.',NULL,NULL,'10_19'),(2406,1895,'Light','U','Endor','•Paploo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/paploo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','2','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each light side icon at same Endor site. May pilot only speeder bikes. Once during each of your control phases, may take one Free Ride into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Ewok scout. Son of Warok. Brave, adventurous thief. Stole an Imperial speeder bike to create a diversion. \'Not bad for a little furball.\'',NULL,'8_24'),(2407,1810,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Obi-Wan\'s Cape','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/obiwanscape.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your Rebel or alien. Character is immune to attrition < 5. Also, When a battle was just initiated where present, may use 1 Force to choose one opponent\'s character of ability = 1 present to move away (for free), or that character is lost.','A symbol of the noble Jedi and his mysterious powers.',NULL,'1_57'),(2408,1821,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Off The Edge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/offtheedge.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target one of your characters at a Cloud City site. Draw destiny. If destiny > character\'s destiny number, retrieve Force equal to the distance. If destiny < character\'s destiny number, lose difference. If destiny = character\'s destiny number, character is lost.','Despite the brutal attacks of the Dark Lord, dying on Cloud City was not Luke\'s destiny.',NULL,'5_59'),(2409,1813,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Obi-Wan\'s Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/obiwanslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Obi-Wan. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.','\'An elegant weapon for a more civilized time.\' Miniaturized power cell. Uses rare crystals to focus the lightblade. This lightsaber was personally built by Obi-Wan.',NULL,'1_157'),(2410,1725,'Light','C','Coruscant','Naboo Blaster Rifle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/nabooblasterrifle.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your warrior. May target a character, creature, vehicle using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +2 > defense value.','Standard issue blaster given to Naboo security volunteers. Noted for its effectiveness in battle and cheap manufacturing cost.','Naboo Blaster Rifle','12_94'),(2411,5238,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 8','•Phantom','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/phantom.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified VCX Shuttle','4','2','2','4','May add 2 pilots and 2 passengers. May deploy (with a pilot) or move as a \'react\' to same system as a Rebel starship. When with Ghost, adds one destiny to total power.','Phoenix Squadron.',NULL,'208_27'),(2412,1852,'Light','C','Death Star II','<>Orbital Mine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/orbitalmine.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy at the same system as a bomber. \'Explodes\' if an opponents starship deploys or moves here. Draw destiny. Add 2 when targeting a capital starship. Starship lost if total destiny > defense value. Orbital mine is also lost.','Often Stolen from the Empire. Used by the Rebellion to protect key spaceports. Can be released to cover the retreat of a fleeing strike force.',NULL,'9_91'),(2413,1900,'Light','C','Special Edition','Patrol Craft','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/patrolcraft.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','4','1','1','3','Power +1 or Coruscant of Bespin. May add 1 driver and 1 passenger. May deploy or move as a \'react.\' At cloud sectors, may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter.','Small, lightly armed, enclosed vehicle widely used throughout the galaxy. Sometimes used as a pleasure craft by wealthy eccentrics.','Patrol Craft','7_153'),(2414,1866,'Light','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','•Ounee Ta','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Light/large/ouneeta.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. You may immediately take top card of Lost Pile into hand. None Shall Pass is unique (•) and a Lost Interrupt. At each opponent\'s <> site, your characters and vehicles are each deploy -3 and your Force generation is +1. (Immune to Alter.)','Jabba\'s decadent behavior makes him susceptible to deception. Leia and Lando exploited this weakness, posing as Jabba\'s kind of scum.','No Escape','112_4'),(2415,1916,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Plo Koon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/plokoon.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','2','5','6','5','Deploys only to Jedi Council Chamber. While at Jedi Council Chamber, immune to attrition and, once per turn if a weapon or battle destiny was just drawn, may cancel and cause a re-draw.','Kel Dor Jedi Council member descended from a long line of Jedi. Known for exceptional sensory skills, Plo Koon\'s control of the Force is unmatched by most.',NULL,'12_21'),(2416,5795,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 10','•Part Of The Tribe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/partofthetribe.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your non-aliens, non-Jedi character. When deployed, choose a species of an alien here. Character gains that species. Aliens of that species may deploy (for -1 Force if non-unique) or move here as a \'react\'. While on Endor, adds one [Light Side Force] icon.','Wookiees are known to be creatures of great emotion and are very protective of family and friends. Chewbacca has come to treat Luke as a member of his own family.',NULL,'210_21'),(2417,5790,'Light','R','Virtual Set 3','•Padme Naberrie (V) (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/padmenaberrieai.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','3','4','7','Cancels Vader\'s game text here. If with a Skywalker, may add one destiny to attrition. Immune to attrition < 3.','Queen Amidala posed as one of her own handmaidens for added safety as well as to keep an eye on her Jedi protectors. Was to be protected by the Jedi at all times.',NULL,'203_36'),(2418,1911,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Planetary Defenses','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/planetarydefenses.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on any interior site. This location may not be targeted by Proton Bombs.','Key installations are protected from bombardment by a complex network of early-warning sensors, emergency shields and fast-response fighters.',NULL,'13_38'),(2419,5082,'Light','U','Virtual Set 4','•Poe Dameron','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/poedameron.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','2','3','4','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Deploy -1 to Jakku. When piloting, adds one battle destiny. Anything he pilots is immune to attrition < 5.','Leader.',NULL,'204_8'),(2420,5804,'Light','R','Virtual Set 10','•Plo Koon (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/plokoon.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','2','5','5','5','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys -2 to same location as Ahsoka (or vice versa). Once per turn, may lose top card of Force Pile to make your character (or piloted [Episode I] starfighter) here forfeit +2 and immune to attrition for remainder of turn.','Kel Dor Jedi Council member descended from a long line of Jedi. Known for exceptional sensory skills, Plo Koon\'s control of the Force is unmatched by most.',NULL,'210_23'),(2421,1924,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Pops','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/pops.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Gold 5, also adds 1 to maneuver and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Piloted Gold 5 at Battle of Yavin. Real name Davish Krail. Veteran pilot. Flew fighters for two decades. Wingman of Gold Leader.',NULL,'1_23'),(2422,1920,'Light','R','Dagobah','Polarized Negative Power Coupling','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/polarizednegativepowercoupling.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Turn every Used Pile face up. All subsequent cards placed in Used Piles are also turned face up. (Players must commit to using cards before revealing them.) Turn used cards face down whenever they are re-circulated.','Imbalance in a converter\'s inverse energy field can improperly polarize the negative axis, causing hyperdrive failure. Replacement often requires an inverted engineer.',NULL,'4_31'),(2423,1799,'Light','C','Dagobah','Nudj','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/nudj.gif?raw=true','Creature','Swamp','2','*','1','0','*Ferocity = destiny - 4. Habitat: planet sites (except Hoth and Tatooine) and Dark Waters. Cumulatively absorbs (temporarily cancels) one [Dark Side Force] icon present. Parasite: None.','Tree-nesting reptile. Favors moist caves and marshes. Extremely docile, despite fearsome appearance. Responsive to Force energy.','Sleen','4_5'),(2424,1773,'Light','C2','Hoth','Nice Of You Guys To Drop By','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/niceofyouguystodropby.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Send one of your missing characters at same site as one of your piloted or driven vehicles to your Used Pile. OR Cancel any attempt by one character to \'hide\' from a battle.','\'Echo Base, this is Rogue 2. I\'ve found them. Repeat. I\'ve found them.\'',NULL,'3_46'),(2425,5725,'Light','PM','Third Anthology','Massassi Base Operations / One In A Million','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ThirdAnthology-Light/large/massassibaseoperations.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Massassi Base Operations:Deploy Yavin 4 system and Yavin 4: Docking Bay.For remainder of game, you may not play Revolution or Force drain at Yavin 4 sites or sectors.{While} this side up, you generate no more than 1 Force from each Yavin 4 site. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one Yavin 4 site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Each Imperial is deploy +2 to Yavin 4.{Flip} this card if you control three Yavin 4 sites and opponent controls fewer than three Yavin 4 sites.{Place} out of play if Yavin 4 is \'blown away.\'One In A Million:{While} this side up, may deploy Death Star system without completing Death Star Plans. Once during each of your deploy phases, may take one Rebel Tech, Death Star system, Attack Run or Proton Torpedoes into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Your total power is +3 in battles at systems. If Death Star is \'blown away,\' adds 3 to Force lost for each opponent\'s Death Star site and, for remainder of game, your Force drains at battleground systems where you have a starfighter present with a pilot character aboard are each +2.',NULL,NULL,'111_4'),(2426,5769,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Obi-Wan Kenobi, Padawan Learner (V) (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/obiwankenobipadawanlearnerai.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','1','6','6','8','Deploys -2 (and landspeed = 2) on Tatooine.  If a card was just stacked on Credits Will Do Fine, may take a non-character card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  While at opponent\'s Watto\'s Junkyard, its Light Side game text is canceled.  Immune to attrition < 4.','Qui-Gon Jinn\'s Padawan. Stayed behind to protect Queen Amidala when Qui-Gon left to explore Mos Espa, but was in constant communication should he be needed.',NULL,'200_145'),(2427,1608,'Light','PM','Jedi Pack','•Luke\'s T-16 Skyhopper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JediPack-Light/large/lukest16skyhopper.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Shuttle','4','2','2','4','Requires 1 pilot to use. May carry 1 passenger. May move as a \'react.\' may \'bullseye\' one Womp Rat per turn. *Landspeed = 4, OR 1 character may shuttle to or from same site for free.','Enclosed vehicle used by Luke Skywalker for his early pilot training. Often raced with Biggs Darklighter through Beggar\'s Canyon.',NULL,'102_4'),(2428,5787,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Padme Naberrie (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/padmenaberrieai.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','3','2','5','Twice per game may deploy Qui-Gon or Obi-Wan here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While present with your Jedi at a site, opponent may not target Amidala with weapons.','Queen Amidala posed as one of her own handmaidens for added safety as well as to keep an eye on her Jedi protectors. Was to be protected by the Jedi at all times.',NULL,'11_9'),(2429,1931,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Power Pivot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/powerpivot.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your piloted starship armed with a starship weapon is in a battle, lose 1 Force to reduce the power of one opponent\'s starship in that battle to zero. OR Place one opponent\'s starship just \'hit\' in Lost Pile.','Using lateral thrusters, an X-wing can suddenly change direction, rotating around to fire at a pursuing ship.','Relentless Pursuit','7_98'),(2430,1943,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Princess Leia','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/princessleia.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','4','7','May only deploy on Hoth or Cloud City. Adds 1 to power of anything she pilots. May deploy (on Hoth or Cloud City) or move as a \'react\' to same site as Han or Luke. Immune to attrition < 3.','Prominent leader in the struggling Alliance. Former member of the Imperial Senate. Beginning to discover her true heritage. Likes scoundrels.',NULL,'5_7'),(2431,1910,'Light','R2','Hoth','•Planet Defender Ion Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/planetdefenderioncannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Artillery','4',NULL,'4','4','Deploy on an exterior Rebel Base site. During a battle at related system, may target a capital starship there using 2 Force. Draw destiny. If destiny +3 > armor, all starship weapons aboard target are lost, power = 0 and hyperspeed = 0.','KDY v-150 surface-to-space heavy ion cannon. The most powerful ground-based weapon in the Rebel arsenal. Reserved for strategic installations due to limited supply.',NULL,'3_78'),(2432,5179,'Light','U','Virtual Set 7','•Profundity','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/profundity.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Mon Calamari Star Cruiser','1','6','6','8','Deploys -2 to a system opponent occupies (-4 if opponent\'s system). May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 3 starfighters, 3 vehicles, and 1 corvette. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2.',NULL,NULL,'207_18'),(2433,1947,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Princess Organa','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/princessorgana.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','7','While at a Rebel Base location, subtracts 1 from opponent\'s Force drains at related locations. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one Leia Of Alderaan, Reflection or leader of ability < 3 to same location from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Adopted by Bail Organa. Former senator of Alderaan. Natural leader. Helped steal the Death Star plans. A key figure in the Rebel Alliance.',NULL,'7_35'),(2434,1944,'Light','R','Virtual Set 1','•Princess Leia (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/princessleia.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','7','Leia\'s deploy cost may not be modified by opponent. Adds one battle destiny if with Han or Vader. May move as a \'react\' to same site as an Imperial. Once per turn, may deploy Leia Of Alderaan or Reflection from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 4.','Prominent leader in the struggling Alliance. Former member of the Imperial Senate. Beginning to discover her true heritage. Likes scoundrels.',NULL,'201_5'),(2435,1963,'Light','C','Theed Palace','Proton Torpedoes','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/protontorpedoes.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your N-1 starfighter. May target a starship using 1 Force. Draw Destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value. While on Bravo Fighter and you are attempting to \'blow away\' Blockade Flagship, adds 2 to your total.','Mainstay weapon of Naboo Defense Fighters. Anakin Skywalker used them to surprising effect, as soon as he found the trigger.',NULL,'14_66'),(2436,1914,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Plea To The Court','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/pleatothecourt.gif?raw=true','Effect','Political','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If no senator here, you may place a senator here from hand to cancel an opponent\'s Force drain. If a justice agenda here, during a battle where opponent has a weapon and you do not, may cancel a just drawn weapon destiny to cause a re-draw.','Amidala did not hold much hope in the options she had. Regardless of how limited the choices, she had to choose one path to try and avert disaster befalling Naboo.',NULL,'12_45'),(2437,1948,'Light','PM','Third Anthology','•Prisoner 2187','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ThirdAnthology-Light/large/prisoner2187.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','4','0','6','Deploys only if Rescue The Princess on table. May not be transferred while imprisoned. Adds 2 to your Force drains here. For remainder of game, your objective cannot be placed out of play and, if Leia not on table, flip Sometimes I Amaze Even Myself.','Princess Leia Organa. Alderaanian senator. Targeted by Vader for capture and interrogation. The Dark Lord of the Sith wanted her alive.',NULL,'111_5'),(2438,1873,'Light','PM','Reflections II','Out Of Commission & Transmission Terminated','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/outofcommission&transmissionterminated.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Use 1 Force to randomly place one card in opponents Lost Pile out of play.  LOST: Cancel one hologram. OR Use 4 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 to destiny for each asteroid sector on table. If total destiny> 3, Imperial Holotable site is \'blown away\' (opponent loses 4 Force).\"',NULL,NULL,'10_16'),(2439,1960,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Protector','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/protector.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Leia and Chewie are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny. OR If Leia is participating in a battle, you may lose Chewie from hand to satisfy all battle damage and attrition against you. OR Cancel I\'d Just As Soon Kiss A Wookiee or Frustration.','\'Chewie, this won\'t help me. Hey! Save your strength. There\'ll be another time. The princess...you have to take care of her.\'',NULL,'5_63'),(2440,1962,'Light','C2','Premiere','Proton Torpedoes','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/protontorpedoes.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your X-wing, Y-wing or B-wing. May target a starship using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value.','Powerful ballistic projectiles. Carries proton-scattering energy warheads. Short range. Pierces energy shields, but blocked by particle shields.',NULL,'1_158'),(2441,1707,'Light','R1','Premiere','Move Along...','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/movealong.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated at a site where your Jedi is present, use 1 force to draw destiny; that number of opponent\'s characters with ability = 1 (your choice) must each move away (for free), or be lost.','Obi-Wan used Jedi \'affect mind\' power to convince stormtroopers, \'These aren\'t the droids you\'re looking for.\'',NULL,'1_96'),(2442,4114,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 1','Perimeter Scan (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/perimeterscan.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Play a Defensive Shield from under your Starting Effect. OR Target opponent\'s just-deployed [Maintenance] card. Target may not battle (or allow opponent to deploy cards from Reserve Deck) for remainder of turn. (Immune to Sense.)LOST: Cancel Trample (unless targeting an Undercover spy).\"','\'It\'s a good bet the Empire knows we\'re here.\'','Turn It Off! Turn It Off! (V)','201_14'),(2443,1812,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Obi-Wan\'s Journal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/obiwansjournal.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Luke or Obi-Wan. Your characters present armed with a unique (•) lightsaber Weapon card may not be Disarmed, once per battle may cancel a weapon destiny just drawn, and that lightsaber\'s Force drain modifiers may not be canceled. Lost if about to be stolen.','Written by Obi-Wan Kenobi. Used by Luke to construct his lightsaber. Contained instructions on building required tools as well. Keyed to self-destruct if not opened by Luke.',NULL,'10_15'),(2444,1970,'Light','C','Cloud City','•Put That Down','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/putthatdown.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your characters was just targeted by a weapon during battle, use 3 Force to cancel that targeting. OR Cancel Double Back or Res Luk Ra\'auf.','Lord Vader interceded between the trigger happy mercenary and his target.',NULL,'5_65'),(2445,1971,'Light','U1','Premiere','Quad Laser Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/quadlasercannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your Corellian Corvette or Falcon. May target a starship using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a starfighter. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Starship blaster, often slung in turret mounts to take advantage of light weight and quick targeting motions. Installed on many starships including the Millennium Falcon.',NULL,'1_159'),(2446,4084,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Put That Down (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/putthatdown.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your character or starship is about to be captured or lost during the weapons segment of a battle, it is hit instead and may not be captured or lost until the damage segment. OR If opponent just played an Interrupt during battle, activate 2 Force.','Lord Vader interceded between the trigger happy mercenary and his target.',NULL,'200_55'),(2447,1754,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Nar Shaddaa Wind Chimes & •Out Of Somewhere','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/narshaddaawindchimes&outofsomewhere.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Once per game, target one non-unique character on table. Draw destiny. If destiny < X, retrieve X Force, where X equals the number of copies of that card you have on table (Immune to Sense). OR Take one non-unique alien into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If opponent just initiated a battle with more than double your total power, search your Reserve Deck. Any one character you find there may immediately deploy as a \'react;\' reshuffle.',NULL,NULL,'10_13'),(2448,1596,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Luke Skywalker, Rebel Scout','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/lukeskywalkerrebelscout.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','6','7','8','May cancel immunity to attrition of any vehicle here. If escorted by Vader and Take Your Father\'s Place on table, during your move phase may relocate Vader (with Luke) to Death Star II: Throne Room. Immune to Always Thinking With Your Stomach and Attrition < 5.','Resourceful scout and member of the Rebel infiltration team assembled to destroy the shield generator. Surrendered to his father so that he would not endanger the mission.',NULL,'10_10'),(2449,1929,'Light','U1','Hoth','Power Harpoon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/powerharpoon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Vehicle','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy on your combat or shuttle vehicle. May target an AT-AT or AT-ST for 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target crashes if destiny + your vehicle\'s maneuver > 8. Your vehicle crashes if destiny = 0.','High-powered harpoon attached to a retractable flexi-steel tow cable and fusion-head disk designed by Beryl Chiffonage as a reserve defense against Imperial AT-ATs.',NULL,'3_79'),(2450,1983,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Qui-Gon Jinn, Jedi Master','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/quigonjinnjedimaster.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','8','9','Deploys -2 to Naboo. Qui-Gon\'s game text may not be canceled. When Qui-Gon wins a lightsaber combat, adds 2 to opponent\'s Force loss. Once per game, may lose 2 Force to deploy a lightsaber on Qui-Gon from Lost Pile. Immune to attrition.','Jedi Master ordered by the Jedi Council to return to Naboo to seek out the mysterious \'dark warrior\' that he had encountered on Tatooine.',NULL,'13_39'),(2451,1974,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Queen Amidala, Ruler Of Naboo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/queenamidalarulerofnaboo.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','3','6','Agendas: justice, peace. While in a senate majority, once during your control phase, may retrieve 1 Force for each Naboo site you control. May be placed on your Political Effect instead of a senator. Immune to attrition < 3.','Naboo leader. Frustrated by the Trade Federation\'s control of her planet, Amidala came to the Senate to plead her case in person.',NULL,'12_22'),(2452,5812,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Queen Amidala (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/queenamidalaai.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','3','4','7','Deploys -1 to Naboo. Amidala and your other Republic characters present are defense value +2, and immune to You Are Beaten, Sniper, and attrition < 3.','Leader. Amidala was only twelve when she was elected Princess of Theed. Now at age fourteen, she is Naboo\'s Queen, and the savior of her planet.',NULL,'14_26'),(2453,1769,'Light','C','Coruscant','•New Leadership Is Needed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/newleadershipisneeded.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a senate majority, activate 1 Force. OR If your opponent has a senate majority, place your character with politics at Galactic Senate in Used Pile to place an opponent\'s character present (your choice) in opponent\'s Used Pile. (Immune to Sense.)','The political process in the Republic is one whereby even the most powerful positions are fraught with peril.',NULL,'12_64'),(2454,1975,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Queen\'s Royal Starship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/queensroyalstarship.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: J-Type 327 Nubian','2','3','4','7','May add 2 pilots and 5 passengers. Weapons may not deploy on this starship. While Ric piloting, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise, and immune to Lateral Damage and attrition < 4.','Chromium-plated, sleek transport ship used by the royalty of the Naboo. Spaceframe was designed around a J-type configuration.',NULL,'12_91'),(2455,1981,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Qui-Gon Jinn','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/quigonjinn.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','8','9','Deploys -2 to Tatooine. Power +1 at same site as Maul. Once during a duel Qui-Gon is in, may cancel a duel destiny just drawn and cause a redraw. Opponent\'s aliens are power -1 at same site. Immune to attrition.','Accepted Obi-Wan Kenobi as his Padawan learner. Was given orders to protect Queen Amidala at all costs.',NULL,'11_10'),(2456,1965,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Pulsar Skate','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/pulsarskate.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Baudo-Class Star Yacht','2','2','2','5','May add 2 pilots and 6 passengers. May add ability of your (•) unique smuggler aboard to X on Kessel Run targeting that smuggler. When Booster, Mirax or Wedge piloting, Immune to attrition < 5.','Owned by legendary Terrik family of smugglers. Used to chase down the pirates who killed Wedge\'s parents. On Corellian Security\'s most wanted list. 37.5 meters long.',NULL,'10_20'),(2457,1693,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Mon Calamari','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/moncalamari.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy with a Star Cruiser, opponent\'s Star Destroyers may not deploy here. Your Star Cruisers deploy -1 here.',NULL,'Mon Calamari','9_59'),(2458,1984,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Qui-Gon Jinn\'s Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/quigonjinnslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Qui-Gon. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.','Qui-Gon was forced to defend himself when Darth Maul tracked them down on Tatooine. He was barely able to escape, in order to fight another day.',NULL,'11_49'),(2459,1976,'Light','C','Dagobah','Quick Draw','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/quickdraw.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Once during each of your draw phases, you may use 2 Force to search your Lost Pile. Take any one blaster you find there and immediately deploy it (for free).','It\'s high noon on Dagobah, his droid\'s reined in and Luke\'s got a fistful of credits.',NULL,'4_32'),(2460,1982,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Qui-Gon Jinn With Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/quigonjinnwithlightsaber.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','7','8','Adds one battle destiny if with Maul. Permanent weapon is •Qui-Gon Jinn\'s Lightsaber (may target a character or creature for free; draw two destiny; target \'hit,\' and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value).','Jedi Master assigned to reveal the mysteries of the Sith. His quest has led him to the planet Naboo',NULL,'14_27'),(2461,4092,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Overseer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/overseer.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified Z-95 Headhunter','3','3','2','5','May add Harc as a pilot. During battle, adds one destiny to total power. If a Dark Jedi or Sith was just deployed to a related site, may deploy a related location from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 4 (< 6 at Bespin).','Used to combat pirate activity in and around Cloud City. Top speed in atmosphere 1,150 kph. Hyperdrive installed by Bespin Motors.',NULL,'200_64'),(2462,1986,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Qui-Gon\'s Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/quigonslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Qui-Gon or [Episode I] Obi-Wan. Adds 1 to this character\'s lightsaber combat total. May target a character for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and it forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value (if hit target is a Dark Jedi, opponent also loses 1 Force).','This lightsaber bore silent witness to the death of two great warriors in the same day. One a Jedi, one a Sith.',NULL,'13_40'),(2463,1927,'Light','C','Special Edition','Portable Scanner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/portablescanner.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your Rebel. Adds 2 to your search party destiny draws where present. Also, once during each of your control phases, may take one device or weapon (except a lightsaber) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Cryoncorp EnhanceScan general-purpose scanner. 1,500-meter lifeform detection range. Motion sensor and metal detection sensors optimized for up to 500 meters.',NULL,'7_53'),(2464,5043,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 3','•R2-D2 & •C-3PO','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/r2d2c3po.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','2','4','7','If about to be leave table (even from Overwhelmed) from Tatooine system and Stolen Data Tapes deployed on this character, may instead be relocated to Dune Sea. Immune to A Gift, Firepower, devices, and opponent\'s Interrupts.','Stranded in the Dune Sea, R2-D2 insisted on heading into rocky canyons where he thought settlements were likely to exist. Threepio had other ideas.',NULL,'203_11'),(2465,1804,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 1','•Obi-Wan Kenobi (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/obiwankenobi.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','5','6','9','Obi-Wan\'s deploy cost may not be increased. Power +1 for each Dark Jedi here. Once per game, may exchange two cards in hand with any one card in Lost Pile. Immune to attrition < 5.','Jedi Knight. Trained by Yoda. Friend of Bail Organa. General Kenobi became a hero of the Old Republic during the Clone Wars. Mentor of Anakin and Luke Skywalker.',NULL,'201_4'),(2466,1996,'Light','U','Special Edition','•R3-A2 (Arthree-Aytoo)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/r3a2.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','1','2','3','When in battle aboard your capital starship at a system or sector, adds 1 to total attrition against opponent for each of your piloted starfighters present in that battle.','Special-purpose astromech capable of coordinating piloting coordinates and approach angles during combat.',NULL,'7_36'),(2467,1987,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Quite A Mercenary','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/quiteamercenary.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Elis Helrot just completed a transport, use 2 Force. Elis and all character transported are lost. (Immune to Sense.) OR Prevent a just deployed smuggler from moving this turn.','Smugglers and other rogues frequent spaceports along trade routes. \'Your friend is quite a mercenary. I wonder if he really cares about anything, or anybody.\'','Oo-ta Goo-ta, Solo?','2_55'),(2468,5813,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Queen Amidala, Ruler Of Naboo (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/queenamidalarulerofnabooai.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','3','6','Agendas: justice, peace. While in a senate majority, once during your control phase, may retrieve 1 Force for each Naboo site you control. May be placed on your Political Effect instead of a senator. Immune to attrition < 3.','Naboo leader. Frustrated by the Trade Federation\'s control of her planet, Amidala came to the Senate to plead her case in person.',NULL,'12_23'),(2469,1997,'Light','R2','Hoth','•R-3PO (Ar-Threepio)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/r3pOarthreepio.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','2','3','Once each turn, during your control phase, for each opponent\'s spy present opponent must lose 1 Force (2 if spy is a droid or is Undercover, 4 if both).','Designed as a response to the threat of Imperial espionage droids. Joins a droid pool and uncovers spies. Has tattoo reading \'Thank The Maker\' on left posterior plating.',NULL,'3_14'),(2470,1993,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 1','•R2-D2 (Artoo-Detoo) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/r2d2.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid',NULL,'1','3','4','While present with a Scomp Link, adds one [Light Side] icon here. While aboard a starfighter, adds 2 to power, maneuver and hyperspeed. Immune to Fire Extinguisher.','Fiesty. Loyal. Heroic. Insecure. Rebel spy. Excels at trouble. Incorrigible counterpart of a mindless philosopher. Has picked up a slight flutter. A bit eccentric.',NULL,'201_6'),(2471,1998,'Light','R','Special Edition','•R3-T2 (Arthree-Teetoo)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/r3t2.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','2','3','While aboard your capital starship, adds 1 to power and 2 to hyperspeed, and that starship is immune to attrition < 4. While at Central Core, Death Star requires +2 to move.','Expanded memory capacity. Escaped from pirates based in Mos Eisley. Programmed with the ability to both enhance and sabotage hyperdrive systems.','R3-T6 (Arthree-Teesix)','7_37'),(2472,1995,'Light','C2','Premiere','R2-X2 (Artoo-Extoo)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/r2x2.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','1','3','While aboard any starfighter, adds 1 to power, maneuver, and hyperspeed.','Typical starfighter pilot assistant. Contains ten coordinates for hyperspace jumps. Built-in tools and computer interfaces. R2-X2 was assigned to Red 10 at Yavin Base.',NULL,'1_24'),(2473,4076,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 0','•R-3PO (Ar-Threepio) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/r3poarthreepio.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','2','3','Destiny +1 when drawn for weapon or battle destiny. During your control phase, if with opponent\'s Undercover spy, opponent loses 2 Force (may not be reduced). If a spy here \'breaks cover\' or is lost, may place R-3PO in Used Pile.','Designed as a response to the threat of Imperial espionage droids. Joins a droid pool and uncovers spies. Has tattoo reading \'Thank The Maker\' on left posterior plating.',NULL,'200_24'),(2474,1990,'Light','C2','Hoth','R2 Sensor Array','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/r2sensorarray.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any R-unit droid. Your character present may move as a \'react\' from a creature attack. Also, adds 3 to search party destiny draws at same and adjacent sites.','Popular R2 astromech accessory manufactured by Industrial Automation. Can monitor radiation levels and detect nearby lifeforms.',NULL,'3_31'),(2475,1992,'Light','R2','A New Hope','•R2-D2 (Artoo-Detoo)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/r2d2.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid',NULL,'1','3','4','While aboard any starfighter, adds 2 to power, maneuver and hyperspeed (3 on Red 5). If at a Scomp link when opponent draws destiny of: 1-3, you may activate one Force; 4-6, you may draw top card from Reserve Deck.','Fiesty. Loyal. Heroic. Insecure. Rebel spy. Excels at trouble. Incorrigible counterpart of a mindless philosopher. Has picked up a slight flutter. A bit eccentric.',NULL,'2_14'),(2476,5817,'Light','PM','Enhanced Cloud City','Quiet Mining Colony / Independent Operation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedCloudCity-Light/large/quietminingcolony.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Quiet Mining Colony:Deploy Bespin system and one Cloud City battleground site.{While} this side up, once during each of your deploy phases, may use 1 Force to deploy a site (or cloud sector) to Bespin from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Opponent loses no more than 1 Force from each of your Force drains at Bespin locations.{Flip} this card if opponent controls no Bespin locations and you control Bespin: Cloud City and at least two Cloud City sites (one if Lando or Lobot on Cloud City).{Place} out of play if Bespin is \'blown away\'Independent Operation:{While} this side up, your aliens, cloud cars and [Independent Starship] starships are immune to attrition < 4. At each Bespin location you control with an alien, your Force drains may not be modified or canceled by opponent. Your [Independent Starship] starships are deploy -1. Once during each of your deploy phases, you may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.{Flip} this card if opponent controls Bespin system (or three Cloud City sites and/or Bespin cloud sectors).{Place} out of play if Bespin is \'blown away\'.',NULL,NULL,'109_4'),(2477,2011,'Light','C2','Premiere','Radar Scanner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/radarscanner.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have at least one vehicle or starship on table, use 1 Force to glance at the cards in the opponent\'s hand for 10 seconds. You may move each Jawa (except Dathcha) and Tusken Raider you find there to opponent\'s Used Pile.','Sensor on Luke\'s landspeeder. Many possible settings. Can scan for life forms, movement or concentrations of metal. Used for traffic control on settled worlds.',NULL,'1_104'),(2478,2004,'Light','C2','Hoth','R5-M2 (Arfive-Emmtoo)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/r5m2arfiveemmtoo.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','1','3','When aboard a capital starship, adds 1 to power and hyperspeed and that starship is immune to attrition < 3.','Programmed to pilot sublight tactical courses. R5 units are in high demand for combat starships. R5-M2 helped plan evacuation routes from Echo Base. Owned by Shawn Valdez.',NULL,'3_15'),(2479,2000,'Light','C2','Premiere','R4-E1 (Arfour-Eeone)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/r4e1.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','1','3','While aboard a non-creature vehicle, adds 1 to power, maneuver and landspeed. May drive transport vehicles.','One of numerous vehicle computer operation droids, manufactured by Industrial Automation. This unit, R4-E1, is a companion of BoShek. Rambunctious. Fiercely independent.','R4-M9 (Arfour-Emmnine)','1_25'),(2480,2003,'Light','C2','A New Hope','R5-D4 (Arfive-Defour)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/r5d4.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','2','3','While aboard any starship, adds 1 to power and maneuver. During your control phase, if aboard your starship damaged by an ion cannon, restores armor/maneuver and hyperspeed.','Cheap astromech droid commonly referred to as \'Red.\' Purposely blew his motivator to prevent splitting up R2-D2 and C-3PO on Tatooine. Poor navigator but skilled mechanic.','R5-A2 (Arfive-Aytoo)','2_15'),(2481,2010,'Light','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','Racing Skiff','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Light/large/racingskiff.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','4','1','2','3','May deploy with a non-unique alien driver as a \'react\'. May add 1 driver and 3 passengers. May move as a \'react\'. If lost, any characters aboard may \'jump off\' (disembark).','Repulsor lift skiffs are used by traders and merchants to safely cross the deserts of Tatooine. Young thrill seekers sometimes upgrade them with high-powered engines.','Racing Skiff','112_6'),(2482,1789,'Light','R','Theed Palace','No Giben Up, General Jar Jar!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/nogibenupgeneraljarjar.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just lost a Gungan from table, place him in your hand. OR If Jar Jar and Tarpals are in a battle together, add two battle destiny.','\'Mesa think of sumting!\'',NULL,'14_43'),(2483,2024,'Light','C','Special Edition','Rapid Fire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/rapidfire.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated, deploy (for free) a vehicle weapon or starship weapon from hand (or Reserve Deck; reshuffle) on your participating vehicle or starship.','Rebel engineers at Echo Base quickly armed T-47 snowspeeders with harpoon guns in preparation for the impending attack.','Heavy Fire Zone','7_100'),(2484,2022,'Light','R','Endor','•Rapid Deployment','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/rapiddeployment.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'At the beginning of your deploy phase, if you occupy an Endor or rebel base site, deploy up to 5 troopers there from Reserve Deck(those troopers deploy -1) and reshuffle. You may not deploy any other characters or starships this turn.','General Solo\'s strike team was made up of the Alliance\'s finest ground troops.',NULL,'8_58'),(2485,2014,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Raithal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/raithal.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, all opponent\'s troopers are forfeit and destiny -1.',NULL,'Raithal','4_90'),(2486,2031,'Light','C','Special Edition','Rebel Ambush','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/rebelambush.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated at a site, each of your troopers present is power +1 (+2 if at a Rebel Base site) and immune to attrition for remainder of turn.','Entrenched Rebel troops defend their ground with surprising fierceness.',NULL,'7_101'),(2487,2032,'Light','R','Coruscant','••Rebel Artillery','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/rebelartillery.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, if you have a weapon (except a lightsaber, or [Permanent Weapon]) at a battleground you control, opponent loses one Force. OR If you just used a weapon (except a lightsaber, or [Permanent Weapon]) to hit a character or starship, opponent loses one Force. (Immune to Sense.)','The Rebel Alliance utilizes every piece of equipment, ammunition and personnel it can muster.','Imperial Artillery','12_66'),(2488,2033,'Light','C2','Premiere','Rebel Barrier','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/rebelbarrier.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to prevent any character or starship just deployed by the opponent from battling or moving for the remainder of this turn.','While being chased through the Death Star, Luke and Leia disabled the blast doors behind them in order to slow down pursuing stormtroopers.','Imperial Barrier','1_105'),(2489,2006,'Light','C2','A New Hope','RA-7 (Aray-Seven)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/ra7.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','4','1','2','3','May transfer character weapons (for free) to or from your other characters present. May carry up to four such weapons at one time.','The RA line of servant droids has fifth-degree primary programming. Low intelligence with capabilities for mental labor only. Common among nobles and high-ranking officials.',NULL,'2_16'),(2490,2036,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Rebel Fleet','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/rebelfleet.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Once per turn, you may cancel a Force drain by placing here from hand any non-unique starfighter. Starfighters may deploy here as if from hand (if Effect canceled by opponent, any starfighters here may immediately deploy for free.)','To avoid unnecessary Imperial entanglements, the Rebel fleet is continuously on the move.','Dreaded Imperial Starfleet','7_73'),(2491,2018,'Light','F','Special Edition','Ralltiir Freighter Captain','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/ralltiirfreightercaptain.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Power +2 at a Ralltiir site. Adds 2 to power and 1 to maneuver of anything he pilots. When piloting a starship and Ralltiir on table, may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. When making a Kessel Run from Ralltiir, doubles X.','After Ralltiir\'s fall to the Empire, many former members of its defense force became smugglers and scouts. Hoping to liberate their planet.',NULL,'7_38'),(2492,2035,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Rebel Commander','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/rebelcommander.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','1','3','2','Adds 1 to forfeit of each of your other Rebels (except leaders) at same site. Bothan spies deploy free to same location.','Commander Bob Hudsol. Typical of hard-line Corellian officers known for caution in battle. Leader of resistance in Bothan space. Developed strong ties to Bothan spynet.',NULL,'2_17'),(2493,2007,'Light','U','Endor','•Rabin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/rabin.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','2','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. Where present, may substitute for a character just selected to be attacked by a creature. When attacking or being attacked, power +2 and may add one destiny.','Ewok. Tamer of beasts. Thief. Loner. Hunter. Survivor.',NULL,'8_25'),(2494,2020,'Light','C','Special Edition','Ralltiir Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/ralltiiroperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','3','While at a Ralltiir site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is forfeit +1 (and power +1 if your trooper is on Ralltiir) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Ralltiir from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','During the Battle of Ralltiir, many Alliance soldiers participated in the defense of the planet from the Empire. Many of Ralltiir\'s population feel indebted to the Rebellion.',NULL,'7_39'),(2495,2026,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Rayc Ryjerd','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/raycryjerd.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (or 4 if trained by Rycar Ryjerd). Any starfighter Rayc pilots is immune to Tallon Roll and is not lost if an asteroid sector is drawn for asteroid destiny.','An \'honest\' smuggler. Working for Jabba to pay off debts for his ship. Rycar\'s son. Even more of an idiot.',NULL,'6_34'),(2496,2038,'Light','C2','Premiere','Rebel Guard','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/rebelguard.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','0','2','1','Power +4 when defending a battle. Cannot move.','Galen Torg was selected for honor guard duty during ceremony following the Battle of Yavin. He is typical of the hard-working, unsung heros in the Rebel Alliance.','Imperial Trooper Guard','1_26'),(2497,2040,'Light','C2','Premiere','Rebel Pilot','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/rebelpilot.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','0','2','2','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots.','Lt. Wenton Chan, from Corulag, is typical of the new pilots who volunteer for dangerous duty in the Rebellion. Few have Academy training. Most learn piloting on skyhoppers.','Imperial Pilot','1_27'),(2498,5128,'Light','C','Virtual Set 5','Rebel Flight Suit (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/rebelflightsuit.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Rebel (or Resistance) pilot. Any starfighter or vehicle character pilots is power +2. If present at a site, may use 1 Force to place this device in Used Pile. Once per game, if character is piloting in battle, may cancel a non-[S] Interrupt.','Pilot fatigues feature digital technology which can be customized for particular starfighters. Increases interface efficiency with a newly assigned craft.',NULL,'205_4'),(2499,5049,'Light','R','Virtual Set 3','Rebel Leadership (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/rebelleadership.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take an admiral or general into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If your admiral is in battle at a system (or your general is in battle at a site), you may either add one battle destiny or prevent opponent from drawing more than one battle destiny.','In times of greatest need, the Rebellion relies on the brilliant leadership provided by commanders fighting for freedom.','Imperial Command','203_17'),(2500,2017,'Light','C1','A New Hope','•Ralltiir','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/ralltiir.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your starships may move here as a \'react.\'',NULL,'Ralltiir','2_65'),(2501,2037,'Light','C','Dagobah','Rebel Flight Suit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/rebelflightsuit.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your pilot character. While piloting any starfighter, combat vehicle or shuttle vehicle, that character is considered to be the \'matching pilot\' (pilot adds 2 to maneuver (limit +2) and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise).','Pilot fatigues feature digital technology which can be customized for particular starfighters. Increases interface efficiency with a newly assigned craft.',NULL,'4_14'),(2502,2048,'Light','C3','A New Hope','Rebel Squad Leader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/rebelsquadleader.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','1','2','3','Adds 1 to forfeit of your other troopers and Rebel Guards at same site. When moving with a \'squad\' of exactly three other troopers and/or Rebel Guards, all four move for 1 Force. Rebel Guards at same site may move.','Lt. Pello Scrambas is a typical veteran officer in the Rebel forces. Loyally served the Organa family for nearly two decades as a guard for the Royal House of Alderaan.','Imperial Squad Leader','2_18'),(2503,5175,'Light','R','Virtual Set 7','•Rebellions Are Built on Hope','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/rebellionsarebuiltonhope.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Table. Your Force generation is +1 at docking bays you occupy. Once per game, may take into hand one Dantooine, Mon Calamari or Yavin 4 system or Profundity from reserve deck; reshuffle. Staging Areas is canceled. (Immune to Alter.)',NULL,NULL,'207_11'),(2504,2054,'Light','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','Rebel Trooper Recruit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Light/large/rebeltrooperrecruit.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','1','1','1','Deploys free to same site as a Rebel leader. When forfeited at same site as a Rebel \'veteran\' (a leader or non-recruit trooper), also satisfies all remaining attrition against you. Once per turn, may target a non-unique Rebel warrior present; target is power +1 for remainder of turn.','New Rebel troopers gain invaluable experience while acting as support for seasoned troops. The Alliance prefers to assign rookies to soldiers on a one-to-one basis.',NULL,'106_6'),(2505,5838,'Light','R','Endor','Rebel Strike Team / Garrison Destroyed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/rebelstriketeam.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Rebel Strike Team:Deploy Endor system and Rebel Landing Site.{While} this side up, opponent loses no more than 1 Force from each of your Force drains at Endor locations. Once during each of your deploy phases, may use 2 Force to take one Bunker or Deactivate The Shield Generator into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.{Flip} this card if Bunker \'blown away\' or if, during your move phase, you control three exterior Endor sites (with two Rebel scouts at each).{Place} out of play if Endor \'blown away.\'Garrison Destroyed:{While} this side up, at each Endor site where you have a Rebel scout, your Force drains may not be modified or canceled by opponent, except by a \'react\'. Rebel scouts are immune to attrition < 4. Once during each of your draw phases, may retrieve one Rebel scout of ability < 3. Your Epic Event destiny draws are each +2.{Flip} this card (unless Bunker \'blown away\') if, during an opponent\'s move phase, opponent controls three exterior Endor sites or Endor system.{Place} out of play if Endor is \'blown away\'.',NULL,NULL,'8_78'),(2506,2055,'Light','C','Dagobah','Recoil In Fear','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/recoilinfear.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force. Each player places hand onto Reserve Deck (if possible), then places Used Pile onto Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Each player then draws cards from Reserve Deck equal to the number of cards just placed from hand onto Reserve Deck (if any).','In combat, a bold and unexpected move can change the entire situation.',NULL,'4_58'),(2507,2045,'Light','C1','Hoth','•••Rebel Scout','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/rebelscout.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','3','May move as a \'react\' (for free) to a battle where you have a Rebel of ability > 2 or a leader.','A Rebel Scout such as Vidar Blin is usually assigned to recon missions. Trained in first-response tactics, many come to the Alliance with prior special forces experience.',NULL,'3_16'),(2508,2056,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Rectenna','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/rectenna.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your starship. You may deploy cards as a \'react\' to a battle at same system or sector.','Fabritech communications and sensor array. Features active/passive scanners, powerful jamming system, ship-to-ship transmitters and short-range target acquisition program.',NULL,'2_27'),(2509,5842,'Light','C1','Virtual Set 11','•••Rebel Trooper Reinforcements','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/rebeltrooperreinforcements.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','4','5','May deploy as a \'react\' to a site. Deploys -2 to a site where opponent has more characters than you. Ambush is a Used Interrupt.','Rebels rely on hidden \'cells\' of undercover operatives. Striking from hidden bases, troops or starfighters can arrive in a battle zone at any time.',NULL,'211_56'),(2510,2043,'Light','C1','Premiere','Rebel Reinforcements','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/rebelreinforcements.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Opponent outnumbers you in total characters and starships on table, use 1 Force to draw destiny. That number of Rebel Troopers and/or Y-Wings, may be retrieved from Lost Pile.','Rebels rely on hidden \'cells\' of undercover operatives. Striking from hidden bases, troops or starfighters can arrive in a battle zone at any time.','Imperial Reinforcements','1_106'),(2511,2039,'Light','R','Death Star II','Rebel Leadership','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/rebelleadership.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Each of your admirals and generals is foreit +1 for remainder of turn. OR If your admiral is in battle at a