nk.',NULL,'208_28'),(2531,2083,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Rendezvous Point','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/rendezvouspoint.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your starships deploy -2 here and are hyperspeed +2 when moving to or from here. Neither player may Force drain here.',NULL,NULL,'7_123'),(2532,5132,'Light','R','Virtual Set 5','•Redemption (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/redemption.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Modified Nebulon-B Frigate','1','3','5','6','May add 4 pilots and 4 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. When deployed, may deploy a non-[maintenance] Rebel aboard from your Lost Pile.','Nebulon-B frigate used as a mobile medical facility. Extra cargo space and weapon batteries have been modified to allow for more armor and more recovery areas.',NULL,'205_8'),(2533,5855,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 9','•Relatively Unprotected','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/relativelyunprotected.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. While you occupy two battlegrounds (or opponent\'s site), you lose no more than 1 Force to Carbon-Freezing or That Thing\'s Operational. (Immune to Alter.) OR Deploy on a Star Destroyer or vehicle; its immunity to attrition is -4 and it may not \'react\'.','\'With the Imperial Fleet spread throughout the galaxy in a vain effort to engage us, it is relatively unprotected.\'',NULL,'209_17'),(2534,2072,'Light','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','•••Red Squadron X-wing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Light/large/redsquadronxwing.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: X-wing','2','3','5','4','Deploy -2 at Yavin 4 or to same location as Red Leader. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2 and adds 2 to power. Proton Torpedoes deploy and fire free aboard.','Most Red Squadron pilots trained under Garven Dreis. Flew top cover during the Battle of Yavin. Became famous for Red 5\'s historic attack run.',NULL,'106_7'),(2535,5856,'Light','R','Virtual Set 11','Rendezvous Point On Tatooine (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/rendezvouspointontatooine.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost Or Starting','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'LOST: Deploy a Tatooine battleground from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  STARTING: If you have deployed a Jabba\'s Palace site, deploy Seeking An Audience and up to two Effects that deploy on table and are always immune to Alter. Place Interrupt in hand.\"','\'When we find Jabba the Hutt and that bounty hunter, we\'ll contact you.\'',NULL,'211_30'),(2536,2087,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Rennek','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/rennek.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','3','Creatures at same site (except Sarlacc) do not attack and cannot be attacked. Up to three times per turn, may use 1 Force to cumulatively add 1 to his power for remainder of turn.','Nerf herder. Personally oversees the herding of Jabba\'s nerfs. Scruffy-looking appearance conceals his expertise in unusual combat techniques.',NULL,'6_35'),(2537,2078,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Reflection','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/reflection.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Leia. Once during each of your control phases, you may use 3 Force to retrieve 1 Force. Also, when an apprentice, adds 1 to her training destiny.','It was hard to imagine the enormous losses the Alliance suffered during the Battle of Hoth. Leia contemplated what she could do to help the Rebellion recover.',NULL,'4_33'),(2538,2064,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Red 7','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-