ration, this consular ship design serves the Republic for a variety of dignitary transportation and diplomatic missions.',NULL,'12_93'),(2545,2104,'Light','C','Dagobah','Retractable Arm','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/retractablearm.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any R-unit droid to give that droid thief skill. Once during each of your control phases, you may use 1 Force to target a weapon or device present. Draw destiny. If destiny > 2, target is \'stolen.\' Target may then be transferred for free. Droid may not be Disarmed.','2 kilo lifting capacity and 85 meter reach. Better than 1 micrometer placement accuracy. Feisty Rebel droids can use this tool for sneaky purposes.',NULL,'4_15'),(2546,2108,'Light','C','Coruscant','•Reveal Ourselves To The Jedi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/revealourselvestothejedi.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 5 Force to reveal opponent\'s hand. If opponent has no duplicate cards there, place this Interrupt in Used Pile. Otherwise USED: place a card revealed in opponent\'s Used Pile,LOST: all cards opponent has two or more of are lost. (Immune to Sense.)\"','Darth Maul was eager to make his presence known.','Kill Them Immediately','12_67'),(2547,2084,'Light','R','Cloud City','Rendezvous Point On Tatooine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/rendezvouspointontatooine.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, use 1 Force to move one of your [Cloud City] characters of ability > 1 to any [Jabba\'s Palace] location where you have presence. If moving to any Jabba\'s Palace site, this movement is free and you do not need presence.','\'When we find Jabba the Hutt and that bounty hunter, we\'ll contact you.\'',NULL,'5_66'),(2548,5864,'Light','C','Virtual Set 9','•Rescue In The Clouds (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/rescueintheclouds.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Peek at the top 3 cards of your Reserve Deck and take one into hand; reshuffle. OR Cancel a just drawn destiny targeting the ability or defense value of your non-Undercover character of ability < 5 at a system or mobile location.  LOST: Cancel Close Call.\"','\'I know where Luke is.\'',NULL,'209_22'),(2549,2060,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Red 3','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/red3.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: X-Wing','3','3','2','5','May add 1 pilot and 1 astromech.','Biggs Darklighter\'s fighter at Battle of Yavin. Part of Ecliptic Evaders squadron near Sullust until transferred to Yavin Base.',NULL,'1_145'),(2550,5866,'Light','R','Special Edition','Rescue The Princess / Sometimes I Amaze Even Myself','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/rescuetheprincess.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Rescue The Princess:Deploy Detention Block Corridor (with Leia of ability < 4 imprisoned there), Docking Bay 327, Yavin 4: Docking Bay and Yavin 4: War Room.{While} this side up, your spies, 8D8, Revolution, Death Star Plans and Detention Block Control Room may not deploy to Death Star. Cards that release captives are immune to Sense and Alter. May not play Nabrun Leids.{Flip} this card if you move Leia to Yavin 4: War Room.{Place} out of play if Leia is lost from table (you may not deploy Death Star Plans for remainder of game).Sometimes I Amaze Even Myself:{While} this side up, for opponent to initiate a Force drain, opponent must use +1 Force. During battle, opponent\'s unique (•) characters, vehicles and starships lost from table are placed out of play; Leia adds one battle destiny; attrition against opponent is +2; and Imperials, Dark Jedi and Imperial starships lose all immunity to attrition.{Flip} this card if Leia is captured.',NULL,NULL,'7_139'),(2551,5871,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 9','•Rey With Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/reywithlightsaber.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','1','5','5','7','Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. Permanent weapon is •Anakin\'s Lightsaber (may target a character for free; draw two destiny; target hit, its forfeit = 0, and you may retrieve 1 Force, if total destiny > defense value).','Female.',NULL,'209_10'),(2552,2105,'Light','U2','Premiere','Return Of A Jedi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/returnofajedi.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Obi-Wan is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve him from the Lost Pile. OR Use 3 Force to search through your Reserve Deck and take Obi-Wan into your hand. Shuffle deck, cut and replace.','\'Where did you dig up that old fossil?\' \'I don\'t think he exists anymore.\' \'Surely he must be dead by now.\' \'I can\'t believe he\'s gone.\' \'Oh, he\'s not dead, not yet.\' Obi\'s back!',NULL,'1_107'),(2553,1988,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•R\'kik D\'nec, Hero Of The Dune Sea','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/rkikdnecheroofthedunesea.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','3','3','Deploys only on Tatooine. Jawa weapons deploy free on R\'kik, when firing one, may add up to 3 to the total weapon destiny just drawn. When he playing Dune Sea Sabacc and wins, wins double.','A tribe of Tusken Raiders, a herd of angry banthas, a raging Krayt Dragon and R\'kik. Minutes later, the Jawa emerged from the Dune Sea, a bantha tusk over his shoulder.',NULL,'6_36'),(2554,2110,'Light','R1','Premiere','Revolution','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/revolution.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on any location. Rotate the location so that icons and game texts switch direction. (If Expand the Empire present, it also switches.) If Revolution later canceled, location rotates back again.','Spies and informants gave Rebels vital data to plan strategic turnabouts, create local insurgencies, and hamper Imperial activities.',NULL,'1_62'),(2555,5133,'Light','R','Virtual Set 5','•Ric in Queen\'s Royal Starship','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/ricinqueensroyalstarship.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: J-Type 327 Nubian','2','6','5','7','May add 1 pilot and 5 passengers. Permanent pilot is *Ric, who provides ability of 3. R2-D2 deploys -2 aboard. While We\'ll Need a New One on table, adds one battle destiny. Immune to attrition < 5.','Chromium-plated, sleek transport ship used by the royalty of the Naboo. Spaceframe was designed around a J-type configuration.',NULL,'205_9'),(2556,2112,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Ric Olie, Bravo Leader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/ricoliebravoleader.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','3','3','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting during a battle at a system where you have two piloted Bravo Squadron starfighters, adds two battle destiny.','Leader of Bravo Squadron\'s attack on the Trade Federation Droid Control Ship at the Battle of Naboo. With the assistance of Anakin Skywalker, his squadron succeeded.',NULL,'14_29'),(2557,2115,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Roche','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/roche.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : During your deploy phase, you may deploy Big One and/or Asteroid Cave to this system from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',NULL,NULL,'7_124'),(2558,2111,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Ric Olie','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/ricolie.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','3','3','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots (or adds 4 if Queen\'s Royal Starship). While piloting Queen\'s Royal Starship, once during a battle Ric is in, may use X Force to reduce attrition against you by X.','Leader of Bravo Squadron. Piloted Amidala\'s Royal Starship from Naboo so that she could plead her case to the Senate. Was able to break the blockade with a little help.',NULL,'12_24'),(2559,2109,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Revealed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/revealed.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Place one opponent\'s Undercover spy in opponent\'s Used Pile. OR If opponent just deployed a spy to a site where opponent has no presence or Force icons, return spy to hand. Any Force used to deploy spy remains used and that card may not deploy this turn.','\'Where am I?\' \'Jabba\'s palace.\' \'Who are you?\'',NULL,'6_73'),(2560,2119,'Light','R1','Hoth','•Rogue 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/rogue1.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: T-47 Snowspeeder','2','3','2','6','May add 2 pilots or passengers. Immune to attrition < 3 if Luke piloting. May move as a \'react\' only to Hoth sites.','Designated Rogue Leader. Led snowspeeder attack during the Battle of Hoth. Enclosed. Piloted by Commander Skywalker, with Dack Ralter as tailgunner.',NULL,'3_66'),(2561,5870,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 4','•Rey (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialAI-Light/large/rey.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','1','4',NULL,'7','Adds 3 to power of anything she pilots. When deployed, may take any card from Used Pile into hand; reshuffle. Your total battle destiny here is +1. Once per turn, may draw bottom card of your Force Pile. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 6 if on Jakku).','Female scavenger.',NULL,'204_9