eder piloted by Derek \'Hobbie\' Klivian. Wingman of Rogue Leader at the Battle of Hoth. Laser cannons modified for improved recharge rate.',NULL,'7_154'),(2566,2126,'Light','C2','Hoth','Rogue Gunner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/roguegunner.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','1','1','1','Adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of anything he is aboard as a passenger.','Tailgunners such as Kesin Ommis from Coruscant are posted to aft gunnery stations on vehicles and starships. Highly trained in weapons operations.',NULL,'3_17'),(2567,2082,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Remote','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/remote.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy at any site. Moves like a character at normal use of the Force. Once during each of your control phases, may: Select one character present to be power or forfeit +1 for remainder of turn. OR Use 2 Force to cancel any seeker present.','Tshhhh. Tshhhh. Zap! \'Look...good against remotes is one thing. Good against the living, that\'s something else.\'',NULL,'2_28'),(2568,2130,'Light','R','Endor','•Romba','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/romba.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','1','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. When on Endor, adds 1 to your Force generation at each Endor site with an Ewok present.','Proud Ewok scout. Defended his tribe against the Empire\'s war machines and stormtroopers.',NULL,'8_26'),(2569,5877,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 9','•Rose Tico','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/rosetico.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','5','1',NULL,'2','If Finn is about to be lost from same site, may place him in your Used Pile instead. During your control phase, if present at a battleground site, and another Resistance character on table (or Paige out of play), may retrieve 1 Force.','Female.',NULL,'209_11'),(2570,5081,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 4','•Rey','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/rey.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','1','4',NULL,'7','Adds 3 to power of anything she pilots. When deployed, may take any card from Used Pile into hand; reshuffle. Your total battle destiny here is +1. Once per turn, may draw bottom card of your Force Pile. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 6 if on Jakku).','Female scavenger.',NULL,'204_9'),(2571,2092,'Light','C','Cloud City','•Rescue In The Clouds','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/rescueintheclouds.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If you have a character on Weather Vane, place that character on your Used Pile.  LOST: Deploy one or more vehicles, starfighters and pilots (at normal use of the Force) as a \'react\' to a cloud sector.\"','\'I know where Luke is.\'',NULL,'5_67'),(2572,2128,'Light','U2','Hoth','•Romas \'Lock\' Navander','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/romaslocknavander.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','1','2','3','Adds 1 to power and maneuver of anything he pilots. Opponent may not \'react\' to or from same location.','Corellian pilot. Defected from the Empire shortly after graduation from the Academy. Tech communications officer at Echo Base. Relays orders to nearby Rebel starships.',NULL,'3_18'),(2573,2135,'Light','C','Theed Palace','Royal Naboo Security Officer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/royalnaboosecurityofficer.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','3','Power -1 while not on Naboo. While you have at least three other non-unique Royal Naboo Security Officers at related Naboo sites, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.','The Royal Naboo Security Forces are used to protect Naboo\'s planetary rulers at all times. Commanded by Panaka, these volunteers have dedicated their lives to their homeland.',NULL,'14_30'),(2574,2125,'Light','C1','A New Hope','•Rogue Bantha','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/roguebantha.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Creature','4','2','2','3','May add 2 \'riders\' (passengers). Bantha ability = 1/2. May move as a \'react.\' Whenever a battle was just initiated at same site, one Tusken Raider present (your choice) is \'trampled\' (immediately lost).','Fled into the wilderness after mistreatment by a young Tusken Raider. Raised by moisture farmer. Friendly toward strangers, but attacks Tusken Raiders on sight.',NULL,'2_76'),(2575,2141,'Light','U1','Premiere','Rycar Ryjerd','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/rycarryjerd.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your non-smuggler to give that character smuggler skill. OR Deploy on your smuggler. That character is power +1. (Immune to Alter.)','A Bimm trader and smuggler of starship weapons. Trusts no one. Does business with anyone. Teaches smuggler apprentices. Has mastered Jawa language.',NULL,'1_63'),(2576,2137,'Light','R1','Hoth','•Rug Hug','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/rughug.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke and Chewie are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny. OR If you have a Rebel and an alien in a battle together, you may add 4 to power only.','Wookiees are known to be creatures of great emotion and are very protective of family and friends. Chewbacca has come to treat Luke as a member of his own family.',NULL,'3_49'),(2577,2143,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Rycar\'s Run','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/rycarsrun.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,