 about to draw a card for weapon or battle destiny, you may instead use card here, then place it in Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','The sando aqua monster is quite a mystery to Naboo oceanographers. A reclusive predator by nature, this undersea giant appears to have no natural enemies.','Sando Aqua Monster','13_41'),(2608,2185,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Scrambled Transmission','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/scrambledtransmission.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Shocking Information is immune to Sense. Any interrupt that examines cards in your Used or Force Pile is lost. Once during each of your control phases, may take one Shocking Information into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','The Rebel Alliance employs sophisticated jamming technology to block Imperial communications.',NULL,'7_74'),(2609,2189,'Light','F','Special Edition','Scurrier','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/scurrier.gif?raw=true','Creature','Scavenger','5','2','2','0','Habitat: planet sites. Landspeed=2. Ferocity +2 when present at Mos Eisley or any _ spaceport site.','Considered to be a nuisance. Feeds on garbage. Its only defense is its speed. Nasty bite attack when surprised or cornered. Grow as big as 1.2 meters long.',NULL,'7_52'),(2610,5899,'Light','C','Virtual Set 11','•See You Around, Kid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/seeyouaroundkid.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel a just-deployed First Order character\'s game text until end of turn. OR Destiny draws during battles at sites may not be canceled this turn. OR During any draw phase, place a card from hand under Used Pile to take any one card into hand from Force Pile; reshuffle.','Blank.',NULL,'211_2'),(2611,2206,'Light','PM','Enhanced Jabba\'s Palace','•See-Thre