f other Cloud City troopers.',NULL,'7_41'),(2628,2250,'Light','C2','Premiere','•••Shistavanen Wolfman','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/shistavanenwolfman.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','2','May move to an adjacent site as a \'react\'.','Lak Sivrak is a typical Shistavanen male. Ferocious, but not aggressive. Often trained as scouts at Imperial academies, but they despise the ambitions of the New Order.',NULL,'1_30'),(2629,2253,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Shocking Information & •Grimtaash','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/shockinginformation&grimtaash.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Target a location. Scomp links there cannot be used for remainder of turn. OR If opponent is about to scan or otherwise look through your hand (unless using Monnok), opponent continues but must lose 4 Force plus card allowing scan. OR If opponent has 13 or more cards in hand, place all but 8 (random selection) in Used Pile.  LOST: Use 4 Force to reveal opponent\'s hand. All cards opponent has two or more of in hand are lost.\"',NULL,NULL,'10_22'),(2630,2230,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Sergeant Hollis','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/sergeanthollis.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','3','When in battle with another Echo Base trooper, adds one battle destiny. Once during each of your control phases, may take one Rebel Ambush into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Power -1 when not on Hoth.','Trooper stationed at Echo Base during the Battle of Hoth. Distinguished himself with several acts of valor, earning the Kenobi Medallion.',NULL,'7_42'),(2631,2012,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Radiant VII','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/radiantvii.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Corellian Republic Cruiser','2','5','4','7','May add 3 pilots and 3 passengers. Has ship-docking capability. While Madakor or Williams piloting, immune to Lateral Damage and attrition < 5.','Optimized for diplomatic missions with sensor-proof pods that have ejection capabilities. Easily identified by its red coloration.',NULL,'12_92'),(2632,2257,'Light','U','Dagobah','•Shoo! Shoo!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/shooshoo.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a droid on table: Cancel an attack just initiated by a creature. OR Immediately move one opponent\'s creature (except an attached creature) to an adjacent location (habitat permitting).','\'Oh! Go away! Go away! Beastly thing!\'',NULL,'4_59'),(2633,2205,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 1','•Seeking An Audience (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/seekinganaudience.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a Jabba\'s Palace site on table, deploy on table. His Name Is Anakin is canceled. Once per turn, if Han frozen, may use 2 Force to deploy a non-[Reflections 3]: C-3PO, Chewie, Lando, Leia or R2-D2 from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per game, may place this Effect out of play to retrieve an alien or [Independent] starship into hand. (Immune to Alter.)','\'With your wisdom, I\'m sure that we can work out an arrangement which will be mutually beneficial and enable us to avoid any unpleasant confrontation.\'','Jabba\'s Haven','201_9'),(2634,2252,'Light','C','Cloud City','•Shocking Information','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/shockinginformation.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target a location. Scomp links there cannot be used for remainder of turn. OR If opponent is about to scan or otherwise look through your hand (unless using Monnok), opponent continues but must lose 4 Force plus the card allowing the scan.','\'R2-D2, you know better than to trust a strange computer.\'','Shocking Revelation','5_68'),(2635,2201,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Security Control','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/securitycontrol.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your unique (•) Republic characters of ability < 4 are forfeit +2. Unless Insurrection on table, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Actions borne of the love for one\'s planet can heavily outweigh those generated from simple battle orders.','Begin Landing Your Troops','12_47'),(2636,2276,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Skull','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/skull.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle or attack, place out of play one non-droid character, creature or creature vehicle from your Lost Pile. Add its destiny number to your total power. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take Fallen Portal or Blast the Door, Kid! into hand and reshuffle.','Bidlo Kwerve was involved in both the procurement and (posthumously) the loss of the rancor.',NULL,'6_74'),(2637,2251,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Shmi Skywalker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/shmiskywalker.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','5','Deploys for free to Slave Quarters. Once per game may take [Tatooine] Threepio into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While in a battle at a site, subtracts one from each of opponent\'s battle destiny draws.','Mother of Anakin Skywalker. As Anakin grew, Shmi realized her son was special. Did her best to hide his abilities from Watto.',NULL,'11_12'),(2638,2102,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Restricted Deployment','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/restricteddeployment.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on opponent\'s side of table. All opponent\'s warriors are deploy +1.','The Empire is too bureaucratic to deploy troops efficiently except under favorable circumstances. Rebel actions across the galaxy force Imperials to split their forces.','Wrong Turn','1_61'),(2639,2249,'Light','U1','Hoth','•Shawn Valdez','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/shawnvaldez.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','1','3','4','Whenever you just initiated a battle at same site as Shawn, your troopers at adjacent sites who have not already battled this turn may immediately move to same site (as a regular move).','Experienced evacuation officer. Charismatic leader of Echo Base troopers. Trained to expedite the evacuation of Rebel installations with maximum efficiency. Poetic musician.',NULL,'3_19'),(2640,2280,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Slayn & Korpil Facilities','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/slaynkorpilfacilities.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Roche system. Once during each of your deploy phases, you may deploy a starship weapon from Reserve Deck on your B-wing; reshuffle. Also, retrieve 2 Force whenever your starfighter or vehicle \'hits\' an opponent\'s starship or vehicle. (Immune to Alter.)','Based in the Roche Asteroid Field. Worked with Admiral Ackbar to develop the B-wing fighter. Verpine owned, and that means quality.',NULL,'7_76'),(2641,2272,'Light','R','Dagobah','Size Matters Not','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/sizemattersnot.gif?raw=true','Jedi Test #4',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Dagobah: Swamp or Dagobah: Bog Clearing. Target a mentor on Dagobah and an apprentice who has completed Jedi Test #3. Attempt when apprentice is present at the beginning of your control phase. Draw training destiny. If destiny + apprentice\'s ability > 15, test completed: Place on apprentice. Immune to attrition < 3. Once during each of your control phases, you may use 2 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take any one card you find there into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.',NULL,NULL,'4_79'),(2642,2274,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Skiff','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/skiff.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','2','3','3','3','Deploy -1 to a Tatooine site. May add 1 driver and 5 passengers. May move as a \'react.\' If lost, any characters aboard may \'jump off\' (disembark).','Top speed of 250 kph. Repulsorlift engine. Equipped with two electromagnetic load lifters. Frequently used by shipping companies to transfer cargo between freighters.','Skiff','6_88'),(2643,2294,'Light','U2','Hoth','Snowspeeder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/snowspeeder.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: T-47 Snowspeeder','1','3','2','4','May add 1 pilot or passenger. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1. May move as a \'react\' to Hoth sites.','Modified Incom T-47 airspeeder. Enclosed. Adapted to the cold by installation of regulator coil heaters. Rebels typically nickname converted speeders after the intended environment.',NULL,'3_69'),(2644,2269,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Sio Bibble','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/siobibble.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','5','Agenda: order. While at same site as Amidala, your Force generation is +2 here. While on Naboo, subtracts one from opponent\'s Force drains at adjacent sites, and your other Republic characters present are power +1.','Governor of Naboo. After initially opposing Amidala in her campaign to become Naboo\'s elected ruler, Sio Bibble is now one of her most ardent supporters.',NULL,'13_42'),(2645,2285,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Smoke Screen','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/smokescreen.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle at a site, if you are about to draw a card for battle destiny, you may instead use the ability number of one of your characters involved in the battle.','Warning: The Alderaanian Medical Association has determined that inhaling carbon-freezing smoke can be hazardous to your health.',NULL,'5_69'),(2646,2297,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Solo Han','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/solohan.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Han is defending a battle alone at a site, add two battle destiny. OR If any alien is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny.','As a smuggler, Solo must always be alert for trouble, even when appearing relaxed. Bounty hunters are eager to claim the price on the Corellian pirate\'s head.',NULL,'1_111'),(2647,2263,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Sic-Six','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/sicsix.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Subtracts 2 from forfeit of each opponent\'s pilots at same site. Prevents characters from moving to or from same or adjacent sites using Elis Helrot or Nabrun Leids.','Gifted engineers. Sic-six believe their technology is superior. Have a poison stinger. Spin vast and intricate webs which create a hazard for landing starships. Avoided by pilots.','Lobel','6_40'),(2648,5079,'Light','R','Virtual Set 4','•Solo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/solo.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien/Resistance','1','4','4','7','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys -1 to Falcon. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Adds one battle destiny if with Chewie or Rey. Once per game, may play an Interrupt from Lost Pile as if from hand (then place that card out of play).','Smuggler.',NULL,'204_11'),(2649,2282,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Slight Weapons Malfunction','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/slightweaponsmalfunction.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your weapon (except a lightsaber) was just fired during a battle, add one battle destiny.','Han was gifted in the art of understatement.',NULL,'7_102'),(2650,4406,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Simple Tricks And Nonsense','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/simpletricksandnonsense.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table.  While you occupy a battleground and opponent occupies less than two battlegrounds, cancel opponent\'s Force drains at non-battleground locations and opponent\'s Force retrieval.','\'Et tu taka bu Jabba now.\'',NULL,'200_28'),(2651,5740,'Light','R','Special Edition','Mind What You Have Learned / Save You It Can','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/mindwhatyouhavelearned.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Mind What You Have Learned:Deploy Dagobah system (may not be converted).{While} this side up, during your deploy phase, may deploy Luke, Yoda (deploy -2), Yoda\'s Hope, At Peace and/or Luke\'s Backpack to Dagobah from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Whenever you draw training destiny, draw two and choose one. Place Luke\'s completed Jedi Tests on table. Your cards at Dagobah may not Force drain or contribute to Force retrieval. Add 4 to each player\'s destiny draw for Sense and Alter.{Flip} this card when Luke completes Jedi Test #5.Save You It Can:{Immediately} retrieve 10 Force and place destiny card from Jedi Test #5 on that Jedi Test.{While} this side up, during your move phase, may use 3 Force to take Luke into hand from a location you control (cards on Luke go to owner\'s Used Pile). Luke\'s Jedi Test are suspended (not lost) whenever Luke not on table. Luke may ignore location deployment restrictions. Opponent may not play Sense or Alter.{Place} out of play if you Force drain at Dagobah or if Luke is placed out of play. Cancel Luke\'s Jedi Tests.',NULL,NULL,'7_138'),(2652,2286,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Smuggler\'s Blues','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/smugglersblues.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a smuggler. May use 2 Force to cancel Limited Resources. Also, if \'trained\' by Rycar Ryjerd and piloting as starship when that starship completes Kessel Run, Rycar\'s Run or The First Transport Is Away, any retrieved Force may be taken into hand.','It\'s the lure of easy credits. It\'s got a very strong appeal. Perhaps you\'d understand better wearing my flight suit. It\'s the ultimate special modification, it\'s the smuggler\'s blues.',NULL,'4_38'),(2653,1884,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Owen Lars & •Beru Lars','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/owenlars&berulars.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','4','3','5','Deploy free to Lars\' Moisture Farm. Draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. If opponent has a Stormtrooper at a Tatooine site, you may not play Harvest. If lost during opponent\'s turn, Luke is power +6 until end of your next turn.','Watchful guardians of Luke Skywalker. When the Lars\' moisture farm was attacked by stormtroopers, Luke\'s life changed forever.',NULL,'10_18'),(2654,2292,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Snivvian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/snivvian.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','2','May deploy as a \'react\'. Power +2 under \'nighttime conditions\'. When at a site, if opponent cancels Nightfall on related system, causes Effect to go to Used Pile and may retrieve 2 Force.','Cadomai is the homeworld of the generally artistic Snivvians. Its cold, dark climate makes them excellent scouts.',NULL,'6_41'),(2655,1803,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Obi-Wan Kenobi','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/obiwankenobi.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','5','5','9','When a battle was just initiated where present, may use 1 Force to choose one opponent\'s character of ability = 1 present to move away (for free), or that character is lost. Immune to attrition < 5.','Jedi Knight. Trained by Yoda. Friend of Bail Organa. General Kenobi became a hero of the Old Republic during the Clone Wars. Mentor of Anakin and Luke Skywalker.',NULL,'1_21'),(2656,5227,'Light','U','Virtual Set 8','•Prophecy Of The Force','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/prophecyoftheforce.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a site. While at a battleground, adds one [Dark Side Force] icon and one [Light Side Force] icon here. Once per turn, if a player just Force drained at a site with total ability > 5, relocate this Effect to that site. Once per game, may retrieve a card with \'Anakin\' in title into hand. (Immune to Alter.)','The turning of Vader and the loss of Palpatine was the beginning of a new era for the entire galaxy.',NULL,'208_14'),(2657,1642,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','Maneuvering Flaps (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/maneuveringflaps.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. During your deploy phase, may reveal an unpiloted combat vehicle from hand to take its matching pilot character (or vice versa) into hand from Reserve Deck and deploy both simultaneously; reshuffle. May not be suspended (Immune to Alter.)','Enhanced steering mechanisms on Rebel T-47s provide increased maneuverability in planetary atmospheres.',NULL,'200_43'),(2658,1664,'Light','C1','Hoth','Medium Repeating Blaster Cannon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/mediumrepeatingblastercannon.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Artillery','1',NULL,'3','1','Deploy on a site. May be moved by two warriors for 1 additional Force. Your warrior present may target up to two characters or two creatures at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw two destiny. Target(s) hit if total destiny > total defense value.','Merr-Sonn Mark II repeating blaster. Accepts power cells from a very wide variety of sources, a benefit for Rebels accustomed to scavenging for supplies.',NULL,'3_77'),(2659,2298,'Light','C2','A New Hope','Solomahal','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/solomahal.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your warrior to give that warrior scout skill. That warrior may move as a \'react.\' OR Deploy on your scout. When that scout \'reacts,\' it is power +2 for remainder of turn. (Immune to Alter.)','Veteran officer of the Old Republic who retired from active duty after the Clone Wars. Makes a living in the Outer Rim Territories passing on his scouting expertise.',NULL,'2_38'),(2660,1582,'Light','C','Tatooine','•Losing Track','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/losingtrack.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: During battle, place top card of opponent\'s Lost Pile on top of their Reserve Deck.  LOST: Use 1 Force to \'repair\' your Podracer. OR Target a Podracer. Draw destiny. If destiny > Podracer\'s destiny number, target is \'damaged.\'\"','\'Wha-? Chuba da noya!\'',NULL,'11_37'),(2661,2307,'Light','C2','Premiere','SoroSuub V-35 Landspeeder','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/sorosuubv35landspeeder.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Transport','4','0','2','3','May add 1 driver and 3 passengers. Moves free if Owen Lars, Beru Lars or Luke aboard. May move as a \'react\'.','Typical old model Courier landspeeder such as the one used by Lars family for trips to Anchorhead. Has cargo compartment. Enclosed seating.',NULL,'1_151'),(2662,2277,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Skywalkers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/skywalkers.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke and Leia are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny OR Cancel Imperial Barrier or Wrong Turn or Retract The Bridge.','Luke and Leia escaped to an unused portion of the Death Star, evading security checkpoints. At a retracted bridge, they swung across on a grappling line through enemy fire.',NULL,'1_110'),(2663,2232,'Light','U','Endor','•Sergeant Junkin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/sergeantjunkin.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','3','3','4','When at Bunker, adds 1 to Deactivate The Shield Generator total for each Explosive Charge here. When Junkin uses a Concussion Grenade, all your characters are immune to that grenade and you may add or subtract 1 from weapon destiny draw.','Demolitions expert and scout. Supervises explosives preparations for covert operations. Consulted with General Madine to plan placement of explosives within control bunker.',NULL,'8_29'),(2664,2247,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Shasa Tiel','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/shasatiel.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','3','Power +1 at any swamp. During opponent\'s control phase, may use 3 Force to examine the cards in opponent\'s Force Pile, reorder however you wish and replace. While at Audience Chamber, all your other Ishi Tibs are power and forfeit +2.','Ishi Tib accountant. One of Mosep\'s assistants. Formerly worked for SoroSuub Inc. Blackmailed into working for Jabba. Hates her job. Searching for a means of escape.',NULL,'6_39'),(2665,2300,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','Someone Who Loves You','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/someonewholovesyou.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Han was just lost and Leia is on table (or vice versa), place the justlost character on your Used Pile instead. OR If Leia is present at a site where Han is captive, release Han. OR Cancel a Force drain at a prison.','Han\'s appreciation toward his mysterious liberator was rather quickly overcome.',NULL,'6_75'),(2666,2311,'Light','C','Endor','•Sound The Attack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/soundtheattack.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Use 1 Force to take into hand one vehicle, weapon or interrupt with \'Ewok\' in the title from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: If your Ewok is defending a battle, add one battle destiny.\"','Ewok warriors on patrol use primitive animal horns to coordinate their defenses.',NULL,'8_59'),(2667,2317,'Light','F','Special Edition','<>Spaceport Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/spaceportdockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force. Your starfighters deploy -1 (or 2 is freighter) here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4.',NULL,'Spaceport Docking Bay','7_126'),(2668,2310,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Soth Petikkin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/sothpetikkin.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','3','4','Once during each of your control phases, when at a Jabba\'s Palace site you control, may use 1 Force to take one alien that is a smuggler, scout, thief or spy into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Persuasive recruiter from Tefau. Possesses limited precognition. Used his contacts in Jabba\'s desert stronghold to find support for the Rebellion.',NULL,'7_43'),(2669,2322,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Speak With The Jedi Council','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/speakwiththejedicouncil.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If the Jedi Council Chamber is not on table, you may deploy it from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: Deploy one Jedi Council member to the Jedi Council Chamber from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.\"','Qui-Gon knew that urgency was required. What had transpired on Tatooine demanded the attention of the Council.',NULL,'12_69'),(2670,2308,'Light','U1','A New Hope','•Sorry About The Mess','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/sorryaboutthemess.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, fire one of your weapons. If Han firing, may add 1 to each weapon destiny draw. (A seeker may be targeted by a character weapon, as if a character with defense value of 4.) Any \'hit\' targets are immediately lost.','\'I\'ve been looking forward to this for a long time.\' \'Yes, I\'ll bet you have.\' Han abruptly ended his conversation with Greedo and flipped Wuher a credit to pay for the cleanup.','Sniper','2_57'),(2671,5815,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Qui-Gon Jinn\'s Lightsaber (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/quigonjinnslightsaberai.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Qui-Gon. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.','Qui-Gon was forced to defend himself when Darth Maul tracked them down on Tatooine. He was barely able to escape, in order to fight another day.',NULL,'11_50'),(2672,1827,'Light','C2','Premiere','Old Ben','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/oldben.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force if any of your characters (except Obi-Wan) was just forfeited from a Tatooine site. Mysterious \'crazy wizard\' steps in and revives (returns from Lost Pile) that character back to same site.','\'That old man\'s just a crazy wizard.\' Obi-Wan lived in Tatooine\'s deserts for years...ready for the right moment to act.',NULL,'1_100'),(2673,1834,'Light','R2','Premiere','On The Edge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/ontheedge.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force and target one Rebel (on table) of ability > 2. Choose a number from 1 to 6. You may retrieve that amount from your Lost Pile if you now draw destiny > chosen number. If you fail, Rebel is lost.','Luke and Leia nearly fell over the retracted bridge across the Death Star\'s central core while trying to elude stormtroopers. They were soon trapped on the precipice.',NULL,'1_101'),(2674,2325,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Special Modifications','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/specialmodifications.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on any starship to add 2 to its armor or maneuver. If on Falcon with Han, Lando or Chewie piloting, also adds 2 to power and forfeit.','Han\'s \'special modifications\' for Millennium Falcon included security mechanisms, deflector shields, hull plating, faster hyperdrive and enhanced weapons.',NULL,'1_65'),(2675,2332,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Spiral','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/spiral.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Corellian Corvette','2','5','5','7','May deploy -3 as a \'react.\' May add 3 pilots, 4 passengers and 1 vehicle. Has ship-docking ability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2.','Has conducted several successful ambushes on Imperial convoys. Veteran crew. Has a reputation for arriving when least expected.',NULL,'7_149'),(2676,2328,'Light','C','Endor','Speeder Bike','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/speederbike.gif?raw=true','Vehicle','Combat: Speeder Bike','4','1','1','3','May add 1 pilot and 1 passenger. May move as a \'react\'. When piloted, vehicle and scouts aboard are immune to attrition < 4. Pilot\'s power = 0. If lost, characters aboard may \'jump off\' (disembark).','Aratech speeder bikes often found their way into Rebel hands. Stolen from troops operating far from Imperial maintenance facilities.','Speeder Bike','8_83'),(2677,2309,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Sorry About The Mess & •Blaster Proficiency','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/sorryaboutthemess&blasterproficiency.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If you just targeted with a blaster, add 3 to your total weapon destiny.  LOST: During your control phase, fire one of your weapons. Any \'hit\' targets are immediately lost. OR Lose 1 Force to place opponent\'s just \'hit\' character in Lost Pile.\"',NULL,'Sniper & Dark Strike','10_23'),(2678,2334,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Squadron Assignments','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/squadronassignments.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. During your deploy phase, you may reveal one unpiloted starfighter from hand to take its matching pilot character from Reserve Deck (or vice versa) and deploy both simultaneously; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Rebel starfighter squadrons take great pride in their proficiency and dedication. Alliance pilots train relentlessly until man and machine function as one.','Combat Response','9_39'),(2679,5923,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 9','•Stardust','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/stardust.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Data Vault. At any time, may relocate Stardust to your spy present. During your control phase, if on your spy at a battleground you occupy, opponent loses 2 Force. If about to leave table, relocate to Data Vault (if possible). (Immune to Alter.)','Blank.',NULL,'209_18'),(2680,1879,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•Outrider','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/outrider.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified Light Freighter','2','3','2','5','May add 2 pilots and 1 passenger. Utinni Effects which retrieve Force are immune to Alter, but are placed out of play when completed. While Dash or Leebo piloting, immune to attrition< 4.','Highly modified Corellian Engineering Corporation YT-2400. KonGar KGDefender military grade ion engines. Griffyn/Y2TG hyperdrive. Never boarded by Imperial customs.',NULL,'10_17'),(2681,2342,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Star Destroyer!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/stardestroyer.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just deployed or moved a Star Destroyer, say \'Star Destroyer!\' After placing interrupt in Used Pile, may place Used Pile on top of Reserve Deck.','Leia\'s perception increased as she became more attuned to the Force. She attained the uncanny ability to spot objects at long distances.',NULL,'7_103'),(2682,2349,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Steady Aim','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/steadyaim.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Add X to one starship weapon destiny (before destiny is drawn) when targeting opponent\'s starship. USED: X=2.LOST: X=4.\"','Although unfamiliar with the quad laser turrets on the Falcon, Luke quickly scored two hits.',NULL,'7_105'),(2683,5814,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Qui-Gon Jinn (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/quigonjinnai.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','8','9','Deploys -2 to Tatooine. Power +1 at same site as Maul. Once during a duel Qui-Gon is in, may cancel a duel destiny just drawn and cause a redraw. Opponent\'s aliens are power -1 at same site. Immune to attrition.','Accepted Obi-WanObi-Wan in Radiant VII  Kenobi as his Padawan learner. Was given orders to protect Queen Amidala at all costs.',NULL,'11_11'),(2684,5046,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 3','•Stolen Data Tapes','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/stolendatatapes.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on R2-D2. If about to leave table (even from Overwhelmed),relocate to Dune Sea (if possible). If at Dune Sea, may relocate to your character there. If at Alderaan (or a \'blown away\' system), tapes \'delivered\'; relocate this Effect to table and may take any card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','\'What\'s so important? What\'s he carrying?\' \'The technical readouts of that battle station. I only hope that when the data is analyzed, a weakness can be found.\'',NULL,'203_14'),(2685,2348,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Stay Sharp!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/staysharp.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, fire one of your starship weapons (for free). If Han or any gunner is aboard that starship, may add 2 to destiny draw. \'Hit\' target is lost. OR If you just fired a weapon in battle, add that weapon\'s destiny number to your total power.','\'Ha haaaaaa!\'',NULL,'7_104'),(2686,2338,'Light','C','Death Star II','Staging Areas','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/stagingareas.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your Force generation is +1 at each docking bay you occupy (or +2 if you control). You non-unique Star Cruisers are deploy -1 and may deploy to same battleground system as any rebel starship. (Immune to Alter.)','The Alliance carefully chooses docking bays from which to launch limited offensives.',NULL,'9_40'),(2687,2365,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Strikeforce','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/strikeforce.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. While you control a battleground site, your Force drain may not be modified or canceled at a system where you have a Star Cruiser or unique(•) starfighter, except by a \'react.\' Place Effect in Used Pile if you lose a battle at a system.','Admiral Ackbar\'s hit-and-fade tactics force the Imperial Navy to spread throughout the galaxy in a futile attempt to engage the Rebels.',NULL,'9_42'),(2688,2321,'Light','F','Special Edition','<>Spaceport Street','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/spaceportstreet.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : During your move phase, may move free between here and any related _spaceport site. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth, Kashyyyk or Yavin 4.',NULL,'Spaceport Street','7_127'),(2689,1777,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Nien Nunb','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/niennunb.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. When at a mobile sector, once per turn you may peek at the top card of your Reserve Deck; you may place that card on top of your Used Pile. When with General Calrissian may add one battle destiny.','Brilliant navigator. Former SoroSuub employee. Turned to pirating when that corporation backed the Empire. Tall for a Sullustan.',NULL,'9_28'),(2690,2304,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Son Of Skywalker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/mast