o Alter.)','Lando\'s confidence in the Rebel strike team on the forest moon was rewarded, and proved to be a decisive factor at the Battle of Endor.',NULL,'11_22'),(2814,2548,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Thedit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/thedit.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Deploys only on Tatooine. When in a battle with at least two of your other Jawas, adds one battle destiny. When your total batle destiny at Thedit\'s site is greater than opponent\'s total battle destiny, Thedit reduces attrition against you by 3.','Organizes perimeter patrols for Kalit\'s territory. Inspiring leader. Keeps a watchful eye for krayt dragons, Tusken Raiders, and Wittin\'s bandits.',NULL,'7_45'),(2815,2531,'Light','R2','Premiere','The Force Is Strong With This One','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/theforceisstrongwiththisone.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke and an Imperial with ability > 2 are involved in the same battle, you may add one battle destiny (add 2 if Imperial is Vader).','Luke\'s piloting skills and Force abilities made his X-wing a difficult target for Darth Vader as they raced down the Death Star trench.',NULL,'1_116'),(2816,2393,'Light','U','Cloud City','•••Swing-And-A-Miss','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/swingandamiss.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just used a lightsaber to target, draw one destiny and subtract that amount from opponent\'s weapon destiny. OR Cancel one Mostly Armless card just played. OR Cancel Dark Strike, End This Destructive Conflict or Focused Attack.','It\'s the bottom of the ninth level of Cloud City. Vader steps up to the platform. Here\'s the delivery. . . oooh, he took a big cut there! The Force sure wasn\'t with him on that one!',NULL,'5_72'),(2817,5792,'Light','R','Theed 