t holosites and opponent must lose an additional 1 Force to draw a card with Shot In The Dark. (Immune to Alter.) OR Deploy on any planet site. Opponent\'s Force drains are -1 here.','\'Greetings, Exalted One. Allow me to introduce myself. I am Luke Skywalker, Jedi Knight and friend to Captain Solo.\' Hologram.','Image Of The Dark (V)','6_56'),(2821,1651,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Master Qui-Gon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/masterquigon.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','8','9','Deploys -2 on Coruscant. If opponent\'s Dark Jedi on table, during your move phase may use 4 Force to return Qui-Gon (and all cards on him) to owner\'s hand. Immune to attrition and You Are Beaten.','Jedi Master currently not on the Council. Although he serves the Council well, there have been times when he has defied their wishes to pursue a path he believes is right.',NULL,'12_16'),(2822,1891,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Panaka, Protector Of The Queen','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/panakaprotectorofthequeen.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','4','4','6','Deploys for free to a Naboo site. While with Amidala at a Naboo site, opponent may not target Amidala with weapons. While on Naboo, immune to attrition < 5.','Leader of the Royal Naboo security Forces. Fought alongside Amidala in order to capture Viceroy Nute Gunray.',NULL,'14_23'),(2823,1964,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Pucumir Thryss','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/pucumirthryss.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','3','While on Cloud City, adds 1 to your Force drains at Cloud City sites and adds 4 to destiny of each of your miners drawn for battle destiny. During your deploy phase, may deploy one non-unique Rebel to same Cloud City site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Former gas miner. One of the Rebellion\'s contacts on Cloud City before it was taken over by the Empire. Wishes to return to Bespin and retake the floating city.',NULL,'6_33'),(2824,2539,'Light','R','Dagobah','•The Professor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/theprofessor.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on your side of the table (free if C-3PO on table). If you have a protocol droid aboard a starship or vehicle in a battle, you may use X Force to reduce the battle damage against you by X (by X + 1 if a Nav Computer character is also aboard).','Protocol droids are programmed to interface with a variety of computer technologies. Quick and precise interpretation can dramatically increase operational efficiency.',NULL,'4_40'),(2825,1902,'Light','C2','Hoth','Perimeter Scan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/perimeterscan.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to glance at any one card which is face-down at a location. OR Use 1 Force to glance at opponent\'s hand. You may move each droid spy and Infantry Mine you find there to opponent\'s Used Pile. OR Cancel Probe Telemetry.','\'It\'s a good bet the Empire knows we\'re here.\'',NULL,'3_48'),(2826,1966,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Punch It!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/punchit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Han or your Lando is piloting a starfighter which is defending a battle at a system, add one battle destiny (add two if starfighter is Falcon). Also, starfighter is immune to attrition for remainder of turn.','Ever since Lando\'s \'little\' maneuver at the Battle of Taanab, his piloting skills had become legendary.',NULL,'5_64'),(2827,2610,'Light','C2','Premiere','Timer Mine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/timermine.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on opponent\'s side at same site as one of your mining droids. \'Explodes\' at beginning of your next turn. Draw destiny. That number of opponent\'s characters there are immediately lost (owner\'s choice). Timer Mine is also lost.','A timer-activated explosive device designed to be placed by a mining droid. Typically used in ore and spice mines for demolition. Also has many military applications.','Timer Mine','1_162'),(2828,2563,'Light','R1','A New Hope','They\'re On Dantooine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/theyreondantooine.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Once per game, use 2 Force to deploy on Dantooine system. Target Death Star. Opponent may not play Commence Primary Ignition until target reaches Dantooine, canceling Utinni Effect.','\'You would prefer another target? A military target? Then name the system!\'',NULL,'2_39'),(2829,1792,'Light','PM','Reflections II','•No Questions Asked','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/noquestionsasked.gif?raw=true','Admiral\'s Order',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Force generation at sectors a player occupies is +1 for that player. Any independent starship with an alien pilot character aboard is immune to attrition < 4 (or adds 2 to immunity). During your control phase, one of your smugglers at a site related to a system occupied by your freighter or independent starship may either fire a blaster or make a regular move using personal landspeed.',NULL,NULL,'10_14'),(2830,2571,'Light','R','Cloud City','•This Is Even Better','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/thisisevenbetter.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Han and Leia are together in a battle you just lost, forfeit one of them to satisfy all battle damage and attrition against you. OR If Han is a captive and a battle was just initiated where you have Leia (or vice versa), add one battle destiny. OR Cancel This Is Still Wrong.','It took escape from Hoth, asteroids, slugs, capture, refreshments with Vader, torture and the inevitable carbon-freezing to get Leia to reveal her true feelings for Han.',NULL,'5_73'),(2831,2582,'Light','R','Endor','•Threepio','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/threepio.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','1','4','5','Deploys -2 on Endor. Adds 1 to attrition against opponent for each Ewok in battle at same site. If just lost from table during battle, may go to Used Pile. At same and related sites, Cloud city icon, Jabba\'s Palace icon, and Endor icon characters are immune to Bad Feeling Have I.','Against his programming to impersonate a deity. Worshiped by the Ewoks. \'Aaaahhhhh-uuuuhhhhh. Aaaahhhhh-uuuuhhhhh. Aaaahhhhhuuuuhhhhh.\'',NULL,'8_31'),(2832,2583,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Threepio With His Parts Showing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/threepiowithhispartsshowing.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','2','3','If in a battle with Shmi at a site, once per battle may place top card of your Used Pile on top of your Reserve Deck. Once per turn may place a card from hand on Used Pile to draw top card from Reserve Deck.','Protocol droid designed by Anakin in order to help his mother. C-3PO was not to be sold when Anakin left with Qui-Gon Jinn for Coruscant.',NULL,'11_13'),(2833,2574,'Light','R','Dagobah','This Is No Cave','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/thisisnocave.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Relocate one starfighter from a Big One to the related site (or vice versa) for free (opens Slug\'s mouth if closed). If smuggler aboard, starfighter is immune to attrition and subtracts 5 from asteroid destiny until end of your next turn. OR Cancel Corrosive Damage.','The largest space slug on record was 900 meters long. Han suspected he had discovered one that was somewhat larger.',NULL,'4_63'),(2834,2593,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Tibrin','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/tibrin.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy, during your control phase, may exchange three cards in hand for any one card in your Lost Pile.',NULL,NULL,'6_87'),(2835,2606,'Light','U1','Hoth','•Tigran Jamiro','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/tigranjamiro.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','4','Deploy only on Yavin 4 or Hoth, but may move elsewhere. Opponent\'s aliens and Imperials may not move from same site as Tigran to an Echo or an interior Yavin site.','Senior logistics officer from Onderon. Left Dantooine to serve on Yavin 4 before coming to Hoth. All personnel entering Echo Base must report to him.',NULL,'3_22'),(2836,2585,'Light','R','Dagobah','Through The Force Things You Will See','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/throughtheforcethingsyouwillsee.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'At the end of any player\'s draw phase, cause that player to place Used Pile face up on top of Reserve Deck. Shuffle, cut, and replace. When face up cards are removed from Reserve Deck, they are treated as normal (no longer face up).','One training exercise for a Jedi\'s apprentice is to invert one\'s view to see things from a different perspective. \'The future, the past. Old friends long gone.\'',NULL,'4_64'),(2837,2570,'Light','U1','Premiere','This Is All Your Fault','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/thisisallyourfault.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Lose a droid to cancel all attrition against you at same site this turn. OR Re-target an opponent\'s weapon to one of your droids at same site as target. If droid is \'hit\', use original target\'s forfeit number.','\'We seem to be made to suffer. It\'s our lot in life.\'','Self-Destruct Mechanism','1_117'),(2838,5976,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Threepio With His Parts Showing (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/threepiowithhispartsshowingai.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','3','1','2','3','If in a battle with Shmi at a site, once per battle may place top card of your Used Pile on top of your Reserve Deck. Once per turn may place a card from hand on Used Pile to draw top card from Reserve Deck.','Protocol droid designed by Anakin in order to help his mother. C-3PO was not to be sold when Anakin left with Qui-Gon Jinn for Coruscant.',NULL,'11_14'),(2839,2560,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•They Win This Round','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/theywinthisround.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just Force drained you at a location, deploy on that location. Opponent\'s Force drains here are +1. Your battle destiny draws here are +1 If you control this location, may place Immediate Effect in Used Pile to retrieve 4 Force. (Immune to Control.)','The Queen realized that you must give up one battle in order to have an advantage in the next.','After Her!','14_37'),(2840,2587,'Light','C','Coruscant','•Thrown Back','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/thrownback.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on table. During your move phase, if opponent has 13 or more cards in hand, you may use 4 Force to place all but 8 (random choice) in Used Pile. Once during any control phase, you may place up to three cards from hand in Used Pile.','Being sent to dispose of two Jedi is the battle droid equivalent of a really bad day at the office.','Drop!','12_49'),(2841,5134,'Light','R','Virtual Set 5','•Tycho In Green Squadron 3','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/tychoingreensquadron3.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: A-Wing','2','3','3','5','May deploy as a \'react\'. Permanent pilot is *Tycho, who provides ability of 2 and adds 3 to his [Death Star 2] Epic Event destiny draws. During battle, may target a starfighter; target\'s immunity to attrition is canceled.','Flown by Tycho Celchu at the Battle of Endor. Modified canopy improves pilot vision in tight confines. Assigned to fly top cover for Millennium Falcon.',NULL,'205_10'),(2842,2639,'Light','F','Special Edition','•Trooper Sabacc','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/troopersabacc.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Requirements: A gambler or trooper at a site. Wild cards: (2-7): Imperial and Rebel leaders. (Troopers may use weapons as wild cards.) Clone cards: Locations and droids. Stakes: One transport vehicle without armor or one character weapon.','Troopers stationed at various outposts play this sabacc variant to pass the time between assignments.','Trooper Sabacc','7_109'),(2843,2611,'Light','U2','A New Hope','•Tiree','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/tiree.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Gold 2, also adds 1 to maneuver and (when in Death Star: Trench) adds 1 to total of Attack Run.','Piloted Gold 2 as defensive cover for Gold Leader during attack run in Death Star trench at the Battle of Yavin.',NULL,'2_21'),(2844,5127,'Light','R','Virtual Set 5','•Tycho Celchu (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual5-Light/large/tychocelchu.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','3','4','Adds 3 to the power of anything he pilots. May reveal from hand to steal an unpiloted TIE from opponent\'s Lost Pile and deploy both simultaneously. Any snub fighter he pilots is maneuver +1 and immune to attrition < 4.','Spy fighting for the memory of his homeworld of Alderaan. Rogue Squadron pilot. Volunteered to fly an A-wing at the Battle of Endor. Former TIE fighter pilot.',NULL,'205_3'),(2845,2655,'Light','R','Endor','•Tydirium','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/tydirium.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Lambda-Class Shuttle','3','2','2','4','May deploy (and your characters may deploy aboard) even without presence of Force icons. May add 2 pilots and 6 passengers. While Tydirium is at a system location, your scouts deploy -1 aboard.','Stolen Imperial Lambda-class shuttle. Supposedly carried parts and technical crew. Delivered General Solo\'s crack team of Rebel scouts to the forest moon of Endor.',NULL,'8_79'),(2846,5044,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 3','•Toryn Farr (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/torynfarr.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','4','1','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. Your total battle destiny here is +1 (+2 if piloting a transport). Once per turn, if a battle just ended, may \'rescue\' (retrieve from Lost Pile OR stack on [Set 0] Evacuation Control) a Rebel of ability < 3 forfeited from same location this turn.','Chief Controller at Echo Command. Responsible for communicating orders to the troops. Personally gives firing orders to Ion Cannon Control.',NULL,'203_12'),(2847,5177,'Light','C','Virtual Set 7','•This is MY Ship!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/thisismyship.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Deploy Ghost and Hera simultaneously from your hand and/or Reserve Deck (for -1 Force each); reshuffle.  LOST: If Chopper, Ezra, Hera, Kanan, Sabine or Zeb in a battle, they each add 1 to your total battle destiny.\"',NULL,NULL,'207_15'),(2848,2561,'Light','C','Dagobah','•They\'d Be Crazy To Follow Us','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/theydbecrazytofollowus.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to target a starship at an asteroid sector or a \'blown away\' system. For remainder of turn, you may add 2 to destiny totals targeting the armor or maneuver of that starship.','Flying into an asteroid field is considered to be certain death except by Han Solo, Rycar Ryjerd and the terminally insane.',NULL,'4_61'),(2849,2679,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','Unfriendly Fire','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/unfriendlyfire.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If an AT-AT, an AT-ST, Jabba\'s Sail Barge or Planet Defender Ion Cannon has just been lost at a site, draw destiny. All cards with that destiny number at that site are lost.','\'Get the gun! Point it at the deck!\'',NULL,'6_78'),(2850,2689,'Light','R1','Premiere','Utinni!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/utinni.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your Jawas is at the same location as any Utinni Effect, \'steal\' that Utinni Effect into your hand, to use or lose as your own. OR Cancel any Interrupt or Effect with \'Jawa\' in the card name.','Jawa trade language word for \'Come here!\' Jawas work communally and scavenge for equipment.','Utinni!','1_118'),(2851,2625,'Light','U2','Premiere','Traffic Control','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/trafficcontrol.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your side of table. During your control phase, you may return any cards from your hand to the top of your Used Pile.','Expert traffic controllers coordinate launches faster than automated launch systems. Rebel bases scramble fighters quickly during Imperial attacks.','Reactor Terminal','1_66'),(2852,2705,'Light','C2','Premiere','Vaporator','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/vaporator.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on any Tatooine site. Cannot be moved. Protects all characters at same site, or an adjacent site, from Gravel Storm.','Essential for life on desert planets. Condenses water vapor from atmosphere. Has purification filters and coolant tanks. Protects against drought and harsh conditions.',NULL,'1_41'),(2853,2722,'Light','C','Dagobah','••Visored Vision','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/visoredvision.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Name an Interrupt card. Opponent must reveal entire Used Pile, without shuffling. Then you choose:USED: Opponent must lose 1 Force for each copy of that Interrupt found there.  LOST: Each copy of that interrupt found there is lost.\"','It\'s 15 parsecs to Kessel, we\'ve replaced the negative power coupling, it\'s dark and we\'re wearing welding goggles. Hit it.',NULL,'4_68'),(2854,5233,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 8','•Walker Sighting (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/walkersighting.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel Too Cold For Speeders. OR Unless opponent\'s AT-AT or AT-ST at a battleground site, retrieve 1 Force for each Rebel Base location you control (limit 3). OR Your Rebels and T-47s at sites where opponent has an AT-AT or AT-ST are power +2 for remainder of turn.','\'Echo station, 3TA. We have spotted Imperial walkers.\' A Rebel tactic is to put as much ground as possible between walkers and Rebel troops, allowing time to prepare a defense.',NULL,'208_22'),(2855,2710,'Light','C2','Hoth','Vehicle Mine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/vehiclemine.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Automated','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy at same exterior site as your mining droid. \'Explodes\' if starfighter (use 5 as defense value) or non-creature vehicle deploys or moves to or across same site.  Draw destiny.  Target lost if destiny +2 > defense value.  Vehicle Mine also lost.','Mine controlled by microcircuitry calibrated to ignore infantry and creatures. Explodes only when triggered by metallic vehicles.','Vehicle Mine','3_81'),(2856,5997,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 11','•Vice Admiral Holdo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/viceadmiralholdo.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','2','1','3','5','Adds 2 to power of any capital starship she pilots. During battle, if piloting a capital starship, may place it and Holdo out of play to add X to your total battle destiny, where X is that starship\'s armor + hyperspeed.','Female leader.',NULL,'211_55'),(2857,2631,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Treva Horme','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/trevahorme.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','2','During your control phase, may \'sell\' one Interrupt card from hand. Opponent must use X Force, where X = destiny of that card or entire Force Pile (opponent\'s choice). Place sold card on opponent\'s Used Pile and activate X Force.','Lutrillian. Primary saleswoman and executive planner for Planet Dreams, Inc. Monitors production schedules and accounting. Really enjoys making a sales pitch.',NULL,'5_9'),(2858,6006,'Light','U','Theed Palace','We Have A Plan / They Will Be Lost And Confused','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/wehaveaplan.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'We Have A Plan:Deploy Theed Palace Throne Room, Theed Palace Hallway, and Theed Palace Courtyard.{For} remainder of game, you may not deploy cards with ability except [Episode I] Jedi, aliens, [Episode I] vehicles, Republic characters and [Republic] starships. Your Destiny is suspended. You lose no Force to Vengeance Of The Dark Prince.{While} this side up, you may not deploy characters to interior Naboo sites. Once per turn, may activate 1 Force.{Flip} this card if you control Theed Palace Throne Room (with Amidala there).They Will Be Lost And Confused:{While} this side up, you lose no more than 2 Force to any Force drain. Your [Republic] starships are power +2 and immunity to attrition of [Trade Federation] starships is canceled. If opponent just drew a battle destiny greater than three, you may use 1 Force to cancel that battle destiny. During your control phase, opponent loses 2 Force for each battleground site you control with Amidala or Panaka.{Flip} this card if opponent controls Theed Palace Throne Room.',NULL,NULL,'14_52'),(2859,2612,'Light','R','Special Edition','•TK-422','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/tk422.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','6','Deploys only as an Undercover spy at same site as an Imperial. While Undercover, Imperials are deploy +1 at related sites. May voluntarily \'break cover\' only during your move phase by using 3 Force. Captured if \'cover broken\' by opponent.','Corellian smuggler. Spy. Han stole the armor and identity of an enemy soldier that boarded the Millennium Falcon. Bluffed his way into the detention area.',NULL,'7_48'),(2860,2673,'Light','U2','A New Hope','Undercover','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/undercover.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your spy at a site and cross spy to opponent\'s side.  Spy is now Undercover.  During your deploy phase, may voluntarily \'break cover\' (lose Effect) if at a site. (Immune to Alter.)','Alliance Intelligence expends considerable resources to infiltrate the Imperial military bureaucracy, but the ISB\'s security sweeps make these shadowy operations dangerous.','Undercover','2_40'),(2861,2727,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Vote Now!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/votenow.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, draw destiny. If destiny > 2, draw up to X cards (maximum 4) from Reserve Deck, where X = your total politics at Galactic Senate minus opponent\'s total politics at Galactic Senate.','\'Vote now! Vote now! Vote now!\'','Vote Now!','12_71'),(2862,2573,'Light','R','Dagobah','This Is More Like It','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/thisismorelikeit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During a battle, lose X Force to reduce attrition against you by X. OR Cancel This Is Just Wrong.','\'You like me because I\'m a scoundrel. There aren\'t enough scoundrels in your life.\' \'I happen to like nice men.\' \'I\'m a nice man.\' \'No you\'re not, you\'re ..\'',NULL,'4_62'),(2863,2676,'Light','PM','Jabba\'s Palace Sealed Deck','•Underworld Contacts','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalaceSealedDeck-Light/large/underworldcontacts.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Tatooine site. Your Force generation here is +1. Opponent may not cancel or modify Force drains at each Tatooine battleground site where you have two aliens with different card titles. At any time, you may use 2 Force to raise your converted Tatooine site to top.','Influence, like any commodity, has a price in the Outer Rim territories.',NULL,'112_10'),(2864,2586,'Light','U','Endor','•Throw Me Another Charge','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/throwmeanothercharge.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take one automated weapon into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Add 1 to Deactivate The Shield Generator total. OR Cancel Trooper Charge, Blasted Droid, Trooper Assault or Dark Jedi Presence.','Han knew that it was urgent that he quickly finished his assignment.',NULL,'8_63'),(2865,2663,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Uh-oh!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/uhoh.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Your side of table. While no Rebels at any Jabba\'s Palace sites, at all such sites: Imperials are deploy +2, Bo Shuda may not be canceled, Expand the Empire is canceled and your non-unique aliens are each forfeit +1 (Immune to Alter.)','Imperial law had no place in the Hutt\'s domain.',NULL,'7_79'),(2866,2776,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Weapons Display','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/weaponsdisplay.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. Each of your starships with two or more starship weapons aboard is power +2. Once during each of your deploy phases, you may use 2 Force to deploy from Lost Pile one starship weapon, vehicle weapon or artillery weapon (for free).','The X-wing\'s display panel allows for different firing patterns for different weapons. This gives the pilot the ability to switch weapon types with minimum time and energy loss.',NULL,'7_80'),(2867,2718,'Light','C','Dagobah','Vine Snake','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/vinesnake.gif?raw=true','Creature','Ophidian','3','0','2','0','Habitat: planet sites (except Hoth). Parasite: Non-droid Character. Each move phase, draw destiny; each time destiny > ability, add 1 to X (X starts at 0). Host is power -X (eaten if power = 0).','Constricts hapless victims. Prey usually struggles at first, then weakens as strength diminishes. Difficult to spot. Common hazard on less-developed worlds.','Vine Snake','4_7'),(2868,2758,'Light','R','Cloud City','•We\'ll Find Han','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/wellfindhan.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy Han to same site as Chewie or your Lando (regardless of deployment restrictions). OR If Chewie and your Lando are in a battle together, subtract 3 from all attrition against you (cannot not fall below zero). OR Cancel I Had No Choice.','\'I promise.\' \'Auuuuuug!\'',NULL,'5_74'),(2869,5153,'Light','R','Virtual Set 6','•The Falcon','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual6-Light/large/thefalcon.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Heavily-Modified Light Freighter','2','3','3','7','May add 2 pilots and 2 passengers. Once per game, during your move phase, may make an additional move. While [Episode VII] Chewie, [Episode VII] Han, or Rey piloting manuver = 6 and immune to attrition < 5.','-',NULL,'206_8'),(2870,5971,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 9','•There Is Another','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/thereisanother.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on Your Destiny unless Leia or Luke has been deployed this game (even as a captive). [Death Star II] Luke and We\'re The Bait are lost. Opponent\'s Objective and [Death Star II] Effects target Leia instead of Luke. Force loss from Take Your Father\'s Place is -1.','Princess Leia Organa. Alderaanian senator. Targeted by Vader for capture and interrotgation. The Datk Lord of the Sith wanted her alive.',NULL,'209_15'),(2871,2614,'Light','U','Tatooine','•Too Close For Comfort','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/toocloseforcomfort.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If your character was just targeted by a weapon, opponent must use 2 Force or the targeting is canceled.  LOST: Cancel Hit Racer or Podracer Collision.\"','Anakin needed all the help he could get to evade Sebulba\'s tactics.',NULL,'11_40'),(2872,5078,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•••Tuanul Villager','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/tuanulvillager.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','3','2','2','3','If with your other Resistance character and present at a site, adds 1 to your Force drains here and may place this character in Used Pile to cancel a just drawn weapon destiny here.','Blank.',NULL,'204_13'),(2873,2751,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•We Don\'t Have Time For This','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/wedonthavetimeforthis.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Amidala and Panaka are in a battle together, add two battle destiny.  OR  Target an interior Naboo site where opponent has a battle droid. Draw destiny. If destiny > number of battle droids at that site, one of them is lost (opponent\'s choice).','Amidala and Panaka have the weapons training to pin down and remove the greatest combat threat.',NULL,'14_45'),(2874,2566,'Light','C','Special Edition','•They\'re Tracking Us','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/theyretrackingus.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just deployed a planet site, deploy the related system from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Cancel one opponent\'s \'react\' unless opponent uses 2 additional Force.','\'Not this ship, sister.\'',NULL,'7_108'),(2875,2618,'Light','U1','Hoth','•Toryn Farr','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/torynfarr.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','4','1','2','3','Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. When at any war room, adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of your Planet Defender Ion Cannon on same planet.','Chief Controller at Echo Command. Responsible for communicating orders to the troops. Personally gives firing orders to Ion Cannon Control.',NULL,'3_23'),(2876,1933,'Light','C','Special Edition','•Precise Hit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/precisehit.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: During a battle at a system or sector, instead of firing one of your starship weapons at a target, reduce that target\'s power by 4 until end of turn.  LOST: During a battle at a system or sector, use 3 Force to cancel one battle destiny just drawn.\"','\'Luke, trust me.\'','Coordinated Attack','7_99'),(2877,2797,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•Wesa Gotta Grand Army','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/wesagottagrandarmy.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Take a Fambaa, Battle Plains, or Boss Nass\' Chambers into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Subtract one from any just drawn weapon destiny.  LOST: Target an opponent\'s undercover spy with your Gungan. Target is lost.\"','\'Gungans no die\'n without a fight.\'',NULL,'14_46'),(2878,5057,'Light','U','Virtual Set 4','•Theron Nett (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/theronnett.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. While at a battleground system, opponent\'s starships may not \'cloak.\' May lose 1 Force (free if piloting Red 10) to cancel a just-drawn weapon destiny targeting a starship he is piloting.','Experienced smuggler from Ord Mantell. Piloted Red 10 at the Battle of Yavin. Long-time wingman of Garven Dreis.',NULL,'204_12'),(2879,2799,'Light','R','Dagobah','•WHAAAAAAAAAOOOOW!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/whaaaaaaaaaoooow.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','7',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one of your characters was just defeated by a Dragonsnake, Rancor, Sarlacc, Dianoga or Wampa, instead of being \'eaten\' that character is \'hurled\' (relocated) to an adjacent site, if possible.','\'You\'re lucky you don\'t taste very good.\'',NULL,'4_71'),(2880,2547,'Light','C','Death Star II','The Way Of Things','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/thewayofthings.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If Yoda is on Dagobah and Jedi Test #3 is present with target apprentice, it is completed. Also, you may not play Surprise Assault. Each apprentice on Dagobah is landspeed = 2 and may not be targeted by Set For Stun. (Immune To Alter.)','\'When nine hundred years old you reach, look as good you will not. Hmmm?\'',NULL,'9_45'),(2881,5974,'Light','C','Virtual Set 9','They Have No Idea We\'re Coming / Until We Win, Or The Chances Are Spent','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual9-Light/large/theyhavenoideawerecoming.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'They Have No Idea We\'re Coming:Deploy Scarif system, Data Vault (with Stardust there), and Massassi War Room.{For} remainder of game, you may not deploy Jedi. Baze, Chirrut, and Rebel troopers are spies.{While} this side up, once per turn, may deploy a Rebel starship (except Home One or [Reflections III] Falcon) or a Scarif site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Each player\'s characters (except Imperials and spies) and vehicles deploy +2 to Scarif sites that player does not occupy.{Flip} this card if you control two Scarif locations.Until We Win, Or The Chances Are Spent:{While} this side up, your spies are defense value +2 (and power +1 if with Stardust) and are immune to Undercover. While Stardust on your spy, opponent may not cancel your Force drains at battlegrounds. Once per turn, may place a Rebel in your Lost Pile out of play to cancel a just drawn destiny targeting the ability or defense value of your Rebel or to make a regular move with your spy during your control phase.{Flip} this card if you do not occupy two Scarif locations (unless Rogue One at a Scarif site you occupy).',NULL,NULL,'209_29'),(2882,2767,'Light','C','Coruscant','•We\'re Leaving','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/wereleaving.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on table. During the damage segment of a battle your opponent initiated, if you have no cards left that can be forfeited, you may place this Effect out of play to cancel all remaining battle damage. (Immune to Alter.)','Qui-Gon realized that sometimes it\'s best to just leave, before any more damage is done.','Mind Tricks Don\'t Work On Me','12_50'),(2883,2734,'Light','U2','Hoth','•Walker Sighting','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/walkersighting.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just moved or deployed an AT-AT to a planet site, search your Reserve Deck for up to three exterior sites of that planet and immediately deploy them.  Shuffle, cut and replace.','\'Echo station, 3TA. We have spotted Imperial walkers.\' A Rebel tactic is to put as much ground as possible between walkers and Rebel troops, allowing time to prepare a defense.',NULL,'3_51'),(2884,2786,'Light','R1','A New Hope','•Wedge Antilles','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/wedgeantilles.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','4','2','2','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Red 2, also adds 2 to maneuver and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. May use 1 Force to take one Corellian Slip into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Highly decorated Corellian. Piloted Red 2 at the Battle of Yavin. A wealthy orphan, he bought a freighter with his inheritance. First joined the Alliance as a weapons smuggler.',NULL,'2_23'),(2885,1499,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Leia, Rebel Princess','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/leiarebelprincess.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','3','4','7','Twice per game, may place top card of Lost Pile on top of Reserve Deck to cancel a Force drain at a related site. Unless opponent\'s non-alien character here, opponent\'s total ability at same site = 0. Immune to attrition < 5 if with Luke, Han or Jabba.','After attracting Luke\'s attention and then Han\'s attention, Leia should not have been surprised when she got more attention than desired from Jabba.',NULL,'13_29'),(2886,2658,'Light','R2','A New Hope','•Tzizvvt','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/tzizvvt.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','3','1','May \'fly\' (move) only during your deploy phase, up to two sites away, for 1 Force. Power +1 at Trash Compactor, any Dagobah site or same site as Dark Waters or Tarkin.','This male Brizzit, from the planet Jandoon, is hiding from the Imperials on the remote world Tatooine. He hopes to procure passage to the Outer Rim before the Empire finds him.',NULL,'2_22'),(2887,1858,'Light','C','Special Edition','Organized Attack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/organizedattack.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: If a battle was just initiated, each of your X-wings and Y-wings present is power +1 and immune to attrition for remainder of turn.  LOST: Lose 1 Force to take up to three non-unique X-wings and/or non-unique Y-wings into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.\"','\'Hold up here and wait for my signal to start your run.\'','All Power To Weapons','7_97'),(2888,5048,'Light','C','Virtual Set 3','•Thrown Back (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/thrownback.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. While no card stacked here, may stack opponent\'s just-played Interrupt here. Opponent may use 3 Force to place an Interrupt here in Used Pile. Once per turn, may place a card from hand on bottom of Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','Being sent to dispose of two Jedi is the battle droid equivalent of a really bad day at the office.','Drop! (V)','203_16'),(2889,2692,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Uutkik','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/uutkik.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Deploys only on Tatooine. Once during each of your control phases, may lose 1 Force to steal into hand one transport vehicle, character weapon or device from opponent\'s Lost Pile.','Experienced Jawa thief. Pilfers equipment and hijacks vehicles from unwary bystanders in Mos Eisley. Het Nkik\'s ugliest cousin.',NULL,'7_49'),(2890,1526,'Light','R','Endor','•Lieutenant Greeve','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/lieutenantgreeve.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','3','2','4','Adds 1 to each of his character weapon destiny draws (characters he \'hits\' are forfeit -3). When firing an A280 Sharpshooter Rifle, may fire repeatedly at same target for 2 Force each time.','Scout. Famous guide who was recruited for Madine\'s commando unit from the forests of Kashyyyk. Sharpshooter who uses one of the BlasTech rifles brought by Corporal Janse.',NULL,'8_18'),(2891,2820,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Wokling (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/wokling.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table.  Your total Force generation is +1.  Once per game, may use 3 Force to take an Effect that has no deploy cost and deploys on another card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  May place this Effect out of play to retrieve 1 Force. (Immune to Alter.)','Every Ewok is taught to be protective of the younger members of their clan.',NULL,'200_47'),(2892,1665,'Light','U2','Hoth','Medium Transport','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/mediumtransport.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Transport','3','1','2','4','May add 1 pilot, 4 passengers and 1 vehicle. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','Passenger and cargo transport built by Gallofree Yards. Enormous cargo bays can be outfitted to safely accommodate large numbers of troops, munitions or supplies.',NULL,'3_65'),(2893,1670,'Light','PM','Reflections II','••Mercenary Armor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/mercenaryarmor.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force (free on Leia) to deploy on a Rebel without armor. Character gains {spy} skill, power +3, armor = 4, and immunity to attrition < 3. Imperial Barrier is canceled. Blasters deploy for free and fire for free on this character.','Worn by hired guns throughout the galaxy. Often used by Rebels when infiltrating underworld organizations. Leia wore Boushh\'s armor when she infiltrated Black Sun.',NULL,'10_11'),(2894,2741,'Light','U','Dagobah','•Wars Not Make One Great','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/warsnotmakeonegreat.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any location. For either player to initiate a battle or Force drain anywhere, that player must use +1 Force. Effect canceled if opponent controls this location.','A Jedi seeks nonviolent solutions to problems, but may fight to preserve the existence of life. An apprentice must learn which battles to fight and which to avoid.',NULL,'4_41'),(2895,1312,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Inner Strength','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/innerstrength.gif?raw=true','Epic Event',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. You may not play Sorry About The Mess or Clash Of Sabers. During any deploy phase, you may place one card face-down under one of your Jedi. (These are that character\'s combat cards.) No character may have more than two combat cards at once. Instead of drawing lightsaber combat destiny or duel destiny, your participating character may use one of his combat cards. Place character\'s combat cards in owner\'s Used Pile when used (or if that character leaves table).',NULL,NULL,'13_24'),(2896,1699,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Mos Eisley Blaster','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/moseisleyblaster.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your alien warrior (free if on Tatooine). May target a character for free. Draw destiny. Target is forfeit -2 for remainder of turn if destiny +2 > defense value.','Easily obtained by the Rebellion. Many are copies of the BlasTech DL-18 design. Plentiful on Tatooine. Used for suppressive fire.','Mos Eisley Blaster','6_89'),(2897,2605,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Tight Squeeze','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/tightsqueeze.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have a lone vehicle or starfighter in a battle or Attack Run at Beggar\'s Canyon, Cloud City, Death Star: Trench or an asteroid sector, use 1 Force. At the end of that battle or Attack Run, opponent must forfeit two participating vehicles or starfighters.','Rebel pilots often join the Rebellion from Outer Rim worlds. Bush pilots fly by the seat of their pants, giving them a huge advantage in close quarters.',NULL,'4_65'),(2898,5685,'Light','U','Virtual Set 11','•Libertine','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/libertine.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: d\'Lanseaux Star Yacht','2','2','2','5','May add 2 pilots and 2 passengers. During your deploy phase, may relocate your character of ability < 4 aboard from a related exterior site. While BB-8, DJ, or Rose aboard, immune to attrition < 5.','Blank.',NULL,'211_34'),(2899,1391,'Light','U1','Hoth','•Jeroen Webb','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/jeroenwebb.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','1','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When in battle with a Rebel leader, subtracts 1 from opponent\'s total battle destiny.','Native of Ralltiir. Spy for Ralltiir\'s underground network after his homeworld was subjugated.',NULL,'3_11'),(2900,1549,'Light','C','Cloud City','•Lift Tube Escape','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/lifttubeescape.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a battle, one of your Lift Tubes present may move as a \'react\' from that battle. OR Place one of your unoccupied Lift Tubes on table in your Used Pile. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take one Lift Tube into hand and reshuffle.','First floor: parasols and powdered blue milk. Second floor: bantha skin rugs, bog-wing drapes and juri juice tables. Third floor: a squadron of Imperial stormtroopers.',NULL,'5_57'),(2901,2839,'Light','R','Special Edition','X-wing Assault Squadron','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/xwingassaultsquadron.gif?raw=true','Starship','Squadron: X-Wing','2','9','*','12','*Replaces 3 X-wings at one location (X-wings go to Used Pile). Permanent pilots provide total ability of 3.','A squadron of X-wings ran interference for Y-wings during their assault on the Death Star. Keeping a tight formation dramatically increased the squadron\'s efficiency.',NULL,'7_150'),(2902,2832,'Light','C','Special Edition','Wrist Comlink','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/wristcomlink.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 1 Force to deploy on your Rebel. Your characters and vehicles at related sites may move as a \'react\' to same or adjacent site.','Favored by scouts and troopers over the hand-held model. Easy to operate in difficult environments.',NULL,'7_54'),(2903,2838,'Light','C2','Premiere','X-wing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/xwing.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: X-Wing','2','3','2','4','Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','Model T-65 by Incom Corporation. Delivered to Alliance by defecting design team. 12.5 meters long. Wings deploy in an \'X\' position for better weapons coverage.',NULL,'1_146'),(2904,2825,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Wookiee Strangle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/wookieestrangle.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to target an opponent\'s non-droid character present with one of your Wookiees. Both players draw destiny. Add ability and power. Target is lost if Wookiee\'s total destiny > target\'s total destiny.','Wookiees have been known to dislocate more than just arms.',NULL,'5_75'),(2905,2843,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Yane','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/yane.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','1','2','2','While at a Theed Palace site or same site as Amidala, opponent\'s Republic characters are deploy +1 here and Yane is forfeit +3. If just lost during a battle, may use 2 Force to place Yane in Used Pile.','The youngest handmaiden, Yane stayed behind on Naboo while Amidala pleaded her case to the Galactic Senate. Musician.',NULL,'12_33'),(2906,2764,'Light','C2','Premiere','We\'re Doomed','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/weredoomed.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you have less than 15 Life Force, play during opponent\'s control phase. For remainder of turn, each time you must lose Force, the loss is cut in half (round up). If R2-D2 or C-3PO on table, round down.','Threepio\'s many misadventures often threatened his continued operation. The luckless protocol droid developed a healthy sense of cynicism, and a keen grasp of the obvious.',NULL,'1_120'),(2907,1822,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Officer Dolphe','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/officerdolphe.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While aboard Bravo 2, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise, and opponent\'s battle destiny draws are -2 at same system.','Growing up in a small town outside of Theed, Porro became adept at speeder control and thrust. His decision to volunteer for Bravo Flight made Ric Olie a very happy man.',NULL,'14_20'),(2908,1726,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Naboo Celebration','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/naboocelebration.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If Amidala at a Theed Palace site (or Boss Nass at an exterior Naboo site), opponent\'s cards with ability deploy +2 there. Once during battle at a Naboo site, if you just drew a Gungan or Royal Naboo Security for battle destiny, opponent loses 1 Force.','The heroic actions of Amidala\'s forces and Boss Nass\' army saved Naboo from the Trade Federation. Definitely a cause for celebration!',NULL,'14_34'),(2909,2908,'Light','U1','A New Hope','Y-wing Assault Squadron','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/ywingassaultsquadron.gif?raw=true','Starship','Squadron: Y-Wing','3','6','*','6','* Replaces 3 Y-wings at one location (Y-wings go to Used Pile). May add 3 pilots or passengers. Permanent pilots provide total ability of 3.','The Rebel Alliance deploys starfighters in triangular formations to minimize exposure to enemy fire. Two function as wingmen to cover one leader.',NULL,'2_74'),(2910,5589,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 10','•Hoth: Main Power Generators (1st Marker) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/hothmainpowergenerators.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : \'Hoth Energy Shield Rules\' in effect. Your artillery weapons here are powered.',NULL,NULL,'210_15'),(2911,2740,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Warrior\'s Courage','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/warriorscourage.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If any warrior is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny. OR If Leia is defending a battle alone at a site, add two battle destiny.','Each Rebel soldier is driven by bravery and a belief in the Rebel Alliance\'s ideal of freedom. Courageous and quick-thinking Rebels often defeat Imperial legions.','Lone Warrior','1_119'),(2912,1574,'Light','R','Endor','•Logray','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/logray.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','2','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. When on Endor, adds 1 to total battle destiny wherever you have any Ewok at an Endor site.','Ewok tribal shaman and medicine man. Musician. Wears the skull of a great Churi bird. Suspicious of outsiders. Revered for his wisdom.',NULL,'8_20'),(2913,1159,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Horace Vancil','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/horacevancil.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','3','2','2','5','Deploys -1 on Naboo. While at Theed Palace Throne Room, once during your control phase may reveal one card (random selection) from opponent\'s hand. Opponent must place card in Used Pile or lose 1 Force.','Part of Amidala\'s advisory council, Horace monitors political crises, as well as providing the Queen with information regarding the current economic state of the city.',NULL,'13_23'),(2914,1687,'Light','C','Special Edition','Moisture Farmer','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/moisturefarmer.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Deploy -1 to a farm or exterior Tatooine site. Power and forfeit +1 when Ardon Crell at Audience Chamber. Once during each of your control phases, may take one Hydroponics Station or Vaporator into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Many native Tatooine citizens shun larger settlements. Form small communities in the desert. Their vaporators harvest water from the atmosphere.',NULL,'7_33'),(2915,1663,'Light','U','Special Edition','Medium Bulk Freighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/mediumbulkfreighter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: YV-Class Freighter','3','3','3','4','Deploys and moves like a starfighter. May add 2 pilots, 6 passengers and 1 vehicle. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Has ship-docking capability. Quad Laser Cannon may deploy aboard.','Modern Corellian design. Length 100 meters. Features engine system similar to that of a Corellian corvette. Dorsal hatch reveals hangar bay.',NULL,'7_144'),(2916,4088,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Obi-Wan in Radiant VII','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/obiwaninradiantvii.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Corellian Republic Cruiser','2','4','5','6','May add 1 pilot. Permanent pilot is •Obi-Wan, who provides ability of 6. Opponent\'s starships may not \'cloak.\' Your total ability here may not be reduced.','Optimized for diplomatic missions with sensor-proof pods that have ejection capabilities. Easily identified by its red coloration.',NULL,'200_63'),(2917,5591,'Light','C2','Hoth','•Hoth: Snow Trench (2nd Marker)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/hothsnowtrench.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Add 1 to each of your weapon destiny draws here.',NULL,NULL,'3_63'),(2918,1132,'Light','U','Cloud City','Hero Of A Thousand Devices','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/heroofathousanddevices.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one of your droids. During your deploy phase, may use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one device that deploys on a droid into hand and reshuffle. Also, you may forfeit devices deployed on this droid (forfeit value = destiny number).','Left to his own devices, Artoo used his spunk and creativity to save his companions\' lives time and time again.',NULL,'5_25'),(2919,2730,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Vul Tazaene','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/vultazaene.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','2','2','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Twice during battle at same system, may use 2 Force to add 2 to any destiny of 2. If present with Tonnika Sisters, Vul and Tonnika Sisters are lost.','Security officer from Kiffex searching for the Tonnika sisters. In love with one of them, he\'s not sure which.',NULL,'6_45'),(2920,5598,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 7','•I Think I Can Handle Myself','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/ithinkicanhandlemyself.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your female character is defending a battle alone at a site, add one destiny to total power (if Rey, she is also immune to attrition). OR Cancel a weapon destiny targeting your female character. OR Add 1 to your Force drain where you have a female character.',NULL,NULL,'207_13'),(2921,1070,'Light','R','Tatooine','•Great Shot, Kid!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/greatshotkid.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If Death Star \'blown away\': Whenever you deploy a unique (*) starship to a system location, retrieve 3 Force; Once per during each of your turns you may deploy (for free) a starship from hand or Reserve Deck and reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','With the destruction of the Death Star, the Rebel Alliance received new-found support throughout the galaxy.',NULL,'11_18'),(2922,2816,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Wise Advice','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/wiseadvice.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Your Immediate Effects may play for free. Whenever opponent cancels your card with Sense or Alter, place that canceled card in Used Pile.','The guidance of experienced Jedi allowed Luke to confront Vader.','Oppressive Enforcement - Defensive Shield','13_47'),(2923,2859,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Yavin 4: Massassi War Room','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/yavin4massassiwarroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, with a leader here, all Stormtroopers and TIEs on table are forfeit -1.',NULL,NULL,'1_139'),(2924,2670,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Uncontrollable Fury','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/uncontrollablefury.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Vader. He is power +2, but neither adds 1 to battle destiny nor allows Tarkin to cancel destiny. Opponent loses 2 Force at end of each of opponent\'s turns in which Vader did not battle and you had a character of ability > 3 on table. (Immune to Alter.)','The rage of the Dark Lord.',NULL,'5_29'),(2925,1119,'Light','C','Death Star II','•Heading For The Medical Frigate','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/headingforthemedicalfrigate.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Starting','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Add 1 to your battle destiny just drawn.  STARTING: Deploy up to three Effects if each of them deploys for free, is always immune to Alter and has \'deploy on table\' (or \'deploy on your side of table\') in its game text. Place Interrupt in Lost Pile.\"','At the Battle of Endor, Rebel starships fought to defend key capital starships, such as the Redemption.','Prepared Defenses','9_51'),(2926,1384,'Light','R','Dagobah','Jedi Levitation','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/jedilevitation.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use X force, where X=(7- ability of your highest ability character on table). Search through your Used Pile and take one card into hand. Shuffle, Cut and replace.','A Jedi can adjust the force within and around an object, causing it to move as the Jedi wills.',NULL,'4_53'),(2927,5710,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Mace Windu (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/macewinduai.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','6','7','Deploys +3 to any location except Jedi Council Chamber. While at Jedi Council Chamber, immune to attrition and once during your control phase, if Amidala at a battleground site and Maul not on table, opponent loses 2 Force.','Senior Jedi Council member who maintains rigorous adherence to the Code. Sent Qui-Gon to Naboo to accompany the Queen and learn more about the mysterious \'dark warrior\'.',NULL,'12_14'),(2928,1124,'Light','C','Death Star II','Heavy Turbolaser Battery','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/heavyturbolaserbattery.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Starship','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 4 Force to deploy on your Star Cruiser. Adds 2 to power. May target a starship using 2 Force. Draw two destiny. Subtract 1 when targeting a capital starship. Otherwise, subtract 6. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.','Built to penetrate the armor of the toughest Star Destroyers. Cooling technology pilfered from the Empire.','Heavy Turbolaser Battery','9_89'),(2929,5077,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 4','•Graveyard Of Giants','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/graveyardofgiants.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Starships and vehicles just lost from Jakku locations are stacked here face down. Unless no cards here, if a player just Force drained on Jakku: that player may retrieve 1 Force (if they Force drained with a scavenger, may randomly retrieve instead), peek at cards stacked here, and then place one in owner\'s Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)','High-speed collisions are a constant danger during chaotic starfighter dogfights. Scanners can be jammed. Pilots rely on vision, increasing the chances of such accidents.',NULL,'204_14'),(2930,1071,'Light','C','Dagobah','Great Warrior','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/greatwarrior.gif?raw=true','Jedi Test #1',NULL,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a Dagobah site. Target a mentor here. Also, target or deploy (regardless of location deployment restrictions) an apprentice here. Attempt when targets are present at the beginning of your control phase. Draw training destiny. If destiny + apprentice\'s ability > 12, test completed: Place on apprentice. All opponent\'s Force drain bonuses are canceled.',NULL,NULL,'4_77'),(2931,5013,'Light','R1','Virtual Set 2','•Wedge Antilles (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Light/large/wedgeantilles.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','4','2','2','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting an [Independent] starfighter, it is maneuver +1 (+2 if Pulsar Skate) and Wedge draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. While with Booster or Mirax, your total battle destiny here is +1.','Highly decorated Corellian. Piloted Red 2 at the Battle of Yavin. A wealthy orphan, he bought a freighter with his inheritance. First joined the Alliance as a weapons smuggler.',NULL,'202_3'),(2932,1216,'Light','U','Endor','•I Hope She\'s All Right','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/ihopeshesallright.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your non-unique scouts are forfeit +1. During every draw phase, unless opponent\'s character of destiny < 4 occupies a battleground site, opponent loses 1 Force. Effect canceled unless your characters of destiny < 4 occupy two battleground sites.','\'I\'m afraid that Artoo\'s sensors can find no trace of Princess Leia.\'','Search And Destroy','8_38'),(2933,1107,'Light','R2','Virtual Set 0','•Han\'s Heavy Blaster Pistol (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/hansheavyblasterpistol.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Han (except TK-422), even as a \'react.\' May target a character or creature for free. Draw destiny. Target hit, its forfeit = 0, and opponent loses 1 Force if destiny +1 > defense value. Once during your control phase, may fire using 1 Force.','BlasTech DL-44 heavy pistol. Short range, but relatively powerful. Carries energy for 25 shots. Illegal or restricted on most systems.',NULL,'200_70'),(2934,1082,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Grondorn Muse','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/grondornmuse.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','3','5','While Grondorn is on Yavin 4, your Yavin Sentry is not unique (•), is doubled, deploys free, applies all three of its modifiers and is immune to Alter. Power -1 when not on Yavin 4.','Formerly belonged to the Corellian militia. Popular musician before the Empire blacklisted his songs for their political content. Joined the Alliance with his wife, Duriet.',NULL,'7_19'),(2935,5180,'Light','C','Virtual Set 7','•Jakku: Docking Bay','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/jakkudockingbay.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.',NULL,NULL,'207_16'),(2936,2871,'Light','R','Dagobah','•Yoda, You Seek Yoda','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/yodayouseekyoda.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Yoda is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve him from the Lost Pile. OR Use 3 Force to search through your Reserve Deck and take Yoda into your hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.','\'Take you to him I will.\'',NULL,'4_73'),(2937,1228,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•I\'ll Try Spinning','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/illtryspinning.gif?raw=true','Admiral\'s Order',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Landed starfighters and vehicles aboard starships are forfeit = 0. Once during your control phase may target your N-1 starfighter and opponent\'s starfighter present at same system. Both players draw destiny. You add your starfighter\'s power and maneuver. Opponent adds starfighter\'s power. Starship with lowest total is lost.',NULL,'The Deflector Shield Is Too Strong','14_1'),(2938,1422,'Light','C','Cloud City','Keep Your Eyes Open','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/keepyoureyesopen.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If a battle was just initiated where you have two smugglers, you may move any or all of your characters, vehicles and starships away (at normal use of the Force). OR Glance at the cards in any Lost Pile and replace unshuffled.','\'Look, don\'t worry. Everything\'s gonna be fine. Trust me.\'',NULL,'5_56'),(2939,2835,'Light','U','Endor','•Wuta','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/wuta.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','2','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each [Light Side Force] icon at