ile. (Immune to Alter.)','The guidance of experienced Jedi allowed Luke to confront Vader.',NULL,'7_81'),(2968,6586,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 10','Quite A Mercenary (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual10-Light/large/quiteamercenary.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Elis Helrot. (Immune to Sense) OR Cancel a smuggler\'s game text for remainder of turn. OR Take [Reflections II] Chewie or Mercenary Armor into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: During your move phase, \'break cover\' of an Undercover spy.\"','Smugglers and other rogues frequent spaceports along trade routes. \'Your friend is quite a mercenary. I wonder if he really cares about anything, or anybody.\'.',NULL,'210_24'),(2969,2916,'Light','C1','A New Hope','•Zutton','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/zutton.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','2','Where present, just before opponent draws battle destiny, you may use 1 Force to reduce opponent\'s total battle destiny by 1.','Snivvian also known as \'Snaggletooth.\' A tortured artist who, like most Snivvians, is driven to live out the stories he creates.',NULL,'2_24'),(2970,1807,'Light','PM','Enhanced Premiere','•Obi-Wan With Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedPremiere-Light/large/obiwanwithlightsaber.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','5','5','8','Permanent weapon is •Obi-Wan\'s Lightsaber (may target a character or creature for free; draw two destiny; target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value).','\'The Force will be with you... always.\'',NULL,'108_4'),(2971,4407,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Your Insight Serves You Well (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/yourinsightservesyouwell.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Scanning Cr