ocation. Also, if \'bantha\' droid is at a docking bay, adds immunity to attrition < 3 to all your starfighters at the related system and related sectors and may cancel Lateral Damage.','Unique treadwell droid cobbled together by Jawas. Now owned by the DeMaals, proprietors of Docking Bay 94. Nicknamed \'bantha\' for its slow and stubborn personality.','WED15-1662 \'Treadwell\' Droid','1_32'),(2980,6014,'Light','PM','Reflections III','We\'ll Handle This / Duel Of The Fates','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/wellhandlethis.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'We\'ll Handle This:Deploy Theed Palace Generator Core, Theed Palace Generator, and Inner Strength.{While} this side up, opponent may not Force drain where opponent has a Dark Jedi, and your Force drains at Naboo sites where you have a Jedi may not be canceled.  Once during your control phase, may target one opponent\'s character present with your Jedi at an interior Theed Palace site.  Target is lost.{Flip} this card if an opponent\'s Dark Jedi is present at an interior Naboo battleground site.Duel Of The Fates:{While} this side up, you may not Force drain or initiate battle at any location where you have a Jedi.  Once during your move phase, your Jedi may initiate lightsaber combat against an opponent\'s Dark Jedi present: Each player draws 2 destiny.  Loser (lowest total) loses 2 Force (cannot be reduced).  If difference is 5 or greater, lost Force must come from Reserve Deck, and losing character is lost.{Flip} this card and retrieve 1 Force if opponent has no Dark Jedi present at any interior Naboo battleground.',NULL,NULL,'13_46'),(2981,2666,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Ultimatum','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/ultimatum.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. While you occupy at least 3 battlegrounds or opponent occupies no battlegrounds, you lose no more than 2 Force from each Force drain or \'insert\' card.','\'Jabba! This is your last chance. Free us or die.\'','Resistance - Defensive Shield','13_44'),(2982,2861,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 0','•Yavin Sentry (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/yavinsentry.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Colo Claw Fish is canceled. Opponent must first use X Force to deploy a non-unique card (except a Jawa or Tusken Raider) to a location, where X = the number of copies of that card at that location.',NULL,NULL,'200_31'),(2983,2869,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Yoda, Master Of The Force','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/yodamasteroftheforce.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','4','3','4','7','Deploys only to Naboo or Coruscant. Once per game, may take a Sense, Control, or Alter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Your Jedi present are immune to attrition < 4 (or < 5 if a Jedi Council member). Immune to attrition.','Jedi Council Member. \'More to say have you?\'',NULL,'13_48'),(2984,1823,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Officer Ellberger','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/officerellberger.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anythings she pilots. While piloting Bravo 5 and at same system as a droid starfighter, adds one destiny to attrition only.','Computer systems troubleshooter whose sour past is not discussed by her squad mates. Years of experience enabled her to predict and adjust to droid starfighter tactics.',NULL,'14_21'),(2985,2773,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Weapon Of A Fallen Mentor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/weaponofafallenmentor.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If your non-[Permanent Weapon] lightsaber was just lost (or stolen) from a site, deploy on your character of ability > 4 at same site. Relocate that lightsaber to this character, who may use that lightsaber, and it may not be stolen. (Immune to Control.)','Darth Maul\'s complacency in what seemed like imminent victory over the Padawan was his downfall. That, and the lightsaber of Obi-Wan\'s fallen teacher.',NULL,'13_45'),(2986,2903,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Yoxgit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/yoxgit.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','Deploys free to a Cloud City or Jabba\'s Palace site. Power + 2 on Cloud City. During your control phase, may use 3 Force to search your Lost Pile and take one weapon or device into hand.','Male Ugnaught. Left Cloud City after the Empire took control. Works for Hermi Odle, helping to supply him with various weaponry. Hopes to someday return to Cloud City.',NULL,'6_47'),(2987,6041,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Yoda, Senior Council Member (AI)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/yodaseniorcouncilmemberai.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','3','4','7','Deploys only to Jedi Council Chamber. While at Jedi Council Chamber, you lose no Force from Dagobah: Cave and, during your move phase, may use 4 Force to relocate your other Jedi here to any site you occupy. Immune to attrition.','Senior Jedi Council member. Responsible for the early training of Obi-Wan Kenobi. When Qui-Gon brought Anakin before the Council, Yoda voted not to train the boy.',NULL,'12_36'),(2988,5925,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•Stolen First Order TIE Fighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/stolenfirstordertiefighter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: TIE/SF','2','2','2','4','May add Poe (or a spy) as a pilot and one passenger. Deploys free to opponent\'s system. While Poe piloting, maneuver +2. If Finn aboard, apply his ability towards drawing battle destiny.','Blank.',NULL,'204_34'),(2989,2557,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Theron Nett','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/theronnett.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Red 10 during battle, adds one destiny to total power only. When at Ord Mantell system, adds 1 to each of your Force drains there.','Experienced smuggler from Ord Mantell. Piloted Red 10 at the Battle of Yavin. Long-time wingman of Garven Dreis.',NULL,'7_46'),(2990,1415,'Light','U','Special Edition','Kashyyyk Operative','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/kashyyykoperative.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','1','3','While at a Kashyyyk site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is forfeit +1 (and power +1 if your Wookiee is on Kashyyyk) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Kashyyyk from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.','Following the subjugation of Kashyyyk by the Empire, the Alliance hired merchants to \'purchase\' Wookiee slaves to be freed.','Kashyyyk Operative','7_24'),(2991,5149,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 6','•Jyn Erso','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual6-Light/large/jynerso.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','4','4','5','May deploy to a site as an Undercover spy. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. If just lost, may peek at opponent\'s hand.','Female Spy.',NULL,'206_4'),(2992,2750,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•We Didn\'t Hit It','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/wedidnthitit.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your Force generation is +1 at systems you control. Opponent\'s non-unique starfighters are deploy +1 (or +2 to a system you occupy). (Immune to Alter.)','When severely outnumbered by opponents, any help is good help.',NULL,'14_38'),(2993,5224,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 8','•Young Skywalker','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/youngskywalker.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','6','6','9','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. If drawn for weapon or battle destiny, may take into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny. Power +1 for each Dark Jedi here. During your control phase, unless a Dark Jedi at a battleground, may retrieve 1 Force. Immune to attrition < 6.','\'I\'ve taken care of everything.\'',NULL,NULL),(2994,2801,'Light','U','Tatooine','•What Was It?','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/whatwasit.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated a duel against one of your non-captive Jedi, deploy on that Jedi. Cancel the duel and relocate this Jedi to an adjacent site. Your duel destiny draws are each +1. (Immune to Control.)','When Qui-Gon got away, Maul knew it would only be a matter of time until the two of them would meet again.',NULL,'11_23'),(2995,6021,'Light','C','Virtual Set 11','•Where\'s Han?','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/whereshan.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Take Han\'s Dice or non-[Maintenance] Han into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. LOST: If you just lost a gambler, take that gambler into hand. OR Once per game, exchange a card in hand with a Resistance Agent or [Episode VII] Skywalker in Lost Pile.\"','Blank.',NULL,'211_50'),(2996,2845,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Yarna d\'al\' Gargan','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/yarnadalgargan.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. While you have fewer than 13 cards in hand, your non-unique cards in hand (except Effects of any kind and Interrupts) are immune to Monnok. (Immune to Alter while you occupy two battlegrounds).','Female dancer from Askajia. Very protective mother. Makes sure that all those she cares about are protected.','Well Guarded','6_59'),(2997,2777,'Light','C','Virtual Set 0','•Weapons Display (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/weaponsdisplay.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Whenever opponent excludes any character(s) from battle, they lose 2 Force. At end of opponent\'s turn, if you control two battlegrounds (a site and a system) and opponent deployed a card with ability and did not inititate a battle, may retrieve 1 Force.','The X-wing\'s display panel allows for different firing patterns for different weapons. This gives the pilot the ability to switch weapon types with minimum time and energy loss.','Firepower (V)','200_30'),(2998,2646,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Tusken Breath Mask','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/tuskenbreathmask.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any Tatooine site where you have just won a battle. Target one of your characters not at Tatooine. Upon reaching, target takes mask. While on Tatooine, target\'s power and forfeit are +2 and has immunity to attrition of exactly 3.','Sand People use a special mask to reclaim exhaled moisture in the hot, harsh environment of Tatooine. Protects by filtering blowing sand and dispersing excess heat.',NULL,'1_67'),(2999,2883,'Light','R','Death Star II','You Must Confront Vader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/youmustconfrontvader.gif?raw=true','Jedi Test #6',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table.  Target a Skywalker who has completed Jedi Test #5.  While target on Dagobah, \'move phase\' on Save You It Can may be treated as \'deploy phase.\'  Until Jedi Test completed, battles you initiate at Vader\'s site are canceled and opponent loses 2 Force at start of your turn unless Vader is at a battleground site.  Attempt during your move phase when Vader with target (even as a non-frozen captive).  Vader and target duel: Each player draws destiny.  Add ability.  Highest total wins.  If target wins, test completed:  Leave on table.  Add one battle destiny in every battle.  Also, target is immune to attrition < 5.',NULL,NULL,'9_55'),(3000,2545,'Light','C','Death Star II','•The Time For Our Attack Has Come','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/thetimeforourattackhascome.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you just initiated a second battle this turn, deploy on table. When you lose a battle, you may place Immediate Effect in Used Pile to cancel all battle damage against you, unless Draw Their Fire on table. (Immune to Control.)','\'With the Imperial Fleet spread throughout the galaxy in a vain effort to engage us, it is relatively unprotected.\'',NULL,'9_44'),(3001,2779,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Weather Vane','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/weathervane.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table.  Any character here may be captured or rescued by a player\'s starship or vehicle controlling Cloud City during that player\'s control phase.  Character here lost if new character arrives.  Effect lost if Cloud City lost. (Immune to Alter.)','The metal rods extending from the bottom of Cloud City are part of the city\'s flotation system. Sensors detect the velocity of wind and the content of local clouds.','Weather Vane','5_30'),(3002,5972,'Light','R','Death Star II','There Is Good In Him / I Can Save Him','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/thereisgoodinhim.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'There Is Good In Him:Deploy Chief Chirpa\'s Hut (with [Death Star II] Luke and Luke\'s Lightsaber there), Endor: Landing Platform and I Feel The Conflict.For remainder of game, you may not play Alter, Strangle, or Captive Fury.{While} this side up, your Force generation is +2 at Luke\'s site. While an Imperial is at Landing Platform, you may not Force drain or generate Force at Luke\'s location. When any Imperial is at Luke\'s site, Luke is captured (seized by an Imperial, if possible, even if not a warrior).{Flip} this card if Luke captured.I Can Save Him:{While} this side up, at end of each of opponent\'s turns, opponent loses 2 Force unless Vader is escorting Luke. At any time, an Imperial escorting Luke may transfer Luke to Vader, if present with Vader. Vader may not transfer Luke. Once during each of your turns, if Vader present with Luke (even as a non-frozen captive), may shuffle Reserve Deck and draw destiny. If destiny > 14, Vader crosses to Light Side, totally depleting opponent\'s Life Force.{Flip} if Luke neither present with Vader nor a captive.',NULL,NULL,'9_61'),(3003,4093,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Wedge In Red Squadron 1','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/wedgeinredsquadron1.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: X-Wing','2','6','4','6','Permanent pilot is •Wedge, who provides ability of 3. During a battle with opponent\'s [Independent Starship] starship, may add one destiny to total power or attrition. Immune to Come With Me, Tallon Roll, and attrition < 4.','Flown by Wedge Antilles as Red 2 at the Battle of Yavin. Redesignated at Endor. Rugged Incom fighter. Victory markers show its role in the attack on the first Death Star.',NULL,'200_67'),(3004,1842,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Oola','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/oola.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','1','2','3','During your control phase, may cause opponent to reveal entire hand by using X Force, where X = number of cards in opponent\'s hand. All unique (•) male Imperials or unique (•) male aliens there are placed in opponent\'s Used Pile.','Female Twi\'lek musician. Became a dancer to live a life of luxury. Has worked for Jabba for only two days. Desperate to escape.','M\'iiyoom Onith','6_29'),(3005,2752,'Light','R','Dagobah','We Don\'t Need Their Scum','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/wedontneedtheirscum.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel Res Luk Ra\'auf.  LOST: If two bounty hunters (or an Imperial and a bounty hunter) are in a battle together, use 2 Force to draw two destiny. Subtract total from opponent\'s attrition and total power (cannot fall below zero).\"','Bounty Hunters. Independent contractors. Highly competitive loners. Powerful. Deadly. Scum.',NULL,'4_70'),(3006,1638,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Mandalorian Mishap','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/mandalorianmishap.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Boba Fett is defending a battle, draw one battle destiny. Subtract that amount from opponent\'s attrition and total power (cannot fall below zero). OR Cancel, for the remainder of the turn, the game text of Jet Pack or any weapon that may fire repeatedly.','Most space-faring adventurers meet their fate with a calm, quiet dignity.',NULL,'6_71'),(3007,2904,'Light','C','Endor','YT-1300 Transport','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/yt1300transport.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified Light Freighter','3','2','3','5','May add 1 pilot, 2 passengers and 1 vehicle. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Quad Laser Cannon and Surface Defense Cannon may deploy (and fire free) aboard.','Reliable and durable. Widely used freighter made by Corellian Engineering Corporation. Sales have dramatically increased in proportion to the fame of Han Solo\'s ship.',NULL,'8_80'),(3008,2891,'Light','U','Tatooine','•You\'ll Find I\'m Full Of Surprises','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/youllfindimfullofsurprises.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke and Vader present at same site, use 1 Force to initiate a duel between them. Either is power +2 if armed with a lightsaber. Draw destiny. Opponent draws two destiny. Both players add power. Loser is placed out of play.','Even though he wasn\'t fully prepared to face the Dark Lord of the Sith, Luke rushed to save his friends.',NULL,'11_41'),(3009,2671,'Light','U1','Hoth','Under Attack','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/underattack.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your control phase, target a vehicle with armor present with your warrior. Draw destiny. If warrior has a Concussion Grenade or a lightsaber, add 3 to destiny draw (7 if both). Vehicle (and grenade) lost if total destiny > armor.','With the Rebels\' limited resources and small numbers, desperate strategies are often required.',NULL,'3_50'),(3010,5053,'Light','U','Virtual Set 3','•Wild Karrde','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual3-Light/large/wildkarrde.gif?raw=true','Starship','Capital: Modified Action VI Freighter','2','3','5','6','May add 3 pilots and 6 passengers. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. During battle, your total battle destiny is +1 for each smuggler aboard. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. Immune to attrition < 5.','Blank.',NULL,'203_21'),(3011,6787,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Your Ship? (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/yourship.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Cancels A Dangerous Time. Each player may play only one card with \'sabacc\' in title each