it +2 when present with a Rebel leader.','Elite troop force assigned to Massassi Base in the jungles of Yavin 4. Responsible for monitoring the perimeter of the Rebel outpost.',NULL,'7_51'),(3038,2592,'Light','C','Cloud City','Tibanna Gas Miner','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/tibannagasminer.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','2','When at a site, adds 1 to your Force drains at related cloud sectors. Also, during your activate phase, if at a Cloud City site and you control Bespin: Cloud City, may cumulatively activate 1 Force for every cloud sector on Bespin.','Long-time Cloud City resident Willrow Hood. Employed by a mining company which is sympathetic to the Rebels and sells them Tibanna gas at a discount.','Tibanna Gas Miner','5_8'),(3039,2909,'Light','PM','Enhanced Cloud City','•••Z-95 Bespin Defense Fighter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/EnhancedCloudCity-Light/large/z95bespindefensefighter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Modified Z-95 Headhunter','2','2','2','3','Permanent pilot provides ability of 1 and adds 1 to power. May add one alien pilot (suspends permanent pilot). Power +2 at Bespin locations. May be carried aboard starships like a vehicle.','Used to combat pirate activity in and around Cloud City. Top speed in atmosphere 1,150 kph. Hyperdrive installed by Bespin Motors.',NULL,'109_5'),(3040,1491,'Light','PM','Jedi Pack','•Leia','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JediPack-Light/large/leia.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','2','4','3','<none>','Adopted daughter of the Viceroy and First Chairman of Alderaan. Became a political leader at a young age. The injustices of the New Order led her to join the Rebellion.',NULL,'102_3'),(3041,2881,'Light','R1','Hoth','You Have Failed Me For The Last Time','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/youhavefailedmeforthelas