 4 passengers. Deploy and move only at interior mobile sites. May move without presence aboard. Also, may move as a \'react\' only to a battle or Force drain (if within range).','System of enclosed high-speed vertical and horizontal transport cylinders. Used in space stations, large starships, Death Stars, etc.','Lift Tube','1_148'),(3060,2856,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Yavin 4: Massassi Headquarters','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/yavin4massassiheadquarters.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : May not be separated from interior Yavin 4 sites. If you control, Attack Run total is +2.',NULL,NULL,'7_134'),(3061,1829,'Light','R','Special Edition','Old Times','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/oldtimes.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If Luke and Biggs are defending a battle together (or are in any battle together at Tatooine), add one battle destiny. OR If Luke and Biggs are making an Attack Run, add one battle destiny to your Attack Run total.','\'I\'ll be right up there with you! And, have I got stories to tell you...\'',NULL,'7_95'),(3062,4074,'Light','R','Virtual Set 0','•Master Qui-Gon (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/masterquigon.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','6','7','7','Deploys -1 to [Episode I] locations. If you just lost Force from an opponent\'s Effect, may take an [Episode I] Interrupt (except Control) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle, or place a card from hand under Credits Will Do Fine. May not be Disarmed. Immune to You Are Beaten and attrition.','Jedi Master currently not on the Council. Although he serves the Council well, there have been times when he has defied their wishes to pursue a path he believes is right.',NULL,'200_22'),(3063,1755,'Light','C2','Premiere','Narrow Escape','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/narrowescape.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If opponent just initiated battle at a site where you have a Rebel of ability > 2 present, move all of your cards with ability there away (using their landspeed).','Blast doors seal off compartments during battles, hull ruptures or as security measures. Thick doors repel blaster rifle shots.',NULL,'1_98'),(3064,1666,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Melas','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/melas.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','2','3','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Power +2 under \'nighttime conditions.\' Immune to attrition < X, where X = number of your aliens present (including himself).','Sarkan smuggler. Smokes an Essoomian gruu pipe to heighten awareness. Exiled from his home planet of Sarka for displaying curiosity in other aliens. Misses his homeworld.',NULL,'7_32'),(3065,1733,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Naboo: Boss Nass\' Chambers','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/naboobossnassschambers.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Once per game may take Boss Nass into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',NULL,NULL,'14_49'),(3066,1768,'Light','C','Dagobah','•Never Tell Me The Odds','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/nevertellmetheodds.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Insert in opponent\'s Reserve Deck. When Effect reaches top it is lost and up to the three lowest destiny numbers of each player\'s characters on table are totaled. Player with lower total loses Force equal to the difference. (Immune to Alter.)','\'You said you wanted to be around when I made a mistake, well, this could be it, sweetheart.\'','3,720 To 1','4_27'),(3067,2900,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Your Insight Serves You Well & •Staging Areas','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/yourinsightservesyouwell&stagingareas.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your Force generation is +1 at each docking bay you occupy. Opponent\'s Dark Jedi are defense value -1. Scanning Crew and 3,720 to 1 are canceled. You may place Effect in Lost Pile to take one [Endor] or [Death Star II] Effect that deploys for free into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',NULL,'You Cannot Hide Forever & Mobilization Points','12_51'),(3068,5736,'Light','U','Virtual Set 11','•Maz\'s Castle: Hidden Recess','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/mazscastlehiddenrecess.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Once per game, if you control, may retrieve a weapon or device into hand.',NULL,NULL,'211_39'),(3069,1867,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Ounee Ta','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/ouneeta.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. At each opponent\'s <> site, your Rebels are each deploy -2 and your Force generation is +1.','Jabba\'s decadent behavior makes him susceptible to deception. Leia and Lando exploited this weakness, posing as Jabba\'s kind of scum.',NULL,'13_37'),(3070,2910,'Light','PM','Official Tournament Sealed Deck','Z-95 Headhunter','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/OfficialTournamentSealedDeck-Light/large/z95headhunter.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Z-95 Headhunter','3','2','2','2','Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1. Power and Maneuver +2 at non-unique cloud sectors. May be carried aboard starships like a vehicle.','Developed by Incom/Subpro. Atmospheric fighter adapted for space travel. AF-4 version refitted with Incom 2a fission engines and two Taim & Bak KX5 laser cannons.',NULL,'106_9'),(3071,1797,'Ligh