 property. Well traveled and skilled in many languages.','Swilla Corey','2_36'),(3075,5014,'Light','U','Virtual Set 2','•Yoda, Keeper Of The Peace','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual2-Light/large/yodakeeperofthepeace.gif?raw=true','Character','Jedi Master','1','3','5','7','Deploys -1 to Coruscant. May lose 1 Force to cancel Force Lightning targeting your character present. Neither player may draw more than one battle destiny here (those destiny draws may not be modified or canceled). Immune to attrition.','Yoda calls upon the Force often to try and foresee what destiny has in store.',NULL,'202_4'),(3076,2911,'Light','R2','Hoth','•Zev Senesca','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/zevsenesca.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','2','2','4','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Rogue 2, also adds 3 to maneuver and may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Born on Kestic Station near the Bestine system. Daring pilot who can fly anything. Found Luke and Han in the Hoth wasteland. Piloted Rogue 2 at the Battle of Hoth.',NULL,'3_27'),(3077,5237,'Light','U2','Virtual Set 8','•Yavin 4: Massassi War Room (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/yavin4massassiwarroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Once per game, may deploy a Rebel leader here from Reserve deck; reshuffle.',NULL,NULL,'208_24'),(3078,2714,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','Vibro-Ax','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/vibroax.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 3 Force to deploy on any alien warrior. Adds 1 to power. May target a character using 1 Force. Both players draw destiny. Target immediately excluded from battle if warrior\'s power + your destiny > target\'s power + opponent\'s destiny.','Vibrating blade powered by an energy cell hidden within the shaft. Used by many moisture farmers to prod banthas and other animals.','Vibro-Ax','6_90'),(3079,1597,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Luke Skywalker, Rebel Scout (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/lukeskywalkerrebelscout.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','6','6','7','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys -2 to a forest. Luke\'s weapon destiny draws are +1. At same site, opponent must first use 1 Force to fire a weapon. During opponent\'s draw phase, if alone on Endor, may retrieve 1 Force. Immune to attrition < 5.','Resourceful scout and member of the Rebel infiltration team assembled to destroy the shield generator. Surrendered to his father so that he would not endanger the mission.',NULL,'200_21'),(3080,1402,'Light','R1','Premiere','•K\'lor\'slug','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/klorslug.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on your side of table. For each unit of ability you have present during a battle, you may use 1 Force to raise your total power by 1. Ability used in this way cannot also be used to draw destiny.','Dejarik hologram of venomous swamp creature from Noe\'ha\'on. Keen senses of smell and vision. Dangerous hunter. Lays eggs - hundreds of ravenously hungry hatchlings.','Molator','1_53'),(3081,6032,'Light','C2','Virtual Set 11','•Yavin 4 (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/yavin4.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If Haven is canceled, place it in your Used Pile.',NULL,NULL,'211_32'),(3082,1564,'Light','U','Special Edition','•Local Defense','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/localdefense.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take one cloud car or [Independent] starship into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If opponent just initiated a battle at a sector where none of your ability comes from Rebels or Rebel starships, add one battle destiny.','Even seasoned smugglers respect a well-planned, well-armed defense.',NULL,'7_94'),(3083,1523,'Light','U','Theed Palace','•Lieutenant Chamberlyn','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/lieutenantchamberlyn.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','4','3','5','Deploys -1 to Naboo. Once per game may deploy a blaster on Chamberlyn from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once during your control phase, may target a battle droid present and draw destiny. If destiny > 3, target lost.','Royal Naboo security officer who became a leader of the underground movement against the Trade Federation. Known for discovering and analyzing battle droid weaknesses.',NULL,'14_16'),(3084,1509,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Let\'s Go Left','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/letsgoleft.gif?raw=true','Admiral\'s Order',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Non-pilot characters aboard starships are forfeit -4. Whenever a player\'s starship is \'hit\', that player loses 1 Force (2 if starship was hit by Proton Torpedoes). At systems where you have only [Republic] starships, all of those starships are immune to attrition < 4. At sites related to a system you occupy, your battle destinies may not be canceled by opponent.',NULL,'Nothing Can Get Through Our Shield','14_2'),(3085,1607,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Luke\'s Lightsaber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/lukeslightsaber.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Luke. Adds 1 to defense value and training destiny. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character, creature, speeder bike, or swoop for free. Draw 2 destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0 if total destiny > defense value.','Weapon of a truly powerful warrior. Constructed by Luke as part of his training.',NULL,'9_90'),(3086,6004,'Light','PM','Reflections II','Watch Your Step / This Place Can Be A Little Rough','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsII-Light/large/watchyourstep.gif?raw=true','Objective',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Watch Your Step:Deploy Cantina, Docking Bay 94 and Tatooine System.{For} remainder of game, opponent activates no Force at your Cantina. Your cards with ability are deploy +6 except Luke, smugglers, freighters, and [Independent] starships. Opponent\'s game text on Kessel is canceled.{While} this side up, once during each of your deploy phases, may take Corellia or Kessel into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.{Flip} this card if you occupy two battlegrounds with smugglers or have completed two Kessel Runs.This Place Can Be A Little Rough:{While} this side up, your Force generation is +1 at each system you control with a smuggler. Opponent\'s Force generation at non-battleground locations is limited to 1. When you have two or more smugglers in a battle, add one battle destiny. Each of your smugglers is forfeit +2. Once during each turn, may play one interrupt from Lost Pile as if from hand (then place that card out of play). Sense, Alter, and Keep Your Eyes Open may not be played.{Flip} this card if you do not occupy two battlegrounds (unless you have completed two Kessel Runs).',NULL,NULL,'10_26'),(3087,2858,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Yavin 4: Massassi Throne Room','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/yavin4massassithroneroom.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If this is your starting location, Light Side goes first in game.',NULL,NULL,'1_138'),(3088,1820,'Light','U','Coruscant','•Odin Nesloor','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/odinnesloor.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'During your move phase, target any or all of your characters at one exterior site to \'transport\' (relocate) to another exterior site. Draw destiny. Use that much Force to \'transport,\' or place Interrupt in Lost Pile.','Odin\'s family mysteriously disappeared during a hyperspace jump. He scours the galaxy for information on them, and his best lead has brought him to Tatooine.','Lana Dobreed','12_65'),(3089,1224,'Light','U','Endor','•I Wonder Who They Found','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/iwonderwhotheyfound.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Han or your war room. Once during each of your deploy phases, may take one That\'s One, Count Me In or I\'m With You Too into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While Han is at an exterior battleground site, he is immune to attrition < 4.','\'General Solo, is your strike team assembled?\'',NULL,'8_39'),(3090,1571,'Light','U','Tatooine','•Loci Rosen','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/locirosen.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','0','4','2','Power +X in a battle at a site, where X equals the number of cards in opponent\'s hand. During your deploy phase, opponent may place any number of cards in their hand in their Used Pile.','Good-willed Mon Calamari merchant. Looking for work. Unfortunately, everywhere he goes he comes up empty handed.',NULL,'11_5'),(3091,1261,'Light','R','Special Edition','Imperial Atrocity','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/imperialatrocity.gif?raw=true','Effect','Immediate','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you occupy at least two battlegrounds and just lost more than 2 Force to a Force drain at a location, deploy on that location (limit one per Force drain). Opponent loses 2 Force for each Imperial Atrocity on table.','The Empire\'s ruthless tactics at times unintentionally create support for the cause of the Rebel Alliance.','Imperial Propaganda','7_65'),(3092,1205,'Light','R','Tatooine','•I Did It!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/ididit.gif?raw=true','Epic Event',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table if you\'ve won a Podrace. Once per game, may place Boonta Eve Podrace out of play to retrieve 4 Force. If you occupy a battleground site and a battleground system, once during each of your control phases may reveal the bottom card of your Lost Pile and place it on top of your Force Pile. At the end of opponent\'s turn opponent must lose 2 Force or place their Force Pile onto their Used Pile.',NULL,NULL,'11_25'),(3093,1749,'Light','U2','Premiere','Nabrun Leids','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/nabrunleids.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'At any time (except during battle), target any or all of your characters at one site to \'transport\' (relocate) to any one other site. Draw destiny. Use that much Force to \'transport,\' or place Interrupt in Lost Pile.','Four-armed smuggler and pilot for hire. A Morseerian male. Breathes methane. Former fighter pilot. He can take you anywhere for the right price.','Elis Helrot','1_97'),(3094,4112,'Light','U','Virtual Set 1','•We\'ll Take The Long Way','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/welltakethelongway.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If We Have A Plan on table, deploy on table. Imperials deploy +1 to Theed Palace Throne Room and, while you occupy that site, you may ignore your Objective\'s location deployment restrictions. Once per game, may take an [Episode I] system and/or a [Theed Palace] leader into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Actions borne of the love of one\'s planet can heavily outweigh those generated from simple battle orders.',NULL,'201_10'),(3095,1227,'Light','R','Death Star II','•I\'ll Take The Leader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/illtaketheleader.gif?raw=true','Admiral\'s Order',NULL,'6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Unique (•) starfighters without permanent pilots are immune to attrition < 4 (or add 2 to immunity if starfighter already has immunity). Starships without pilot characters aboard are power -2. At docking bays related to systems you occupy, your Force drains are +1. Once per turn, your starfighter just lost from a system may be relocated to a related docking bay.',NULL,'Fighters Coming In','9_4'),(3096,1165,'Light','C2','Hoth','Hoth Survival Gear','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/hothsurvivalgear.gif?raw=true','Device',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on any Rebel or warrior. While on Hoth, that character is power and forfeit +1 and is immune to Frostbite, Exposure and Ice Storm.','Cold-weather gear worn and carried by Echo Base troops. Enhances their ability to function and survive in Hoth\'s hostile environment.',NULL,'3_30'),(3097,5226,'Light','R','Virtual Set 8','•Luke\'s Blaster Pistol (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual8-Light/large/lukesblasterpistol.gif?raw=true','Weapon','Character','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on non-Jedi Luke. May target a character for free. Target loses any immunity to attrition for remainder of turn. Draw destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if destiny +2 > defense value. If about to be lost, may lose 1 Force to place on bottom of Used Pile.','Merr-Sonn Model 57. Part of an arms lot purchased for the Alliance from a black market dealer on Ord Mantell. Carried by Luke as a backup for his father\'s lightsaber.',NULL,'208_29'),(3098,1610,'Light','U','Endor','•Lumat','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/lumat.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','0','1','1','Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. When on Endor, adds 1 to total weapon destiny whenever you have any Ewok using an Ewok weapon at an Endor site.','Ewok archer. Wood carver. Tribal elder that advises Chief Chirpa. Crafts and maintains weapons.',NULL,'8_21'),(3099,1098,'Light','R1','Premiere','•Han Solo','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/hansolo.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','1','3','3','6','Once during battle, may use 1 Force to cancel and re-draw your just drawn destiny. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Falcon, also adds 2 to maneuver and may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.','Smuggler, gambler and \'freelance law-bender.\' Crafty Corellian pirate. Rebel hero. Owns Millennium Falcon. Co-pilot Chewbacca promised him \'life-debt.\' Has bounty on head.',NULL,'1_11'),(3100,1331,'Light','C2','Premiere','It Could Be Worse','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/itcouldbeworse.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If you must lose Force for any reason, reduce the loss by X amount by using X Force.','After escaping Detention Block AA-23. Rebels found themselves in the trash compactor. Leia point out, \'It could be worse.\' It soon was.',NULL,'1_90'),(3101,1095,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Han (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual0-Light/large/han.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','4','3','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Force retrieval with Or Be Destroyed is immune to Secret Plans. While armed with a blaster, Han is defense value +2. While Or Be Destroyed on table, immune to attrition < Han\'s power.','Corellian. Graduated with honors from the Imperial Academy. Dishonorably discharged. Wanders the galaxy building a reputation as a gambler and a hot-shot pilot.',NULL,'200_14'),(3102,1627,'Light','U','Death Star II','•Major Olander Brit','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/majorolanderbrit.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','3','2','2','3','Power and forfeit +1 while present with Major Panno. When with Major Panno at a site, adds one battle destiny. When present with a Scomplink, cancels Counter Assault at a related site where you have a spy or scout.','Communications expert. Staff monitors entire spectrum of electromagnetic signals. Politically minded. Followed Panno to the Alliance.',NULL,'9_26'),(3103,2811,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Wioslea','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/wioslea.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','5','2','1','2','During your control phase, may use 1 Force to target an opponent\'s unoccupied transport vehicle or droid present. Draw destiny. If destiny > target\'s destiny number, use Force equal to target\'s deploy cost to \'purchase\' target (use as if stolen).','Bought Luke\'s landspeeder for Spaceport Speeders. A Vuvrian female. Gambler who owes Jabba 1,000 credits in wagering debts. Speaks many languages.',NULL,'1_33'),(3104,2787,'Light','R','Death Star II','•Wedge Antilles, Red Squadron Leader','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/DeathStarII-Light/large/wedgeantillesredsquadronleader.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','3','3','6','Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots.  When piloting, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise (if Red 2, also adds 2 to maneuver).  When in battle with another Red or Rogue squadron pilot, once per battle may cancel one battle destiny just drawn.','Corellian commander and leader of Rogue Squadron. Chose to have Rogue Squadron relaim the designation \'Red Squadron\' at the battle of Endor.',NULL,'9_31'),(3105,5169,'Light','U1','Virtual Set 7','•Major Caluan Ematt','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/majorcaluanematt.gif?raw=true','Character','Resistance','2','4','4','5','May deploy -2 as a react to an [Episode VII] site. At the end of each turn, you must use 2 Force, lose 2 Force, or return Ematt to your hand.',NULL,NULL,'207_7'),(3106,1764,'Light','U','Tatooine','•Neck And Neck','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Tatooine-Light/large/neckandneck.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If difference between opponent\'s and your highest race totals < 4, lose 1 Force. Opponent draws no race destiny next control phase. OR If both players have < 10 Life Force remaining, both players retrieve 4 Force.','When Anakin had finally caught up with Sebulba, he knew he needed to make some kind of a move to break away from the Dug and win the race.',NULL,'11_38'),(3107,2873,'Light','U','Dagobah','•Yoda\'s Hope','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/yodashope.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on a character. When on the mentor, adds 1 to training destiny draws. If on Yoda, you may lose Effect to search your Reserve Deck and take into hand one card with \'levitation\' in the title. Shuffle, cut and replace.','\'You must feel the Force around you. Here, between you, me, the tree, the rock, everywhere! Yes, even between the land and the ship.\'',NULL,'4_44'),(3108,6048,'Light','PM','Virtual Set 0','•Your Insight Serves You Well (Death Star II) (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ResetDS-Light/large/yourinsightservesyouwellv.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Plays on table. Scanning Crew is canceled. If an \'insert\' card was just inserted or revealed, it is canceled. You lose no Force to Boonta Eve Podrace. While you occupy three battlegrounds, Watto\'s Box is suspended.','Luke knew that while the dark side was quicker and more seductive, eventually evil would turn on itself.',NULL,'13_49'),(3109,5640,'Light','C','Virtual Set 11','•Kamino','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual11-Light/large/kamino.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : Once per turn, may use 1 Force to deploy a Kamino site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',NULL,NULL,'211_43'),(3110,1674,'Light','U1','A New Hope','M-HYD \'Binary\' Droid','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ANewHope-Light/large/mhydbinarydroid.gif?raw=true','Character','Droid','2','2','3','5','Adds 2 to forfeit of each non-droid character at same and adjacent sites. At any time, any player may use 1 Force to turn M-HYD off (face down) or on again (face up).','Pretentious hydroponics droid. Specializes in working with binary load lifters and vaporators. Proficient in a number of languages but prefers to converse only in binary.',NULL,'2_12'),(3111,1429,'Light','R2','Premiere','•Kessel Run','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/kesselrun.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on Kessel. Target one of your smugglers at another system. X=parsec distance between the two systems. When target reaches Kessel, opponent draws destiny. If = 0, starship lost. Otherwise, by returning to first system, \'retrieve\' X Lost Force.','Planet Kessel has infamous glitterstim spice mines attracting smugglers and pirates. A \'Kessel run\' is a long, dangerous hyper-route they must travel quickly.',NULL,'1_52'),(3112,1435,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Kiffex','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/kiffex.gif?raw=true','Location','System','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you occupy with exactly 2 starships, your total power here is +2 and Vul Tazaene anywhere is doubled.',NULL,'Kiffex','6_83'),(3113,1339,'Light','C','Jabba\'s Palace','•••Ithorian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/ithorian.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','2','Power and forfeit +2 while Momaw Nadon at Audience Chamber. While at any jungle, swamp, forest or exterior Endor site, adds one [Dark Side Force] icon and one [Light Side Force] icon. Prevents [Selective Creature] creatures from attacking where present.','Good natured, optimistic herders from Ithor. Plant trees and reforest areas. Sided with Rebellion at great risk to their home planet.',NULL,'6_20'),(3114,1388,'Light','R','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jedi Mind Trick','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/jedimindtrick.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel a Force drain at a site if Luke is at an adjacent site.  LOST: If your character of ability > 4 is present with an opponent\'s leader, release a captive from a related prison (canceled if opponent loses 2 Force).\"','\'You will bring Captain Solo and the Wookiee to me.\'',NULL,'6_68'),(3115,5173,'Light','C','Virtual Set 7','•They\'re Tracking Us (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual7-Light/large/theyretrackingus.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cancel Program Trap; droid it was deployed on may taken into owner\'s hand (Immune to Sense.) OR Add or subtract 1 from opponent\'s just drawn destiny. OR Activate 1 Force.','\'Not this ship, sister.\'','A Dark Time For The Rebellion (V)','207_14'),(3116,1318,'Light','R','Coruscant','•Insurrection & •Aim High','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Coruscant-Light/large/insurrection&aimhigh.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Unique (•) Rebels of ability < 3 are forfeit +1. Nabrun Leids and Elis Helrot are limited to owner\'s move phase and exterior sites only. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. When opponent retrieves X cards, opponent must first use X Force or that retrieval is canceled. (Immune to Alter.)',NULL,'Imperial Arrest Order & Secret Plans','12_44'),(3117,2907,'Light','C2','Premiere','Y-wing','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/ywing.gif?raw=true','Starship','Starfighter: Y-Wing','3','2','1','2','May add 1 pilot or passenger. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.','Rugged Rebel Alliance fighter. BTL-S3 has room for a second pilot to assist weapons operations. 16 meters long. Built by Koensayr.',NULL,'1_147'),(3118,1466,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Lando Calrissian','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/landocalrissian.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','2','3','6','Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if piloting Falcon). Power +1 for every Cloud City location you control. When playing Sabacc, may add 1 to or subtract 1 from your total.','Gambler. Scoundrel. Former owner of the Millennium Falcon. Despite a notorious past, has become a successful chief administrator of a Tibanna gas mining facility.','Lando Calrissian','5_5'),(3119,2836,'Light','U2','Hoth','•Wyron Serper','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Hoth-Light/large/wyronserper.gif?raw=true','Character','Rebel','2','1','2','3','Once during each of your control phases, may peek at X cards randomly selected from opponent\'s hand, where X = number of [Dark Side Force] icons at same site. Also, when you are drawing destiny, adds 2 to the destiny of any card with \'scan\' in the title.','Rebel spy. Served undercover as a sensor specialist aboard the Star Destroyer Avenger. Assigned to scan for Imperial ships through the meteor activity of the Hoth system.',NULL,'3_26'),(3120,5076,'Light','C','Virtual Set 4','•We\'re Leaving (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/wereleaving.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Once per game, may stack the top card of your Lost Pile beneath Credits Will Do Fine. May examine cards stacked beneath Credits Will Do Fine and place any two in owner\'s Lost Pile to take a starship into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle (or retrieve into hand).','Qui-Gon realized that sometimes it\'s best to just leave, before any more damage is done.',NULL,'204_15'),(3121,1317,'Light','U','Endor','•Insurrection','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/insurrection.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Unique (•) Rebels of ability < 3 are forfeit +2. Nabrun Leids and Elis Helrot are limited to owner\'s move phase and exterior sites. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)','Rebel insurgents and local activists are the first step in breaking the Imperial stranglehold on a world.','Imperial Arrest Order','8_40'),(3122,2808,'Light','R','Endor','•Wicket','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Endor-Light/large/wicket.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','3','2','Deploys only on Endor.  Power and forfeit +1 for each [Light Side Force] icon at same Endor site.  When in battle, may target one opponent\'s character present.  Draw destiny.  Target excluded from battle if destiny > ability.','Ewok scout. Son of Shodu and Deej. Found Leia and befriended her. Persuaded his tribe to help.',NULL,'8_32'),(3123,2806,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•Whoooo!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/whoooo.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Take a unique (•) N-1 starfighter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If a battle was just initiated at a system where opponent has a droid starfighter, all droid starfighters at that system are power -1 for remainder of turn.','\'Look! One of ours, out of the main hold!\'',NULL,'14_47'),(3124,1354,'Light','U','Jabba\'s Palace','•Jabba\'s Palace: Audience Chamber','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/JabbasPalace-Light/large/jabbaspalaceaudiencechamber.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : If you control, Scum And Villainy is canceled. May deploy Bo Shuda from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',NULL,'Jabba\'s Palace: Audience Chamber','6_81'),(3125,2860,'Light','U2','Premiere','•Yavin Sentry','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/yavinsentry.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Use 2 Force to deploy at any Yavin 4 site. Declare one of the following to affect that site and adjacent sites while \'sentry\' present: Opponent\'s deploy +1. OR Opponent\'s ability required for battle destiny +1. OR Your total power +1.','Rebel sentries are stationed on raised sensor platforms. On watch for Imperial scouts and other hazards, they supplement data gathered by Yavin Base\'s main sensors.',NULL,'1_68'),(3126,2643,'Light','U','Dagobah','Tunnel Vision','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Dagobah-Light/large/tunnelvision.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Lost','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Search your Force Pile and take one card into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.','Han could always see the light at the end of the tunnel.',NULL,'4_67'),(3127,1973,'Light','R','Theed Palace','•Queen Amidala','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/queenamidala.gif?raw=true','Character','Republic','2','3','4','7','Deploys -1 to Naboo. Amidala and your other Republic characters present are defense value +2, and immune to You Are Beaten, Sniper, and attrition < 3.','Leader. Amidala was only twelve when she was elected Princess of Theed. Now at age fourteen, she is Naboo\'s Queen, and the savior of her planet.',NULL,'14_25'),(3128,1396,'Light','R','Special Edition','•Joh Yowza','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/SpecialEdition-Light/large/johyowza.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','3','2','2','3','Power +2 on Endor or when present with your musician. When opponent draws destiny, Joh may \'jam\' (place that card face down under Joh). Holds one card at a time. If Joh leaves table, place card under Joh in opponent\'s Used Pile.','Yuzzum musician and thief. Singer for The Max Rebo Band. Stage name given to him by Sy Snootles. Jabba likes his performance, even though the Hutt despises Yuzzum.',NULL,'7_23'),(3129,2798,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•Wesa Ready To Do Our-sa Part','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/wesareadytodooursapart.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. If your Gungan was just lost from a site, may place him here. Once per battle, may place one of your Gungans here out of play to add 4 to your total power during that battle.','Every Gungan that died on the battle plains gave Amidala and her troops that much more time to capture the Viceroy.',NULL,'14_39'),(3130,4110,'Light','R','Virtual Set 1','•Lando Calrissian (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual1-Light/large/landocalrissian.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','1','3','3','6','Smuggler. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When deployed, may take a character with \'Cloud City\' in lore into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. During battle, may use 1 Force to cancel the game text of a Dark Jedi (except Vader) at same site.','Gambler. Scoundrel. Former owner of the Millennium Falcon. Despite a notorious past, has become a successful chief administrator of a Tibanna gas mining facility.',NULL,'201_1'),(3131,2863,'Light','U1','Premiere','•Yerka Mig','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/yerkamig.gif?raw=true','Effect','Utinni','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy at any location. You may move Mig like a character. Target an opponent\'s character, who may apprehend (cancel) Mig by reaching same location. Until then, during all battles at same and adjacent sites to Mig, opponent\'s total power is -1.','An Imperial bureaucrat with high security clearance who resigned and fled in remorse after the occupation of his home planet, Ralltiir. Now a fugitive from the ISB.',NULL,'1_69'),(3132,1112,'Light','R','Cloud City','•Haven','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/haven.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on one of the following systems: Rendezvous Point, Hoth, Yavin 4, Alderaan or Sullust. Your starships deploy -2 and your pilots deploy -1 here. When battling here, you may add one battle destiny. Effect canceled if opponent controls this system. (Immune to Alter.)','After pursuit, asteroids, a slug, Jedi training, capture, torture, escape, a duel, losing Han and losing a hand, Luke and Leia finally made it to the Alliance\'s rendezvous point.',NULL,'5_24'),(3133,2810,'Light','U','Cloud City','•Wiorkettle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/CloudCity-Light/large/wiorkettle.gif?raw=true','Character','Alien','2','1','2','3','Power +1 if with Zutton. During your control phase, may use 1 Force to place one asteroid sector from hand onto Used Pile, search Reserve Deck, take one site into hand and reshuffle.','A Snivvian on Cloud City, working for Planet Dreams, Inc. Terraforms asteroids, creating habitable atmospheres. Responsible for the aesthetics of the created environments.',NULL,'5_11'),(3134,2855,'Light','C2','Premiere','•Yavin 4: Jungle','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Premiere-Light/large/yavin4jungle.gif?raw=true','Location','Site','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Light: : A Rebel alone here battles at power +2 and is immune to attrition.',NULL,'Yavin 4: Jungle','1_137'),(3135,2902,'Light','PM','Reflections III','•Your Ship?','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/ReflectionsIII-Light/large/yourship.gif?raw=true','Defensive Shield',NUL