fore any cards have been forfeited, cause all attrition for both sides to be reduced to zero.','Sarcastic, Sardonic, Irreverent. Impertinent. Exasperating. Disrespectful. Outrageous and charming. Han was a scoundrel but Leia began to realize that she loved him.',NULL,'4_74'),(3138,1337,'Light','C','Theed Palace','•It\'s On Automatic Pilot!','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/TheedPalace-Light/large/itsonautomaticpilot.gif?raw=true','Effect',NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Deploy on table. Your N-1 starfighters are forfeit +2. During every draw phase, opponent loses 1 Force unless they occupy a battleground system. Effect lost if you do not occupy two battleground systems with [Republic] starships.','Once he was airborne, Ric Olie transmitted rendezvous coordinates to every N-1 starfighter. It was all the direction Anakin Skywalker needed.','At Last We Are Getting Results','14_33'),(3139,5069,'Light','U','Virtual Set 4','•You Do Have Your Moments (V)','https://github.com/swccgpc/holotable/blob/master/Images-HT/starwars/Virtual4-Light/large/youdohaveyourmoments.gif?raw=true','Interrupt','Used Or Lost','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'USED: Cancel and redraw a just drawn destiny.LOST: A just drawn battle destiny is +3.\"','Sarcastic, Sardonic, Irreverent. Impertinent. Exasperating. Disrespectful. Outrageous and charming. Han was a scoundrel but Leia began to realize that she loved him.','Close Call (V)','204_23');
